NK122(kho)002:0: dam pa bde gshegs kyis mdzad pa'i theg dgu spyi
NK122(kho)002:1: bcing gi 'grel bshad nyi ma'i 'od zer zhes bya
NK122(kho)002:2: ba slob dpon ye shes rgyal mtshan gyis mdzad pa
NK122(kho)002:3: bzhugs so // na mo rat+na tra y+aa ya /
NK122(kho)002:4: rje btsun dpal ldan bla ma dam pa rnams dang
NK122(kho)002:5: yi dam rgyud sde bzhi'i lha tshogs bka' sdod chos
NK122(kho)002:6: skyong ba'i srung ma dang bcas pa rnams la phyag
NK122(kho)002:7: 'tshal lo // mchod do skyabs su mchi'o //
NK122(kho)002:8: chos dbyings mnyam nyid gdal khyab chen po'i ngang //
NK122(kho)002:9: 'khor 'das gnyis med ro gcig klong du gyur //
NK122(kho)002:10: mkhyen brtse'i bdag nyid dpal ldan dbang phyug che //
NK122(kho)002:11: kun bzang bde bar gshegs la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK122(kho)002:12: gang zhig byang chub mchog tu sems bskyed cing //
NK122(kho)002:13: gang du grangs med gsum du tshogs gnyis bsags //
NK122(kho)002:14: gang der mdzad pa bcu gnyis mngon sangs rgyas //
NK122(kho)002:15: bcom ldan thub dbang khyed la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK122(kho)002:16: kun bzang thugs las rnam 'phrul thugs kyi sras //
NK122(kho)002:17: theg chen gsang sngags zab mo 'dzin byed cing //
NK122(kho)002:18: gdul daka'i gdul bya ma lus 'joms mdzad pa //
NK122(kho)002:19: bcom ldan rdo rje bsnams la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK122(kho)002:20: gti mug ma rig mun pa'i klong chen der //
NK122(kho)002:21: ye shes sgron me'i gsal rgyun rab tu bltams //
NK122(kho)002:22: bdag blo'i the tshom dra ba gcod mdzad pa'i //
NK122(kho)002:23: mgon po 'jam pa'i dbyangs la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK122(kho)002:24: kun mkhyen rgyal ba'i gsung rab pad+mo'i tshal //
NK122(kho)002:25: 'grel bshad nyi ma'i zer gyis rnam par phye //
NK122(kho)002:26: dad ldan rkang drug ldan la dga' ston 'gyed //
NK122(kho)002:27: lo pan skyes mchog nyin byed rnams la 'dud //
NK122(kho)002:28: sangs rgyas bstan pa gangs ri dri med la //
NK122(kho)002:29: thos bsam sgom gsum sgrub tshul seng ge 'gying //
NK122(kho)002:30: lta ngan ri dwags tha dag 'joms mdzad pa //
NK122(kho)002:31: rgya gar 'phags pa'i mkhas grub rnams la 'dud //
NK122(kho)002:32: rgya gar mkhas pa'i rigs su sku 'khrungs shing //
NK122(kho)002:33: kha ba can du chos kyi sgron me sbar //
NK122(kho)002:34: bde ba can der blo gros snying por grags //
NK122(kho)002:35: bstan pa'i srog shing dam pa nyid la 'dud //
NK122(kho)002:36: thos bsam sgom pa'i don la legs sbyangs nas //
NK122(kho)002:37: dal 'byor lus la bslab gsum rgyan gyis mdzes //
NK122(kho)002:38: 'chad rtsod rtsom pa'i don la ma rmongs pa'i //
NK122(kho)002:39: bstan 'dzin bod kyi skyes mchog rnams la 'dud //
NK122(kho)002:40: sde snod rgya mtsho'i dbus nas legs skyes shing //
NK122(kho)002:41: nyams myong bdud rtsi'i 'dab ma mdangs gsal cing //
NK122(kho)002:42: bcud 'dod rkang drug ldan rnams tshim mdzad pa //
NK122(kho)002:43: drin chen bla ma rnams la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK122(kho)002:44: thub dbang bstan pa legs bshad chu gter las //
NK122(kho)002:45: ded dpon chen po sangs rgyas gnyis pa yis //
NK122(kho)002:46: legs par srubs las legs bshad rin chen 'byung //
NK122(kho)002:47: rnam bshad 'chad nyan rgyal mtshan rtse mor phyar //
NK122(kho)002:48: lung rig du mas byi dor byed na snyams //
NK122(kho)002:49: de yang rang bzo ma yin mkhas pa'i gzhung //
NK122(kho)002:50: legs bshad rnams la yang yang dpyad pa dang //
NK122(kho)002:51: gzhung lugs 'di yang mang du thos pa dang //
NK122(kho)002:52: bla ma rnams kyi man ngag gsung sgros rnams //
NK122(kho)002:53: legs par sbyar nas ban chung bdag gis ni //
NK122(kho)002:54: 'grel bshad nyi ma'i 'od zer brjod par bya //
NK122(kho)002:55: 'on kyang dus kyis mnar ba'i skye bo phal pa 'gas //
NK122(kho)002:56: phyin ci log rtog ma dag snang ba 'char //
NK122(kho)002:57: legs bshad zer yang log bshad du ma 'byung //
NK122(kho)002:58: pha rol 'gran dang grags pa 'dod phyir dang //
NK122(kho)002:59: zas nor longs spyod 'du 'dzi spel phyir phyung //
NK122(kho)002:60: snyam pa'i bsam pas cung zad ma dpyad mdzod //
NK122(kho)002:61: 'dir sde snod gsum dang rgyud sde bzhi'i srog shing theg pa mtha' dag gi shan 'byed /
NK122(kho)002:62: phyi rol pa dang nang pa'i grub mtha' ma 'dres par gsal bar byed pa'i me long /
NK122(kho)002:63: gtan tshig gis gtan la phab /
NK122(kho)002:64: lung rig gis gdar sha bcad /
NK122(kho)002:65: grub mtha' ma nor bar dmigs nas blangs pa'i man
NK122(kho)002:66: ngag slob dpon chen po dam pa bde bar gshegs
NK122(kho)002:67: pas mdzad pa'i theg pa spyi bcing 'di la /
NK122(kho)002:68: 'chad nyan ci ltar bya ba'i tshul dang /
NK122(kho)002:69: gang 'chad par bya ba chos kyi rnam bzhag /'chad
NK122(kho)002:70: nyan mthar phyin pa'i rgyu mtshan dang gsum du gnas
NK122(kho)002:71: pa las / dang po la gnyis te /
NK122(kho)002:72: 'chad pa po slob dpon gyi rnam bzhag /
NK122(kho)002:73: nyan pa po slob ma'i mtshan nyid do //
NK122(kho)002:74: 'chad pa po slob dpon gyi mtshan nyid la gsum te /
NK122(kho)002:75: slob dpon de'i mtshan nyid dang /
NK122(kho)002:77: chos bshad pa'i phan yon dang gsum yod /
NK122(kho)002:80: tshul khrims kyis lus dag pa /
NK122(kho)002:81: thos bsam gyis ngag dag pa /
NK122(kho)002:82: ting nge 'dzin gyis sems dag pa /
NK122(kho)002:83: byams sems snying rje byang chub sems dang ldan pa'i chos bzhi dang ldan dgos te /
NK122(kho)002:84: chos rgyal dri ma med pa'i mdo las //
NK122(kho)002:85: tshul gnas thos dang ting 'dzin gyis //
NK122(kho)002:86: lus gtsang smra mkhas sems mi g.yo //
NK122(kho)002:87: sems can kun la byams sems ldan //
NK122(kho)002:88: de 'dra bshes gnyen dam par mdzod //
NK122(kho)002:91: chos kun mnyam pa nyid kyi don shes pa //
NK122(kho)002:92: rgyud gzhung zab mo bshad pa la mkhas pa /
NK122(kho)002:95: dkyil chog tha dag la mkhas shing khong du chud pa /
NK122(kho)002:96: brgyud pa'i zam ma chad pa /
NK122(kho)002:97: dbang bzhi'i chu bo ma nub pa /
NK122(kho)002:98: byin rlabs nyams myong gi drod ma yal ba /
NK122(kho)002:99: snyan rgyud dam tshig gi gnad ma 'chug pa zhig dgos te /
NK122(kho)002:101: gzhi rtsa stong pa nyid du shes //
NK122(kho)002:102: rgyud bshad sngags kyi sbyor ba mkhas //
NK122(kho)002:103: thugs rje che la 'dod pa chung //
NK122(kho)002:104: dbang rnams thob cing ting 'dzin gsal //
NK122(kho)002:106: gzhan yang shes bya'i sde snod tha dag la mkhas na legs mod kyis /
NK122(kho)002:107: 'on kyang rang gi gzhung lugs khas gang blangs pa'i
NK122(kho)002:108: tshig don ma lus pa khong du chud pa zhig
NK122(kho)002:110: gnyis pa des chos bshad pa'i tshul ni /
NK122(kho)002:111: dam chos pad+ma dkar po las /
NK122(kho)002:112: mkhas pas dus su sems par byed pa ni //
NK122(kho)002:113: khang bur zhugs te de bzhin sgo bcad nas //
NK122(kho)002:114: chos 'dod thams cad la ni tshul bzhin blta //
NK122(kho)002:115: langs nas zhum pa med pa'i sems kyis shod //
NK122(kho)002:116: mkhas pa bde la rtag tu gnas par 'gyur //
NK122(kho)002:117: bde la 'dug nas de bzhin chos kyang ston //
NK122(kho)002:118: gtsang zhing yid du 'ong ba'i sa phyogs der //
NK122(kho)002:119: yangs pa'i stan ni rab tu bshams bting nas //
NK122(kho)002:120: bzang po'i tshon gyis legs par kha bsgyur ba'i //
NK122(kho)002:121: chos gos gtsang ma de ni rab bgos nas //
NK122(kho)002:122: rngul gzan nag po de ni bshams byas la //
NK122(kho)002:123: sham thabs cha tshang legs par rab bgos nas //
NK122(kho)002:124: bcos bu'i ras rnams sna tshogs legs bting pa //
NK122(kho)002:125: rkang rten bcas pa'i khri la rab 'dug pa //
NK122(kho)002:126: rkang pa legs par bkrus la steng 'dzeg nas //
NK122(kho)002:127: gdong dang bzhin gyi mdangs ni rab snum zhing //
NK122(kho)002:128: chos kyi stan de la ni rab 'dug nas //
NK122(kho)002:129: sems can lhags pa rtse gcig gyur rnams la //
NK122(kho)002:130: gtam mang rnam pa sna tshogs nye bar ston //
NK122(kho)002:131: dge slong dag dang dge slong ma rnams dang //
NK122(kho)002:132: dge bsnyen dag dang dge bsnyen ma dag dang //
NK122(kho)002:133: rgyal po dge dang rgyal bu rnams la yang //
NK122(kho)002:134: mkhas de rtag tu phrag dog med par ni //
NK122(kho)002:135: sna tshogs don ldan snyan pa'i gtam yang ston //
NK122(kho)002:136: le lo dag kyang rnam par rab spangs nas //
NK122(kho)002:137: skyo ba'i rnam pa'i 'du shes bskyed mi bya //
NK122(kho)002:138: mkhas pa mi dga' thams cad rnam par spangs //
NK122(kho)002:139: byams pa'i stobs ni 'khor la bsgom par bya //
NK122(kho)002:140: nyin mtshan du yang chos mchog rab tu bsgom //
NK122(kho)002:141: mkhas pa de ni bye ba khrag khrig gi //
NK122(kho)002:142: 'khor rnams mgu zhing de bzhin dga' bar byed //
NK122(kho)002:143: de la nam yang 'dod pa cung zad med //
NK122(kho)002:144: zas dang skom dang bza' ba bca' ba dang //
NK122(kho)002:145: gos dang mal cha chos gos rnams dang ni //
NK122(kho)002:146: na ba'i gso sman dag kyang mi bsam ste //
NK122(kho)002:147: 'khor rnams la ni ci yang mi bslang ngo //
NK122(kho)002:148: gzhan tu mkhas pa rtag tu bdag nyid dang //
NK122(kho)002:149: sems can 'di dag sangs rgyas thob par shog /
NK122(kho)002:150: phan phyir 'jig rten chos gang bstan pa de //
NK122(kho)002:151: bdag gi bde ba'i yo byad kun snyams sems //
NK122(kho)002:152: ces gsungs pa'i lung 'di dag gi don nyams su blangs shing phyag len la theg par mdzod /
NK122(kho)002:153: gzhan yang rnyed pa dang bkur sti 'dod pa'i phyir bshad na /
NK122(kho)002:155: gzhan dang 'gran pa dang grags pa 'dod pa'i phyir
NK122(kho)002:156: bshad na yul mtha' 'khob kyi rgyal po gdug pa
NK122(kho)002:158: ces dran pa nyer bzhag las gsungs so //
NK122(kho)002:159: mdor na tshe 'di'i bsam pa tha dag spangs nas /
NK122(kho)002:160: chos kyi sbyin pa 'dis slob ma 'di dag gis
NK122(kho)002:161: thog drangs nas sems can thams cad kyi shes rab
NK122(kho)002:162: gsum bskyed cing / nyon mongs pa thams cad bsal ba dang /
NK122(kho)002:163: ma 'ongs pa na mngon par rdzogs pa sangs rgyas pa'i tshe /
NK122(kho)002:164: chos kyi 'khor lo bskor bas sems can thams cad
NK122(kho)002:165: sangs rgyas kyi sa la bkod par bya'o snyam pa'i
NK122(kho)002:166: bsam pa rnam par dag pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:169: rgya chen chos kyi snod gyur pa //
NK122(kho)002:170: theg pa dman la dkri mi bya //
NK122(kho)002:171: dman la zab dang rgya che dang //
NK122(kho)002:173: rang nyid tshig dang don la ma rmongs pa /
NK122(kho)002:174: slob ma dbang po rno rtul dang rjes su mthun pa'i chos /
NK122(kho)002:175: mdo rgyas rab 'bring tha ma la sogs pa ma nor bar bshad pa'i dus su /
NK122(kho)002:178: gnyis ka'i rna bar snyan cing yid chags pa'i tshul du bshad cing /
NK122(kho)002:179: rjes dge ba'i rtsa ba rdzogs pa'i byang chub du bsngo bas zin par bya'o //
NK122(kho)002:180: gzhan yang gsang sngags kyi bshad tshul la mtha' drug /
NK122(kho)002:183: bshad thabs 'dren pa'i tshig bcu rnams ni gzhan du shes par bya'o //
NK122(kho)002:184: gsum pa de ltar bshad pa'i phan yon ni /
NK122(kho)002:185: sbyin pa rnams kyi nang nas chos kyi sbyin pa mchog tu gsungs pas /
NK122(kho)002:186: rang gzhan gyi nyon mongs pa thams cad bsal ba'i rgyu yin pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:187: tshe rabs thams cad du shes bya thams cad la ma rmongs pa'i rgyu yin pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:188: dam pa'i chos dang nam yang mi 'bral zhing /
NK122(kho)002:189: ma 'ongs pa na chos kyi 'khor lo bskor ba
NK122(kho)002:190: la sogs pa yon tan dpag tu med par gsungs
NK122(kho)002:191: pa ste / byams pa seng+ge sgras zhus pa'i mdo las //
NK122(kho)002:192: stong gsum 'jig rten khams 'di gser dag gis //
NK122(kho)002:193: bkang ste gzhan la sbyin pa byin pa bas //
NK122(kho)002:194: tshig bzhi tshigs su bcad pa gcig brjod na //
NK122(kho)002:195: ci ltar phan 'dogs de ltar 'gyur ba yin //
NK122(kho)002:197: des 'chad pa po slob dpon gyi mtshan nyid de song nas /
NK122(kho)002:198: gnyis pa nyan pa po slob ma'i mtshan nyid la gsum ste /
NK122(kho)002:199: chos nyan pa po slob ma'i mtshan nyid dang /
NK122(kho)002:201: nyan pa'i phan yon dang gsum /
NK122(kho)002:203: drang zhing g.yo sgyu med pa /
NK122(kho)002:205: chos don du gnyer ba dang gsum ldan pa zhig dgos te /
NK122(kho)002:206: dbu ma bzhi brgya pa las /
NK122(kho)002:207: gzur gnas blo ldan don gnyer ba /
NK122(kho)002:208: nyan pa'i snod kyis bya bar brjod /
NK122(kho)002:210: klong gsal nyi ma'i rgyud las //
NK122(kho)002:211: dad ldan snying rje gtong phod che //
NK122(kho)002:212: rgyud dul sdig 'dzem dbang po rno //
NK122(kho)002:213: gsang thub nyams len brtul shug spyod //
NK122(kho)002:214: skyo ngal sdug bsran snying rus che //
NK122(kho)002:215: de ni gsang sngags gsang ba'i snod //
NK122(kho)002:217: gnyis pa nyan pa'i tshul ni /
NK122(kho)002:219: phran bzang gis rgyal bu zla bar chos zhus pa'i gtam rgyud 'di gsungs pa /
NK122(kho)002:220: rab tu dma' ba'i stan la 'dug /
NK122(kho)002:221: dul ba'i dpal ni rnam par bskyed //
NK122(kho)002:222: dga' dang ldan pa'i mig gis blta //
NK122(kho)002:223: tshig gi bdud rtsi 'thung ba bzhin //
NK122(kho)002:224: gus pas bskyed cing rtse gcig btung //
NK122(kho)002:225: rab tu dang la dri med yin //
NK122(kho)002:226: nad pas sman pa'i tshig nyan bzhin //
NK122(kho)002:227: rim gro bskyed de chos nyon cig /
NK122(kho)002:229: nga rgyal dang ni ma dad dang //
NK122(kho)002:230: don du gnyer ba med nyid dang //
NK122(kho)002:231: phyi rol rnam g.yeng yid sdud dang //
NK122(kho)002:232: skyo bas nyan pa'i dri ma yin //
NK122(kho)002:234: de dag spangs nas chos dang chos smra ba la gus par bya ste /
NK122(kho)002:235: sdong po bkod pa'i mdo las /
NK122(kho)002:236: bdag nyid la nad pa'i 'du shes dang /
NK122(kho)002:237: dge ba'i bshes gnyen la sman pa'i 'du shes dang /
NK122(kho)002:238: chos la sman gyi 'du shes dang /
NK122(kho)002:239: nan tan rjes su bsgrub pa la nad 'tsho ba'i 'du shes bskyed par bya'o //
NK122(kho)002:241: de la shes rab gsum gyis skyon gsum spang dgos te /
NK122(kho)002:242: thos pa'i dus su snod kha sbubs lta bu'i skyon spangs te ma yengs par nyan /
NK122(kho)002:243: bsam pa'i dus su snod zhabs rdol lta bu'i skyon spang dgos te /
NK122(kho)002:245: sgom pa'i dus su snod dug can lta bu'i skyon spang dgos te /
NK122(kho)002:246: nyon mongs pa'i gnyen por gtong /
NK122(kho)002:247: gzhan yang don ma rtogs par tshig tsam zin pa
NK122(kho)002:248: la brten nas gzhan la 'chol bar smra zhing gang
NK122(kho)002:249: zag dam pa rnams la skur pa 'debs pa gzhog
NK122(kho)002:250: ral lta bu'i skyon dang bzhi spangs nas nyan dgos
NK122(kho)002:251: te / dgongs pa 'dus pa'i mdo las //
NK122(kho)002:252: bstan pa'i snod min snod ngan dag /
NK122(kho)002:253: rnam pa bzhir bsdu bye brag rnams //
NK122(kho)002:254: ma 'ongs rnams kyi don phyir du //
NK122(kho)002:255: brtags nas spangs bar bya phyir bshad //
NK122(kho)002:257: mdor na chos nyan pa'i tshe yang /
NK122(kho)002:258: srid zhu gus pa'i tshul du thal mo sbyar cing /
NK122(kho)002:259: gzhi dad pa chen pos btud /
NK122(kho)002:263: sems kyi dbang po kha bye /
NK122(kho)002:265: don gyi sbrang rtsi myong dgos par bshad do //
NK122(kho)002:266: gsum pa de ltar nyan pa'i phan yon la gnyis te /
NK122(kho)002:267: bla ma bsten pa'i phan yon dang /
NK122(kho)002:268: chos nyan pa'i phan yon gnyis /
NK122(kho)002:270: yul 'khor skyong gis zhus pa'i mdo las //
NK122(kho)002:271: dge ba'i bshes gnyen rtag tu bsten bya zhing //
NK122(kho)002:272: sdig pa'i grogs po rtag tu spang bar bya //
NK122(kho)002:273: de dag gis ni bzang lam khrid par byed //
NK122(kho)002:274: ngan 'gro las kyang rab tu bzlog par byed //
NK122(kho)002:277: byang chub sems dpa'i sde snod las //
NK122(kho)002:278: dge ba dang ni sdig pa'i chos //
NK122(kho)002:279: ma thos par ni shes mi 'gyur //
NK122(kho)002:281: thos pas shes rab rnam par 'phel //
NK122(kho)002:282: thos pas sdig las ldog par byed //
NK122(kho)002:283: thos pas don ma yin pa spang //
NK122(kho)002:286: khyad par sngags kyi gzhung don zab mo thos bsam
NK122(kho)002:287: byas pas 'ching ba thams cad las grol nas shes
NK122(kho)002:288: bya thams cad la thogs pa med cing mthar sku
NK122(kho)002:289: lnga lhun grub kyi sangs rgyas thob pa yin te
NK122(kho)002:291: dper na gyi ling sgrogs 'grol ltar //
NK122(kho)002:292: rnam grol thos bsam sgom pa yis //
NK122(kho)002:293: shes rgyud kun grol thogs med 'gro //
NK122(kho)002:296: thos bsam sgom pa'i rnal 'byor gyis //
NK122(kho)002:297: rang byung kun ngam lhun gyis grub //
NK122(kho)002:300: thos bsam byas pas lta mthar phyin //
NK122(kho)002:302: 'o na thos pa kho nas chog gam zhe na /
NK122(kho)002:304: thos pas nyon mongs pa sun phyung /
NK122(kho)002:306: bsgom pas drung 'byin pa yin pas /
NK122(kho)002:307: bsam pa dang sgom pa dgos so //
NK122(kho)002:308: thos pa kho na nyon mongs pa'i gnyen por ma song bas rgyud mi 'dul ba yin te /
NK122(kho)002:312: ma skyes dgra'i gtam rgyud lta bu'o //
NK122(kho)002:313: rje btsun gong ma rnams kyis //
NK122(kho)002:315: sgom pas nang gi sgro 'dogs gcod //
NK122(kho)002:317: sgom pa gtso bor ston pa ni 'di lta ste //
NK122(kho)002:318: tha snyad gtsor byed bshad pa'i dpe //
NK122(kho)002:319: dper na 'on pa rol mo mkhan //
NK122(kho)002:320: sil snyan glu la dga' byed kyang //
NK122(kho)002:321: bdag nyid 'on pas ma thos ltar //
NK122(kho)002:322: ma sgom chos kyang de dang 'dra //
NK122(kho)002:323: dper na rkyal mkhan chu yis khyer ba bzhin //
NK122(kho)002:324: rkyal ba'i lo rgyus sems la yod gyur kyang //
NK122(kho)002:325: ma rkyal bar du thar bar mi 'gyur ba //
NK122(kho)002:326: shes nas ma bsgom chos kyang de dang mtshungs //
NK122(kho)002:328: de yang da res kyi skye gnas bar do 'dir /
NK122(kho)002:329: thos bsam sgom gsum la blo 'jug nas thar pa'i gzhung lam chen por slebs dgos te /
NK122(kho)002:331: e ma bdag la skye gnas bar do shar dus 'dir //
NK122(kho)002:332: tshe la long med le lo spangs byas la //
NK122(kho)002:333: thos bsam sgom gsum don la ma yengs 'jug /
NK122(kho)002:334: snang sems lam slong sku gsum mngon gyur bya'o //
NK122(kho)002:337: dang po thos pa'i shes rab kyis //
NK122(kho)002:338: phyi nang chos la sgro 'dogs gcod //
NK122(kho)002:339: bar du bsam pa'i shes rab kyis //
NK122(kho)002:340: de don rgyud la 'dres par byed //
NK122(kho)002:341: tha ma sgom pa'ishesa rab gyis //
NK122(kho)002:342: bdag tu 'dzin pa'i nyon mongs zhi //
NK122(kho)002:343: ces gsungs pa ltar du nyams su blang bar bya'o //
NK122(kho)002:344: chos rang rgyud du song na /
NK122(kho)002:345: thos pa rgya che na yang rung mod kyis /
NK122(kho)002:346: tshe dang ldan pa lam phran brtan dang /
NK122(kho)002:347: glen pa steng rgyas 'od srung la sogs pa rnams
NK122(kho)002:348: tshig rkang re re'i thog nas grol bar gsungs so
NK122(kho)002:349: // des 'chad nyan ci ltar byed pa'i tshul de song nas /
NK122(kho)002:350: gnyis pa gang 'chad par bya ba dam chos kyi rnam bzhag la gsum ste /
NK122(kho)002:351: gang zag 'jug ngo shes par bya ba'i phyir dam
NK122(kho)002:352: pa'i chos ngos bzung ba dang don ma nor bar
NK122(kho)002:353: shes par bya ba'i phyir bshad pa'i thabs bstan pa
NK122(kho)002:354: dang / bshad bya gzhung don dngos dang gsum du gnas pa las /
NK122(kho)002:356: rtogs pa brjod bya don dang /
NK122(kho)002:357: lung brjod byed tshig gnyis yin te /
NK122(kho)002:359: ston pa'i dam chos rnam gnyis te //
NK122(kho)002:360: lung dang rtogs pa'i bdag nyid do //
NK122(kho)002:361: de 'dzin byed par smra byed dang //
NK122(kho)002:362: sgrub par byed pa kho na yin //
NK122(kho)002:364: lung chos la bka' bstan gnyis yod de /
NK122(kho)002:365: lhas bu'i zhus pa'i mdo las //
NK122(kho)002:366: bka' dang bstan chos gnyis su chos rnams 'dus //
NK122(kho)002:367: legs par gsungs pa de'i dgongs 'grel dang //
NK122(kho)002:368: ces sangs rgyas kyis legs par gsungs pa'i bka' dang /
NK122(kho)002:369: de'i dgongs pa 'grel pa bstan bcos gnyis su bshad pa las /
NK122(kho)002:374: de gang zhig dngos kyi bdag rkyen sangs rgyas las byung ba'o //
NK122(kho)002:376: chen po gong na yod pa ya gi nas mar gsungs pa'i phyir bka' zhes pa ste /
NK122(kho)002:377: sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das skye 'phags thams cad kyi gtso bor gyur pa'i phyir /
NK122(kho)002:378: dper na 'jig rten gyi khams na rgyal po'i bka' zhes pa lta bu'o //
NK122(kho)002:379: gsum pa dbye ba la drug ste /
NK122(kho)002:385: bdag rkyen gyi sgo nas dbye ba'o //
NK122(kho)002:387: yul w+aa ra n+aa si na bden pa bzhi'i chos kyi 'khor lo bskor ba dang /
NK122(kho)002:388: bar du bya rgod phung po'i ri bo la mtshan
NK122(kho)002:389: nyid med pa'i chos kyi 'khor lo bskor ba dang
NK122(kho)002:390: / tha ma grong khyer yangs pa can na don
NK122(kho)002:391: dam rnam par nges pa'i chos kyi 'khor lo bskor
NK122(kho)002:392: / ba'o // gnyis pa brjod bya'i sgo nas dbye ba ni /
NK122(kho)002:393: kun rdzob ston pa drang don dang /
NK122(kho)002:394: don dam ston pa nges don du bsdu ba yin /
NK122(kho)002:395: sangs rgyas rnams kyi chos gsungs pa //
NK122(kho)002:396: bden pa gnyis la yang dag brten //
NK122(kho)002:398: gsum pa brjod byed kyi sgo nas dbye ba ni /
NK122(kho)002:400: mdo sde dbyangs bsnyad lung bstan dang //
NK122(kho)002:401: tshigs bcad ched brjod gleng gzhi dang //
NK122(kho)002:402: rtog brjod de lta bu byung dang //
NK122(kho)002:403: skyes rabs shin tu rgyas pa dang //
NK122(kho)002:404: rmad byung gtan la dbab pa dag /
NK122(kho)002:405: gsung rab yan lag bcu gnyis yin //
NK122(kho)002:407: bzhi pa gnyen po'i sgo nas dbye na /
NK122(kho)002:408: de yang gdul bya sems can thams cad kyi rgyud la nyon mongs pa 'dod chags dang /
NK122(kho)002:411: dug gsum cha mnyam pa dang bzhi po re re
NK122(kho)002:412: la yang nyi khri chig stong re re yod pa
NK122(kho)002:413: tshogs pas brgyad khri bzhi stong du 'gyur la /
NK122(kho)002:414: de'i gnyen por chos kyi sgo mo brgyad khri bzhi stong gsungs par 'dod /
NK122(kho)002:415: kun byed rgyal po'i rgyud las /
NK122(kho)002:416: 'dod chags 'dul ba'i gnyen por gsungs pa ni //
NK122(kho)002:417: 'dul ba'i sde snod nyi khri chig stong gsungs //
NK122(kho)002:418: zhe sdang 'dul ba'i gnyen por gsungs pa ni //
NK122(kho)002:419: mdo sde'i sde snod nyi khri chig stong gsungs //
NK122(kho)002:420: gti mug 'dul ba'i gnyen por gsungs pa ni //
NK122(kho)002:421: mngon pa'i sde snod nyi khri chig stong gsungs //
NK122(kho)002:422: thams cad 'dul ba'i gnyen por gsungs pa ni //
NK122(kho)002:423: sde snod bzhi pa nyi khri chig stong gsungs //
NK122(kho)002:424: mdor na brgyad khri bzhi stong gsungs pa yang //
NK122(kho)002:425: nyon mongs 'dul ba'i gnyen por gsungs par zad //
NK122(kho)002:427: lnga pa gdul bya'i sgo nas dbye ba ni /
NK122(kho)002:428: gdul bya dbang po rno rtul gyi sgo nas theg pa che chung gnyis su bsten pa'o //
NK122(kho)002:429: drug pa bdag rkyen gyi sgo nas dbye ba la bzhi /
NK122(kho)002:430: zhal nas gsungs pa'i bka' dang /
NK122(kho)002:431: byin gyis brlabs pa'i bka' dang /
NK122(kho)002:432: rjes su gnang ba'i bka' dang /
NK122(kho)002:434: dang po ston pa'i bdag rkyen gyis tshad ma zhal nas gsungs pa ste /
NK122(kho)002:435: sdud pa tshigs su bcad pa lta bu'o //
NK122(kho)002:436: byin gyis brlabs pa'i bka' la gsum ste /
NK122(kho)002:437: de la sku'i byin gyis brlabs pa ni /
NK122(kho)002:438: ston pa'i phyag byang chub sems dpa' byams pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:439: kun tu bzang po gnyis kyi spyi bor bzhag nas
NK122(kho)002:440: byams pas mdo sde sa bcu pa gsungs pa dang
NK122(kho)002:441: / kun tu bzang pos mdo sde phal po che gsungs pa lta bu'o //
NK122(kho)002:442: gsung gi byin gyis brlabs pa'i bka' ni /
NK122(kho)002:444: rab 'byor khyod shes rab kyi pha rol du phyin pa las brtsam ste spob par byos shig /
NK122(kho)002:446: rab 'byor gyis brgya byin la bshad pa bzhin no //
NK122(kho)002:448: mkhas pa 'ga' zhig gis gsum du dbye ste /
NK122(kho)002:449: thugs thugs rjes byin gyis brlabs pa ni /
NK122(kho)002:450: ston pa nyid zhal bzhugs pa'i ring la /
NK122(kho)002:454: lha cha'i sgra las kyang chos sgra 'byung zhing don du 'gyur bar bshad /
NK122(kho)002:455: thugs bden stobs kyi byin gyis brlabs pa'i bka' ni /
NK122(kho)002:456: ston pa nyid kyi ring la lha dang klu dang /
NK122(kho)002:457: gnod sbyin la sogs pa rnams kyis chos gsungs nas don du 'gyur bar bshad /
NK122(kho)002:458: thugs ting nge 'dzin gyi byin gyis brlabs pa'i bka' ni /
NK122(kho)002:459: bcom ldan 'das zab mo'i ting nge 'dzin la bzhugs
NK122(kho)002:460: pa'i byin rlabs spyan ras gzigs dbang phyug dang sh+aa
NK122(kho)002:462: spyan ras gzigs kyis sh+aa ri'i bu la shes rab snying po bshad pa lta bu'o //
NK122(kho)002:463: rjes su gnang ba'i bka' ni /
NK122(kho)002:467: snying rje pad+ma dkar po las /
NK122(kho)002:469: ngas gsungs pa'i chos thams cad la 'di skad bdag
NK122(kho)002:470: gis thos pa'i dus gcig na zhes pa'i gleng gzhi
NK122(kho)002:471: 'khod / skabs su mtshams sbyor gyi tshig chug /
NK122(kho)002:472: tha ma bcom ldan 'das kyis gsungs pa la mngon par bstod do //
NK122(kho)002:474: ces gnang ba byin pa lta bu'o //
NK122(kho)002:475: lung bstan gyi bka' ni gsang sngags yin te /
NK122(kho)002:476: mdo sde gdams ngag 'bogs pa las /
NK122(kho)002:478: 'dren pa'i theg pa gsum po dag /
NK122(kho)002:479: bcom ldan 'das kyis gsungs lags na //
NK122(kho)002:480: rgyu 'bras lhun grub du spyod cing //
NK122(kho)002:481: sangs rgyas gzhan du mi 'tshol ba'i //
NK122(kho)002:482: nges pa'i theg pa cis ma gsungs //
NK122(kho)002:485: rgyu la mos pa rgyu chos kyi //
NK122(kho)002:486: 'khor lo rab tu bskor byas nas //
NK122(kho)002:487: rdo rje theg pa'i nye lam zhig /
NK122(kho)002:491: nga ni 'di nas mi snang nas //
NK122(kho)002:492: lo ni brgyad dang bcu gnyis na //
NK122(kho)002:493: rgyal po dza zhes bya ba la //
NK122(kho)002:494: sngon du ltas snang snang bar gyur //
NK122(kho)002:495: ces gsungs pas gsang sngags phal che ba ni /
NK122(kho)002:496: sprul sku sh+aakya seng ge 'das nas lo nyi shu rtsa brgyad kyi dus su dar ba byung //
NK122(kho)002:497: 'di la rgyud sde bzhi'i dbye ba /
NK122(kho)002:498: rgyud sde bzhir 'jog pa'i rgyu mtshan /
NK122(kho)002:499: 'og rang rang gi theg pa'i skabs su bshad pas der shes par bya'o //
NK122(kho)002:500: de la gzhung lugs 'di nyid bka' ma yin cing /
NK122(kho)002:501: de'i dgongs pa 'grel ba'i bstan bcos yin no //
NK122(kho)002:507: rtsom pa pos bka' la brten nas brjod bya gsal bar byed pa ste /
NK122(kho)002:509: ci ltar sgron glog nyi zla nor bu la //
NK122(kho)002:510: brten nas mig dang ldan pas blta ba bzhin //
NK122(kho)002:511: de bzhin don tshig chos spob 'od mdzad pa //
NK122(kho)002:512: thub la brten nas ngas 'dir yang dag bshad //
NK122(kho)002:515: rgyu nyon mongs pa dug gsum la /
NK122(kho)002:516: gnyen po bslab pa gsum ldan du 'chos zhing 'bras
NK122(kho)002:517: bu ngan song dang srid pa'i sdug bsngal las skyob
NK122(kho)002:518: par byed pas na bstan bcos te /
NK122(kho)002:520: nyon mongs dgra rnams ma lus 'chos pa dang //
NK122(kho)002:521: ngan 'gro'i srid las skyobs byed gang yin pa //
NK122(kho)002:522: 'chos skyobs yon tan phyir na bstan bcos te //
NK122(kho)002:523: gnyis po 'di dag gzhan gyi lugs la med //
NK122(kho)002:526: ston pa'i bstan pa rtogs sla'i phyir //
NK122(kho)002:527: tshig zur bcos phyir nges tshig 'grub //
NK122(kho)002:530: don med don log don dang ldan //
NK122(kho)002:531: thos rtsod sgrub pa lhur len dang //
NK122(kho)002:532: ngan g.yo brtse bral sdug bsngal 'byin //
NK122(kho)002:533: bstan chos drug bral gsum du 'dod //
NK122(kho)002:535: de la brjod bya'i don med pa dang brjod bya don du gnyer bya ma yin pa gnyis dang /
NK122(kho)002:537: mu stegs byed kyi rtog ge sde bzhi dang /
NK122(kho)002:538: dug sbyor la sogs pa ngan g.yo dang /
NK122(kho)002:539: 'tshe ba chos su smra ba ste /
NK122(kho)002:540: drug po 'di dag la bstan bcos kyi sgra 'jug kyang spang bya'o //
NK122(kho)002:541: brjod bya spang dor gyi don dang ldan pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:542: yang dag pa'i rtogs pa bskyed pa'i sgrub pa lhur len pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:543: ngan song dang 'khor ba'i sdug bsngal 'byin par byed pa ste /
NK122(kho)002:544: gsum po ni chos 'di'i lugs kyi blang bya bka'
NK122(kho)002:545: la ba rten pa'i brjod bya thar pa'i lam dang
NK122(kho)002:546: rjes su mthun pa'i bstan bcos te /
NK122(kho)002:548: gang zhig rgyal ba'i bstan pa 'ba' zhig gi //
NK122(kho)002:549: dbang byas rnam g.yeng med yid can gyis bshad //
NK122(kho)002:550: thar pa thob pa'i lam dang rjes mthun pa //
NK122(kho)002:551: de ni drang srong gsung bzhin spyi bor blangs //
NK122(kho)002:554: phal pa dang khyad par gnyis so //
NK122(kho)002:556: 'phags pa klu sgrub kyis mdzod brtag dus mtsho che chung //
NK122(kho)002:557: skye bo rnams la skye bo gso thig /
NK122(kho)002:558: blon po rnams la shes rab brgya pa //
NK122(kho)002:559: btsun mo rnams la g.yos sbyor brgya pa /
NK122(kho)002:560: dkon gnyer rnams la spos sbyor brgya pa /
NK122(kho)002:563: sa pan gyi legs bshad la sogs pa rnams yin no //
NK122(kho)002:564: 'di rnams mngon mtho'i rgyu yin zhing nges legs kyi brten du 'gyur srid de /
NK122(kho)002:566: mi'i chos lugs legs sbyang na //
NK122(kho)002:567: lha yul bgrod pa thag mi ring //
NK122(kho)002:568: lha dang mi yi them skas la //
NK122(kho)002:569: bgrod na thar pa gam du 'dug /
NK122(kho)002:571: khyad par gyis bstan bcos la /
NK122(kho)002:572: bka' spyi'i dgongs pa 'grel pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:577: zhar la bzo gso gnyis kyang shes par bya'o //
NK122(kho)002:578: dang po sgra'i bstan chos la gsum /
NK122(kho)002:583: brgya byin gyis mdzad pa'i in+d+ra b+y+aa ka ra na dang /
NK122(kho)002:584: slob dpon tsan+d+ra go mis mdzad pa'i sgra tsan+d+ra pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:586: sgra mtshams sbyor lnga pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:587: smri tis mdzad pa'i smra sgo mtshon cha dang /
NK122(kho)002:589: bod kyi lo ts+aa ba ka cog dag yig dang /
NK122(kho)002:590: dge slong rdo rje dbang phyug gi dkar lid dang /
NK122(kho)002:591: mkhan po grags pa seng+ge'i gang+ga'i chu rgyun dang /
NK122(kho)002:592: sa skya ba'i rin chen sgrom bu la sogs pa rnams yin no //
NK122(kho)002:593: snyan ngag la slob dpon dga' byed kyi snyan ngag me long dang /
NK122(kho)002:596: mkhas pa bde blos mdzad pa'i gzhon nu lnga pa /
NK122(kho)002:597: sa skya pan chen gyis mdzad pa'i mkhas pa 'jug pa'i sgo dang /
NK122(kho)002:600: ngag lam bzhi pa la sogs pa rnams yin no //
NK122(kho)002:601: sdeb sbyor la phyi rol pa'i dmar ser rgyal ba'i lhas byas pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:602: slob dpon shan ti bas byas pa'i rin chen 'byung gnas dang /
NK122(kho)002:603: slob dpon dpa' bos byas pa'i bkra chen dang bkra chung rnams yin no //
NK122(kho)002:605: slob dpon dbyig gnyen gyi rig pa'i sgrom dang /
NK122(kho)002:606: phyogs glang gi tshad ma kun las btus pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:607: de nyid kyi 'grel pa slob dpon chos kyi grags pas sde bdun mdzad pa las /
NK122(kho)002:608: gtso bo lus lta bu'i bstan chos ni /
NK122(kho)002:609: shin tu rgyas pa rnam 'grel dang /
NK122(kho)002:610: cung zad bsdus pa rnam nges dang /
NK122(kho)002:611: shin tu bsdus pa rig thig dang gsum mo //
NK122(kho)002:612: 'khor yan lag lta bu'i bstan chos ni /
NK122(kho)002:616: gtan tshigs thig pa dang bzhi'o //
NK122(kho)002:617: bzo'i rig pa la slob dpon klu sgrub kyis mdzad pa'i gser 'gyur rtsi'i bstan chos /
NK122(kho)002:618: sku rten ci ltar byed pa'i tshul 'dul ba lung
NK122(kho)002:619: las bshad pa'i khyams su skyes rabs la sogs pa'i
NK122(kho)002:620: bzhengs lugs mdo rtsa sogs su snang bas gzhan du
NK122(kho)002:621: shes par bya'o // gso ba rigs pa'i skor la /
NK122(kho)002:624: drang srong nyi shu rtsa gcig /
NK122(kho)002:625: slob dpon klu grub kyi rig pa rtsa ba'i mdo /
NK122(kho)002:628: yan lag bzhi'i mdo dang bzhi brgyad do //
NK122(kho)002:629: sangs rgyas kyi bka' gzhung yan lag brgyad pa la sogs pa rnams yin no //
NK122(kho)002:630: gnyis pa bye brag gi dgongs pa 'grel ba'i bstan bcos ni /
NK122(kho)002:631: bka' dang po'i dgongs 'grel la lta ba'i cha gsal bar ston pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:632: spyod pa'i cha gsal bar ston pa'o //
NK122(kho)002:634: theg chung gi mngon pa sde bdun te //
NK122(kho)002:635: chos kyi phung po sh+aa ri'i bus //
NK122(kho)002:636: gdags pa'i bstan bcos moo 'gal bus //
NK122(kho)002:637: khams kyi tshogs ni gang pos byas //
NK122(kho)002:638: rnam shes tshogs ni lha skyid kyis //
NK122(kho)002:639: ye shes la 'jug ka t+ya'i bus //
NK122(kho)002:640: rab tu 'byed pa dbyig bshes kyis //
NK122(kho)002:641: yang dag 'gro ba'i rnam grangs ni //
NK122(kho)002:642: gsus po che yis byas zhes grags //
NK122(kho)002:644: de rjes dgra bcom pa chos skyobs kyis sangs rgyas 'das nas lo brgya'i dus su /
NK122(kho)002:645: mngon pa sde bdun gyi don bsdus nas bye brag du smra ba'i bshad mdzod chen po mdzad /
NK122(kho)002:646: de'i don bsdus pa dbyig gnyen gyis mdzod kyi gnas brgyad /
NK122(kho)002:647: slob dpon thogs med kyis mngon pa kun las btus pa mdzad do //
NK122(kho)002:648: spyod pa'i cha gsal bar ston pa yon tan 'od kyis 'dul ba mdo rtsa dang /
NK122(kho)002:650: sh+aakya 'od kyi dge tshul gyi ka ri ka sum brgya pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:652: dgra bcom pa sa ga lhas byas pa'i 'dul ba me tog 'phreng brgyud /
NK122(kho)002:653: slob dpon dul ba'i lhas mdzad pa'i ka ri ka lnga bcu pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:654: de'i 'grel pa ka ma la sh+ai las mdzad pa'i sgo brgyad ma lta bu'o //
NK122(kho)002:656: lta ba'i cha gsal bar ston pa ni /
NK122(kho)002:657: slob dpon klu sgrub kyi dbu ma rig pa'i tshogs drug /
NK122(kho)002:658: dbu ma rtsa ba shes rab /
NK122(kho)002:663: tha snyad grub pa dang drug /
NK122(kho)002:664: rje btsun byams pas byas pa'i mngon rtog rgyan lta bu'o //
NK122(kho)002:665: spyod pa'i cha gsal bar ston pa ni mdo kun las btus pa dang spyod 'jug lta bu'o //
NK122(kho)002:667: lta ba'i cha gsal bar ston pa ni /
NK122(kho)002:669: dbus mtha' rnam par 'byed pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:670: chos dang chos nyid rnam par 'byed pa /
NK122(kho)002:676: pra ka ra na sde brgyad rnams yin no //
NK122(kho)002:677: spyod pa'i cha gsal bar ston pa ni /
NK122(kho)002:678: tsan+d+ra go mi'i sdom pa nyi shu pa lta bu'o //
NK122(kho)002:679: de yan chad kyis sde snod gsum la brten pa'i
NK122(kho)002:680: bstan bcos kyis rkang bzung mdo tsam gcig yin la
NK122(kho)002:681: / rgyud sde bzhi la brten pa'i man ngag rnams ni logs su shes par bya'o //
NK122(kho)002:682: 'dir yi ges 'jigs pa'i phyir ma bkod do //
NK122(kho)002:683: theg pa spyi bcing 'di nyid ni /
NK122(kho)002:684: de rnams kyi nang nas sgrub pa lhur len gyi bstan bcos yin /
NK122(kho)002:685: brjod bya'i don la theg pa rim pa dgu yod
NK122(kho)002:686: pa kun gyi don ston pa yin pas 'di nyid
NK122(kho)002:687: theg pa spyi la 'jug pa'i bstan bcos yin /
NK122(kho)002:688: 'o na phyogs gsang sngags nang pa rnam gsum du ngos bzung ba dang mi 'gal lam zhe na /
NK122(kho)002:690: theg pa 'og ma rnams gsang sngags pa'i lam stegs su bshad pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:692: yar ldan gyi tshul du gsang sngags nang pa bshad
NK122(kho)002:693: pa'i zhor la theg pa 'og ma rnams kyi grub
NK122(kho)002:694: matha'i 'dod so kun rgyas par 'byung ba yin /
NK122(kho)002:695: de ltar yang 'di nyid kyi rgyud kyi khungs ni dgongs 'dus las /
NK122(kho)002:696: sangs rgyas thams cad kyi spyi mdo dgongs pa 'dus pa zhes pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:698: spyi lung gsang ba'i snying po zhes pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:700: theg pa gsum gyis nges 'byung la //
NK122(kho)002:701: theg pa gcig gis 'bras bur gnas //
NK122(kho)002:702: zhes gsungs pas 'gal ba med do //
NK122(kho)002:703: gnyis pa don ma nor bar shes par bya ba'i phyir /
NK122(kho)002:704: bshad pa'i thabs bstan pa la gsum ste /
NK122(kho)002:705: seng+ge'i 'gros kyis spyi don gyi khog dbub pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:706: stag mo'i 'gros kyis gzhung don gyi sa bcad pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:707: rus sbal 'gros kyis tshig don gyi 'bru gnyer ba'o //
NK122(kho)002:708: dang po bka' thams cad phun sum tshogs pa lngas 'chad pa yin kyang /
NK122(kho)002:709: 'di nyid bka' la rten pa'i bstan bcos sam /
NK122(kho)002:710: man ngag yin pas rtsis 'go lngas 'chad par byed de /
NK122(kho)002:712: thos chung gsar bu yid ches bskyed pa'i phyir //
NK122(kho)002:713: man ngag spyi don rtsis 'gos glad nas gzhom //
NK122(kho)002:715: khungs btsun zhing yid ches par bya ba'i phyir /
NK122(kho)002:716: slob dpon gang gis mdzad pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:717: bka' dang mi 'gal zhing theg pa'i gzhung tshugs par bya ba'i phyir /
NK122(kho)002:718: rgyud gang nas btus shing phyogs gar gtogs pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:719: bstan pa la mtshan nges shing don gyi mdo tsam cig rtogs par bya ba'i phyir /
NK122(kho)002:720: mtshan ci la btags pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:721: brtsam pa la don yod par bya ba'i phyir /
NK122(kho)002:722: dgos ched gang gi don du mdzad pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:723: dbu zhabs gyi don shes shing khung du chud par bya ba'i phyir /
NK122(kho)002:724: dbu zhabs su don bstan pa dang lnga'o //
NK122(kho)002:725: dang po ni spyir bstan bcos rtsom pa'i tshad la /
NK122(kho)002:726: rab chos nyid bden pa'i don mthong ba /
NK122(kho)002:727: 'bring yi dam lha'i zhal mthong zhing lung bstan thob pa /
NK122(kho)002:728: tha ma bka'i gzhung don khrol zhing theg pa'i shan 'byed cing la zlos pa /
NK122(kho)002:729: tshig don mkhas shing bye brag phyed pa gcig gis brtsam dgos par 'byung ba yin /
NK122(kho)002:731: chos nyid mngon du rtogs pa rab //
NK122(kho)002:732: bla ma yi dam mkha' 'gro yis //
NK122(kho)002:733: lung bstan thob pa 'bring po yin //
NK122(kho)002:734: la shan bka' lung tshig la mkhas //
NK122(kho)002:735: bye brag phyed pa tha ma yin //
NK122(kho)002:737: gzhung 'di nyid kyi rtsom pa po dam pa bde bar gshegs pa ni /
NK122(kho)002:738: sngon sbyangs pa yun ring la dar drag pa'i stobs kyis gzhung 'di las /
NK122(kho)002:739: dkyil 'khor gsum po dbyer med cing //
NK122(kho)002:740: shes bya kun gyi gzhir gnas la //
NK122(kho)002:741: thams cad ngo bo mnyam pa yin //
NK122(kho)002:743: gsang sngags thun mong ma yin pa'i grub mtha' 'khor
NK122(kho)002:744: 'das dbyer med mnyam pa nyid kyi don yul bral
NK122(kho)002:745: gyi ye shes chen po mngon du gyur pa yin
NK122(kho)002:746: te / drod rtags kyi ye shes 'char tshul la
NK122(kho)002:747: sogs pa yon tan bsam gyis mi khyab pa las
NK122(kho)002:748: te / / 'dir cha shas tsam zhig smos na /
NK122(kho)002:749: sngon gyi gnas dran pa'i mngon par shes pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:750: pha rol gzhan gyi sems rgyud shes pa'i mngon par shes pa dang ldan pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:751: sangs rgyas 'od dpag tu med pa'i ston 'khor zhing khams dang bcas pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:752: mi bskyod pa'i ston 'khor zhing khams dang bcas pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:753: skye rab mang po'i gong rol du dbyer med dam
NK122(kho)002:754: mdzad pa'i 'phags pa 'jam dpal dang 'du 'bral med
NK122(kho)002:755: par zhal gzigs shing lung bstan thob pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:756: brgyud pa'i grub thob rnams dang thugs dam gyi lha bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis dang /
NK122(kho)002:757: khro bo dang bde mchog la sogs pa'i dkyil 'khor lha tshogs mang po dang /
NK122(kho)002:758: chos skyong ma mgon la sogs pa rnams dus rgyun
NK122(kho)002:759: chad med par zhal mngon sum du gzigs pa dang
NK122(kho)002:760: / rgyu 'bras kyi theg pa bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i brjod bya shan 'byed cing /
NK122(kho)002:761: la zlos pa'i tshig don la nor 'khrul dang lhag chad mi mnga' bas /
NK122(kho)002:762: rtsom tshad rab 'bring tha gsum ga dang ldan pa'i slob dpon des mdzad do //
NK122(kho)002:764: rtsom pa'i tshad rab 'bring gnyis gong dang 'dra la /
NK122(kho)002:765: tha ma rig pa'i gnas la mkhas pa zhig dgos ces bya bar yang snang /
NK122(kho)002:767: bla ma de nyid gdul bya'i dbang gis bod kyi dge ba'i bshes gnyen du byon nas /
NK122(kho)002:768: sku skye ba 'di la rig pa'i gnas lnga zhal
NK122(kho)002:769: gyis mi bzhes kyang skyes rabs snga ma rnams su
NK122(kho)002:770: rgya gar gyi pan+di ta mkhas grub 'dzom pa mang
NK122(kho)002:771: por sku 'khrungs pa'i phyir rtsom tshad de nyid kyang
NK122(kho)002:773: gnyis pa bka' dang mi 'gal zhing theg pa'i gzhung
NK122(kho)002:774: tshugs par bya ba'i phyir rgyud gang nas btus shing
NK122(kho)002:777: kun bzang la sogs rgyal ba rgya mtsho yi //
NK122(kho)002:778: bstan pa dam chos rgya mtsho ji snyed rnams //
NK122(kho)002:780: spyir rgyu 'bras kyi theg pa kun nas btus shing /
NK122(kho)002:781: khyad par du gsang sngags nang pa rnam gsum la brten pa'i man ngag yin /
NK122(kho)002:784: rtsa rgyud gsang ba'i snying po la brten pa shas che ba yin /
NK122(kho)002:785: 'di yi dang po lus rnam bzhag gi skabs su
NK122(kho)002:786: ldog phyogs lngas chos thams cad gtan la dbab pa
NK122(kho)002:787: dang / don mdzad tshul gyi skabs su gdul bya
NK122(kho)002:788: 'dul thabs theg pa yang re re'i gsum gsum du
NK122(kho)002:789: dang / gnas pa yin / ces gdul bya gsum 'dul thabs gsum /
NK122(kho)002:790: theg pa gsum du bzhed pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:791: don dam nges pa'i theg pa'i skabs su /
NK122(kho)002:792: gol bzhi theg pa dgu dang /
NK122(kho)002:793: gol ba mu stegs dgu phyi nang shan 'byed pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:796: dbang bsgyur thabs kyi theg pa yin /
NK122(kho)002:797: ces kun 'byung ba 'dren pa'i theg pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:798: dka' thub rig byed kyi theg pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:799: dbang bsgyur thabs kyi theg pa gsum du bsdus par bzhed pa rnams /
NK122(kho)002:800: mdo dgongs 'dus nyid kyi gzhung lugs yin la /
NK122(kho)002:801: gzhung 'di nyid nas 'byung ba'i shes byed kyi lung
NK122(kho)002:802: rnams kyang dgongs 'dus kyi nang nas 'byung ba mang
NK122(kho)002:803: ba yin no // gsang ba'i snying po'i le'u bcu
NK122(kho)002:804: gsum pa shin tu gsang ba man ngag gi le'u
NK122(kho)002:805: ba yin no // las / ma rtogs pa dang log par rtog /
NK122(kho)002:806: phyogs rtogs yang dag nyid ma rtogs //
NK122(kho)002:807: 'dul ba dgongs pa gsang ba dang //
NK122(kho)002:808: rang bzhin gsang ba'i don rnams te //
NK122(kho)002:810: don dam nges pa'i theg pa'i khog dbub pa'i tshig byas shing /
NK122(kho)002:811: slar yang de nyid kyi gzhung bsdu ba ni /
NK122(kho)002:813: gtan tshigs de gnyis kyi phyir /
NK122(kho)002:814: phyogs bskyed rdzogs gnyis kar gtogs pa grub cing /
NK122(kho)002:815: rdzogs pa chen po ni thams cad kyi la bzla yin pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:816: thams cad de las 'phros zhing der 'dus pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:818: nang pa rnam gsum ya bkar ma yin pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:819: gcig gis gcig 'byin par gsungs pa yin /
NK122(kho)002:820: bdud rtsi chen po'i rgyud las kyang //
NK122(kho)002:821: rgyud dang lung dang man ngag kyang //
NK122(kho)002:822: 'bangs dang rje dang rgyal po'i tshul //
NK122(kho)002:823: khyad par rtsal 'phang thag ring yang //
NK122(kho)002:824: gcig la gcig brten gcig gi ngang //
NK122(kho)002:826: gzhung 'di nyid rgyud lung gnyis kyis khog dbub cing /
NK122(kho)002:827: 'di nyid rdzogs pa chen por la bzla ste /
NK122(kho)002:828: thams cad rdzogs pa chen por gtan la 'bebs cing bstan pa'i phyir /
NK122(kho)002:829: phyogs rdzogs pa chen por gtogs pa nges par grub pa yin /
NK122(kho)002:830: gsum pa mtshan ci la btags pa ni /
NK122(kho)002:831: spyir mtshan gyi 'dogs lugs la lnga las /
NK122(kho)002:832: bcom ldan 'das kyi phyag tu 'bras sa lu ljang
NK122(kho)002:833: pa nyag ma gcig bsnams pa la dper mdzad nas
NK122(kho)002:834: rten cing 'brel bar 'byung ba bcu gnyis gsungs pa
NK122(kho)002:835: la / sa lu ljang pa'i mdo ces pa lta bu dpe la btags pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:836: shwa lo ka'i grangs la btags pa pha rol du phyin pa 'bum zhes pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:837: le'u'i grangs la btags la sgyu 'phrul rgyas pa brgyad
NK122(kho)002:838: cu pa zhes pa lta bu rnams grangs la btags
NK122(kho)002:839: pa dang / lha'i bus zhus pa'i mdo /
NK122(kho)002:840: zhes pa lta bu gang zag la btags pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:841: bcom ldan 'das srin yul lang ka pu rir gshegs nas gsungs pa la /
NK122(kho)002:842: lang kar gshegs pa'i mdo ces pa lta bu yul las btags pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:843: don las btags pa dang lnga las /
NK122(kho)002:844: 'di ni don las btags pa yin /
NK122(kho)002:846: rdo rje sems dpa'i zhus len ces pa lta bu don gyi gtso bo la btags pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:847: chu gtor ces pa lta bu rgyu'i gtso bo la btags pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:848: de gnyis ni gtso bo las btags pa yin cing /
NK122(kho)002:849: rim gsum ces pa lta bu don gyi rnam grangs la btags pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:850: don bsdus ces pa lta bu don mdor bsdus pa las btags pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:851: spyi mdo sangs rgyas thams cad kyi dgongs pa 'dus
NK122(kho)002:852: pa lta bu don rang gi ngo bo la btags
NK122(kho)002:854: 'di nyid don rang gi ngo bo la btags pa
NK122(kho)002:855: theg pa kun gyi spyi bcing ces bya ba yin
NK122(kho)002:856: / de la theg pa ni 'deg par byed pa yin la /
NK122(kho)002:857: kun gyi spyir 'khor lo rgyun dang /
NK122(kho)002:859: cho 'phrul mngon 'byung gi theg pa gsum /
NK122(kho)002:860: bye brag tu theg pa dgu zhar byung mu stegs dang bcas pa kun ste /
NK122(kho)002:862: de dag gi don ma lus pa 'dir 'dus pa la ni spyi bcing zhes brjod pa yin /
NK122(kho)002:863: bye brag tu don dam nges pa'i theg pa'i don 'chad na /
NK122(kho)002:866: 'di las 'dir theg pa'i don gyis na theg pa ste /
NK122(kho)002:867: yar ldan glang chen gyi dpe /
NK122(kho)002:869: khang pa sgo mang gi dpe la sogs pa mang yang /
NK122(kho)002:870: 'dir re zhig gru gzing gi dpes mtshon ste /
NK122(kho)002:872: nyan thos kyi theg pa'i sgor 'jug pa'i gang zag ni /
NK122(kho)002:873: 'di theg pa ste mi lta bu /
NK122(kho)002:874: bden pa bzhi'i chos kyi 'khor lo ni /
NK122(kho)002:875: 'dis theg pa ste gru gzing lta bu /
NK122(kho)002:876: khams gsum gyi chos rgyu dang 'bras bur bcas pa ni /
NK122(kho)002:877: 'di las theg pa ste chu lta bu'o //
NK122(kho)002:878: dgra bcom pa skyes bu zung bzhi gang zag ya
NK122(kho)002:879: brgyad ni 'dir theg pa ste skam sa lta bu'o
NK122(kho)002:880: // de bzhin du theg pa gong ma rnams kyi
NK122(kho)002:881: sgor 'jug pa'i rten gyi gang zag ni 'di theg
NK122(kho)002:883: theg pa gong ma gong ma rnams kyi gzhung lugs
NK122(kho)002:884: ci lta ba'i don ston pa'i lung dang rtogs pa'i
NK122(kho)002:885: chos rnams ni 'dis theg pa ste /
NK122(kho)002:887: khams gsum gyi sdug bsngal rgyu dang 'bras bur bcas pa'i steng du /
NK122(kho)002:888: theg pa 'og ma 'og ma'i rgyu 'bras bu dang bcas pa bzhag pa ni /
NK122(kho)002:889: 'di las theg pa ste chu lta bu /
NK122(kho)002:890: theg pa gong ma gong ma rnams kyi 'bras bu
NK122(kho)002:891: mthar thug pa ni 'dir theg pa ste skam sa
NK122(kho)002:892: lta bu yin pa'i phyir theg pa ste /
NK122(kho)002:893: de nyid don dam nges pa'i theg pa'i sgra don gtso bor 'chad pa yin la /
NK122(kho)002:894: theg pa gnyis po ni don 'gyur cha shas tsam 'byung ba la bzhag gsungs /
NK122(kho)002:895: bzhi pa dgos ched gang gi don du mdzad pa ni /
NK122(kho)002:896: bshad pa dam bca' ba'i skabs su /
NK122(kho)002:897: shes ldan kun la phan gdag phyir /
NK122(kho)002:899: ma 'ongs pa'i gang zag gzhung 'di nyid kyi don
NK122(kho)002:900: go zhing bde blag tu rtogs nus pa rnams kyi
NK122(kho)002:902: de la yang rang bzo ma yin nam snyam na ma yin te /
NK122(kho)002:903: gzhung gi zhabs don gyi skabs su /
NK122(kho)002:904: kun bzang la sogs rgyal ba rgya mtsho yi //
NK122(kho)002:905: bstan pa dam chos rgya mtsho ji snyed rnams //
NK122(kho)002:907: gzhung lugs rgya mtsho tsam la brten pa'i man ngag yin /
NK122(kho)002:908: 'o na mdo rgyud rgya mtsho tsam las 'byung ba nyid kyis chog ste /
NK122(kho)002:909: gzhung 'di nyid brtsam pa bldab par 'gyur bas dgos pa med dam snyam na /
NK122(kho)002:911: gzhung gi zhabs don gyi skabs su /
NK122(kho)002:912: rgya che rgya mtsho chu las ngang pas 'o ma'i bcud blang ci bzhin tu /
NK122(kho)002:913: theg pa'i bye brag phyogs dang min des grub 'di bsdus /
NK122(kho)002:915: mdo rgyud rgya mtsho tsam du rgya che zhing grangs
NK122(kho)002:916: mang ba rnams su 'thor zhing tshig tshogs rgya che
NK122(kho)002:917: bas sdud shin tu dka' bar gnas pa las /
NK122(kho)002:918: phyi rabs pa tshig tshogs mang pos 'jigs pa rnams kyi don du /
NK122(kho)002:919: gzhung tshogs nyung ngus don rgya chen po bsdus nas bstan pa'i phyir /
NK122(kho)002:921: 'di la brten te phyi rabs pa rnams kyis rgya
NK122(kho)002:922: chen po'i don bde blag tu rtogs par 'gyur ba'i
NK122(kho)002:924: dgos pa med pa'i skyon med de /
NK122(kho)002:926: bde blag tu ni rtogs pa zhes //
NK122(kho)002:927: bya ba brtsam pa'i dgos pa yin //
NK122(kho)002:929: 'on kyang lhag chad can du 'gyur snyams na /
NK122(kho)002:930: bshad par dam bca' ba'i skabs su /
NK122(kho)002:931: tshad ma gsum dang mi 'gal bar zhes 'byung ba ltar yin pas /
NK122(kho)002:932: lhag chad du 'gro ba'i skyon med do //
NK122(kho)002:933: lnga pa dbu zhabs su don bstan pa ni /
NK122(kho)002:935: zhabs gsum du shes par byas shing de nyid la yang /
NK122(kho)002:936: spyi don lngas bstan pa yin /
NK122(kho)002:937: chos nyid ye nas gnas pa'i gnas lugs dang /
NK122(kho)002:938: de ma rtogs pa sems kyi 'khrul tshul /
NK122(kho)002:939: 'khrul pa de nyid la ye shes kyis gzigs tshul /
NK122(kho)002:940: gzigs nas thugs rje skyes tshul /
NK122(kho)002:941: skyes nas don mdzad tshul lo //
NK122(kho)002:943: 'khor lo rgyun gyi theg pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:944: cho 'phrul mngon byung gi theg pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:945: don dam nges pa'i theg pas don mdzad tshul lo //
NK122(kho)002:946: don dam nges pa'i theg pa la phyi rol mu stegs pa'i grub mtha' dang /
NK122(kho)002:947: nang pa sangs rgyas pa'i grub mtha' gnyis /
NK122(kho)002:948: nang pa la yang theg pa rim pa dgu /
NK122(kho)002:949: theg pa re re la don bdun bdun ste /
NK122(kho)002:951: spyod pa tshul khrims lam gyi yun /
NK122(kho)002:952: 'bras bu dag dang bdun bdun du shes par bya'o //
NK122(kho)002:953: des spyi don gyis khog phub pa de song nas /
NK122(kho)002:954: gzhung don gyis sa bcad pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:955: tshig don gyis 'bru gnyer ba gnyis /
NK122(kho)002:956: bshad bya gzhung don dngos kyi skabs dang sbyar ba yin no //
NK122(kho)002:958: bstan pa'i srog shing yin la /
NK122(kho)002:959: de'ang 'chad pa pos legs par bshad cing /
NK122(kho)002:960: nyan pa po'i rim gyis gzhan la spel bas /
NK122(kho)002:961: dam pa'i chos mi nub cing dar zhing rgyas par bya ba'i phyir /
NK122(kho)002:962: dpon slob gnyis kas sangs rgyas kyi bstan pa la bya ba chen po byas pa yin no //
NK122(kho)002:963: gzhan yang dpon slob rang rang gis gzhung don khong du chud cing rtogs pa 'phel ba dang /
NK122(kho)002:964: mthar thug rnam mkhyen thob pa'i dgos pa yod do //
NK122(kho)002:966: lta ba lta ba gtsor brjod mod //
NK122(kho)002:967: don du shes rab kun mnyam nyid //
NK122(kho)002:968: ded dpon rin chen ci bzhin tu //
NK122(kho)002:969: gdod matha'i bye brag 'dir shes dgos //
NK122(kho)002:971: gzhan las chos nyan pa'i phan yon ni //
NK122(kho)002:972: byams pa seng+ge'i sgras zhus pa'i mdo las //
NK122(kho)002:973: 'khor tshogs rnams la chos bstan dus //
NK122(kho)002:975: thos pas byang chub thob gyur na //
NK122(kho)002:976: nyan phyir lhag pa smos ci dgos //
NK122(kho)002:978: 'di yang sangs rgyas kyi bka' yin pas the tshom dang som nyi mi bya'o //
NK122(kho)002:979: theg pa spyi bcing gi 'chad nyan bkod pa mu
NK122(kho)002:980: tig 'phreng chung ces bya ba re zhig rdzogs so
NK122(kho)002:981: //// spyi don gsum pa bshad bya gzhung dngos kyi don la gsum ste /
NK122(kho)002:982: sngon 'gro bstan bcos kyi 'brel btsal ba klad kyi don dang /
NK122(kho)002:983: dngos gzhi bstan bcos kyi lus bzhag pa gzhung gi don dang /
NK122(kho)002:984: mjug brtsam tshul dge ba bsngo ba zhabs kyi don dang gsum /
NK122(kho)002:987: bshad par dam bca' ba gnyis /
NK122(kho)002:989: bgrang chos kyi kha byang thun mong gi mchod par brjod pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:991: 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pa la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK122(kho)002:992: zhes pa ni bshad pa'i gzhir drang /
NK122(kho)002:993: de'i khyad par gyi chos la lnga /
NK122(kho)002:996: slob dpon chen po dam pas /
NK122(kho)002:997: rjes 'jug tu chos 'chad nyan pa rnams kyis /
NK122(kho)002:998: gang la na 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pa la /
NK122(kho)002:999: de yang rgyu mtshan nyid kyi theg pa ltar bshad na /
NK122(kho)002:1000: dang po byang chub mchog tu sems bskyed nas /
NK122(kho)002:1001: bar du bskal pa grangs med gsum la lam rim gyis sbyangs nas /
NK122(kho)002:1002: mdzad pa bcu gnyis kyi tshul du /
NK122(kho)002:1004: snyom 'jug gi sgrib pa gsum las grol nas /
NK122(kho)002:1005: chos nyid la matha'i skyon dang sgrib pa'i zug rngu mi mnga' bas 'jam zhes bya ba yin /
NK122(kho)002:1007: rtogs bya chos kyi dbyings rang bzhin gyis rnam par dag pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:1008: de nyid rtogs pa'i ye shes dbyer med pa ni
NK122(kho)002:1009: chos kyi sku ste rtogs pa bdag gi dpal des
NK122(kho)002:1010: rang don phun sum tshogs pa bstan la /
NK122(kho)002:1011: de nyid gzugs skur snang nas gdul bya nye ring rnams kyi mgon dang dpal du gyur pa ni /
NK122(kho)002:1013: des gzhan don phun sum tshogs pa bstan cing /
NK122(kho)002:1014: de gnyis kyis rtogs pa phun sum tshogs pa bstan la /
NK122(kho)002:1015: chos sku'i ngo bo la bsgres rgud med pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:1016: tshangs spyod dge ba spyod pa mthar phyin cing /
NK122(kho)002:1017: gzhon nu lo brgyad pa'am bcu drug pa lta bu'i cha lugs 'dzin pas /
NK122(kho)002:1018: gzhon nu zhes bya ba yin /
NK122(kho)002:1019: de lta bu'i spangs rtogs phun sum tshogs pa de mngon du gyur pa yin /
NK122(kho)002:1020: mtshan nyid theg pa'i lugs la sangs rgyas pa'i dus su spangs rtogs mthar phyin pa gcig la bzhed /
NK122(kho)002:1022: sngags ltar na sems nyid rang byung gi ye shes la spang gnyen ro gcig pa ste /
NK122(kho)002:1023: gzung 'dzin gyi dri ma ka nas dag pas 'jam /
NK122(kho)002:1024: bde legs yon tan thams cad brtsal ba med par
NK122(kho)002:1025: lhun gyis grub pas na dpal sems nyid skye 'jig
NK122(kho)002:1027: de lta bu'i don de mngon du rtogs par gyur pa ste /
NK122(kho)002:1029: 'jam pa rdul bral dri ma med //
NK122(kho)002:1030: dpal ni kun skyobs ye shes yin //
NK122(kho)002:1031: bsgres rgud bral bas gzhon nur gyur //
NK122(kho)002:1032: gzhon nur gyur pas yid blo gros //
NK122(kho)002:1035: sngon byung slob dpon chen po dam pas bstan bcos brtsom pa'i thog mar /
NK122(kho)002:1036: rjes 'jug tu 'chad nyan pa rnams kyis nyan bshad byed pa'i thog mar /
NK122(kho)002:1042: 'og sku lnga'i mchod brjod kyi skabs su 'chad do //
NK122(kho)002:1043: khyad par gyi mchod par brjod pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:1045: mnyam pa nyid kyi sku ni /
NK122(kho)002:1046: 'khor 'das thams cad sems nyid kyi ngang la dbyer med ro gcig par gyur pa yin /
NK122(kho)002:1047: dper na bu ram las bzos pa'i gzugs 'gros /
NK122(kho)002:1048: ci ltar snang yang mngar ba la ro gcig pa lta bu'o //
NK122(kho)002:1049: 'di ni khyad par gsang sngags kyi chos kyi sku yin no //
NK122(kho)002:1050: chos sku ni de nyid gzung 'dzin gyi dri ma ka nas dag pa la bya'o //
NK122(kho)002:1051: gdul bya'i ngo la chos sku kun tu bzang po dang rdo rje 'chang zhes zer ro //
NK122(kho)002:1052: gsang ba'i sku ni gsang sngags bla med kyi dgongs pa /
NK122(kho)002:1053: bde stong dbyer med kyi ye shes chags rtog lam khyer mthar phyin pa la bya'o //
NK122(kho)002:1054: de nyid gdul bya'i ngo la /
NK122(kho)002:1056: kha sbyor yan lag bdun ldan gyi longs sku chen po'i /
NK122(kho)002:1057: longs spyod rdzogs sku ni thun mong gi longs sku yin te /
NK122(kho)002:1058: ma 'gag pa 'khor ba la longs spyod /
NK122(kho)002:1059: mi dmigs pa 'das pa longs spyod pa ste /
NK122(kho)002:1060: gzugs sgra dri ro reg bya rnams dang stong pa
NK122(kho)002:1061: skye med kyi gnas lugs gnyis dbyer med du lam
NK122(kho)002:1062: khyer byas pas / dbu rgyan snyan cha la sogs pa /
NK122(kho)002:1063: mtshan dpes spras pa longs sku rnam par snang mdzad lta bu /
NK122(kho)002:1064: gdul bya sa bcu pa'i byang sems rnams kyi ngor shar ba'o //
NK122(kho)002:1065: sprul pa'i sku ni gdul bya'i rgyud la byams sogs
NK122(kho)002:1066: snying rje 'gag med du cir yang 'char ba dang
NK122(kho)002:1067: / de nyid gnas lugs kyi ngang la khyer bas
NK122(kho)002:1068: mthar phyin pa sangs rgyas pa'i dus su sprul sku
NK122(kho)002:1070: mchog gi sprul sku sh+aakya thub pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:1071: dman pa la thub pa lnga po dang /
NK122(kho)002:1072: bzo'i rgyal po karma bi shwa /
NK122(kho)002:1073: mgar gyi rgyal po mgar lha yug pa /
NK122(kho)002:1074: sman gyi rgyal po 'tsho byed gzhon nu la sogs
NK122(kho)002:1075: pa rnams kyi skur snang nas gdul bya mos pa
NK122(kho)002:1077: tshogs sbyor man chad mnar med dmyal ba yan chad kyi don byed pa'o //
NK122(kho)002:1079: de bzhin nyid du son pa dang //
NK122(kho)002:1080: sna tshogs zhen pa grol bar zad //
NK122(kho)002:1081: gdod nas ma bslad kun gyi gnas //
NK122(kho)002:1082: rang bzhin brjod 'das chos kyi sku //
NK122(kho)002:1083: ngo bo bstan dka' yon tan gzhi //
NK122(kho)002:1084: gsang ba'i sku zhes nga yis brjod //
NK122(kho)002:1085: ngo bo gnyis kyi longs spyod la //
NK122(kho)002:1086: mi 'dzin pa ltar dbang phyug che //
NK122(kho)002:1087: ma byung ma myong rgyun mi 'chad //
NK122(kho)002:1088: cir yang 'char ba sprul pa'i sku //
NK122(kho)002:1090: sku de rnams go bde ba'i phyir theg pa yar 'dzeg gam /
NK122(kho)002:1091: lam rtogs tshul gyi sgo nas ngo sprod nas 'bru gnon pa yin /
NK122(kho)002:1092: sprul pa mar 'gyed kyi dbang du yin na /
NK122(kho)002:1093: kun bzang dgongs pa chos nyid las ma g.yos pa
NK122(kho)002:1094: bzhin du gdul bya dag ma dag gi snang ngor
NK122(kho)002:1095: sprul pa sna tshogs ston pa'o //
NK122(kho)002:1096: dper na zla ba'i dkyil 'khor gcig las ma g.yos
NK122(kho)002:1097: bzhin du chu rdzing tha dag gi nang du zla
NK122(kho)002:1098: ba'i gzugs du mar snang ba lta bu'o //
NK122(kho)002:1099: rig pa skad cig ma'i thog tu sku lnga po
NK122(kho)002:1100: ngo sprod rgyu yod pa bla ma'i zhal las shes
NK122(kho)002:1101: par bya'o // 'dir gzhung bshad kyi dbang du'o //
NK122(kho)002:1102: sku lnga dngos su bstan pa yin la de'i shugs
NK122(kho)002:1103: la lung gra chad la nyal ba zur la bslang
NK122(kho)002:1104: ba 'chad pa pos gnyer bya yin pas /
NK122(kho)002:1105: brda' sprod pa'i ngos nas gsung lnga /
NK122(kho)002:1106: dgongs pa zab pa'i ngos nas thugs lnga /
NK122(kho)002:1107: dgos 'dod 'byung ba'i ngos nas yon tan lnga /
NK122(kho)002:1108: bya ba byed pa'i ngos nas phrin las lnga ste /
NK122(kho)002:1109: sku rigs rgyan 'khor lo nyi shu rtsa lnga /
NK122(kho)002:1110: ma 'dres la yongs su rdzogs pa'i don /
NK122(kho)002:1111: kun tu bzang po'i dgongs pa la rdzogs pa'am /
NK122(kho)002:1112: sems nyid rang byung gi ye shes gnas lugs kyi don las ma g.yos pas bdag nyid ces bya'o //
NK122(kho)002:1113: bcom ldan 'das zhes pa'i don la theg pa dgu la bcom lugs dgu yod kyang /
NK122(kho)002:1114: da res 'dir gsum gyi 'dod pa bshad do //
NK122(kho)002:1115: de yang mtshan nyid ltar na /
NK122(kho)002:1116: dang po byang chub mchog tu sems bskyed de /
NK122(kho)002:1117: bar du bskal pa grangs med gsum la tshogs bsags
NK122(kho)002:1118: nas mthar mdzad pa bcu gnyis kyi tshul du bdud
NK122(kho)002:1119: bzhi bcom nas sangs rgyas pa yin /
NK122(kho)002:1120: bcom ldan 'das chu bo nee ra dza na'i 'gram du dka' thub dka' spyad mdzad pa'i rjes la /
NK122(kho)002:1121: bu mo legs skyes mas 'o thug drangs pas sku
NK122(kho)002:1122: gser gyi gtan pa phyis pa ltar du gyur pas
NK122(kho)002:1123: ni / phung po'i bdud bcom mo //
NK122(kho)002:1124: lo brgyad cu la gshegs chis mdzad pa las /
NK122(kho)002:1125: lcags mgar gyi bu'i don du lo gnyis bzhugs pas /
NK122(kho)002:1127: bdud dga' rab dbang phyug gi bu mo rnams kyis
NK122(kho)002:1128: bslu brid byas pa la se gol btog pas rgan
NK122(kho)002:1129: mo bdun du gyur pas ni /
NK122(kho)002:1130: nyon mongs pa'i bdud bcom mo //
NK122(kho)002:1131: byang chub kyi shing drung na srod la bdud thams
NK122(kho)002:1132: cad kyi bdud dmag bye ba dung phyur rnams lhag
NK122(kho)002:1133: nas / mtshon cha'i char phab mi snyan pa sna tshogs bsgrags pa'i dus su /
NK122(kho)002:1134: bcom ldan 'das byams snying rje'i ting nge 'dzin la
NK122(kho)002:1135: zhugs pas phyi rol gyi mtshon cha rnams pad+ma'i tshogs
NK122(kho)002:1136: su gyur / sgra mi snyan pa rnams chos kyi sgra dang /
NK122(kho)002:1137: bstod pa du ma'i tshogs su byung ba ni /
NK122(kho)002:1138: lha'i bu'i bdud bcom pa'i yin te /
NK122(kho)002:1140: nyon mongs las dang de bzhin skye //
NK122(kho)002:1141: nyon mongs shes bya'i sgrib de bzhin //
NK122(kho)002:1142: mi mthun phyogs kyi chos rnams kun //
NK122(kho)002:1143: de bcom pas na bcom zhes bya //
NK122(kho)002:1145: che ba'i yon tan drug dang ldan pas ldan zhes bya ste /
NK122(kho)002:1147: dbang phyug dang ni gzugs bzang dang //
NK122(kho)002:1148: dpal dang grags dang ye shes dang //
NK122(kho)002:1149: brtson 'grus phun sum tshogs ldan pa //
NK122(kho)002:1150: drug po de la ldan zhes bya //
NK122(kho)002:1152: dbang phyug ni tshogs gnyis mthar phyin pa'i dbang gis 'khor 'das la mnga' mdzad cing bsgyur ba'o //
NK122(kho)002:1153: gzugs bzang ba ni mtshan dpes spras pa'o //
NK122(kho)002:1154: dpal ni bdag don gzhan don gyi don gnyis phun sum tshogs pa'o //
NK122(kho)002:1155: grags pa ni che ba'i yon tan sangs rgyas kyi
NK122(kho)002:1156: zhing dang sems can gyi gnas thams cad du khyab
NK122(kho)002:1157: pa'o // ye shes ni ji ltar ji snyed gnyis so //
NK122(kho)002:1158: brtson 'grus ni 'bad pa med pa'i brtson 'grus kyis
NK122(kho)002:1159: skad cig tsam yang ma yengs par gdul bya'i re
NK122(kho)002:1160: ba skong ba'o // srid zhi'i mthar mi gnas pas 'das zhes bya ste /
NK122(kho)002:1162: shes pas srid la mi gnas dang //
NK122(kho)002:1163: snying rjes zhi la mi gnas dang //
NK122(kho)002:1165: mi gnas khyod la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK122(kho)002:1167: gsang sngags ma h+aa yo ga ltar na bcom zhes pa phrin las kyi mtshan te /
NK122(kho)002:1168: nyon mongs pa lnga ma spangs ye shes lnga'i ngo bor gyur pa ni /
NK122(kho)002:1170: phung po lnga nyid ma spangs rigs lnga'i ngo bor gyur pa ni /
NK122(kho)002:1172: sems nyid skye 'jig med pa'i don mngon du gyur pa ni /
NK122(kho)002:1174: lha rtog ro gcig du gyur pa ni /
NK122(kho)002:1175: lha bu'i bdud bcom pa yin ste /
NK122(kho)002:1177: bdud bzhi la sogs rig pa'i gdeng gis bcom //
NK122(kho)002:1179: ldan zhes pa yon tan gyi mtshan ste /
NK122(kho)002:1180: sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las lnga'am /
NK122(kho)002:1181: nyi shu rtsa lnga la sogs pa thugs rang rig
NK122(kho)002:1182: pa'i ye shes la rang bzhin gyis ldan pa ste
NK122(kho)002:1184: sku lnga sogs yon tan brjod las 'das //
NK122(kho)002:1186: 'das zhes pa mtshan nyid kyi mtshan ste gong gi
NK122(kho)002:1187: yon tan de dag thams cad kyang yod med rtag
NK122(kho)002:1188: chad kyi mtha' las 'das pa yin te /
NK122(kho)002:1190: rang gi ngo bo 'di zhes bstan du med //
NK122(kho)002:1192: man ngag ltar na 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad
NK122(kho)002:1193: ngo bo nyid kun tu bzang mo'i mkha' klong yangs
NK122(kho)002:1194: pa'i ngang du chub pas bcom /
NK122(kho)002:1195: kun bzang rol pa 'gag pa med par shar bas ldan /
NK122(kho)002:1196: byang chub kyi sems bde ba chen por mtha' thams cad ma spangs dag pas 'das zhes pa'o //
NK122(kho)002:1197: dpal zhes pa'i don la gsum ste /
NK122(kho)002:1198: gzhi rang bzhin lhun gyis grub pa'i dpal ni /
NK122(kho)002:1199: gzhi mnyam pa nyid kyi gnas lugs la bya'o //
NK122(kho)002:1200: rig pa rang snang ba'i dpal ni /
NK122(kho)002:1201: gzhi de nyid rtogs pa'i lam la bya'o //
NK122(kho)002:1202: thugs rje chen po zhar las byung ba'i dpal ni /
NK122(kho)002:1203: de nyid rtogs pa mthar phyin cing gdul bya'i yul
NK122(kho)002:1204: la gzugs sku rnam gnyis kyis don mdzad pa la
NK122(kho)002:1208: mar dang snum pa lta bu /
NK122(kho)002:1209: ngo bo nyid kyis ldan pa yin te /
NK122(kho)002:1210: gong du bshad pa'i dpal gsum po de dang /
NK122(kho)002:1211: rig pa gnyis ye nas dbyer med pa la ldan zhes bya'o //
NK122(kho)002:1212: kun bzang zhes pa'i don la bzhi ste /
NK122(kho)002:1213: rang bzhin kun tu bzang po ni /
NK122(kho)002:1215: rtogs pa kun tu bzang po ni /
NK122(kho)002:1216: de nyid rtogs pa'i lam la bya'o //
NK122(kho)002:1217: spyod pa kun tu bzang po ni /
NK122(kho)002:1218: de nyid spyod lam rnam bzhir khyer thabs la bya'o //
NK122(kho)002:1219: dus dang gnas skabs kun tu bzang po ni /
NK122(kho)002:1221: res 'ga' med pa lta bu ma yin par /
NK122(kho)002:1222: spyod lam rnam bzhi thams cad du rtsol med chos sku'i 'khor yug la bya'o //
NK122(kho)002:1223: spyod lam thams cad du sku dang ye shes su rgyas pa de la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK122(kho)002:1225: dam pas bstan bcos brtsam pa'i thog mar /
NK122(kho)002:1226: 'chad nyan pa rnams kyis 'chad nyan byed pa'i thog mar /
NK122(kho)002:1227: tshul ci ltar na gsum ste /
NK122(kho)002:1228: spyod pa ya rabs kyi phyag ni /
NK122(kho)002:1229: lus gus pa dang bcas pas mal lnga sa la gtug /
NK122(kho)002:1230: ngag dwangs ba dang dad pas bstod pa'i dbyangs su bcas /
NK122(kho)002:1231: yid ting nge 'dzin gyis phyag 'tshal ba yin te /
NK122(kho)002:1233: lus dang ngag yid dang bas phyag bagyi'o //
NK122(kho)002:1235: sgrub pa thabs kyi phyag ni /
NK122(kho)002:1236: gzhung 'di nyid kyi don bstan pa'i zab pa dang
NK122(kho)002:1237: rgya che ba'i don rnams bde blag tu rtogs shing
NK122(kho)002:1238: / nyams su len pa ni sgrub pa thabs kyi phyag yin te /
NK122(kho)002:1240: gang gis rtogs nas 'jug pa yis //
NK122(kho)002:1243: de ltar ston pa khyad par can gnyis kyi thugs kyi dgongs pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:1244: slob dpon chen po dam pa bde bar gshegs pa'i
NK122(kho)002:1245: thugs kyi dgongs pa gnyis shar nub kyi nam mkha'
NK122(kho)002:1246: ltar dbyer med pa'i ngang du rtogs pa ni mi
NK122(kho)002:1249: ci ltar chu la chu bzhag dang //
NK122(kho)002:1250: ci ltar mar la mar bzhag bzhin //
NK122(kho)002:1251: rang gi ngang gi ye shes dang //
NK122(kho)002:1254: dgos pa gang gi ched du 'tshal ba la /
NK122(kho)002:1255: dngos brtsam pa po gnyis las /
NK122(kho)002:1256: dngos la spyi dang bye brag gnyis /
NK122(kho)002:1257: spyi la slob dpon nyid kyi mchod par brjod pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:1258: yi ge'i dkyus su bkod pa'i dgos pa gnyis /
NK122(kho)002:1260: spyir skyes bu ya rabs pa rnams kyis /
NK122(kho)002:1262: rang mos pa'i lha la mchod par brjod nas 'jug pa yin te /
NK122(kho)002:1263: bye brag tu rgya gar gyi yi ge pa rnams kyi yi ge'i klad du /
NK122(kho)002:1264: na ma sh+ri ng+ham zhes pa bris la /
NK122(kho)002:1265: de ltar du rgya gar gyi pan+di ta rnams kyis /
NK122(kho)002:1266: bstan bcos brtsam pa'i klad du /
NK122(kho)002:1267: brjod bya dang mthun pa'i mchod par brjod cing /
NK122(kho)002:1268: de bzhin du 'dir yang slob dpon chen pos ston pa khyad par can gnyis la /
NK122(kho)002:1271: tshogs rdzogs cing bar chad brgyud nas dag ste /
NK122(kho)002:1272: brtsam pa mthar phyin pa'i dgos pa yod do //
NK122(kho)002:1273: yi ger bkod pa'i dgos pa ni /
NK122(kho)002:1274: ston pa khyad par can gnyis la mchod par brjod pas /
NK122(kho)002:1275: ma 'ongs pa'i gang zag shes rab dang ldan pa rnams /
NK122(kho)002:1276: gzhung 'di nyid du 'jug pa'i dgos pa yod /
NK122(kho)002:1277: bye brag tu 'tshal ba'i dgos pa ni /
NK122(kho)002:1278: 'jam dpal la phyag 'tshal ba'i dgos pa ni /
NK122(kho)002:1279: skye ba mang po'i gong nas thugs dam gyi lha yin pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:1281: zhal gzigs shing lung bstan thob pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:1282: gdul bya rnams kyi shes rab kyi lhar gyur pa'i phyir /
NK122(kho)002:1283: mchod par brjod pa yin la /
NK122(kho)002:1284: kun tu bzang po ni nang pa rnam gsum gyi rgyud kyi ston pa yin pa'i phyir /
NK122(kho)002:1288: ched du brjod pa'i tshom las //
NK122(kho)002:1289: bsod nams bsags pa'i mi dag la //
NK122(kho)002:1290: gzhan las gyur pa'i gnod pa'am //
NK122(kho)002:1291: lha'am bdud kyi rigs rnams kyis //
NK122(kho)002:1292: bar chad bya bar mi nus so //
NK122(kho)002:1294: gnyis pa dgos ched tsam po pa la gnyis te /
NK122(kho)002:1296: gzhung mdzes pa'i dgos ched gnyis /
NK122(kho)002:1298: thams cad mkhyen pa la phyag 'tshal lo snang na /
NK122(kho)002:1300: de bzhin du 'jam dpal la mngon pa'o //
NK122(kho)002:1301: sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa' la na /
NK122(kho)002:1303: rigs gsum mgon po la na /
NK122(kho)002:1305: rigs bzhi rdo rje 'chang la na /
NK122(kho)002:1307: rnam par snang mdzad la na /
NK122(kho)002:1309: rdo rje sems dpa' la na /
NK122(kho)002:1311: bcom ldan 'das sgrol byed thugs rje'i rgyal po la phyag 'tshal lo byas na /
NK122(kho)002:1313: kun tu bzang po la phyag 'tshal lo byas na /
NK122(kho)002:1314: rdzogs pa chen po 'chad par mngon no //
NK122(kho)002:1317: theg pa thams cad ston cing /
NK122(kho)002:1318: mthar rdzogs pa chen por la bzla ba yin pas /
NK122(kho)002:1319: kun tu bzang po la phyag 'tshal ba'o //
NK122(kho)002:1320: gnyis pa gzhung mdzes pa'i dgos pa ni /
NK122(kho)002:1322: yul gyi rgyan ni ri bo /
NK122(kho)002:1323: mi'i rgyan rgyal po yin pa bzhin du /
NK122(kho)002:1324: ston pa khyad par can gnyis la phyag 'tshal bas /
NK122(kho)002:1325: bstan pa mdzes pa'i rgyan du bzhag pa yin no //
NK122(kho)002:1326: skyabs gnas kyi dge 'dun la mchod par brjod pa'o //
NK122(kho)002:1327: grangs 'phags pa zhes pa ni khyad zhugs pa'i sgra yin te /
NK122(kho)002:1329: so so'i skye bo tshogs sbyor pa las 'phags te /
NK122(kho)002:1330: theg pa rang rang gi bdag med nyid kyi don rtogs pa'o //
NK122(kho)002:1332: dge 'dun dang ming tha dad ste stong chen rab 'byams las /
NK122(kho)002:1333: tshogs kyi dam pa lha mis mchod 'os pas /
NK122(kho)002:1334: dge 'dun phyag 'tshal ces gsungs pa ltar ro //
NK122(kho)002:1337: theg dman nyan rang gi dge 'dun dang /
NK122(kho)002:1338: theg chen la zhugs kyang smon 'jug gi sems bskyed ma skyes pa ni /
NK122(kho)002:1341: gang la phul na don che ba /
NK122(kho)002:1344: theg chen la zhugs na smon 'jug gnyis kyi sems bskyed legs por skyes pa ni /
NK122(kho)002:1347: gang la sems kyi dam pa rin chen pa //
NK122(kho)002:1348: skyes pa de yi sku la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK122(kho)002:1351: theg chen mthong lam pa yan chad /
NK122(kho)002:1352: sa thob pa'i byang chub sems dpa' rnams yin te /
NK122(kho)002:1354: gang la gnod pa byas kyang bder 'brel ba //
NK122(kho)002:1355: bde ba'i 'byung gnas de la skyabs su mchi //
NK122(kho)002:1357: kun la zhes pa ma lus pa'i sgra yin te /
NK122(kho)002:1358: theg pa dgu'i 'phags pa'i tshogs kun la'ang /
NK122(kho)002:1359: tshul gong ma bzhin du phyag 'tshal ba'o //
NK122(kho)002:1360: nas zhes pa 'brel mtshams sbyar ba'i tshig yin te /
NK122(kho)002:1361: gang du mchod par brjod pa'i mtha' sdud /
NK122(kho)002:1362: 'og tu bshad pa dam bca' ba'i mgo 'dren pa'o //
NK122(kho)002:1363: dgos 'brel gyi sgo nas bshad par dam bca' ba'o //
NK122(kho)002:1365: de la spyir nang pa'i bstan bcos tha dag la dgos 'brel bzhi tshang dgos la /
NK122(kho)002:1366: sgos su theg pa spyi bcing gi brjod byed kyi
NK122(kho)002:1367: tshig tshogs 'di nyid la dgos 'brel bzhi tshang ba
NK122(kho)002:1368: yin te / de yang dgos 'brel bzhi ngos bzung ba dang /
NK122(kho)002:1369: dgos 'brel bzhi grangs nges pa'i rgyu mtshan dang /
NK122(kho)002:1370: gzhung don dgos 'brel bzhi dngos bstan pa dang gsum /
NK122(kho)002:1371: dang po ngos bzung ba ni /
NK122(kho)002:1376: dgos 'brel bzhir grangs nges pa'i rgyu mtshan ni /
NK122(kho)002:1377: kha cig gis bstan bcos 'di la 'jug par mi bya ste /
NK122(kho)002:1378: brjod bya'i don med pa'i phyir /
NK122(kho)002:1379: dper na bya rog so rtog gi bstan bcos bzhin /
NK122(kho)002:1380: ces pa'i log rtog gi gnyen por brjod bya don dang ldan par bstan no //
NK122(kho)002:1381: kha cig gis bstan bcos 'di la brjod bya'i don dang ldan yang /
NK122(kho)002:1382: don de nyams su blang bya ma yin te /
NK122(kho)002:1383: dper na sog po bar rtsi ka'i yul nam bag mar len pa'i bstan bcos bzhin /
NK122(kho)002:1384: ces pa'i log rtog gi gnyen por dgos pa bstan no //
NK122(kho)002:1385: kha cig gis bstan bcos 'di la brjod bya'i don dang dgos pa gnyis yod kyang /
NK122(kho)002:1386: mthar thug gi 'bras bu thob pa'i nus pa ma yin te /
NK122(kho)002:1387: klu 'jog po'i gtsug gi nor bu len pa'i bstan bcos lta bu'o //
NK122(kho)002:1388: zhes pa'i log rtog gi gnyen por nying dgos bstan la /
NK122(kho)002:1389: kha cig gis bstan bcos 'di la brjod bya'i don dang /
NK122(kho)002:1392: thabs bstan bcos 'di dang ma 'brel ste /
NK122(kho)002:1394: skam lung chu phyar gong ma na /
NK122(kho)002:1395: rabs chad bu dgu pha dang bcu //
NK122(kho)002:1396: mda' lnga mdung gcig 'phang dang drug /
NK122(kho)002:1397: a ru ra ni tsha ba'i nad la phan //
NK122(kho)002:1398: ces pa lta bu yin ces pa'i log rtog gi gnyen por 'brel pa bstan pa yin no //
NK122(kho)002:1399: gzhung don dgos 'brel bzhi dngos su bstan pa ni /
NK122(kho)002:1400: theg pa kun gyi spyi bcing brjod ces pa ni brjod bya'i don yin la /
NK122(kho)002:1401: shes ldan kun la phan gdag phyir /
NK122(kho)002:1403: 'phags tshogs kun la zhes pas gnas skabs kyi nying dgos bstan /
NK122(kho)002:1405: sku lnga'i bdag nyid bcom ldan 'das //
NK122(kho)002:1406: zhes pas mthar thug gi nying dgos bstan /
NK122(kho)002:1407: de yang brjod byed kyi tshig la brten nas /
NK122(kho)002:1409: de la brten nas gnas skabs dang mthar thug gi 'bras bu thob pa ni /
NK122(kho)002:1411: de rnams ni spyi don gyi bshad pa yin la /
NK122(kho)002:1412: da ni gzhung don gyi 'bru gnyer na /
NK122(kho)002:1413: ma 'ongs pa'i gang zag shes rab dang ldan pa kun la shes rab gsum bskyed de /
NK122(kho)002:1415: de yang tshul ji ltar du phan gdags zhes na /
NK122(kho)002:1416: brjod bya'i don mi gsal ba gsal bar byed pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:1417: rgya chen po mdor bsdus pa dang rgyud 'khrugs pa ldeb /
NK122(kho)002:1419: man ngag gab pa mngon sum du ngo sprod nas /
NK122(kho)002:1420: don phyin ci ma log pa bde blag tu rtogs par byed pa ni /
NK122(kho)002:1421: bstan bcos brtsam pa'i dgos pa yin pa'i phyir /
NK122(kho)002:1423: bde blag tu ni rtogs pa zhes //
NK122(kho)002:1424: bya ba brtsam pa'i dgos pa yin //
NK122(kho)002:1426: de yang rang bzo ma yin nam zhe na /
NK122(kho)002:1429: bla ma dam pa'i man ngag dang /
NK122(kho)002:1430: rang gi nyams myong gis rtogs pa'i tshad ma gsum
NK122(kho)002:1431: dang nam yang mi'agala bar brjod bya'i don mngon sum
NK122(kho)002:1432: du gtan la phab pa ste /
NK122(kho)002:1434: de bzhin bde bar gshegs pa'i rgyud //
NK122(kho)002:1435: bla ma mkhas pa'i man ngag dang //
NK122(kho)002:1436: rang gi nyams kyi bye brag rnams //
NK122(kho)002:1437: tshad ma gsum la brten nas ni //
NK122(kho)002:1439: theg pa ni 'deg par byed pa ste /
NK122(kho)002:1440: theg pa dgu po'i rten gyi gang zag gang yin
NK122(kho)002:1441: pa de theg pa de nyid kyi sgor zhugs te
NK122(kho)002:1442: / bar du chud ma zos shing mthar rang rang
NK122(kho)002:1443: gi 'bras bu la sbyor zhing skyol bar byed pas
NK122(kho)002:1445: de la 'dir yar ldan glang po'i dpe /
NK122(kho)002:1446: khang pa sgo mang gi dpe /
NK122(kho)002:1449: la sogs pa rnams kyi sgo nas theg pa'i sgra
NK122(kho)002:1450: don bshad du yod pa rnams 'og 'jug sgo theg
NK122(kho)002:1451: pa'i skabs su bshad par bya'o //
NK122(kho)002:1456: don dam nges pa'i theg pa kun dang /
NK122(kho)002:1457: bye brag tu theg pa rim pa dgu /
NK122(kho)002:1458: zhar byung mu stegs dang bcas pa'i don 'dir 'dus pas na /
NK122(kho)002:1461: skyes bu ya rabs rnams kyis bya ba ci byed
NK122(kho)002:1462: kyang dam bca' ba las mi 'da' ba bzhin du
NK122(kho)002:1464: thugs kyi dgongs pa zhal du byung ste /
NK122(kho)002:1465: bstan bcos 'di nyid brtsam par dam bca' ba'o //
NK122(kho)002:1467: gzhan don brtse ba can rnams srog phyir yang //
NK122(kho)002:1468: rang gi nus tshad lhod par mi bya ste //
NK122(kho)002:1469: skyes bu dam pa'i khur lci khur ba dag /
NK122(kho)002:1470: nyams nga'i lam du nam yang 'dor mi byed //
NK122(kho)002:1472: gzhung gi don la gnyis te /
NK122(kho)002:1473: bstan bcos kyi lus rnam par bzhag pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:1474: yan lag rgyas par bshad pa'o //
NK122(kho)002:1477: ldog phyogs lngas lus bzhag pa dngos dang /
NK122(kho)002:1479: chos rnams ces pa'i skabs 'dir mkhas pa 'ga' zhig gis /
NK122(kho)002:1483: de ni ha cang thal drag pa yin te /
NK122(kho)002:1485: mi go bar yang mi bshad cing //
NK122(kho)002:1486: thal drag par yang bshad mi bya //
NK122(kho)002:1488: shes bya 'khor 'das lam gsum gyis bsdus pa'i chos rnams kun gyi gnas tshul ni /
NK122(kho)002:1489: theg pa re re la yang 'dod lugs re re yod kyang /
NK122(kho)002:1490: da res 'dir mdo dgongs pa 'dus pa'i lugs /
NK122(kho)002:1491: lung a nu yo ga'i bzhed kyis chos nyid ngo
NK122(kho)002:1492: bo gcig la ldog phyogs mi 'dra ba rnam pa
NK122(kho)002:1494: de yang chos nyid ye nas gnas pa'i tshul dang /
NK122(kho)002:1495: de ma rtogs sems can gyi 'khrul tshul dang /
NK122(kho)002:1496: 'khrul ba de nyid la thugs rje'am ye shes kyis gzigs tshul dang /
NK122(kho)002:1497: gzigs nas thugs rje'i skye tshul /
NK122(kho)002:1498: skyes nas gdul bya'i don mdzad tshul dang lnga'o //
NK122(kho)002:1499: de nyid ma 'dres yongs rdzogs mnyam pa chen por bstan pa'o //
NK122(kho)002:1501: de ltar mtshon tshul lnga po brjod de rim par
NK122(kho)002:1502: bstan cing tha dad pa ltar snang yang bdag nyid
NK122(kho)002:1503: chen po ste / sems kyi gnas lugs sam rang
NK122(kho)002:1504: byung ye shes de nyid chos thams cad kyi rtsa
NK122(kho)002:1505: ba thams cad de las 'phros shing de'i ngang las
NK122(kho)002:1506: logs su ma g.yos pa yin no //
NK122(kho)002:1508: 'gag med snang lugs kyi ngang du ma 'dres la /
NK122(kho)002:1509: skye med gnas lugs kyi ngang du yongs su rdzogs pas na /
NK122(kho)002:1511: dus la snga phyi don la tha dad ngo bo
NK122(kho)002:1512: la bzang ngan med par rang byung ye shes kyi
NK122(kho)002:1514: mnyam zhing rdzogs pa yin no //
NK122(kho)002:1515: rgyas par bshad pa lnga ste /
NK122(kho)002:1516: gzhi chos nyid ye nas gnas pa'i tshul lnga po de ma rtogs te 'khrul tshul dang /
NK122(kho)002:1517: de la sangs rgyas kyi ye shes gzigs tshul dang /
NK122(kho)002:1518: gzigs nas thugs rje'i skyes tshul dang /
NK122(kho)002:1519: skyes nas don mdzad tshul rgyas par bshad pa'o //
NK122(kho)002:1524: lus rnam bzhag gi skabs su ldog phyogs lngas bstan pa'i /
NK122(kho)002:1525: thog ma gzhi ye nas gnas pa'i gnas tshul bstan
NK122(kho)002:1526: pa'i don nyid rgyas par bshad cing gsal bar bstan
NK122(kho)002:1531: skye ba med pa dkyil yin /
NK122(kho)002:1532: 'gag pa med pa 'khor gyis bskor ba'o //
NK122(kho)002:1534: gzhi ji bzhin pa'i dkyil 'khor skye ba med pa dbyings dang /
NK122(kho)002:1535: 'gag pa med pa rang bzhin lhun gyis grub pa'i dkyil 'khor ye shes dang /
NK122(kho)002:1536: de gnyis su med pa rtsa ba byang chub sems kyi dkyil 'khor du dbyer med cing /
NK122(kho)002:1537: shes bya 'khor 'das lam gsum gyis bsdus pa'i chos
NK122(kho)002:1538: rnams kun gyi gzhir gnas pas thams cad ngo bo
NK122(kho)002:1539: mnyam nyid ro gcig pa'i don yin no //
NK122(kho)002:1540: 'di lta bu ni sems can thams cad sangs rgyas
NK122(kho)002:1541: kyi snying po can mthar thug sangs rgyas thob pa
NK122(kho)002:1543: dkyil 'khor gsum du sangs rgyas lugs ni /
NK122(kho)002:1544: gzhi ci bzhin pa bcos slad dang bral ba chos skur sangs rgyas pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:1545: rang bzhin lhun gyis grub pa rtsol ba med par
NK122(kho)002:1546: rang snang ba 'gag med sprul skur sangs rgyas pa
NK122(kho)002:1547: dang / rtsa ba byang chub sems kyi dkyil 'khor
NK122(kho)002:1548: ni gnyis su med par longs spyod rdzogs pa'i skur
NK122(kho)002:1551: ye nas sangs rgyas bde chen nyid //
NK122(kho)002:1552: skye 'gag med pa'i snying po ste //
NK122(kho)002:1553: bya ba med pa'i dkyil 'khor gsum //
NK122(kho)002:1554: ye nas grub zin lhun gyis grub //
NK122(kho)002:1557: sna tshogs zhen bcas kyi rtog pa'i mtshan ma can yod pas /
NK122(kho)002:1558: de dgrol ba'i phyir sems can thams cad dang gzhi ci bzhin pa'i dkyil 'khor du ngo sprad /
NK122(kho)002:1559: sangs rgyas bya ba bzang po gcig log na yod par 'dzin pa'i rtogs pa yod pas /
NK122(kho)002:1560: de grol ba'i phyir sems can dang rang bzhin lhun gyis grub pa'i dkyil 'khor du ngo sprad /
NK122(kho)002:1561: sna tshogs gnyis 'dzin gyi rtog pa yod pas de
NK122(kho)002:1562: grol ba'i phyir sems can dang rtsa ba byang chub
NK122(kho)002:1563: sems kyi dkyil 'khor du ngo sprad pa yin no
NK122(kho)002:1566: 'khrul pa 'khor ba'i rgyu dpe'i dang bcas pa /
NK122(kho)002:1571: lhan cig skyes pa'i ma rig pa'i mthus ma rtogs pa yin /
NK122(kho)002:1572: gzhi ye shes rang byung sangs rgyas su gnas kyang nges pa'i shes pa ma skyes pa ni /
NK122(kho)002:1573: rgyu lhan cig skyes pa'i ma rig pa yin te /
NK122(kho)002:1574: rang ngo rang gis ma shes pa'o //
NK122(kho)002:1575: dper na rgyal po'i phru gu 'bangs su 'khyams pa bzhin no //
