NK122(kho)002:1577: sems nyid ye nas sangs rgyas kyang //
NK122(kho)002:1578: mun pas bsgribs pas de ma shes //
NK122(kho)002:1580: de ltar lhan cig skyes pa'i ma rig pas rang
NK122(kho)002:1581: ngo rang gis ma shes pa de dag sems blun
NK122(kho)002:1585: sdod dam zhe na mi sdod ste /
NK122(kho)002:1586: rkyen nye bar len pa'i ma rig pa'i mthus ye
NK122(kho)002:1587: shes log par rtog ste gzung 'dzin sna tshogs su
NK122(kho)002:1589: dper na rgyal po'i phrug gu de yang rang ngo ma shes pa tsam nas sdod dam zhe na /
NK122(kho)002:1593: lag na khyi gsod kyi ber rga thogs nas /
NK122(kho)002:1594: 'bangs phal pa'i spyod ngan sna tshogs byed do //
NK122(kho)002:1596: phyin ci log la 'chol nyog spyod //
NK122(kho)002:1597: gzung 'dzin don la rab tu chags //
NK122(kho)002:1602: nyon mongs pa dug gsum gyis bskyed pa'i las dge
NK122(kho)002:1603: sdig gnyis kyis mtho ris dang ngan song du 'phen
NK122(kho)002:1604: pa de rkyen bzhi dag gis 'khrul pa'i stobs rgyas
NK122(kho)002:1605: par byed do // de la rkyen bzhi ni /
NK122(kho)002:1606: rgyu'i rkyen kun gzhi la yod pa'i bag chags /
NK122(kho)002:1607: dmigs pa'i rkyen gzugs la sogs pa /
NK122(kho)002:1608: de ma thag pa'i rkyen dbang yul rnam shes tshogs
NK122(kho)002:1609: pa'i skad cig ma bdag po'i rkyen yid kyis shes
NK122(kho)002:1610: pa'o // skabs 'dir rig pa skad cig ma'i thog nas 'khrul lugs /
NK122(kho)002:1611: 'bangs 'khyams stongs thun gyis ngo sprad cing rgyas par bshad pa ni bla ma'i zhal las shes so //
NK122(kho)002:1613: rgyud drug las kyis 'gro ba dang /
NK122(kho)002:1614: ye shes dbyings su 'gro ba gnyis yod pa las /
NK122(kho)002:1615: 'dir rgyud drug las kyis 'gro ba yin te /
NK122(kho)002:1616: rgyud lnga'i lam du dug lnga ste //
NK122(kho)002:1618: drug ni mtho ris kyi gnas gsum dang ngan song gnas gsum mo //
NK122(kho)002:1619: 'khrul pa ni de ma yin la der 'dzin pa'o //
NK122(kho)002:1620: snang ba ni las dang log rtog gi blo ngor 'khrul gzugs rnams shar ba ni med bzhin du /
NK122(kho)002:1621: bden par zhen pa'i mthus rmi lam gyi mthu brtas pa bzhin yin te /
NK122(kho)002:1622: dper na zla grags kyi a pha bzhin yin no //
NK122(kho)002:1625: mnyam pa nyid bde gshegs snying po las 'khrul tshul dang /
NK122(kho)002:1628: e ma thog ma med pa'i dus na /
NK122(kho)002:1629: bde bar gshegs pa'i snying po ste sems can thams
NK122(kho)002:1630: cad sangs rgyas kyi snying po can yin pa las
NK122(kho)002:1631: rang ngo rang gis ma shes te /
NK122(kho)002:1632: rang gi rnam rtog las gsum bsags pa'i stobs kyis
NK122(kho)002:1633: don la 'khor ba med bzhin tu snang ba sprul
NK122(kho)002:1634: pa dang sgyu ma bzhin no //
NK122(kho)002:1635: de yang mtho ris kyi bde ba dang ngan song gi sdug bsngal dang /
NK122(kho)002:1636: yul te gnas mtho dman dang dus snga phyi dang
NK122(kho)002:1637: lus bzang ngan las sogs kyi sgras che chung rnams
NK122(kho)002:1638: la nang du bdag dang phyi rol la bdag gir
NK122(kho)002:1640: 'khor ba don la med kyang 'khrul ba'i stobs kyis phung khams skye mched la snang tshul lo //
NK122(kho)002:1642: gong du gsang ba'i snying po'i lung song nas /
NK122(kho)002:1643: 'dir nam mkha' che'i lung drangs 'dod pas /
NK122(kho)002:1645: srid pa ni khams gsum 'khor ba'i chos ming tsam
NK122(kho)002:1646: las don du med kyang log pa'i stobs tsam gyis
NK122(kho)002:1648: gtan tshigs de bas na ting nge 'dzin mnyam pa nyid kyi don dang bral ba'o //
NK122(kho)002:1649: mnyam pa nyid kyi don dang bral ba de la
NK122(kho)002:1650: skyon ci yod spyod lam du ci shar na 'khrul
NK122(kho)002:1651: gzugs shar ba las mi 'da' bas tha tshig gam
NK122(kho)002:1652: dam tshig gis phyi snod kyi 'jig rten dang /
NK122(kho)002:1653: nang bcud kyi sems can gnyis so //
NK122(kho)002:1654: de las kyang byed pa med par rang bzhin gyis
NK122(kho)002:1655: phung po lnga khams bco brgyad skye mched bcu gnyis
NK122(kho)002:1656: po ci lta ba bzhin du gnas so //
NK122(kho)002:1657: sdug bsngal 'khor tshul dang bcas pa'o //
NK122(kho)002:1659: nang bcud kyi sems can rnams /
NK122(kho)002:1669: bzhi po de dag ni 'khor ba'i 'bras bu'o //
NK122(kho)002:1671: rgyu snga ma la brten cing 'bras bu phyi ma dang 'brel bas rten 'brel ces bya'o //
NK122(kho)002:1672: bcu gnyis zhes bshad pa la /
NK122(kho)002:1673: phyi rten cing 'brel bar 'byung ba bcu gnyis /
NK122(kho)002:1674: nang rten cing 'brel bar 'byung ba bcu gnyis las /
NK122(kho)002:1675: phyi rten cing 'brel ba 'byung ba bcu gnyis ni /
NK122(kho)002:1677: rkyen dang 'brel ba drug dang bcu gnyis so //
NK122(kho)002:1678: nang rten cing 'brel ba bcu gnyis ni /
NK122(kho)002:1679: ma rig pa la sogs pa bcu gnyis kyi tshul dag tu /
NK122(kho)002:1680: phyi rten cing 'brel ba bcu gnyis kyis phyi snod 'khor ba dang /
NK122(kho)002:1681: nang rten cing 'brel pa bcu gnyis kyis nang bcud
NK122(kho)002:1682: kyi sems can gnyis ga lus can rnams la dngos
NK122(kho)002:1683: su 'khor la lus med rnams la bag chags kyi
NK122(kho)002:1684: tshul 'khor ba'o // rten 'brel bcu gnyis kyi don
NK122(kho)002:1685: rgyas par bshad rgyu yod kyang 'og rang sangs rgyas
NK122(kho)002:1686: kyi theg pa'i skabs su 'chad par bya'o //
NK122(kho)002:1687: 'khrul tshul 'di rnams kyi don bshad pa la 'khor
NK122(kho)002:1688: ba'i brgyud rgyu ba'i bde bar gshegs pa'i snying po
NK122(kho)002:1689: yin / lhan cig skyes pa'i rgyu lhan skyes ma rig pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:1692: gsum gnyis bzhi'i rkyen dag gis /
NK122(kho)002:1694: las nyon gnyis dus ni thog ma med pa'i dus nas /
NK122(kho)002:1695: ngo bo ni gzung 'dzin gyi mthu brtas pa yin te /
NK122(kho)002:1696: rdzogs chen klong lnga'i rgyud las /
NK122(kho)002:1697: gzhi ni chos sku dri bcas yin //
NK122(kho)002:1698: dus ni thog ma med nas 'khrul //
NK122(kho)002:1699: rkyen ni gnyis 'dzin shes bya ste //
NK122(kho)002:1700: 'khrul ba rang gi ngo bo ni //
NK122(kho)002:1701: nang du ngar 'dzin phra zhing rlom //
NK122(kho)002:1702: phyir ni gzung 'dzin rtog pa rgyas //
NK122(kho)002:1704: 'di rnams kyi don rgyas par blang ngo //
NK122(kho)002:1707: dbyer med mkhyen pas ma 'dres yongs su gzigs tshul dang /
NK122(kho)002:1709: shes bya'i chos thams cad mkhyen pa'i sangs rgyas kyi
NK122(kho)002:1710: ye shes kyis yul gdul bya gzigs shing mkhyen par
NK122(kho)002:1712: yul yul can gyi rnam par rtog pa mi mnga'
NK122(kho)002:1713: bar yul bral gnyis med kyi ngang du sa ler
NK122(kho)002:1714: mkhyen no // de yang gtan tshig ci'i phyir ni /
NK122(kho)002:1715: ci snyed mkhyen pa'i ye shes ma 'dres par ci
NK122(kho)002:1716: lta ba mkhyen pa'i ye shes kyi ngang du yongs
NK122(kho)002:1717: su rdzogs pas ni mkhyen pa'o //
NK122(kho)002:1719: rnam rtog mi mnga' dus gsum sa ler mkhyen //
NK122(kho)002:1720: de ni nges pa don gyi thams cad mkhyen pa yin //
NK122(kho)002:1721: rdo rje sems dpa' mkhyen pa'i mchog tu gsungs //
NK122(kho)002:1723: ci snyed mkhyen pas ma 'gag par gzigs tshul dang /
NK122(kho)002:1725: gzung 'dzin gnyis kyis log par rtog cing der btags
NK122(kho)002:1726: pa'i kun btag rnam par dag cing mthar phyin pas
NK122(kho)002:1727: ye shes la snang zhing mkhyen /
NK122(kho)002:1728: de gtan tshig ci'i phyir na de bzhin mnyam pa
NK122(kho)002:1729: nyid kyi gnas lugs las mi gzhan pa'i phyir dang
NK122(kho)002:1730: sangs rgyas kyi thugs rje chen po gdul bya'i smon
NK122(kho)002:1731: lam dang 'brel pa yod pas na 'gro ba drug
NK122(kho)002:1732: tu gzigs nas mtho dman ma lus par snang zhing
NK122(kho)002:1734: chos kun ma lus bdag gsal phyir //
NK122(kho)002:1735: ye shes rnam grangs bsam mi khyab //
NK122(kho)002:1737: ci lta bas skye med du gzigs tshul lo //
NK122(kho)002:1739: de ltar du mkhyen yang chos nyid de bzhin nyid las ma g.yos te /
NK122(kho)002:1740: chos kyi dbyings su dbyer med kyang /
NK122(kho)002:1742: bstan bya lhag ma can gyi tshig dang /
NK122(kho)002:1743: skyon can gyi tshig gnyis yod pa las /
NK122(kho)002:1744: 'dir skyon can gyi tshig yin no //
NK122(kho)002:1745: gzung 'dzin dang bral ba'i rig pa de nyid la
NK122(kho)002:1746: ye shes yul bral dus gcig tu 'char yang gzung
NK122(kho)002:1747: 'dzin dang ma bral na mi 'char la de bzhin
NK122(kho)002:1748: nyid las ma g.yos pa dang chos kyi dbyings su
NK122(kho)002:1749: dbyer med pas mi phan no zer ba lta bu'o
NK122(kho)002:1751: mkhyen ldan ye shes snying po yi //
NK122(kho)002:1752: gang yang mi mkhyen rang gsal mkhyen //
NK122(kho)002:1753: mtha' dang dbus su mi dmigs pas //
NK122(kho)002:1755: mkhyen pa'i ye shes kyi skabs 'dir khams gsum gyi
NK122(kho)002:1756: sems can thams cad mkhyen pa'i yul du byas nas
NK122(kho)002:1757: mkhyen nam yul med du mkhyen /
NK122(kho)002:1758: yul du mkhyen na sangs rgyas kyi dgongs pa gzung 'dzin can du 'gro ba'i skyon yod /
NK122(kho)002:1759: yul med du mkhyen na dbu ma ye shes med par smra ba ltar /
NK122(kho)002:1760: sangs rgyas kyi ye shes rgyun chad par 'gyur ba'i skyon yod /
NK122(kho)002:1762: mkhyen zhing gzigs pa dang mi 'thad zhe na /
NK122(kho)002:1764: thugs rje'i yul yod pa'i sgro mi 'dogs te /
NK122(kho)002:1765: ci lta ba mkhyen pa'i ye shes dri ma ka dag mngon du gyur pa'o //
NK122(kho)002:1766: med par skur pa mi 'debs te /
NK122(kho)002:1767: ci snyed mkhyen pa'i ye shes ni /
NK122(kho)002:1768: ci lta mkhyen pa'i ye shes kyi rang rlabs las ma g.yos bzhin du /
NK122(kho)002:1769: shes bya shwa mang gi sul bzhin du mkhyen pa ste /
NK122(kho)002:1770: phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i bsdus pa'i 'khor 'das kyi chos
NK122(kho)002:1771: thams cad gzhon nu ma la pra phab pa bzhin
NK122(kho)002:1772: du rtog med rang gsal du mkhyen to //
NK122(kho)002:1773: gzhan yang yul du byas nas yang mkhyen ste /
NK122(kho)002:1774: yul yul can du ma 'gag la /
NK122(kho)002:1775: mthar ma reg pa'i tshul du mkhyen te /
NK122(kho)002:1776: de yang gnyis su ma 'gag la /
NK122(kho)002:1777: gnyis kyi mthar ma lhung bas skyon las grol lo //
NK122(kho)002:1779: dus gsum mnyam nyid la sngon gyi mtha' mi dmigs /
NK122(kho)002:1781: da lta ba mi dmigs zhes pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:1782: yang dus gsum mi dmigs pa'i tshul gyis dus gsum mi shes pa med pa ni /
NK122(kho)002:1783: byang chub sems dpa' chen po'i theg pa chen po'o //
NK122(kho)002:1784: ces gsungs pa la sogs gsungs so //
NK122(kho)002:1785: thugs rje skyes tshul la gsum ste /
NK122(kho)002:1789: dang po nye bar bstan pa ni /
NK122(kho)002:1791: de ltar gzigs nas thugs rje skye tshul ni /
NK122(kho)002:1792: thugs spros pa thams cad bral bar rje dgos bsgos pa med par kun la khyab pa /
NK122(kho)002:1793: chen po gong na med pa de lta bu'i sangs
NK122(kho)002:1794: rgyas kyi dgongs pa la spro bsdu dang 'byung 'jug
NK122(kho)002:1795: mi mnga' yang gdul bya'i ngo la skye tshul bzhi'i
NK122(kho)002:1796: tshul du / 'byung tshul ni rgyas par bshad cing gsal bar bstan pa ni 'di lta ste /
NK122(kho)002:1799: rtag pa rgyun gyi thugs rje skye tshul chu chen
NK122(kho)002:1800: po'i gzhung lta bu ni dper na chu bo chen
NK122(kho)002:1801: po'i gzhung la dbyar dgun ston dpyid med par rgyun
NK122(kho)002:1803: sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa' chen po rnams
NK122(kho)002:1804: kyi thugs rje skyes pa na rgyun chad med pa'o
NK122(kho)002:1805: // rang bzhin shugs kyis skye tshul nyi ma'i 'od zer lta bu ni /
NK122(kho)002:1806: dper na nyi ma nam mkha'i mthongs su shar ba'i
NK122(kho)002:1807: 'od zer dro 'jam rtsol med du ngang ngam shugs
NK122(kho)002:1809: rgyal ba'i thugs rje la rtsol rtog dang skyo dub med par ngang ngam shugs kyis 'byung ba'o //
NK122(kho)002:1810: dang ces pa ni 'og ma sdud pa'i tshig yin no //
NK122(kho)002:1811: yul dang 'phrad nas thugs rje skye ba'i tshul long sprang gi smre sngags 'don pa bas kyang /
NK122(kho)002:1812: mdze nad gdug can gyis zin pa'i mdze pho la lhag par ster ba lta bu ni /
NK122(kho)002:1813: dper na spyir sdug phong thams cad snying rje'i yul yin kyang /
NK122(kho)002:1814: khyad par du mdze pho rkang chad lag rdum dang
NK122(kho)002:1815: 'phrad na bzod thabs med pa'i snying rje skye ba
NK122(kho)002:1816: bzhin / spyir 'gro drug gi sems can thams cad snying rje'i yul yin kyang /
NK122(kho)002:1817: khyad par du ru t+r+aa thar pa nag po nyon mongs pa dug gsum rags par smin pa la /
NK122(kho)002:1818: thugs rje khyad par can skye ba yin no //
NK122(kho)002:1819: dang zhes pa ni gzhan rnams sdud pa'i tshig yin no //
NK122(kho)002:1820: bskul zhing gsol ba btab pa'i thugs rje skye tshul sdud pa'o //
NK122(kho)002:1821: bskul zhing gsol ba btab pa'i rkyen nam shugs kyis
NK122(kho)002:1822: thugs rje skye tshul sdug phong slong ba la ster
NK122(kho)002:1824: dper na sprang po rnams kyis sme sngags kyi 'o dod bod pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:1825: pha 'bab bsdus nas ster ba bzhin sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa' chen po rnams la yang /
NK122(kho)002:1826: bskul zhing gsol ba gdab na thugs rje khyad par can skyes pa'o //
NK122(kho)002:1829: rtag pa rgyun gyi thugs rje skye ba dang /
NK122(kho)002:1830: rang bzhin shugs kyi thugs rje skye ba dang /
NK122(kho)002:1831: yul dang 'phrad nas thugs rje skye ba dang /
NK122(kho)002:1832: bskul zhing gsol ba gdab nas thugs rje skyes pa'o //
NK122(kho)002:1835: rang bzhin thugs rje'i rgyun dang /
NK122(kho)002:1837: khyab byed sangs rgyas kyi dgongs pa nam mkha' lta bu'i ye shes kyis /
NK122(kho)002:1838: khyab bya 'byung bzhi lta bu'i gdul bya sems can
NK122(kho)002:1839: rnams la khyab tshul nam mkhas 'byung ba bzhi la
NK122(kho)002:1840: khyab bya khyab byed kyis bya rtsol med par bda'
NK122(kho)002:1841: khyab pa / de dpe yin la /
NK122(kho)002:1842: don rang byung gi ye shes kyi gdul bya sems
NK122(kho)002:1843: can thams cad la mtha' ngan pa bri ba med
NK122(kho)002:1844: pa dbus bzang po bkol ba med pa'i tshul du
NK122(kho)002:1845: khyab cing rgyun chad med pa'o //
NK122(kho)002:1846: thugs rje 'di ni rang bzhin dbang btsan ste /
NK122(kho)002:1847: thugs spros pa thams cad dang bral ba rje bsgos
NK122(kho)002:1848: pa med par khams gsum sems can kun la stor
NK122(kho)002:1851: spros bral thugs kyi chos nyid de /
NK122(kho)002:1852: kun la khyab pa'i rje nyid do //
NK122(kho)002:1856: gang la 'char na 'gro drug gdul bya thams cad la /
NK122(kho)002:1857: gang 'char na 'byung chen lnga khams gsum sems can
NK122(kho)002:1858: yongs la nye ring med par snyoms pa'i thugs rje'i
NK122(kho)002:1859: tshul ci ltar na sangs rgyas kyi thugs rje 'byung
NK122(kho)002:1860: ba chen po lnga yongs la snyoms pas gdul bya
NK122(kho)002:1861: 'gro drug sems can thams cad kyi bskyed pa'i rgyu
NK122(kho)002:1862: 'tsho ba'i zas brten pa'i gnas sogs khong du mthun
NK122(kho)002:1863: pa'i grogs la sogs pa'i bya ba byed pa rnams
NK122(kho)002:1864: kyi sgo nas ngan pa spangs bzang po len pa
NK122(kho)002:1866: thugs rje 'di ni gnas lugs kyi don ngo ma
NK122(kho)002:1867: shes pa'i sems can rnams la 'byung ba lngas don
NK122(kho)002:1869: don la theg pa la ma zhugs shing rigs sad pa'i gdul bya rnams yin no //
NK122(kho)002:1870: ye shes thugs rje'i rgyun la gnyis te /
NK122(kho)002:1874: dper na nyi ma lta bu'i thugs rje'i ye shes /
NK122(kho)002:1875: gling bzhir gnas pa'i snang ba kun la mtha' ngan
NK122(kho)002:1876: pa dbri ba dang dbus bzang po bkol ba med
NK122(kho)002:1877: par khyab pa ci lta ba bzhin du yang dag
NK122(kho)002:1878: par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kyi thugs rjes gdul bya
NK122(kho)002:1879: ngan pa spangs ba dang bzang po len pa med
NK122(kho)002:1880: pa'i tshul du thugs rje 'char ba yin te /
NK122(kho)002:1882: nyi ma'i 'od zer gcig btang bas //
NK122(kho)002:1884: de nyid lung gis gsal bar bstan pa'o //
NK122(kho)002:1886: des gzhung don song nas kun 'dus rig pa'i mdo las lung drangs 'dod pas yang ces bya'o //
NK122(kho)002:1887: sku dang ye shes dbyer med pa'i phyir sku'i mchog bcos bslad thams cad dang bral bas na /
NK122(kho)002:1888: rang bzhin sku dang ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor ni
NK122(kho)002:1889: zla ba nya rgyas pa lta bur yul yul can
NK122(kho)002:1890: dang gzung 'dzin gyi spros pa mi mnga' yang /
NK122(kho)002:1891: thugs rje nyi shar bzhin du gdul bya nye ring med par snyoms par mdzad pa'o //
NK122(kho)002:1892: zhes kun 'dus rig pa'i mdo las de ltar gsungs pa'i phyir /
NK122(kho)002:1893: lung de dag gis gzhung 'dir tshur bgrod cing drangs par gyis dang go zhing rtogs par yang sla /
NK122(kho)002:1895: ye shes thugs rje'i rgyud 'di ni thams cad mkhyen
NK122(kho)002:1896: pa'i dgongs pa ye shes la rgyun chad med pa'i
NK122(kho)002:1897: cha la bya'o // sprul pa thugs rje'i rgyun la gnyis te /
NK122(kho)002:1898: sprul pa thugs rje'i rgyun dngos dang /
NK122(kho)002:1899: ye shes thugs rje'i rgyun du gzigs tshul lo //
NK122(kho)002:1904: gong du ye shes thugs rje'i rgyun /
NK122(kho)002:1905: nang dgongs pa'i cha gtsor ston pa de song nas //
NK122(kho)002:1906: de'i phyi rol na de nyid sprul pa'i skur dag
NK122(kho)002:1907: ma dag gi khams su thugs rje'i 'char tshul bshad
NK122(kho)002:1908: pas na / yang na ces bya'o //
NK122(kho)002:1909: 'khor ba ma stong gi bar du sprul pa'i sku
NK122(kho)002:1910: rtag pa rgyun du thugs rje 'byung ba ni 'di
NK122(kho)002:1911: lta ste / gdul bya'i sems can gyi khams rnams ma lus par /
NK122(kho)002:1912: dag dang ces pa dag la ma grags pa 'og
NK122(kho)002:1913: min la rnam par snang mdzad la sogs pa'i zhing
NK122(kho)002:1914: khams lnga la bzhugs pa'i longs sku phal pa lnga
NK122(kho)002:1915: ni sprul sku mtshan nyid pa longs sku btags pa
NK122(kho)002:1916: dang / sum cu rtsa gsum du brgya byin lha'i bla mar grags pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:1917: dag la grags pa zhing khams dang mdo rgyud rnams
NK122(kho)002:1918: su grags pa'i sprul sku sh+aakya thub pa la sogs
NK122(kho)002:1920: ma dag la grags pa zhing khams mdo rgyud rnams su grags pa'i thub pa lnga po dang /
NK122(kho)002:1921: ma dag la ma grags pa stag dang ri bong /
NK122(kho)002:1922: gru dang gzing la sogs pa'o //
NK122(kho)002:1923: sprul pa'i sku ni 'khor lo bskor ba'i tshul ltar rgyun mi chad /
NK122(kho)002:1924: yang na gdul bya las dang smon lam dag pa
NK122(kho)002:1925: rnams la dag pa grag pa zhing khams mdo rgyud
NK122(kho)002:1926: rnams su grags pa'i sprul pa'i sku sh+aakya thub pa
NK122(kho)002:1927: la sogs pa'i sangs rgyas stong la sogs pa rnams
NK122(kho)002:1930: gang zhig gdul bya dag pa yi //
NK122(kho)002:1931: chu yi snod ni thams cad la //
NK122(kho)002:1932: bde gshegs nyi ma'i gzugs brnyan ni //
NK122(kho)002:1933: dpag tu med pa gcig car 'char //
NK122(kho)002:1935: gdul bya las dang smon lam ma dag pa rnams la /
NK122(kho)002:1936: sangs rgyas sprul pa'i sku dngos su mi snang ste /
NK122(kho)002:1937: ma dag pa la grags pa'i thub pa lnga po
NK122(kho)002:1938: dang stag dang ri bong gru dang gzings la sogs
NK122(kho)002:1941: ji ltar chu'i snod chags na //
NK122(kho)002:1942: zla ba'i gzugs brnyan mi snang ngo //
NK122(kho)002:1943: de bzhin sems can ngan pa la //
NK122(kho)002:1944: sangs rgyas gzugs kyang mi snang ngo //
NK122(kho)002:1947: lha yi rgyal pos char phab kyang //
NK122(kho)002:1948: sa bon ma rung mi 'khrungs ltar //
NK122(kho)002:1949: sangs rgyas rnams ni byon gyur kyang //
NK122(kho)002:1950: skal pa ngan pas bzang mi myong //
NK122(kho)002:1952: 'o na 'gro don ye mi 'byung ba yin nam zer na /
NK122(kho)002:1954: ci srid 'khor ba ma stong gi bar du /
NK122(kho)002:1955: ston pa la sogs sangs rgyas kyi phrin las 'dug pa yin te /
NK122(kho)002:1957: srid pa ci srid gnas kyi bar //
NK122(kho)002:1958: ston pa la sogs mdzad pa 'jug /
NK122(kho)002:1960: gzhan yang thugs rje'i phrin las kyi skabs 'dir /
NK122(kho)002:1961: thugs rje phrin las rgya che ba /
NK122(kho)002:1964: lhun gyis grub pa bzhi'i sgo nas shes bya'i gting mtha' rig par bya'o //
NK122(kho)002:1965: lung gis gsal bar bstan pa'o //
NK122(kho)002:1967: dgongs pa 'dus pa'i lung las kyang ni 'di skad gsungs /
NK122(kho)002:1968: sngar sprul pa ni ma byung ma myongs la da yang rgyun du 'byung ba'o //
NK122(kho)002:1970: don gyi go rim bsdeb bya ba yin pas /
NK122(kho)002:1972: de bzhin gshegs pa rnams ni gnas lugs de bzhin nyid las ma g.yos par /
NK122(kho)002:1973: sems can gyi khams mtha' thug pa med pa rnams
NK122(kho)002:1974: su 'du shes mi mkhyen pa gang yang med do
NK122(kho)002:1975: // de bzhin gshegs pa rnams ni gnas de bzhin nyid las ma g.yos par /
NK122(kho)002:1976: sems can gyi khams mtha' thug pa med pa rnams su gzugs mi gzigs pa gang yang med do //
NK122(kho)002:1977: sgra mi gsan pa dang spyod pa mi 'grel pa ni gang yang med do //
NK122(kho)002:1981: kun bzang gis de skad gsungs pa kun mkhyen yang
NK122(kho)002:1982: dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kyis yul gdul byar
NK122(kho)002:1983: gyur pa thams cad kun mi mkhyen pa gang yang
NK122(kho)002:1984: med de / de gtan tshig ci'i phyir mkhyen na
NK122(kho)002:1985: rang bzhin mnyam nyid kyi gnas lugs la 'khor 'das
NK122(kho)002:1986: dbye ba med pa'i phyir dang /
NK122(kho)002:1987: gzung 'dzin gyi zhen pa gnyis dag pa'i phyir dang /
NK122(kho)002:1988: sangs rgyas kyi thugs rje dang gdul bya'i smon lam gyi 'brel ba yod pa'i phyir /
NK122(kho)002:1989: yul yul can gyi zhen pa mi mnga' bar yul
NK122(kho)002:1990: bral gnyis med kyi ngang du sa ler mkhyen no
NK122(kho)002:1991: // rang bzhin shugs kyis skye ba la gnyis te /
NK122(kho)002:1995: skye tshul gnyis pa bya stsol med par rang bzhin
NK122(kho)002:1996: shugs kyis skye ba nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor ltar bshad
NK122(kho)002:2001: rang bzhin shugs kyis skye ba'i rgyu mtshan dang /
NK122(kho)002:2003: 'das ma 'ongs da lta dus gsum gyi bde bar gshegs pa thams cad ni /
NK122(kho)002:2004: dper na nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor thams cad la mun
NK122(kho)002:2005: pa ka nas dag pa ltar gzung 'dzin gyi zhen
NK122(kho)002:2006: pa gnyis kyi mun pa dngas pas thams cad mkhyen
NK122(kho)002:2007: rung ba yin / gdul bya 'gro drug gi sems
NK122(kho)002:2008: can rnams ni mun pa ste las dang nyon mongs
NK122(kho)002:2012: gnyid sad pa yi skyes bu'i drung /
NK122(kho)002:2013: gnyid kyis non pa ci lta bzhin /
NK122(kho)002:2015: dper na skyes bu mngon shes can gyi drung na
NK122(kho)002:2016: skyes bu gzhan zhig gnyid du song ba'i rmi lam
NK122(kho)002:2017: du / rnag mdze rab tu 'bar bas /
NK122(kho)002:2018: lus sems sdug bsngal bar gyur pa las /
NK122(kho)002:2019: skyes bu mngon shes can de'i thugs yul na /
NK122(kho)002:2020: gnyid du song ba'i skyes bu de la /
NK122(kho)002:2021: mdze ma byung ba yang mkhyen /
NK122(kho)002:2022: mdze ma byung ba bzhin du kho la mdze nad byung ba'i snang bas nyam thag par yang mkhyen /
NK122(kho)002:2023: de las grol bar byed pa'i thabs gnyid sad par byed pa yang mkhyen pa bzhin no //
NK122(kho)002:2024: zhes rje btsun gong ma rnams kyis gsungs so //
NK122(kho)002:2025: tshul 'di dag ma go ba kha gcig gis sangs rgyas kyi ye shes dang /
NK122(kho)002:2026: sems can gyi 'khrul rtog gnyis 'dres zer ro //
NK122(kho)002:2027: 'o na sangs rgyas pa'i dus su nyan thos kyi dgra bcom pa lta bu 'gog par thal /
NK122(kho)002:2028: rnam pa thams cad mkhyen pa'i ye shes zer mi rung ngo //
NK122(kho)002:2030: dam pa rnams kyi thugs rje yis //
NK122(kho)002:2031: mi gzigs mi mkhyen gang yang med //
NK122(kho)002:2033: yang dag pa'i go ba blang bar bya'o //
NK122(kho)002:2034: yul dang 'phrad nas thugs rje skye ba la gsum ste /
NK122(kho)002:2038: dpe'i sgo nas zhabs bsdu ba'o //
NK122(kho)002:2040: gdul byed kyi sangs rgyas rnams yul gdul bya sems can rnams dang /
NK122(kho)002:2041: 'phrad nas thugs rje skye ba la /
NK122(kho)002:2042: spyi dang bye brag mang yang gzhung 'dir phyogs gcig nye bar mtshon pa ni 'di lta ste /
NK122(kho)002:2045: sngon byung gol gzhi lo rgyus dang bcas pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:2047: 'dir bshad gzhi gcig brgyab na go bde ba yin /
NK122(kho)002:2048: log ces pa bshad pa'i gzhir drangs de'i khyad par gyi chos la bzhi /
NK122(kho)002:2049: gang log na ru tra thar pa nag po sogs kyi sgras 'khor rnams bsdu ba'o //
NK122(kho)002:2051: rdo rje theg pa la brten nas log ste /
NK122(kho)002:2053: gsang sngags rdo rje theg pa ma h+aa yo ga'i sbyor sgrol gyi don las log /
NK122(kho)002:2056: sngon bskal pa'i ming ni kun bkod /
NK122(kho)002:2057: sangs rgyas mngon byung gi rgyal po'i bstan pa'i dus /
NK122(kho)002:2058: tshul ci ltar du log na /
NK122(kho)002:2059: khyad par las kyi sbyongs pa'i sa ces gsang sngags
NK122(kho)002:2060: sgra ci bzhin par spyad pas las ngan pa sna
NK122(kho)002:2062: de yang sngon bskal pa dpag tu med pa'i sngon rol du /
NK122(kho)002:2063: bskal pa'i ming ni kun bkod /
NK122(kho)002:2064: sangs rgyas mngon phyung rgyal po'i bstan pa'i dus su /
NK122(kho)002:2065: sde snod gsum dang rgyud sde bzhi yi chos dar
NK122(kho)002:2066: zhing yod pa de'i dus su khyim bdag ko'u 'di
NK122(kho)002:2067: na ya zhes bya ba gcig yod do //
NK122(kho)002:2068: de'i bu thar pa nag po zhes bya ba gcig yod de /
NK122(kho)002:2070: dge slong thub dka' gzhon nu zhes bya ba gcig yod pa /
NK122(kho)002:2071: thugs 'jam zhing gsung drang por smra ba /
NK122(kho)002:2072: mtshan nyid gsum dang rgyud sde bzhi'i chos la mkhas shing /
NK122(kho)002:2073: sems can rang rang gi las dang mthun pa'i lam
NK122(kho)002:2074: ston pa la mkhas pa gcig yod pa la thar
NK122(kho)002:2075: pa dad nas / dan phag g.yog du khrid nas song ba la /
NK122(kho)002:2077: dan phag dge bsnyen byas nas 'dul ba gnang bkag gi chos bstan pa la /
NK122(kho)002:2078: kho khyim bdag gi rigs yin pas bsrung ma thub /
NK122(kho)002:2079: dge slong dag sems can rang rang gi spyod pa
NK122(kho)002:2080: dang mthun pa'i lam ston pa la mkhas pa yin
NK122(kho)002:2083: de yang srid gsungs pa las /
NK122(kho)002:2084: 'o na nga rang gi spyod pa mthun pa'i chos gcig ston par zhu /
NK122(kho)002:2087: ci bzhin pa de ma bcos na //
NK122(kho)002:2088: dngos po bzhi la gnas spyad kyang //
NK122(kho)002:2089: nam mkha' la ni sprin bzhin du //
NK122(kho)002:2092: thar pas gsang sngags gnyis med kyi don ni ma rtogs /
NK122(kho)002:2093: dngos rang rgyud pa'i dngos po bzhi la spyad par byas /
NK122(kho)002:2095: gsang sngags gnyis med kyi don rtogs cing /
NK122(kho)002:2096: dngos po bzhi la ma spyod pas /
NK122(kho)002:2098: slob dpon la zhus pa las slob dpon ni thugs drang por gnas cing /
NK122(kho)002:2099: ngo ru ngo dga' med par /
NK122(kho)002:2100: de ni dan phag ltar ro //
NK122(kho)002:2102: thar pa ma dad nas kho 'khrugs shing dpon slob
NK122(kho)002:2103: gnyis ka yul khams 'di nas bud ces zer nas
NK122(kho)002:2104: / skye ba mang por mi 'phrad pa'i smon lam btab /
NK122(kho)002:2105: de'i rjes la kho rang gi dngos po bzhi la gnas spyad nas /
NK122(kho)002:2108: rdzun dang tshig rtsub thams cad smras /
NK122(kho)002:2109: kho rang gis gang sod thams cad bsad /
NK122(kho)002:2110: rang gis ma sod pa yang bya gcan la sogs gsos nas bsad de /
NK122(kho)002:2111: las ngan pa khyad par can la sbyangs pa'i tshul
NK122(kho)002:2112: gyis log /'bras bu rang gzhan la gnod pa dang
NK122(kho)002:2114: gnod ces pa bshad pa'i gzhir drangs /
NK122(kho)002:2115: de'i khyad par gyi chos la bzhi gang gis gnod
NK122(kho)002:2116: na gol sa rnams su song bas ru tra thar
NK122(kho)002:2117: pa nag po 'khor dang bcas pas gnod pa la
NK122(kho)002:2118: dag ces bya'o // gang la gnod na /
NK122(kho)002:2119: bdag gzhan kun la gnod pa la zhes pas bdag
NK122(kho)002:2120: ngan song gsum dang 'khor ba'i kha brgyud gzhan sdug
NK122(kho)002:2121: bsngal gyi rgya mtsho chen po la bskyur ba'o //
NK122(kho)002:2122: dus nam gnod na dge slong thub dka' gzhon nu la bsten pa log pa'i rjes thog nas /
NK122(kho)002:2123: tshul ci ltar du gnod na /
NK122(kho)002:2125: dug sbrul gcan gzan gyi rigs rnams su skye ba lnga brgyar skyes zhing /
NK122(kho)002:2126: byed pa rgyu mthun gyis thog mar rang gis gzhan gsod /
NK122(kho)002:2127: myong ba rgyu mthun gyis mthar gzhan gyis rang gsod pa'i sdug bsngal myong zhing /
NK122(kho)002:2128: de nas dmyal bar bskal pa chen po stong phrag bcu gnyis su skyes nas /
NK122(kho)002:2129: tsha grang gi sdug bsngal myong /
NK122(kho)002:2130: de nas yi dwags su bskal pa chen po drug tu skyes nas sdug bsngal myong /
NK122(kho)002:2131: de nas dud 'gror bskal pa chen po gsum du skyes nas sdug bsngal myong /
NK122(kho)002:2132: de nas srin po gnya' can ces bya ba'i srul
NK122(kho)002:2133: po rtog 'dod can ces bya bar skye ba blangs
NK122(kho)002:2134: / skye ba de'i phyi ma la /
NK122(kho)002:2135: srin yul lang ka pu rir /
NK122(kho)002:2136: srin mo smad 'tshong ma'i bur skyes te /
NK122(kho)002:2138: zhag gsum nas kho'i ma shi nas mtshan ngan par
NK122(kho)002:2139: yongs su grags nas kho rang gi ma'i ro dang
NK122(kho)002:2140: lhan gcig du / dug shing nal byi zhes bya
NK122(kho)002:2141: ba'i rtsa ba na dur phag gti mug gi tshang
NK122(kho)002:2143: dug sbrul zhe sdang gi tshangs bcas pa /
NK122(kho)002:2144: mkha' la 'dod chags kyi dug bya lding ba'i rtsar bskyal ba'o //
NK122(kho)002:2145: der dang po ma'i nu ma nus pas 'atsho'o //
NK122(kho)002:2146: de nas chu ser dang khrag gis 'tshos /
NK122(kho)002:2149: der ro bskyel mi dang bcas pa zos /
NK122(kho)002:2150: de nas gzhan zhag bcur gsos pa pas /
NK122(kho)002:2151: kho zhag gcig gi skyed che bar song nas /
NK122(kho)002:2152: sngon gsang sngags las gol ba dang /
NK122(kho)002:2153: sha chen zos pa'i stobs kyis lus sngo skya thal ba'i mdog can du gyur /
NK122(kho)002:2154: bya sha zan gyi gshog pa /
NK122(kho)002:2155: gcan khrag 'thung gi mchu sder skyes te /
NK122(kho)002:2156: dur khrod de'i ma mo dang /
NK122(kho)002:2158: gzhan yang rgya gar so sa gling la sogs pa
NK122(kho)002:2159: dur khrod chen po'i gnas brgyad kyi ma mo dang
NK122(kho)002:2161: de nas 'dzam bu'i gling gi dreg byed rnams dang /
NK122(kho)002:2162: de nas srin yul pa rnams dang /
NK122(kho)002:2163: de nas rgyal po ma tang ka ru na bsgral nas ro 'dzam bu'i gling du 'phang ba la /
NK122(kho)002:2164: dur khrod chen po'i gnas brgyad du gyur /
NK122(kho)002:2165: de nas 'bras bu che ba'i lha man chad dbang du bsdus nas /
NK122(kho)002:2166: srin yul du pho brang bcas so //
NK122(kho)002:2167: dur khrod kyi gzhal yas khang brtsig /
NK122(kho)002:2168: da ru kad kyi mda' yab dang /
NK122(kho)002:2169: zhing lpags kyi gdug rgyal mtshan bla re rnams byas so //
NK122(kho)002:2171: skye mched mu bzhi ma gtogs pa /
NK122(kho)002:2172: srid gsum log pa'i lam du bkod de /
NK122(kho)002:2174: thams cad mkhyen pas gzigs te btul nas zag med la bkod pa'o //
NK122(kho)002:2176: kun mkhyen rgyal ba rgya mtsho rnams kyi thugs rjes
NK122(kho)002:2177: ru tra thar pa nag po 'dul ba'i dus la
NK122(kho)002:2178: bab par yongs su gzigs nas deng sang gi sh+aakya
NK122(kho)002:2179: thub pa 'dis sems bskyed sa'i sh+aakya thub pa la
NK122(kho)002:2180: zhi bas thul cig gsungs nas /
NK122(kho)002:2181: lung bstan pas btul kyang ma thul ste /
NK122(kho)002:2182: bu chung khyod kyis bdag thul ba ma yin /
NK122(kho)002:2183: sngon nga gnod byin gyi sde dpon drag po zhes
NK122(kho)002:2184: bya bar gyur pa na khyod kho na nyid lta
NK122(kho)002:2186: nga'i bstan pa la zhugs shig zer ba las kyang ma nyan na /
NK122(kho)002:2187: da khyod kyi dbang du bdag ga la 'gyur /
NK122(kho)002:2188: go zu ser mo de gzor la /
NK122(kho)002:2189: rang gi dka' thub la legs par mnos shig /
NK122(kho)002:2191: de nas de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyis sangs
NK122(kho)002:2192: rgyas mang po'i gdung dang sde'i sprul pa sangs rgyas
NK122(kho)002:2193: spyan ras gzigs dbang phyug khros pa'i rta mgrin la
NK122(kho)002:2194: lung bstan nas thul gcig gsungs nas /
NK122(kho)002:2195: rta mgrin gyis hu lu hu lu h'u ces /
NK122(kho)002:2197: rtser rtser rta skad drag po'i sgra phyung ba las /
NK122(kho)002:2198: kho yang zhum zhing bag 'khum par gyur te /
NK122(kho)002:2200: ru tra ma trang ma ru tra /
NK122(kho)002:2201: zhes bsgrags nas nga rgyal phyung ste /
NK122(kho)002:2203: sngon yang khyod lta bus bdag ma non pas /
NK122(kho)002:2204: khyod kyis bdag ci la thul /
NK122(kho)002:2205: nyid kyi gnas gang yin par bde bar mnos shig /
NK122(kho)002:2207: de nas rta mgrin kho'i khong pa'i nang du zhugs nas dbu kho'i gtsug du phyung /
NK122(kho)002:2209: ngag du h'u h'u zhes brjod pas /
NK122(kho)002:2210: khos ma bzod pas 'o dod kyi sgras 'bod pa ni /
NK122(kho)002:2214: rta mgrin kho'i spyi gtsug du phyung ste nam mkha' la rta'i bshug glu len nas /
NK122(kho)002:2215: kho la lung bstan pa ni /
NK122(kho)002:2217: phrin las bzhi las drag pos 'dul bar 'gyur ro gsungs /
NK122(kho)002:2218: de nas de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyis sngon
NK122(kho)002:2219: yod sdig can 'dis bdag gzhan kun la gnod par
NK122(kho)002:2220: byas pas da yang ma bsgral na bdag gzhan kun
NK122(kho)002:2222: bka'i chad pa'i mdo 'di gsungs so //
NK122(kho)002:2223: shin tu gdug cing gtum pa la /
NK122(kho)002:2224: zhi bas phan par mi 'gyur te //
NK122(kho)002:2225: shes rab thabs kyi ngo bo las //
NK122(kho)002:2226: khro bor de bzhin gshegs kun mdzad //
NK122(kho)002:2227: khro bo'i tshul can khros pas kyang //
NK122(kho)002:2228: 'jig rten gsum dag bsgral nus na //
NK122(kho)002:2229: sangs rgyas thugs rje khros pa yis //
NK122(kho)002:2230: khams gsum ma lus smos ci dgos //
NK122(kho)002:2231: gdul dka' ma lus 'dul ba dang //
NK122(kho)002:2232: dam tshig la sdang rnam spyod phyir //
NK122(kho)002:2233: 'bar ba chen po'i gar dgu las //
NK122(kho)002:2234: dur khrod gar gyi phyag rgyar mdzod //
NK122(kho)002:2235: zhes drag pos gdul ba thag bcad do //
NK122(kho)002:2236: sngon drang srong thub dka' gzhon nu gnas su gyur pa ni dpal cher por gyur to //
NK122(kho)002:2237: g.yog po dan phag gnas gyur pa rdo rje srin po yin /
NK122(kho)002:2238: thar pa nag po ni las ngan gyis ru tra ra smin pa'o //
NK122(kho)002:2239: de yang dpal chen pos ru tra lta bu'i rgyan
NK122(kho)002:2240: cha lugs sku gzi brjid dang ldan pa gcig tu
NK122(kho)002:2241: sprul nas ru tra'i thod mkhar brtsigs pa'i nang nas
NK122(kho)002:2242: chung ma nye gnas kro ti shwa ri ma dang
NK122(kho)002:2243: sbyor te / rdo rje srin po h'u gcig tu sprul nas kho btul ba'o //
NK122(kho)002:2244: de yang dpal chen po nyid thugs chos sku zhi ba'i dbyings las ma g.yos par /
NK122(kho)002:2245: sku 'bar ba chen po'i cha lugs kyis /
NK122(kho)002:2247: khro bo dbu gsum phyag drug pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:2248: dbu dgu phyag bco brgyad pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:2249: dbu nyi shu rtsa gcig phyag bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis dang /
NK122(kho)002:2250: dbu dgu brgya phyag stong brgyad brgya la sogs par snang nas ru tra 'khor bcas te /
NK122(kho)002:2251: dbang mo nyi shu rtsa brgyad dang bcas pas pho
NK122(kho)002:2252: thams cad bsgral ba'i tshul du dug gsum spangs pa
NK122(kho)002:2253: med par gnas su sbyangs nas sems rnam par shes
NK122(kho)002:2254: pa mthong ba'i lam la sogs pa zag pa med
NK122(kho)002:2256: mo thams cad sbyor ba'i tshul gyis 'dod chags spangs
NK122(kho)002:2257: pa med par zag pa med pa'i mthong lam la
NK122(kho)002:2258: sbyor ba'o // de yang dpal chen pos ru tra
NK122(kho)002:2259: bsgral nas mi gtsang ba'i 'dam rdzabs su btsud pa'i
NK122(kho)002:2260: sbyor ba'o // dus su / sme sngags 'di blang ngo //
NK122(kho)002:2264: dpa' bo lha rje thugs rje chung //
NK122(kho)002:2265: da yang ci mdzad myur du mdzad //
NK122(kho)002:2266: myur du bsgral na yun du bde //
NK122(kho)002:2267: ma sring bu mo chung ma rnams //
NK122(kho)002:2268: 'bangs su mchi na bdag gi lus 'bul lo //
NK122(kho)002:2269: dbus su mchi skal mi ldan gyis //
NK122(kho)002:2271: phud la 'tshal skal mi ldan gyis //
NK122(kho)002:2272: lhag ma kha chus bran la rtsol //
NK122(kho)002:2273: ces bran 'khor du khas blangs nas /
NK122(kho)002:2274: sngar gyi las ngan dran nas 'di lta ste //
NK122(kho)002:2275: thugs rje chen po bcom ldan rdo rje sems //
NK122(kho)002:2276: dri med dung mdog mchog tu gzugs bzang ba //
NK122(kho)002:2277: rnam dag 'od gsal nyi zla 'bum brdal bzhin //
NK122(kho)002:2278: dpa' bo 'od zer stong khams lham me ba //
NK122(kho)002:2279: khams gsum 'gro ba kun gyi gnyen gcig po //
NK122(kho)002:2280: byams mgon thugs rje'i lha khyod dgongs su gsol //
NK122(kho)002:2281: bdag ni thog ma med pa'i dus mtha' nas //
NK122(kho)002:2282: lam log lam stor srid pa'i 'khor bar 'khyams //
NK122(kho)002:2283: sngon tshe las ngan sdig pa sbyang pas gnong //
NK122(kho)002:2284: 'khor ba'i sdug bsngal rgya mtshor bying gyur de //
NK122(kho)002:2285: zhe sdang 'bar ba'i mes ni rang rgyud bsregs //
NK122(kho)002:2286: gti mug mun ltar 'thibs pas shes rab rmongs //
NK122(kho)002:2287: 'dod chags rgya mtsho'i 'dam du rnam shes bying //
NK122(kho)002:2288: nga rgyal drag po'i ri bos ngan 'gror mnan //
NK122(kho)002:2289: 'phrag dog rlung dmar 'tshubs mas 'khor bar g.yeng //
NK122(kho)002:2290: bdag tu lta ba'i mdud pa dam pos bcing /
NK122(kho)002:2291: sdug bsngal mi zad drag po char du 'bab //
NK122(kho)002:2292: 'di 'dra'i sdug bsngal shin tu mi bzod na //
NK122(kho)002:2293: byams mgon thugs rje can gyis bzod lags sam //
NK122(kho)002:2294: bdag ni blun rmongs las ngan sdig po che //
NK122(kho)002:2295: las kyi dbang gis 'dod khams ru trar skyes //
NK122(kho)002:2296: skyes pas 'gyod do las la yi re chad //
NK122(kho)002:2297: yid chad 'gyod kyang las dbang bcos su med //
NK122(kho)002:2298: las kyi shugs ni chu bo'i gzhung dang 'dra //
NK122(kho)002:2299: las dbang chu klung 'phral du ga la bzlog /
NK122(kho)002:2300: rnam smin thams cad rang gi las la byung //
NK122(kho)002:2301: las kyis mnar ba'i skye bo bdag 'dra ba //
NK122(kho)002:2302: bskal pa grangs med skye ba ci snyed du //
NK122(kho)002:2303: gdos bcas lus blang grangs med zhig gyur te //
NK122(kho)002:2304: sha rus bsags na 'jig rten gtos dang mnyam //
NK122(kho)002:2305: rnag khrag bsags na rgya mtsho chen po tsam //
NK122(kho)002:2306: las 'phro bsags na bsam 'das brjod mi long //
NK122(kho)002:2307: khams gsum bgrang zhing skye shi'i kha brgyud cing //
NK122(kho)002:2308: byas pa'i las rnams don med chud re zos //
NK122(kho)002:2309: zhes pa la sogs pa gdung ba du ma bton no //
NK122(kho)002:2310: dpal chen pos de'i len du //
NK122(kho)002:2311: sdig can log pa'i stobs ldan khyod //
NK122(kho)002:2312: thog ma med pa'i dus mtha' nas //
NK122(kho)002:2314: sus kyang ma byas rtsa ba rang las byung //
NK122(kho)002:2315: bskal pa grangs med de snyed du //
NK122(kho)002:2316: skye ba mang po'i lus blangs nas //
NK122(kho)002:2317: gzugs phung grangs med zhig 'gyur cing //
NK122(kho)002:2318: sha rus stong gsum 'jig rten tsam //
NK122(kho)002:2319: rnag khrag rgya mtshor 'khyil gyur kyang //
NK122(kho)002:2320: don med par ni chud zos pa //
NK122(kho)002:2321: sus kyang ma byas rang gi las //
NK122(kho)002:2322: de tsam cha gcig don spyod na //
NK122(kho)002:2323: da tsam don gyis sangs rgyas zin //
NK122(kho)002:2324: rang gis mnar ba'i ru tra khyod //
NK122(kho)002:2325: dang po bka' bgo log par byas //
NK122(kho)002:2326: de nas mngon pa'i ri bo brtsegs //
NK122(kho)002:2327: de nas yid bzhin nor bu bsreg /
NK122(kho)002:2328: tha mar dngos po bzhi spyad pas //
NK122(kho)002:2329: rnal 'byor theg pa chen po'i don //
NK122(kho)002:2330: ma rtogs pa dang log par rtog /
NK122(kho)002:2331: phyogs rtogs yang dag nyid ma rtogs //
NK122(kho)002:2332: ci bzhin ma sbyang 'phra men gyis //
NK122(kho)002:2333: srid pa log pa'i 'bras bur smin //
NK122(kho)002:2334: e ma'o las ngan snying re rje //
NK122(kho)002:2335: ces rgyud yongs su sbyang ba'i chos du ma bshad do //
NK122(kho)002:2336: de ni bar skabs la mtshar chos su bris pa'o //
NK122(kho)002:2337: ru tra de nyid phung po bsgral zhing /
NK122(kho)002:2338: sems zag med sangs rgyas kyi sa la bkod nas /
NK122(kho)002:2339: gsang mtshan yang rdo rje ro lang tshogs kyi bdag por ming btags pa'o //
NK122(kho)002:2340: dbang bskur dam la bzhag cing /
NK122(kho)002:2341: sangs rgyas bstan pa bsrung bar khas blangs pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:2342: khyad par du gsang sngags rdo rje theg pa'i rgyud kyi bsrungs mar mnga' gsol nas /
NK122(kho)002:2343: da lta mgon po legs ldan du grags pa'o //
NK122(kho)002:2344: sngags 'chang rnams kyi bsrung mar bskos pa yin no //
NK122(kho)002:2345: ma 'ongs pa'i dus na zhing khams thal bas kheb pa zhes bya bar /
NK122(kho)002:2346: de bzhin gshegs pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs
NK122(kho)002:2347: rgyas thal ba'i dbang po'i dbyangs zhes bya bar dpal
NK122(kho)002:2349: ru tra'i rnam thar rgyas par bshad 'dod na /
NK122(kho)002:2350: mdo dgongs pa 'dus pa'i le'u nyi shu pa ma
NK122(kho)002:2351: dag skye rgyud bstan pa'i le'u nas bzung ste le'u
NK122(kho)002:2352: sum cu so gcig gi bar le'u bcu gcig gis
NK122(kho)002:2353: ston pa yin pas zhib par der gzigs mdzod /
NK122(kho)002:2354: dpe'i sgo nas zhabs bsdu ba'o //
NK122(kho)002:2356: dper na sbyin bdag phyung po yis //
NK122(kho)002:2357: long sprang mthong bar gyur pa'i tshe //
NK122(kho)002:2358: snying rje'i zas kyis tshim byas nas //
NK122(kho)002:2359: bkres pa'i sdug bsngal bsal bzhin no //
NK122(kho)002:2361: 'grel pa mkhas pa'i dbye lugs la /
NK122(kho)002:2362: gang dka' ba thams cad rgyus pa bsed bsed byed dgos pa yin la /
NK122(kho)002:2363: sla ba rnams ni yi ge mang dogs pa'i phyir mi 'grel ba yin no //
NK122(kho)002:2364: bskul zhing gsol ba gdab nas thugs rje skye tshul la gsum ste /
NK122(kho)002:2370: gdul byed yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas la /
NK122(kho)002:2371: yul gdul bya rnams kyis bskul zhing gsol ba btabs
NK122(kho)002:2372: pas na thugs rje skye ba la spyi bye brag
NK122(kho)002:2373: mang yang / gzhung 'dir phyogs gcig nye bar mtshon nas /
NK122(kho)002:2374: rgyas par bshad cing gsal bar bstan pa ni /
NK122(kho)002:2376: rgyas par bshad pa la gnyis /
NK122(kho)002:2377: sngon byung du gsol ba gdab pa'i chos byung tshul /
NK122(kho)002:2378: rjes 'jug gis gsol ba gdab pas gnas skabs mthar thug gi 'bras bu thob tshul lo //
NK122(kho)002:2380: lung gi chos byung tshul dang rgyud kyi chos byung tshul lo //
NK122(kho)002:2383: dam pa'i rigs can lngas rgyal ba rnams la gsol ba gdab pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:2385: ston pa mya ngan 'das rjes nas /
NK122(kho)002:2387: ston pa dbye na bzhi ste /
NK122(kho)002:2388: 'dren pa rang byung gi ston pa ni /
NK122(kho)002:2389: bcom ldan 'das thub pa'i dbang po /
NK122(kho)002:2390: rgyal tshab brgyud kyi ston pa ni mi pham mgon po /
NK122(kho)002:2391: byin rlabs kyis ston pa ni thub pa lnga po /
NK122(kho)002:2392: bsod nams kyis ston pa la gsum ste /
NK122(kho)002:2393: sku'i ston pa de gzugs brnyan gyi lha sku /
NK122(kho)002:2394: gsung gi ston pa de po ti glegs bam /
NK122(kho)002:2395: thugs kyi ston pa gang zag chos kyi mig can man ngag dang ldan pa rnams yin /
NK122(kho)002:2396: 'dir ni 'dren pa rang byung gi ston pa sh+aakya
NK122(kho)002:2397: seng ge mya ngan las 'das khar yul yangs pa
NK122(kho)002:2399: 'khor mang po dang dbyar zla gsum la bzhugs /
NK122(kho)002:2400: ston ra ba'i nya la 'khor gyi nang na mo'u
NK122(kho)002:2401: 'gal gyi bu rdzu 'phrul cher spyod la bka' stsal
NK122(kho)002:2402: pa / rdzu 'phrul chen spyod khyod song la 'jig rten drug gi phyogs bcu na /
NK122(kho)002:2403: nga'i slob ma gang dag 'khod cing ci snyed pa rnams sdus shig /
NK122(kho)002:2404: gdams ngag nges par bzhag par bya ba dag yod do //
NK122(kho)002:2406: rdzu 'phrul can des thams cad bsdus nas 'di skad bsgrags te /
NK122(kho)002:2407: rgyal ba'i zhing gyur rigs drug gang su dag /'di bar nges zhing phyogs pa kun nyon shig /
NK122(kho)002:2408: dug gsum 'joms par 'dod pa kun 'dus shig /
NK122(kho)002:2410: dam pa'i rig can lnga ma gtogs gzhan kun 'dus pa la bcom ldan 'das kyis /
NK122(kho)002:2411: kye grogs po dag shes par gyis shig /
NK122(kho)002:2412: chos thams cad ni mi rtag pa'o //
NK122(kho)002:2413: 'byor pa thams cad ni mthar rgud pa'o //
NK122(kho)002:2414: dngos po thams cad ni nges par 'jig pa'o //
NK122(kho)002:2415: gang zag srog gi dbang po la skye shi yod pa'i phyir /
NK122(kho)002:2416: nga yongs su mya ngan la 'da' bas /
NK122(kho)002:2417: su dag the tshom ma chod pa rnams kyis dri bar gyis shig /
NK122(kho)002:2418: de skad ces gsungs pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:2420: 'dren pa theg pa rnam gsum la //
NK122(kho)002:2421: gang dag rim par bkod lags na //
NK122(kho)002:2422: byang chub gzhan nas mi tshol ba'i //
NK122(kho)002:2423: nges pa'i theg chen yongs ma gsungs //
NK122(kho)002:2425: bcom ldan 'das kyis de'i lan du /
NK122(kho)002:2426: gsang sngags 'byung bar lung bstan pa ni /
NK122(kho)002:2427: mya ngan las 'das pa'i mdo dang /
NK122(kho)002:2428: dgongs pa 'dus pa'i le'u gnyis pa ltar shes par bya'o //
NK122(kho)002:2429: lo brgyad dang bcu tsho gnyis te lo nyi shu rtsa brgyad kyi dus na /
NK122(kho)002:2430: li tsa byi dri ma med par grags pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:2431: sogs kyi sgras bzhi bsdus te gang zhe na /
NK122(kho)002:2434: gnod sbyin skar mda' gdong dang /
NK122(kho)002:2435: srin po blo gros thabs ldan dang /
NK122(kho)002:2436: dam pa'i rigs can rnam pa lnga po de ting nge 'dzin las langs te /
NK122(kho)002:2437: lang ka'i yul gyi grong brdal /
NK122(kho)002:2440: byan lag mchong gi ri ma la ya drag shul
NK122(kho)002:2441: gnam lcags yod pa'i rtse la lhag nas 'dus pa'o
NK122(kho)002:2443: bdag cag dam pa'i rigs can lnga dang gzhan gsang
NK122(kho)002:2444: sngags kyi snod du rung ba kun gyi don gyi
NK122(kho)002:2445: phyir / mgrin gcig tu shin tu nyams thag pa'i
NK122(kho)002:2446: nga ros smre sngags kyi gdung tshig nyi shu rtsa
NK122(kho)002:2447: phyir / gsum gyis / phyogs bcu'i rgyal ba la gsol ba gdab pa 'di lta ste /
NK122(kho)002:2448: dang po e ma'o kyi hud kye ma blong //
NK122(kho)002:2449: ston pa sgron ma'i 'od nub na //
NK122(kho)002:2450: 'jig rten mun pa gang gis sel //
NK122(kho)002:2452: tshad ma'i zhal de mi bzhugs pas //
NK122(kho)002:2453: tshad mas gsungs pa'i bstan pa la //
NK122(kho)002:2456: tshad mar dam bcas gang zag gis //
NK122(kho)002:2457: des ma rnyed pa'i gang zag la //
NK122(kho)002:2458: phan par bya phyir bka' bgros pa //
NK122(kho)002:2459: gtan la pheb par 'gyur zhig gu //
NK122(kho)002:2461: legs nyes 'byed pa'i spyan gzum pas //
NK122(kho)002:2462: bka' nyid khyad du gsod pa yi //
NK122(kho)002:2463: skyon gyis spyi gtsug mthar phyin pa //
NK122(kho)002:2466: log pa'i bstan pa'i sprin 'khrigs pas //
NK122(kho)002:2467: bden pa gnyis kyi nyi zla nub //
NK122(kho)002:2468: 'gro ba gang zhig lam tshol ba //
NK122(kho)002:2472: bdud dang srin po mu stegs dang //
NK122(kho)002:2473: gnod sbyin 'byung po mi ma yin //
NK122(kho)002:2474: ma rung gdug pa sus btul 'gyur //
NK122(kho)002:2476: dri med bstan pa'i bdud rtsi 'di //
NK122(kho)002:2477: nub na shin tu ma rung na //
NK122(kho)002:2478: rtsal dang ldan pa su zhig gis //
NK122(kho)002:2481: bslab pa dam pa rin po che //
NK122(kho)002:2482: dral na shin tu ma rung na //
NK122(kho)002:2483: skyes bu dam pa gang zhig gis //
NK122(kho)002:2486: ston pa mi bzhugs de rjes na //
NK122(kho)002:2487: ston pa'i slob ma ci snyed pa //
NK122(kho)002:2488: 'phags dang gang zag tha dad pa //
NK122(kho)002:2489: lung bstan 'byung ba gang su zhig /
NK122(kho)002:2491: bstan pa nam mkha' 'dra ba la //
NK122(kho)002:2492: mos pas tha dad par bzung nas //
NK122(kho)002:2493: yin dang ma yin cha 'dzin cing //
NK122(kho)002:2496: de nyid nges par rigs gcig la //
NK122(kho)002:2497: lung mi mthun par tha dad spyod //
NK122(kho)002:2498: rigs rnams tha dad rigs rnams su //
NK122(kho)002:2499: bslad cing bcos par mi 'gyur ram //
NK122(kho)002:2501: rin thang med pa'i rin po che //
NK122(kho)002:2502: mi mkhas gang zag tha dad pas //
NK122(kho)002:2503: nyon mongs 'dod pas khrid dbang gis //
NK122(kho)002:2504: dug dang barje bar mi 'gyur ram //
NK122(kho)002:2506: chos kyi rgyal po bstan pa de //
NK122(kho)002:2507: 'di sngon phan chad zhal bzhugs te //
NK122(kho)002:2508: ma rung pa rnams 'chos bgyid na //
NK122(kho)002:2509: gdug pa dad par mi 'gyur ram //
NK122(kho)002:2511: gang der sangs rgyas bstan pa'i yun //
NK122(kho)002:2512: ci srid gcig tu gnas par 'gyur //
NK122(kho)002:2514: gang der sngon byung gang ltar byung //
NK122(kho)002:2517: ston pa'i bstan pa tha ma'i tshe //
NK122(kho)002:2518: nges par bstan pa gyur zhig gu //
NK122(kho)002:2520: bslab pa 'dzin pa'i slob ma rnams //
NK122(kho)002:2521: tha mar ci ltar 'gyur zhig gu //
NK122(kho)002:2524: gang ltar su yi bstan par gshegs //
NK122(kho)002:2525: zhing khams phyogs ni gang na bzhugs //
NK122(kho)002:2526: de nas bstan pa ci zhig sgrogs //
NK122(kho)002:2528: da yang 'jig rten mgon med rnams //
NK122(kho)002:2529: mgon gcig skyabs su gang zhig 'gyur //
NK122(kho)002:2531: 'phrul gyi blo dang gros stor na //
NK122(kho)002:2532: blo dang gros ni gang nas brtsal //
NK122(kho)002:2534: nges pa'i don 'di ma rnyed na //
NK122(kho)002:2535: da yang nges don gang las bzung //
NK122(kho)002:2537: mchod gnas yid brtan mi bzhugs na //
NK122(kho)002:2538: sku gdung ci ltar 'gyur zhig gu //
NK122(kho)002:2540: slad kyi mchod gnas ci la bgyis //
NK122(kho)002:2544: e ma ho kye hud kye ma blong //
NK122(kho)002:2545: ces yongs su gdung ba bton //
NK122(kho)002:2546: de'i de ltar nyi shu rtsa gsum yang dgongs 'dus nang na yod do //
NK122(kho)002:2547: bskul pa gsan nas lcang lo can du 'dus te gsang bdag la bka' bsgo mdzad pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:2549: gsol bas gdab pa'i rjes thog nas /
NK122(kho)002:2550: phyogs bcu'i rgyal ba rgya mtsho rnams kyis dam pa'i rigs can lngas bskul zhing gsol bas gtab pa /
NK122(kho)002:2551: de thugs rjes dgongs nas de dag gis longs spyod
NK122(kho)002:2552: rdzogs pa'i sku dang sprul pa'i sku'i cha lugs su
NK122(kho)002:2553: chos sku gzugs skur bzhengs nas /
NK122(kho)002:2554: gsang bdag gi gnas ri rab kyi byang phyogs su
NK122(kho)002:2555: lcang lo can gyi pho brang yang dag don gyi
NK122(kho)002:2557: lung chen mdo dgongs 'dus la sogs pa rnams kyi
NK122(kho)002:2558: tshig gis bgro ba byas shing bskul ba ni 'di
NK122(kho)002:2559: lta ste / kye ho gsang ba'i bdag po khyod //
NK122(kho)002:2560: sngon gyi go cha yal lam ci //
NK122(kho)002:2561: 'jig rten sdug bsngal mi shes sam //
NK122(kho)002:2562: snying rjes sa la bab nas kyang //
NK122(kho)002:2563: 'jig rten gdung ba bsal bar rigs //
NK122(kho)002:2564: gsang bdag gis zhal gyis bzhes pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:2566: gsang bdag phyag na rdo rje rgyal tshab chen po de yis /
NK122(kho)002:2567: bka' bsgo ba'i rjes thog nas dam pa'i rigs can lnga'i gdung ba bsal bar zhal gyis bzhes pa'o //
NK122(kho)002:2568: tshul ci ltar du bzhes na /
NK122(kho)002:2569: thog ma tha ma med pa nas //
NK122(kho)002:2570: bskul ba'i dus na gang byung ba //
NK122(kho)002:2571: bdag kyang de bzhin cho 'phrul snang //
NK122(kho)002:2573: ma la yar byon nas gsang sngags gsungs pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:2575: gsang bdag phyag na rdo rje ri ma la ya'i
NK122(kho)002:2576: rtse la byon nas dam pa'i rigs can lnga la
NK122(kho)002:2577: chos bshad pa'i dus su 'khor rnams the tshom skyes
NK122(kho)002:2578: te dri ba byas pa ni 'di lta ste /
NK122(kho)002:2579: e ma ho ngo mtshar snying re rje //
NK122(kho)002:2580: skyes bu chen po khyod su zhig /
NK122(kho)002:2581: gang nas byung ste gang ltar byung //
NK122(kho)002:2582: gang la brten nas gang du byon //
NK122(kho)002:2583: don gyi ched ka ci zhig dris //
NK122(kho)002:2585: nga ni cis yang mi bskyod de //
NK122(kho)002:2586: mi 'khrug rdo rje sems dpa' yin //
NK122(kho)002:2587: snying rjes g.yo zhing bskyod pas na //
NK122(kho)002:2588: srid pa gsum gyi gnyen gcig po //
NK122(kho)002:2589: stong pa chen po nga yi yul //
NK122(kho)002:2590: rdo rje'i rigs can nga yi gdung //
NK122(kho)002:2591: pha ni thabs mchog dpag tu med //
NK122(kho)002:2592: ma ni shes rab brjod las 'das //
NK122(kho)002:2593: zhes pa la sogs pa lan du ma gsungs so //
NK122(kho)002:2594: 'di rnams kyi don rgyas par shes 'dod na /
NK122(kho)002:2595: dgongs 'dus le'u lnga pa'i nang du zhib bo //
NK122(kho)002:2596: de nas dus der gsang bdag phyag na rdo rjes
NK122(kho)002:2597: dam pa'i rigs can lnga la gsang sngags rdo rje
NK122(kho)002:2598: theg pa ste / lung a nu yo ga'i chos /
NK122(kho)002:2599: mdo snga ma bdun dang phyi ma bdun char bzhin du phab pa'o //
NK122(kho)002:2600: de la mdo snga ma bdun ni /
NK122(kho)002:2601: chos nyid nam mkha' mdzod kyi mdo dang /
NK122(kho)002:2603: kun 'dus rig pa yang dag gi mdo /
NK122(kho)002:2604: sems lung chen mo rdzogs chen gyi mdo /
NK122(kho)002:2605: rngam pa glog phreng sgyu 'phrul gyi mdo /
NK122(kho)002:2606: khu byug rol pa phur pa'i mdo /
NK122(kho)002:2613: rdo rje ma gol ba'i mdo /
NK122(kho)002:2615: spyi sdom sangs rgyas thams cad kyi dgongs pa 'dus pa'i mdo dang bcu bzhi'o //
NK122(kho)002:2616: gnas tha dad du gdul bya so so'i mos pa bzhin du gsang sngags bshad tshul lo //
NK122(kho)002:2618: de yang gnas ri rab kyi rtse sum cu rtsa gsum na /
NK122(kho)002:2619: ston pa rnam par snang mdzad dang /
NK122(kho)002:2620: phyag na rdo rje'i skur snang nas /
NK122(kho)002:2621: 'khor sum cu rtsa gsum pa'i lha rnams la /
NK122(kho)002:2622: bstan pa yo ga 'bum sde dang /
NK122(kho)002:2623: phyag na rdo rje'i rgyud la sogs pa rnams dus de nyid du bshad do //
NK122(kho)002:2624: de yang yo ga'i rgyud la /
NK122(kho)002:2626: bshad rgyud rdo rje rtse mo /
NK122(kho)002:2627: dpal mchog dum bu bzhi pa /
NK122(kho)002:2628: byin rlabs ston pa ngan song sbyong rgyud /
NK122(kho)002:2629: ngan song sbyong rgyud la dkyil 'khor bcu gnyis yod pa las /
NK122(kho)002:2630: kun rig rtsa ba'i dkyil 'khor ni rnam snang gis gsungs /
NK122(kho)002:2631: dkyil 'khor bcu gcig de phyag na rdo rjes gsungs so //
NK122(kho)002:2632: dang zhes pa ni 'og ma sdud pa'i tshig yin no //
NK122(kho)002:2634: ston pa ma rgyud kyi lha kye'i rdo rje /
NK122(kho)002:2635: bde mchog la sogs pa rnams kyi skur snang nas /
NK122(kho)002:2636: 'khor mkha' 'gro ma rnams la bstan pa bde mchog sdom 'byung gi rgyud dang /
NK122(kho)002:2637: dgyes pa'i rdo rje'i rgyud gsum ste /
NK122(kho)002:2641: gzhan yang ma h+aa ma ya /
NK122(kho)002:2642: gdan bzhi la sogs pa rnams dus de nyid du bshad pa'o //
NK122(kho)002:2643: gnas lha min dbang po'i khang bzang dang /
NK122(kho)002:2644: zhes pa ni ri rab kyi khong gseng du /
NK122(kho)002:2645: ston pa 'jam dpal gshin rje'i gshed kyi skur snang nas /
NK122(kho)002:2646: 'khor lha ma yin rnams la ston pa gshin rje gshed kyi skor la /
NK122(kho)002:2649: gdong drug ste gsar ma skor bzhi yin /
NK122(kho)002:2655: 'di rnams kyi rgyud rkang bzung cig smos na /
NK122(kho)002:2656: 'jam dpal gsang ba grub pa'i rgyud me lce 'bar
NK122(kho)002:2657: ba 'phreng ba'i rgyud gzhon nu gdong drug gi rgyud
NK122(kho)002:2658: khro bo sme brtsegs kyi rgyud zla gsang nag po'i
NK122(kho)002:2659: rgyud / bzlog byed 'char kha nag po rgyud /
NK122(kho)002:2662: rtog bdun rtog gsum gyi rgyud /
NK122(kho)002:2665: gshin rje'i las kyi rgyud la /
NK122(kho)002:2667: gshin rje gshed nag po bsad pa'i rgyud /
NK122(kho)002:2668: dgongs pa khro bo 'dus pa'i spyi dril gyi rgyud /
NK122(kho)002:2669: gshin rje dmar nag gi rgyud /
NK122(kho)002:2671: shan pa dmar nag gsod byed kyi rgyud /
NK122(kho)002:2672: 'khor lo nag po 'ching byed kyi rgyud /
NK122(kho)002:2673: rak+sha glang mgo gtub byed kyi rgyud /
NK122(kho)002:2674: zang kha dmar po sbyin bsreg gi rgyud /
NK122(kho)002:2675: phrin las rnam bzhi mnan pa'i rgyud /
NK122(kho)002:2676: bla mtsho nag po bsrung 'khor gyi rgyud /
NK122(kho)002:2677: myur du bsad pa drag po'i rgyud /
NK122(kho)002:2678: rgyu mchog rol pa bskang ba'i rgyud /
NK122(kho)002:2679: mngon shes bsgrub pa pra phab kyi rgyud /
NK122(kho)002:2680: ma ru rtsi bzhi sngags kyi rgyud /
NK122(kho)002:2681: ur mo rtog pa bco brgyad pa'i rgyud la sogs
NK122(kho)002:2682: pa rnams yin gnas ni gnod sbyin rgyal po'i pho
NK122(kho)002:2684: ri rab kyi byang phyogs lcang lo can gyi pho brang du /
NK122(kho)002:2685: ston pa rdo rje phur pa'i skur snang nas /
NK122(kho)002:2686: 'khor gnod sbyin rnams la bstan pa rdo rje phur
NK122(kho)002:2687: pa'i rgyud la sogs pa rnams dus de nyid du
NK122(kho)002:2688: bshad do // de yang phur pa'i rgyud la /
NK122(kho)002:2689: byi to ta ma 'bum sde'i rgyud /
NK122(kho)002:2690: rnal 'byor dam pa gsang chen gyi rgyud /
NK122(kho)002:2691: ki la ya 'bru bcu gnyis kyi rgyud /
NK122(kho)002:2694: bzlog phur bcu gnyis kyi rgyud /
NK122(kho)002:2695: rdo rje phur pa nyi ma'i 'od zer gyi rgyud /
NK122(kho)002:2696: phrin las rnam bzhi rgyud do //
NK122(kho)002:2697: byi to ta ma las kyi rgyud la /
NK122(kho)002:2704: ma tshangs ba kha skong ba'i rgyud lnga'o //
NK122(kho)002:2705: dang po rtsa ba'i rgyud lnga ni /
NK122(kho)002:2707: pad+ma gsang ba gsung gi rgyud /
NK122(kho)002:2708: rdo rje gsang ba thugs kyi rgyud /
NK122(kho)002:2709: rat+na 'bar ba yon tan gyi rgyud /
NK122(kho)002:2710: ral gri 'bar ba phrin las kyi rgyud do //
NK122(kho)002:2712: phur pa mya ngan las 'das pa'i rgyud /
NK122(kho)002:2715: yan lag gi rgyud bcu ni /
NK122(kho)002:2716: khro bo rnam rgyal la sogs khro bo rnams la rgyud re gsungs so //
NK122(kho)002:2720: bla ma'i man ngag 'jig rten snang byed kyi rgyud do //
NK122(kho)002:2721: me tog gi rgyud bcu ni /
NK122(kho)002:2723: 'jig rten rab tu gsang ba'i rgyud /
NK122(kho)002:2726: gsang ba srog len gyi rgyud /
NK122(kho)002:2728: mya ngan 'das pa phyi ma'i rgyud /
NK122(kho)002:2731: dur khrod khu byug rol pa'i rgyud do //
NK122(kho)002:2735: shwa na dmar nag gi rgyud /
NK122(kho)002:2737: ma tshang pa kha bskongs pa'i rgyud lnga ni /
NK122(kho)002:2742: ki la ya bcu gnyis kyi rgyud do //
NK122(kho)002:2743: mkha' 'gro pho mo'i gnas rnams su //
NK122(kho)002:2746: mkhar chu rta gdong dkar mo gnas //
NK122(kho)002:2747: tsa ri phag gdong ser mo'i gnas //
NK122(kho)002:2748: stag tshang nyi zla dmar mo'i gnas //
NK122(kho)002:2749: til gro thal byed dril bu'i gnas //
NK122(kho)002:2750: zhes gsungs pas 'di bzhi ni bod yul na yod la /
NK122(kho)002:2751: rgya gar gyi gnas phran rnams su /
NK122(kho)002:2752: gsang sngags ma rgyud kyi ston pa rnams su snang nas /
NK122(kho)002:2754: bstan pa ma rgyud kyi 'phros rgyud rnams dus de nyid du bshad do //
NK122(kho)002:2755: gdul bya so so'i mos pa bzhin //
NK122(kho)002:2756: bstan pa'i snying po gsang sngags bshad //
NK122(kho)002:2758: gong du bshad pa'i lha dang /
NK122(kho)002:2763: 'di rnams la la ni sprul pa yin la /
NK122(kho)002:2764: la la ni rang rgyud pa ltar du gsang sngags phyi nang gi chos bshad do //
NK122(kho)002:2765: gzhan yang bdud stobs chen gyi gnas su /
NK122(kho)002:2766: ston pa dpal pad+ma dbang chen gyi skur snang nas /
NK122(kho)002:2768: bstan pa dpal pad+ma dbang chen gyi rgyud la sogs pa dus de nyid du bshad do //
NK122(kho)002:2769: de yang dbang chen gsung gi rgyud la /
NK122(kho)002:2771: rngog ma leb rgan gyi rgyud /
NK122(kho)002:2772: dbang rgyas gnyis med kyi rgyud /
NK122(kho)002:2776: dregs pa tshar gcod kyi rgyud dregs pa dbang chen dbang sdud kyi rgyud /
NK122(kho)002:2780: dbang chen rngam brjid kyi rgyud la sogs pa rnams gsungs so //
NK122(kho)002:2781: gzhan yang klu dug can gyi gnas su /
NK122(kho)002:2782: ston pa spyan ras gzigs bdud rtsi sman gyi sku dang ldan pa de dang /
NK122(kho)002:2783: phyag rdor bya khyung la sogs pa'i skur snang nas
NK122(kho)002:2784: 'khor klu rigs rnams la bstan pa phyag na rdo
NK122(kho)002:2785: rje'i rgyud dang / bya khyung gi rgyud dang /
NK122(kho)002:2786: spyan ras gzigs kyi rgyud la sogs pa rnams gdul
NK122(kho)002:2787: bya so so'i mos pa bzhin du bstan pa tha
NK122(kho)002:2788: dag gi bcud 'dus pa'i snying po zab cing rtogs
NK122(kho)002:2789: par dka' ba'i gsang ba de nyid rtogs na yon
NK122(kho)002:2790: tan thams cad kyi gzhir gyur pa'i sngags zhes bya
NK122(kho)002:2791: ba de nyid du bshad do //
NK122(kho)002:2792: rgyud kyi chos byung tshul lo //
NK122(kho)002:2794: sprul sku sh+aakya seng ge 'das nas /
NK122(kho)002:2795: lo nyi shu rtsa brgyad kyi dus su /
NK122(kho)002:2796: dam pa'i rigs can lngas phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas la gsol ba gdab /
NK122(kho)002:2797: phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas kyis gsang bdag la bka' bsgo mdzad /
NK122(kho)002:2798: gsang bdag gis ma la ya'i rtse la byon nas /
NK122(kho)002:2799: dam pa'i rigs can lnga la lung a nu yo ga'i chos kyi 'khor lo bskor ro //
NK122(kho)002:2800: de dang dus mnyam du rgyal po dza'i khang thog na tan+t+ra sde bco brgyad kyi char phab nas /
NK122(kho)002:2801: rgyal po 'khor dang bcas pa grol lugs 'di lta ste /
NK122(kho)002:2802: tshul ci ltar du grol na /
NK122(kho)002:2804: nga ni 'di nas mi snang nas //
NK122(kho)002:2805: lo ni brgyad dang bcu gnyis na //
NK122(kho)002:2806: lha gnas gsum du grags pa yi //
NK122(kho)002:2807: bstan pa'i snying po dam pa zhig /'dzam gling shar lho'i phyogs mtshams su //
NK122(kho)002:2808: mi las skal ldan rigs can ste //
NK122(kho)002:2809: rgyal po dza zhes bya ba la //
NK122(kho)002:2810: sngon gyi ltas rnams snang bar 'gyur //
NK122(kho)002:2812: rgyal po dza la rmi ltas bdun byung ste /
NK122(kho)002:2813: de yang rmi ltas bdun ni //
NK122(kho)002:2814: ri ma la ya de'i shar lho na //
NK122(kho)002:2815: tri shang a su ra'i brag phug zhes bya ba na /
NK122(kho)002:2816: phug na rin chen zur brgyad dod pa /
NK122(kho)002:2817: sgo rin po che zla gam du dod pa /
NK122(kho)002:2818: logs la ngo mtshar gyi ri mo 'byung ba /
NK122(kho)002:2819: logs brag seng ge dkar mo lta bu khyi tshugs lta bu yod pa /
NK122(kho)002:2820: mkhar yang thog gsum rim dang bcas pa /
NK122(kho)002:2821: steng na bya ka len ta ka'i tshang bcas nas /
NK122(kho)002:2822: chos thams cad thig le nyag gcig tu sgrog nas yod pa /
NK122(kho)002:2823: rtsa ba bdud rtsi'i chu mig rang rdol du yod pa /
NK122(kho)002:2824: mdun na me tog gi snam bu yod pa /
NK122(kho)002:2825: shing yal ga phyogs bzhir gyes pas /
NK122(kho)002:2826: dus bzhi'i dgra las skyobs pa ltar yod pa /
NK122(kho)002:2827: shing de'i me tog dang 'bras bu sman du 'gyur te /
NK122(kho)002:2828: zos pas nad sna tshogs sos pa /
NK122(kho)002:2829: de lta bu'i nyams dga' ba'i gnas der /
NK122(kho)002:2830: las dang skal bar ldan pa rnams bgrod dus thar la /
NK122(kho)002:2831: las dang skal bar mi ldan pa rnams ni mi thar pa'i gnas khang de na /
NK122(kho)002:2832: skal ldan rgyal po dza gsang sngags phyi rgyud la sgrub pa mdzad cing bzhugs pa las /
NK122(kho)002:2833: rmi ltas bdun zhag re la rmi yang skad /
NK122(kho)002:2834: zhag gcig la rmi yang skad /
NK122(kho)002:2836: phyag na rdo rje mdun gyi nam mkha' la byon nas /
NK122(kho)002:2838: gdul bya thams cad kyi rtog sgrib sbyangs /
NK122(kho)002:2839: gsung gi gnas nas bstan pa dang theg pa'i sgras
NK122(kho)002:2840: bsgrags pas gdul bya thams cad kyis go bar mdzad
NK122(kho)002:2841: / thugs kyi gnas nas rdo rje 'od 'bar ba byung nas rgyal po'i thugs kar thim /
NK122(kho)002:2842: spyi bo'i gtsug nas nyi ma byung nas /
NK122(kho)002:2843: rgyal po'i gtsug tu thim pa rmis so //
NK122(kho)002:2844: de yang dgongs 'dus kyi 'grel pa lung bstan rdo rje las //
NK122(kho)002:2845: sku gsung thugs rtags thim pa dang //
NK122(kho)002:2848: dus gsum gyi bde bar gshegs pa thams cad kyis nyi ma dang zla ba la bcibs nas /
NK122(kho)002:2849: phyag na gser gyi 'khor lo rtsibs stong dang ldan
NK122(kho)002:2850: pa bsnams nas sems can thams cad la chos kyi
NK122(kho)002:2852: de yang chos kyi bgro ba mdzad pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:2855: nam mkhar sprin gser gyi kha dog can chags /
NK122(kho)002:2857: cho 'phrul gyi 'brug sgra las dam pa chos kyi sgra 'ur ti ri ri sgrogs par rmis te /
NK122(kho)002:2858: de yang chos sgra chen po sgrogs pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:2861: nam mkha'i sprin gseb nas bdud rtsi'i chu rgyun bab ste sa phyogs thams cad chag chag gdab /
NK122(kho)002:2862: gdul bya thams cad kyi rtog sgrib sbyangs nas /
NK122(kho)002:2863: kun kyang rdo rje rnal 'byor zhes gsang sngags kyi sgra 'ur ti ri ri grags pa rmis so //
NK122(kho)002:2864: de yang bdud rtsi char du bab pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:2867: nam mkha'i sprin gseb nas rin po che'i sgrom gyi nang nas /
NK122(kho)002:2868: rin po che mthing gi shog gu la /
NK122(kho)002:2869: gser gyi rgya rang nan du bris pa'i po ti
NK122(kho)002:2870: glegs bam rnams skar mda' thang la bab pa lta
NK122(kho)002:2872: rin chen char du phab pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:2875: po ti glegs bam de rnams la /
NK122(kho)002:2876: rig 'dzin dang byang chub sems dpa' rnams la las ni mchod pa phul /
NK122(kho)002:2877: la las ni bskor ba byed /
NK122(kho)002:2878: la las ni bstod pa byed pa'i sgra sgrogs pa rmis so //
NK122(kho)002:2880: p+au tsa rgya chen byas pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:2883: nam mkha'i mthongs nas gzugs su ma grub pa'i lung bstan pa'i sgra /
NK122(kho)002:2884: las dang skal bar rab ldan cing //
NK122(kho)002:2885: bsod nams chen po dra ma khyod //
NK122(kho)002:2886: sprul pa ci ltar lung bstan zhing //
NK122(kho)002:2887: rgyal ba 'byung bar lung bstan pas //
NK122(kho)002:2888: bstan pa'i snying po dam pa zhig /
NK122(kho)002:2889: skal ldan khyod la sgrogs par bya'o //
NK122(kho)002:2891: der rgyal po mnal sad de /
NK122(kho)002:2892: mkhar gyi yang thog du sku 'chag du byon pas /
NK122(kho)002:2893: gsang bdag phyag na rdo rje'i sku /
NK122(kho)002:2894: rgyu rin po che smug po las grub pa khru
NK122(kho)002:2895: gang gcig bzhugs gyin gda' skad de la phyag lan
NK122(kho)002:2896: gsum 'tshal / bskor ba lan gsum byas /
NK122(kho)002:2897: zhabs spyi bo'i gtsug tu blangs te //
NK122(kho)002:2898: e ma'o ngo mtshar mchog gi sku //
NK122(kho)002:2899: 'dren pa mchog gi dpal lags gang //
NK122(kho)002:2900: mos pa'i yid kyi lha mchog khyod //
NK122(kho)002:2901: sngon tshe gong nas bsgrub pa yis //
NK122(kho)002:2902: las kyis 'brel ba'i lha mchog khyod //
NK122(kho)002:2903: bskal pa brgyar yang mi gtong ngo //
NK122(kho)002:2905: yi dam gyis lhar bzung nas zla ba bdun du bsgrub pa mdzad pas /
NK122(kho)002:2906: po ti dang glegs bam de rnams mngon sum du bab cing /
NK122(kho)002:2907: de'i byin rlabs kyis snang ba dpe cha shar ba yin skad /
NK122(kho)002:2908: der rgyal pos po ti dang glegs bam de rnams la brtags pas /
NK122(kho)002:2909: rtogs par 'dug kyang gdul bya gzu lum dang ras cho can dgag par bya ba'i phyir /
NK122(kho)002:2910: ma rtogs pa ltar du gnang nas /
NK122(kho)002:2911: 'jig rten gyi khams na mkhyen pa su che /
NK122(kho)002:2913: za hor gyi yul na rgyal po u pa ra dza zhes bya ba mkhyen pa che zer /
NK122(kho)002:2916: rgyal po'i thugs kyi rtog pa ma chod kyis dogs nas byon du ma bzhed skad /
NK122(kho)002:2917: po ti dang glegs bam rnams rta dang glang po
NK122(kho)002:2918: che la khol la thongs shig dang bas brtag go
NK122(kho)002:2919: zer nas / po ti dang glegs bam rnams stag sgro dang gzig sgro'i nang du bcug nas /
NK122(kho)002:2921: du ru ka la sogs pa'i spos sna tshogs dang /
NK122(kho)002:2924: pu tsa sna tshogs dang bcas te spyan drangs nas /
NK122(kho)002:2925: khong gis brtags pas tshig gcig kyang brda ma mjal skad /
NK122(kho)002:2926: sngon gyi mtshan rtags dang sbyar na rgyal po nyid rang gis rtogs par 'gyur ro //
NK122(kho)002:2927: gsung nas tshur spyan drangs skad /
NK122(kho)002:2928: yang rgyal po nyid kyis brtag pas rtogs par 'dug kyang /
NK122(kho)002:2929: ma rtogs pa ltar byas nas /
NK122(kho)002:2930: yang 'jig rten na mkhyen pa su che dris pas
NK122(kho)002:2931: sangs rgyas rin chen mang gi sprul pa dge slong
NK122(kho)002:2932: ku ku ra dza mkhyen pa rgya che'o zhes zer
NK122(kho)002:2934: rgyal po'i thugs kyi rtog pa ma chod kyis dogs nas byon du ma gnang par /
NK122(kho)002:2935: po ti dang glegs bam rnams stag sgro dang gzig sgro'i nang du bcug /
NK122(kho)002:2937: du ru ka la sogs spos sna tshogs dang /
NK122(kho)002:2938: gdugs dang rgyal mtshan la sogs pa mchod pa'i bye brag sna tshogs pas spyan drangs nas /
NK122(kho)002:2939: dge slong ku ku ra dza nyid kyis brtags pas
NK122(kho)002:2940: sgyu 'phrul dra ba'i rgyud le'u stong phrag brgya pa'i
NK122(kho)002:2941: rgyud bya ba de'i nang nas /
NK122(kho)002:2942: rdo rje sems dpa'i thugs sgrub kyi le'u 'am /
NK122(kho)002:2943: rdo rje sems dpa' zhal mthong gi le'u rtogs te /
NK122(kho)002:2944: zla ba bdun du sgrub pa mdzad pas rdo rje
NK122(kho)002:2945: sems dpa' ting nge 'dzin gyi ngo kha la byon
NK122(kho)002:2946: nas rigs kyi bu sid+d+hi ci 'dod /
NK122(kho)002:2948: bstan pa dang theg pa tha dag rtogs pa'i dngos grub zhu /
NK122(kho)002:2950: phyag na rdo rjes lung bstan par 'gyur gyis gsungs nas mi snang bar song skad /
NK122(kho)002:2951: yang zla ba bdun bsgrub pa mdzad pas /
NK122(kho)002:2952: phyag na rdo rje mngon sum du byon nas rdo rje lan gsum bsor nas /
NK122(kho)002:2953: spang len brtul shugs spyod pa'i dbang //
NK122(kho)002:2954: dge bar bskur bas sdig pa med //
NK122(kho)002:2956: rtsol ba dang bcas pa mtshan nyid theg pa spangs nas /
NK122(kho)002:2957: rtsol ba med pa gsang sngags kyis theg pa nyams su len pa khyod la /
NK122(kho)002:2959: theg pa thams cad rdzogs par dbang bskur ro //
NK122(kho)002:2961: dge bsnyen li tsa byi dri ma med pa la zhus gcig par lung bstan /
NK122(kho)002:2962: ku ku r+aa dzas gsang ba'i bdag po'i bka' bzhin du bsgrub cing /
NK122(kho)002:2963: sgyu 'phrul dra ba stong phrag brgya ba'i rgyud las /
NK122(kho)002:2964: tan+t+ra sde chen bco brgyad du byas nas /
NK122(kho)002:2965: skal ldan rgyal po dza la gsungs /
NK122(kho)002:2966: tan+t+ra sde chen po bco brgyad la /
NK122(kho)002:2979: yon tan gyi rgyud gsum ni /
NK122(kho)002:2986: ki la ya 'bru bcu gnyis kyi rgyud /
NK122(kho)002:2988: de dag thams cad kyi spyi rgyud /
NK122(kho)002:2990: dam tshig sa ma ya 'bum sde bkod pa'i rgyud /
NK122(kho)002:2991: rdo rje thabs kyi zhags pa'i rgyud /
NK122(kho)002:2992: de ltar tan+t+ra sde chen po bco brgyad po rgyal po dzas seng ha r+aa dza la /
NK122(kho)002:2993: des sras mo go ma la /
NK122(kho)002:2994: des khyi'i rgyal po ku ku r+aa dza la /
NK122(kho)002:2995: des ro lang bde ba'i dngos grub /
NK122(kho)002:2996: des rdo rje bzhad pa la /
NK122(kho)002:2997: des za hor gyi rgyal po pra chen ha sti la /
NK122(kho)002:2998: des slob dpon sangs rgyas gsang ba la /
NK122(kho)002:2999: des slob dpon bi ma mi tra la sogs pa'i pan+di ta lnga brgya la gsungs /
NK122(kho)002:3000: de nas rim bzhin brgyud nas rtsa ba'i bla ma'i bar du'o //
NK122(kho)002:3001: da ni gzhung don ngo bo 'bru gnyer na /
NK122(kho)002:3002: gsang sngags bla med rdo rje theg pa sgyu 'phrul
NK122(kho)002:3003: gyi sgo nas tshom bu tshogs kyis sgrub pa'i byin
NK122(kho)002:3004: rlabs kyi rkyen gyis rgyal po dza zhes kyang bya
NK122(kho)002:3005: / d+ha he ta'o zhes kyang bya //
NK122(kho)002:3006: lung bstan rdo rje zhes kyang bya /
NK122(kho)002:3007: in+d+ra bo d+hi zhes kyang bya ba 'di ni sangs
NK122(kho)002:3008: rgyas thub pa'i dbang po rang gi zhal slob yin
NK122(kho)002:3009: par snang / 'di tshom bu 'bum dang bcas dbyings su gshegs pa'o //
NK122(kho)002:3010: sogs kyi sgras ku ku ra dza dang /
NK122(kho)002:3011: dge slong u pa ra tsa dang /
NK122(kho)002:3013: sras mo go ma de bi la sogs pa'i skal
NK122(kho)002:3014: ldan sgrub pa po 'khor dang bcas pa rnams kyis
NK122(kho)002:3015: tshe gcig lus gcig gis dbang po rab don gnyis
NK122(kho)002:3016: yongs su rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas zhes bya ba thob
NK122(kho)002:3017: par gyur ste / de yang dbang 'bring phyag rgya chen po'i rig 'dzin dang lhun grub rig 'dzin /
NK122(kho)002:3018: dbang po tha ma rnam smin rig 'dzin dang tshe dbang rig 'dzin nam yang thob nges so //
NK122(kho)002:3019: 'khor bcas zhi ba chen por gshegs /
NK122(kho)002:3021: gsang sngags ma h+aa yo ga'i lugs kyis tshom bu tshogs bsgrubs nas /
NK122(kho)002:3022: 'khor yang 'khor dang bcas pa grol bar bshad do //
NK122(kho)002:3023: dge slong ku ku r+aa dza'i gtsor byas pa'i tshom bu khri /
NK122(kho)002:3024: seng nga'i yul gyi dge slong u pa ra dza'i gtso byas pa'i tshom bu stong /
NK122(kho)002:3025: sras r+aa dza ha sti gtsor byas pa'i tshom bu lnga brgya /
NK122(kho)002:3026: sras mo go ma de bi'i gtsor byas pa'i tshom
NK122(kho)002:3027: bu brgya la sogs pa skal ldan sgrub pa po
NK122(kho)002:3028: rnams 'khor bcas zhing chen po chos skur gshegs pa'o
NK122(kho)002:3029: // de yan chad ni lung a nu yo ga
NK122(kho)002:3030: dang rgyud ma h+aa yo ga'i chos kyi byung tshul
NK122(kho)002:3031: // yin la / 'o na bka' rdzogs pa chen po dus nam gyi tshe na byung ce na /
NK122(kho)002:3032: de rnams dang dus mtshungs par thub pa mya ngan las 'das rjes /
NK122(kho)002:3033: lo nyi shu rtsa brgyad kyi dus su /
NK122(kho)002:3034: rgyu 'bras kyi chos rnams rdzogs nas /
NK122(kho)002:3035: sum cu rtsa gsum du kun dga' snying po la rmi ltas bzhi byung ste /
NK122(kho)002:3036: thub drug gis bskor ba byas te rang thim pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:3037: bdud dang khyab 'jug dang gu lang gsum jur mid byas pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:3038: phyag tu nyi zla thogs te 'jig rten gyi mun pa bsal ba dang /
NK122(kho)002:3039: nam mkha' la sprin rin po che'i kha dog lta bu las char bab ste /
NK122(kho)002:3040: rtsi thog rgyas pa rmis nas /
NK122(kho)002:3041: lha'i dbang po la bshad pas lha'i dbang pos rtsol med kyi theg pa 'byung bar shes te /
NK122(kho)002:3042: rgyal ba thams cad la rtsol ba med pa'i theg pa gsung du gsol /
NK122(kho)002:3045: kye dus gsum gshegs pa'i rgyal ba yis //
NK122(kho)002:3046: rtsol bcas theg pa mthar bstan nas //
NK122(kho)002:3047: rtsol med theg pa bstan du gsol //
NK122(kho)002:3048: zhes gsol ba gdab pas rgyal ba thams cad kyis rdo rje sems dpa' bskul /
NK122(kho)002:3049: rdo rje sems dpas phyag na rdo rje thugs ka nas bton nas /
NK122(kho)002:3050: 'chad pa'i skyes bu gsang ba'i bdag por dbang bskur ste //
NK122(kho)002:3051: dus gsum rgyal ba thams cad kyis //
NK122(kho)002:3053: sku gsung thugs kyi gsang ba 'chang //
NK122(kho)002:3054: khyed ni smra ba'i seng ge ste //
NK122(kho)002:3055: rtsol med 'dul ba'i gang zag la //
NK122(kho)002:3056: lhun grub theg pa gsung du gsol //
NK122(kho)002:3058: phyag rdor gyis rgyal ba rigs lnga las gzhi 'bras kyi the tshom bcad nas /
NK122(kho)002:3059: lha gnas gsum du rtsol med kyi bstan pa gsungs tshul dang /
NK122(kho)002:3060: de nas gsang bdag phyag na rdo rjes sprul sku
NK122(kho)002:3061: dga' rab rdo rje gsang ba rdzogs pa chen po'i
NK122(kho)002:3062: bstan pa'i bdag por dbang bskur nas /
NK122(kho)002:3063: u rgyan gyi yul dri med d+ha na ko sha'i mtsho gling du /
NK122(kho)002:3064: 'jam dpal bshes gnyen la sogs pa rnams la /
NK122(kho)002:3065: brjod bya klong dgu rjod byed sho la ka 'bum
NK122(kho)002:3066: phrag drug cu rtsa bzhi dus skad cig ma gcig
NK122(kho)002:3067: du gsungs pa'o // de yang sems sde'i skor la
NK122(kho)002:3068: 'bum phrag nyi shu rtsa gcig klong sde la nyi
NK122(kho)002:3069: du gsungs pa'o // shu rtsa gnyis / man ngag skor la nyi shu rtsa gcig go //
NK122(kho)002:3073: rang grol mngon sum du bstan pa man ngag gi skor dang gsum /
NK122(kho)002:3078: yang gsang rgyal bu chung gi skor dang bzhi /
NK122(kho)002:3083: yang gsang bla na med pa'i skor dang bzhi'o //
NK122(kho)002:3084: de la sogs rdzogs chen gyi skor la /
NK122(kho)002:3085: rgyud sde mang du yod kyang gzhan du shes par bya'o //
NK122(kho)002:3086: 'dir yi ge mang dogs pa'i phyir ma bris so //
NK122(kho)002:3087: rjes 'jug gis gsol ba btab pas gnas skabs dang mthar thug gi 'bras bu thob tshul lo //
NK122(kho)002:3089: slad nas te rgyal po dza dang dam pa'i rigs
NK122(kho)002:3090: can lnga la sogs pa rnams kyi rjes su 'jug
NK122(kho)002:3091: cing 'gro bar byed pa'i rgya gar dang bod kyi
NK122(kho)002:3092: skal ldan sgrub pa po 'khor dang bcas pa rnams
NK122(kho)002:3093: kyis rtse gcig mos pa'i dbang gis thog mar bla
NK122(kho)002:3094: ma mtshan nyid dang ldan pa btsal nas dbang bzhi
NK122(kho)002:3095: yongs su rdzogs par zhus te /
NK122(kho)002:3097: rgyud gsang ba'i snying po la sogs pa la thos bsam byas nas /
NK122(kho)002:3098: lta spyod dkyil 'khor dbang dam dang //
NK122(kho)002:3099: phrin las sgrub pa'i las rim dang //
NK122(kho)002:3100: sngags dang phyag rgya mchod pa bcu //
NK122(kho)002:3106: mi 'da' bar byed pa dam tshig /
NK122(kho)002:3107: don gnyis sgrub par byed pa phrin las /
NK122(kho)002:3108: nyams su len pa sgrub pa /
NK122(kho)002:3111: gnas su stobs pa mchod pa ste /
NK122(kho)002:3112: rgyud kyi dngos po bcu'i don /
NK122(kho)002:3113: ma nor bar shes par byas te bsnyen pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:3116: bsgrub pa chen po dang bzhi'i yan lag gzhung bzhin du spyad nas /
NK122(kho)002:3117: rang rang gi yi dam gyi lha la gsol ba btab pas don gnyis 'grub pa'o //
NK122(kho)002:3118: skabs 'dir bsnyen bsgrub bzhi'i stongs thun brjod par bya'o //
NK122(kho)002:3119: de la spyir gsang sngags kyi sgor 'jug pa'i rnal
NK122(kho)002:3120: 'byor pa rnams kyi lam gyi gzhi ma bsnyen bsgrub
NK122(kho)002:3121: bzhi yin no // de yang glang po che rab 'bog gi rgyud las /
NK122(kho)002:3122: bsnyen bsgrub rnam pa bzhi'i sgor 'jug pa'i rnal 'byor pa rnams kyis zhes gsungs pa'i phyir ro //
NK122(kho)002:3123: de la dkyil 'khor la brten pa'i bsnyen bsgrub bzhi /
NK122(kho)002:3124: lam rim 'jug gi bsnyen sgrub bzhi /
NK122(kho)002:3128: dang po dkyil 'khor gyi bsnyen bsgrub bzhi ni /
NK122(kho)002:3129: gsang sngags ma h+aa yo ga'i lta ba legs par rtogs pa bsnyen pa /
NK122(kho)002:3130: de ting kun ting rgyu'i ting nge 'dzin /
NK122(kho)002:3131: lha phyag rgya gcig pa yab rkyang du sgom pa nye bsnyen /
NK122(kho)002:3133: yum gyi mkha' gsang byin gyis brlabs nas sras kyi dkyil 'khor bsgom ste /
NK122(kho)002:3134: phyi rol dkyil 'khor du bkod pa sgrub pa chen po'o //
NK122(kho)002:3135: lam rim 'jug gi bsnyen sgrub bzhi ni /
NK122(kho)002:3136: gsang sngags ma h+aa yo ga'i lta ba rtogs nas /
NK122(kho)002:3137: de ting kun ting sgom pa tshun chad bsnyen pa /
NK122(kho)002:3139: phyag rgya gcig pa yan lag gi lha nyi khri bzhi stong tshun chad nye bsnyen /
NK122(kho)002:3140: tshom bu tshogs sgrub sgrub pa /
NK122(kho)002:3141: tshogs sgrub kyi tha mar dngos grub blangs pas /
NK122(kho)002:3142: rig 'dzin bzhi gang yin pa gcig thob pa sgrub pa chen po'o //
NK122(kho)002:3143: sgrub pa'i bsnyen bsgrub bzhi ni /
NK122(kho)002:3147: phyi rgyud la dkar gtor bka' bsgo byed pa tshun chad bsnyen pa /
NK122(kho)002:3148: zhag grangs ci tsam byed pa'i tshun chad la 'od
NK122(kho)002:3149: zer dkar po phyir bkyes nas phyi snod kyi sgrib
NK122(kho)002:3151: phyed phyin chad la zhag tha ma ma gtogs 'od
NK122(kho)002:3152: zer dmar po bkye nas nang bcud kyi sgrib pa
NK122(kho)002:3154: nub tha ma la 'od zer mthing ka bkye nas /
NK122(kho)002:3155: snod bcud gnyis ka'i sgrib pa sbyangs nas dngos grub blang ba ni /
NK122(kho)002:3157: dbang gi bsnyen bsgrub bzhi ni /
NK122(kho)002:3158: nub dang po sa'i cho ga bsnyen pa /
NK122(kho)002:3159: nub gnyis pa sta gon gyi cho ga nye bsnyen /
NK122(kho)002:3160: nub gsum pa dngos gzhi'i cho ga la slob dpon dang slob ma 'jug pa bsgrub pa /
NK122(kho)002:3161: dbang bzhi yongs rdzogs dngos su bskur pa ni bsgrub pa chen po'o //
NK122(kho)002:3162: gsang ba'i bsnyen sgrub bzhi ni /
NK122(kho)002:3163: yum gzung ma mtshan nyid dang ldan pa btsal nas /
NK122(kho)002:3165: zas bsrung tshun chad bsnyen pa /
NK122(kho)002:3167: 'dod pa'i bstan bcos kyis bde ba rgyas par byed pa ni nye bsnyen /
NK122(kho)002:3168: phyag rgya bzhis rol pa bsgrub pa /
NK122(kho)002:3169: yum gyi mkhar thig le dbab bzlog bskyil dgram byed pa ni bsgrub pa chen po'o //
NK122(kho)002:3170: bsnyen sgrub yan lag gzhung bzhin spyod cing /
NK122(kho)002:3171: bskyed rdzogs kyis bsam gtan la brtson 'grus dang ldan
NK122(kho)002:3172: nas rang gi yi dam gyi lha zhi ba dang
NK122(kho)002:3173: / khro bo gang yin de la gsol ba btab pa mthar phyin pas /
NK122(kho)002:3174: dag bya las kyi sgrib pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:3175: nyon mongs pa'i sgrib pa gnyis dag par 'gyur ste /
NK122(kho)002:3176: 'dod par bya ba rang gi yi dam gyi lha
NK122(kho)002:3177: zhi ba dang khro bo gang yin pa de'i zhal
NK122(kho)002:3179: gnas skabs lam 'gyur gyi rig 'dzin thob cing /
NK122(kho)002:3180: mthar thug byang chub tu lung ston pa dang 'bras
NK122(kho)002:3181: bu sangs rgyas pa rnams mngon sum du byas so
NK122(kho)002:3184: de dag ces pa ni gong du snyegs pa dang sdud pa'i tshig yin te /
NK122(kho)002:3185: gong du bshad pa'i rgya bod kyi skal ldan sgrub
NK122(kho)002:3186: pa po rnams kyis gnas skabs dang mthar thug gi
NK122(kho)002:3187: 'bras bu mngon du byas pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:3188: rgyal po dza la sogs pa'i skal ldan sgrub pa
NK122(kho)002:3189: po rnams zhing chen po chos kyi skur gshegs pa
NK122(kho)002:3190: dang dam pa'i rigs can lnga la gsang ba'i bdag
NK122(kho)002:3192: mdo dgongs pa 'dus pa dngos su bshad pa de dag /
NK122(kho)002:3193: sangs rgyas kyi thugs rje gdul bya sems can rnams
NK122(kho)002:3194: kyis bsgrub pa dang de'i 'bras bu gdul bya la
NK122(kho)002:3196: sgrib pa gnyis dag cing 'bras bu mngon sum du
