NK122(kho)002:3197: thob pa ni bskul zhing gsol ba gdab pa'i thugs
NK122(kho)002:3198: rjes skye tshul yin par rgyal ba kun tu bzang
NK122(kho)002:3199: pos gsungs so // thugs rjes skyes nas don mdzad tshul la gnyis te /
NK122(kho)002:3203: bgrang ngo bo mdor bstan pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:3205: sangs rgyas kyi thugs rje skyes nas gang la gang
NK122(kho)002:3206: 'dul gyis don mdzad tshul rgyas par bshad cing gsal
NK122(kho)002:3207: bar bstan pa ni 'di lta ste /
NK122(kho)002:3210: don dam nges pa'i theg pa dang rnam pa gsum
NK122(kho)002:3211: du gdul bya'i don mdzad tshul shes par bya ste
NK122(kho)002:3212: / de yang gdul bya gsum 'dul thabs gsum theg
NK122(kho)002:3213: pa'ang gsum ste de re re la yang gsum gsum
NK122(kho)002:3221: 'dod yon la zhen pa'i gdul bya dang /
NK122(kho)002:3222: 'khor ba las nges par 'byung ba'i gdul bya dang /
NK122(kho)002:3223: shin tu gdul dka' drag po'i gdul bya dang gsum la /
NK122(kho)002:3226: 'khor lo rgyun gyi theg pa dang don dam nges
NK122(kho)002:3227: pa'i theg pa dang cho 'phrul mngon 'byung ba'i theg
NK122(kho)002:3231: 'dod la zhen pa'i gdul bya de la /
NK122(kho)002:3232: 'khor lo rgyun gyi theg pa des /
NK122(kho)002:3233: rang bzhin shugs kyis 'dul ba dang /
NK122(kho)002:3234: nges par 'byung ba'i gdul bya de la /
NK122(kho)002:3235: don dam nges pa'i theg pa des /
NK122(kho)002:3236: gnyen po thabs kyis 'dul ba dang /
NK122(kho)002:3237: gdul dka' drag po'i gdul bya de la /
NK122(kho)002:3238: cho 'phrul mngon 'byung gi theg pa des /
NK122(kho)002:3239: las ngan las rgyun gcod pas 'dul ba dang gsum mo //
NK122(kho)002:3240: de ltar gdul bya dang theg pa dang 'dul thabs su bstan pa yin /
NK122(kho)002:3241: de yang mdo dgongs pa 'dus pa las rgyas par
NK122(kho)002:3242: bshad cing rgya che la grangs mang bar yod kyang
NK122(kho)002:3243: gzhung 'dir rgya che grangs mang rnams mdor bsdus nas
NK122(kho)002:3245: rgyas par bshad pa la gnyis te /
NK122(kho)002:3249: gong du bshad pa'i gdul bya gsum 'dul thabs gsum /
NK122(kho)002:3250: theg pa dang gsum po'i don de dag rgyas par
NK122(kho)002:3251: bshad cing gsal bar bstan pa ni 'di lta ste
NK122(kho)002:3252: / rgyas bshad dngos de la gsum ste /
NK122(kho)002:3253: 'dod la zhen pa'i gdul bya 'khor lo rgyun gyi theg pas gdul ba dang /
NK122(kho)002:3254: gdul dka' drag po'i gdul bya cho 'phrul mngon 'byung gi theg pas 'dul ba dang /
NK122(kho)002:3255: nges par 'byung ba'i gdul bya don dam nges pa'i theg pas 'dul ba'o //
NK122(kho)002:3260: bskal pa'i 'khor lo bskal phran nyi shu'i bar la
NK122(kho)002:3261: mi chad par rgyun gyi theg pa'i gdul bya ni
NK122(kho)002:3265: gzugs med khams dang khams gsum du gnas pa'i 'gro ba rnams ni /
NK122(kho)002:3267: gzugs khams pa gzugs dang dga' ba la zhen /
NK122(kho)002:3268: gzugs med khams pa snyom 'jug gi ting nge 'dzin la zhen pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:3271: mthun pa'i grogs kyi zhen pa gsum gyi 'dod pa dang ma bral ba'i phyir /
NK122(kho)002:3272: 'dod la zhen pa'i gdul bya zhes brjod de /
NK122(kho)002:3275: 'khor lo rgyun gyi theg pa de yang /
NK122(kho)002:3276: ye'am thog ma med pa'i dus nas sangs rgyas pas
NK122(kho)002:3277: zhes gsang sngags kyi rgyud sde rnams su grags pa
NK122(kho)002:3279: sa chu spyan dang ma ma ki //
NK122(kho)002:3280: me rlung gos dkar sgrol ma ste //
NK122(kho)002:3281: nam mkha' dbyings kyi dbyings phyug ma //
NK122(kho)002:3282: srid gsum ye nas sangs rgyas zhing //
NK122(kho)002:3284: 'byung ba chen po lngar snang ba gang yin pa 'di dag /
NK122(kho)002:3285: thugs spros pa thams cad dang bral ba rje bsgo
NK122(kho)002:3286: ba med par kun la khyab pa'i don 'gyur med
NK122(kho)002:3287: rtag pa'i sangs rgyas yin te /
NK122(kho)002:3290: ma bcos rtog bral ye nas dag /
NK122(kho)002:3292: 'byung chen po lnga'i ngo bo sus kyang ma bcos /
NK122(kho)002:3293: rtog pa thams cad dang bral ba ye nas chos kyi dbyings su dag pas na sangs pa'am /
NK122(kho)002:3295: gzhan don du sangs rgyas kyi thugs rje 'byung ba
NK122(kho)002:3296: chen po lngas zas skom la sogs pa dus rtag
NK122(kho)002:3297: pa rgyun du 'byung ba'i phyir na rgyas pa'am /
NK122(kho)002:3299: snang stong gi mthar mi gnas pas na /
NK122(kho)002:3302: de nyid ye nas sangs rgyas ni //
NK122(kho)002:3303: nam mkha' rnam par snang mdzad dang //
NK122(kho)002:3304: sa ni mi g.yo rdo rje yin //
NK122(kho)002:3305: chu ni rin chen 'byung ldan nyid //
NK122(kho)002:3306: me ni snang ba mtha' yas yin //
NK122(kho)002:3307: rlung ni kun byed gdon mi za //
NK122(kho)002:3308: thams cad stong par ye sangs rgyas //
NK122(kho)002:3309: des khyab ma 'dres rgyas pa ni //
NK122(kho)002:3310: ma bcos ye nas sangs rgyas pa //
NK122(kho)002:3318: 'khor lo rgyun gyi theg pa 'byung ba lnga po des /
NK122(kho)002:3319: 'gro drug sems can thams cad kyi don du dang po skye ba'i rgyu byed pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:3320: bar du 'tsho ba'i longs spyod kyis rkyen byed pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:3321: rten byed pa'i gnas la sogs pas don ci ltar mdzad na yang /
NK122(kho)002:3322: 'byung ba lnga'i ngo bo la rtog pa mi mnga' bas mi rtog ces bya /
NK122(kho)002:3323: de'i ngang la rang shug gis skye 'tsho rten gsum gyi dgos 'dod kun 'byung bas na /
NK122(kho)002:3324: ngang ngam shugs kyis rgyun chad med pa'i tshul gyis bskal pa'i 'khor lor gnas pa'o //
NK122(kho)002:3326: drangs gong du bstan pa de ltar 'khor lo rgyun gyi theg pa yis /
NK122(kho)002:3327: rang bzhin ngang ngam shugs kyis gdul bar bya ste /
NK122(kho)002:3328: 'gro ba sems can thams cad kun gyi skye bar byed pa'i rgyu /
NK122(kho)002:3330: brten par byed pa'i gnas la sogs pa'i sgo nas /
NK122(kho)002:3331: nam yang 'dul ba ni 'di lta ste /
NK122(kho)002:3332: dang po phal pa'i sems brgyad skyes /
NK122(kho)002:3333: mthar theg chen la legs par 'jug pa'i dpe ni /
NK122(kho)002:3334: sa bon lta bu'i sems dang gcig /
NK122(kho)002:3335: myu gu lta bu'i sems dang gnyis /
NK122(kho)002:3336: sdong bu lta bu dang gsum /
NK122(kho)002:3337: yal ga lta bu dang bzhi /
NK122(kho)002:3338: lo ma lta bu dang lnga /
NK122(kho)002:3339: me tog lta bu dang drug /'bras bu lta bu dang bdun /
NK122(kho)002:3340: gsos su gyur pa lta bu'i sems dang brgyad do //
NK122(kho)002:3341: dang po 'dun pa'i shes pa so so'i skye bo'i
NK122(kho)002:3342: sa nas 'khor ba la skyo ba skye zhing myang
NK122(kho)002:3343: 'das brod nas chos byed dgos snyams pa ni sa
NK122(kho)002:3344: bon lta bu'o // rang gi pha ma dang mdza'
NK122(kho)002:3345: bshes la sbyin pa gtong ba ni myu gu lta
NK122(kho)002:3346: bon lta bu'o // bu'o // phyogs ris mi byed par gtong ba ni sdong bu lta bu'o //
NK122(kho)002:3347: dge sbyong la sogs pa'i yul thams cad nas gtong ba ni yal ga lta bu'o //
NK122(kho)002:3348: des lag pa brkyang nas gtong zhing spro ba bskyed pa ni lo ma lta bu'o //
NK122(kho)002:3349: lhug par gtong zhing spro ba cher bskyed pa ni me tog lta bu'o //
NK122(kho)002:3350: bsnyen gnas la sogs pa'i sdom pa sna re bsrung ba ni 'bras bu lta bu'o //
NK122(kho)002:3351: mos pa'i lha dkon mchog gsum mchod pa ni gsos su gyur pa lta bu'o sems so //
NK122(kho)002:3353: phal pa'i sems brgyad mthar gnas tshe //
NK122(kho)002:3354: snying po rang bzhin mtshungs pa dang //
NK122(kho)002:3355: bshes gnyen mgon la lung gnyis thob //
NK122(kho)002:3356: ces gsungs pa lta bu yin no //
NK122(kho)002:3357: 'khor lo rgyun gyi theg pa des gdul bya la phan ci ltar thogs na /
NK122(kho)002:3358: dang po skye 'tsho rten gsum gyi bya ba byas pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:3359: bar du phal pa'i sems brgyad skye ba dang /
NK122(kho)002:3360: mthar don dam nges pa'i theg pa'i snod du rung ba ni /
NK122(kho)002:3362: dam pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas rnams
NK122(kho)002:3363: kyis don dam nges pa'i chos kyi 'khor lo rab
NK122(kho)002:3365: chos nyams su blangs pa kun kyang mthar zag pa
NK122(kho)002:3366: med pa'i dbyings su 'phags pa'i lam la bkod do
NK122(kho)002:3367: // cho 'phrul mngon 'byung gi theg pa la bzhi ste /
NK122(kho)002:3372: dang po nye bar bstan pa ni /
NK122(kho)002:3373: sangs rgyas kyi thugs rje'i cho 'phrul /
NK122(kho)002:3374: phyi me chu rlung gsum nang nad mug mtshon gsum
NK122(kho)002:3375: gyi bskal pas gdul bya 'dul bar dka' ba rnams
NK122(kho)002:3376: kyi ngor mngon sum par 'byung ba'i tshul rgyas par
NK122(kho)002:3377: bshad cing gsal bar bstan pa ni 'di lta ste
NK122(kho)002:3378: / dam pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas
NK122(kho)002:3379: rnams kyis don dam nges pa'i theg pas dngos su
NK122(kho)002:3380: 'dul ba'i spyod yul du ma gyur pa ste /
NK122(kho)002:3382: shin tu dug gsum bdo ba'i phyir /
NK122(kho)002:3383: de yang 'dod chags chu ltar khol /
NK122(kho)002:3385: gti mug mun ltar du 'thib pa'i don gyis 'dul bar dka'/
NK122(kho)002:3387: 'khor lo rgyun gyi theg pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:3388: don dam nges pa'i theg pas 'dul bar dka' ba'i snyigs ma lnga'i sems can rnams la /
NK122(kho)002:3392: nang nad mug mtshon gsum gyi bskal pa'i 'khor los
NK122(kho)002:3393: gdul bya de'i rgyud la zas skom la zhen cing
NK122(kho)002:3394: chags pa la mug ge'i bskal pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:3395: gti mug can gyi ngor dran pa nyams shing rmongs par byed pa nad kyi bskal pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:3396: zhe sdang can gyi ngor 'khrugs par byed pa mtshon gyi bskal pa yis /
NK122(kho)002:3399: las ngan pa mi dge ba bcu'i rgyun gcod cing
NK122(kho)002:3400: 'du shes ngan pa rnams kyi 'phro bsgyur ba'i phrin
NK122(kho)002:3401: las ni / dam pa rgyal bas chos kyi sgo
NK122(kho)002:3402: mo brgyad khri bzhi stong gi 'khor lo bskor bar
NK122(kho)002:3403: las ni / byas nas kyang / sangs rgyas kyis
NK122(kho)002:3404: 'dul bar ma gyur pa de dag la phyi nang
NK122(kho)002:3405: gi bskal pa'i 'khor los las ngan pa'i rgyun gcod
NK122(kho)002:3406: las ni / byas nas kyang / par byed pa'o // rgyas bshad la gnyis te /
NK122(kho)002:3411: mug ge'i bskal pas zas skom gyi zhen pa gcod pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:3413: 'di rnams la bshad gzhi gcig brgyab na go bde ba yin pas /
NK122(kho)002:3414: gcod ces pa bshad pa'i gzhir drang /
NK122(kho)002:3415: de'i khyad par gyi chos la bzhi /
NK122(kho)002:3417: gdul bya 'dul bar dkar ba 'dod chags can rnams kyi ngo bor /
NK122(kho)002:3418: pad+ma he ru ka nyid mu ge'i bskal par snang nas gcod ste /
NK122(kho)002:3420: 'dam skyes pad ltar 'khor bar sku 'khrungs shing //
NK122(kho)002:3421: lhag mthong me chen bskal pas thams cad bsreg /'dod chags tshul gyis 'dod chags 'joms mdzad ma //
NK122(kho)002:3422: 'dod chags 'joms mdzad pad+ma he ru ka /
NK122(kho)002:3425: zas skoms la sogs pa'i 'dod yon la zhen cing
NK122(kho)002:3426: chags pa'i sems rnam par shes pa'i tshogs drug dang
NK122(kho)002:3427: / nyon mongs pa can gyi yid kyis las ngan
NK122(kho)002:3428: pa sna tshogs bsags pa'i rgyun de dbang med du
NK122(kho)002:3430: dus nam gyi tshe gcod na /
NK122(kho)002:3431: da lta ni gnas pa'i bskal pa yin la /
NK122(kho)002:3432: de yang tshe lo brgyad khri'i dus su sangs rgyas rnam gzigs byon /
NK122(kho)002:3433: de nas lo gnyis brgya re zhing re re 'grib pa bdun khri'i dus su gtsug tor can byon /
NK122(kho)002:3434: drug khri'i dus su thams cad skyob byon /
NK122(kho)002:3435: de gsum gyi dus bstan pa mtshan nyid sde gsum dar /
NK122(kho)002:3437: kri ya gsum khri'i dus su gser thub /
NK122(kho)002:3441: de nas brgya re zhing re re 'grim pa'i tshe
NK122(kho)002:3442: lo brgya pa'i dus su sh+aakya thub pas bla med
NK122(kho)002:3444: thub pa chen po 'di yi bstan pa ni /
NK122(kho)002:3445: skal bzang las lo stong gnas par gsung zhing /
NK122(kho)002:3446: zla ba snying pos zhus pa'i mdo las /
NK122(kho)002:3447: lo nyis stong gnas par gsungs so //
NK122(kho)002:3449: lo bdun stong gnas par gsungs pa las /
NK122(kho)002:3450: sru skye dgu'i bdag mo la sogs pa bud med rab tu byung bas lo nyis stong 'grib ste /
NK122(kho)002:3451: sangs rgyas kyi bstan pa lo lnga stong gnas zhes bshad do //
NK122(kho)002:3452: de'i lnga brgya phrag bcu la /
NK122(kho)002:3456: rtags tsam 'dzin pa'i dus la gcig go //
NK122(kho)002:3460: rgyun du zhugs kyi le'u zhes bya'o //
NK122(kho)002:3463: ting nge 'dzin tshul khrims kyi le'u zhes zer ro //
NK122(kho)002:3467: rtags tsam 'dzin pa ni lnga brgya tha ma yin no //
NK122(kho)002:3468: 'di ni tshe lo bzhi bcu'i dus su rgyal po dpung dmar can gyi ring la 'ong ba yin /
NK122(kho)002:3469: de'i gtam rgyud rgyas par bshad rgyu yod kyang yi ge mang gis dogs pa'i phyir ma bris so //
NK122(kho)002:3470: de nas lo brgya re zhing re re 'grim pas /
NK122(kho)002:3471: tshe lo sum cu'i dus su tshul ci ltar du gcod na /
NK122(kho)002:3472: zas skoms kyi sred pa zhi bar byed pa /
NK122(kho)002:3473: lus srog 'tsho ba'i zas skoms dang bral ba mug
NK122(kho)002:3474: ge'i chos bzhi dang ldan pa'i bskal pa yis lo
NK122(kho)002:3477: za ma bdun la 'byung ste dbang med pa'i tshul du gcod par byed do //
NK122(kho)002:3478: de yang da lta dge 'dun la tshogs sog byed /
NK122(kho)002:3479: sems can la sbyin pa gtong /
NK122(kho)002:3480: rang rang gis kyang sems bskyed nas phyi dro'i zas bcad tsam dang /
NK122(kho)002:3481: chos phyir dka' ba spyad na de lta bu'i bskal pa las grol zhing thar bar 'gyur ro gsungs /
NK122(kho)002:3482: nad kyi bskal pas lus kyi zhen pa gcod pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:3486: gdul bya 'dul dka' ba'i gti mug can gyi ngor /
NK122(kho)002:3487: bud+d+ha he ru ka nyid nad kyi bskal bar snang nas gcod //
NK122(kho)002:3488: gti mug tshul gyis gti mug 'jom mdzad pa //
NK122(kho)002:3489: gti mug 'jom mdzad bud+d+ha he ru ka /
NK122(kho)002:3492: gti mug gis lus mi gtsang bar zhen cing bdag
NK122(kho)002:3493: la chags pa'i las ngan pa'i rgyun de dbang med
NK122(kho)002:3495: dus nam gyi tshe gcod na /
NK122(kho)002:3496: tshe lo sum cu'i dus su mi'i sa bon tsam cig las ma lus pa las /
NK122(kho)002:3497: lo je 'grib du song bas tshe lo nyi shu pa'i dus su'o //
NK122(kho)002:3499: sdug bsngal dang len gyi bzod pa dang ldan par
NK122(kho)002:3500: byed pa dran pa nyams shing rmongs par byed pa'i
NK122(kho)002:3504: za ma bdun du 'byung ste dbang med pa'i tshul du gcod par byed do //
NK122(kho)002:3505: de yang da lta nad pa'i nad g.yog byed /
NK122(kho)002:3507: dge 'dun la sman gyi dngos po a ru ra
NK122(kho)002:3508: tsam phul na de lta bu'i bskal pa la grol
NK122(kho)002:3510: mtshon gyi bskal pas gnyen 'dun gyi zhen pa gcod pa'o //
NK122(kho)002:3513: gang gis na gdul bya 'dul bar dka' ba zhe sdang can gyi ngor /
NK122(kho)002:3514: zhe sdang 'joms par byed pa'i thabs 'dzin pa ste /
NK122(kho)002:3515: badz+ra he ru ka nyid mtshon cha dar ba'i bskal par snang ba yis /
NK122(kho)002:3516: dngos por gyur tshad mtshon cha snang nas gcod par byed do //
NK122(kho)002:3517: thabs 'dzin mtshon cha'i bskal pas dngos po 'jig /
NK122(kho)002:3518: zhe sdang tshul gyis zhe sdang 'jom mdzad pa //
NK122(kho)002:3519: zhe sdang 'jom mdzad badz+ra he ru ka /
NK122(kho)002:3522: nye du gnyen 'brel la sogs pa bdag gzhan gyi dngos po thams cad gcod pa'o //
NK122(kho)002:3524: tshe lo nyi shu'i dus su mi'i sa bon tsam las ma lus pa las /
NK122(kho)002:3525: mi je 'phel lo je 'grib du song bas /
NK122(kho)002:3526: tshe lo bcu pa'i dus su gcod /
NK122(kho)002:3528: gcig gis gcig la gnod sems skyes nas /
NK122(kho)002:3529: dngos po gyur tshad mtshon char snang nas lag tu 'dzin pa /
NK122(kho)002:3532: mi'i sa bon tsam las ma lus par /
NK122(kho)002:3533: dbang med du gcod par byed do //
NK122(kho)002:3534: de yang da lta gzhan la srog gcod mi bcol /
NK122(kho)002:3535: rang gis kyang srog gcod spangs nas /
NK122(kho)002:3536: de lta bu'i bskal ba las grol zhing thar bar 'gyur ro //
NK122(kho)002:3538: mtshon gyi bskal pa yan chad ya thog ring mo yin la /
NK122(kho)002:3539: mtshon gyi bskal pa'i rjes su mi'i sa bon tsam las ma lus la /
NK122(kho)002:3540: bong gi ring ba la khru gang ngam /
NK122(kho)002:3541: rkang gang thung ba la mtho gang ngam chag gang tsam tshe ring ba la lo bcu /
NK122(kho)002:3542: thung ba la nges pa med rta sbang la rkub skyag /
NK122(kho)002:3543: lug ril gyis rten ma byed /
NK122(kho)002:3544: nub mo skyes pa nang par me slong bgyid pa yod /
NK122(kho)002:3545: de'i tshe byams pa'i sprul pa lus khru do yod pa tshe lo nyi shu pa gcig byon nas /
NK122(kho)002:3546: khyed rnams kyi mi dge ba srog gcod pa spongs dang /
NK122(kho)002:3547: tshe lo dang por lus nga dang mnyam par 'gyur ro //
NK122(kho)002:3549: sems can rnams kyis srog gcod pa spangs nas rim gyis /
NK122(kho)002:3551: lo yang nyi shu thub par 'gyur ro //
NK122(kho)002:3552: de bzhin du byams pa'i sprul pa rim bzhin du byon nas /
NK122(kho)002:3553: mi dge ba bcu spangs bcol /
NK122(kho)002:3554: pha rol du phyin pa bcu rdzogs par byas nas /
NK122(kho)002:3555: lo lnga bcu re zhing re re 'phel bas /
NK122(kho)002:3556: brgyad khrir phyin pa'i dus na /
NK122(kho)002:3558: de nas lnga bcu re zhing re re 'grib pas tshe lo sum cu pa'i dus na /
NK122(kho)002:3561: bcu pa na mtshon gyi bskal pa 'byung la /
NK122(kho)002:3562: de ni bar khug gcig yin cing /
NK122(kho)002:3563: de 'dra'i khug pa bco brgyad la sangs rgyas stong la bzhi chag pa 'byung la /
NK122(kho)002:3564: tha ma ma thog thung ngu la lo brgya re
NK122(kho)002:3565: zhing re re 'phel ba'i brgyad khrir phyin pa'i tshe
NK122(kho)002:3568: mthar mnar med du 'chi ba yod kyang skye ba med pa dus mnyam pa yin no //
NK122(kho)002:3569: phyi'i bskal pa la bzhi ste /
NK122(kho)002:3571: me'i bskal pas dngos 'dzin 'joms pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:3573: gcod ces pa bshad pa'i gzhir grangs /
NK122(kho)002:3574: de'i khyad par gyi chos la gsum /
NK122(kho)002:3576: sangs rgyas kyi lhag mthong ngam so sor rtog pa'i ye shes sam /
NK122(kho)002:3577: yang na pad+ma he ru ka nyid me'i bskal par snang ba yis gcod par byed de /
NK122(kho)002:3579: lhag mthong me chen bskal pas thams cad bsreg /'dod chags tshul gyis 'dod chags 'jom mdzad pa //
NK122(kho)002:3580: 'dod chags rdo rje pad+ma he ru ka /
NK122(kho)002:3582: gang gcod na dngos po gzung 'dzin gcig nas gcig tu 'brel ba'i dra ba ma lus gcod do //
NK122(kho)002:3583: tshul ci ltar du gcod na /
NK122(kho)002:3587: thog mar dmyal khams bcu drug 'og ma nas rim pa ltar yar 'pho /
NK122(kho)002:3590: de nas gling bzhi pa rnams 'pho ste /
NK122(kho)002:3591: byang sgra mi snyan pa'i mi rnams rgyal chen rigs bzhi'i gnas su 'pho /
NK122(kho)002:3592: shar nub gnyis 'dzam bu'i gling du 'pho nas bdud rtsis zhag zos pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:3593: bsam gtan dang po rgyud la skye te /
NK122(kho)002:3594: nam mkha' la sgra grags pa la /
NK122(kho)002:3596: dben pa la gnas pa rnams ni /
NK122(kho)002:3597: dga' ba dang bde ba'i rang bzhin can yin no //
NK122(kho)002:3599: sems can rnams la las dbang gis bsam gtan skyes /
NK122(kho)002:3600: bsam gtan dang po'i gnas su song /
NK122(kho)002:3601: de nas lha ma yin nas 'dod lha rigs drug
NK122(kho)002:3602: po la sogs pa rnams bsam gtan dang po'i gnas
NK122(kho)002:3603: su 'pho / bsam gtan dang po'i lha rnams kyang bsam gtan gnyis pa'i gnas su 'pho ste /
NK122(kho)002:3604: de rnams la bar bskal bcu dgu'i yun du thogs /
NK122(kho)002:3606: da lta'i nyi ma 'di bas kyang bdun 'gyur gyis tsha ba gcig nas drug gi bar dang /
NK122(kho)002:3607: de bas kyang bdun 'gyur gyis tsha ba gcig ste bdun gyis rim pa bzhin du rtsi shing dang /
NK122(kho)002:3609: gang ga la sogs pa chu chen dang /
NK122(kho)002:3612: phyi'i rgya mtsho pus nub tsam dang /
NK122(kho)002:3614: ri dang gling la sogs bsregs nas mthar ma de nyid kyang med nas stong pa yin /
NK122(kho)002:3615: de la bar bskal gcig yin te /
NK122(kho)002:3616: 'jig pa la bar bskal nyi shu'o //
NK122(kho)002:3617: de nas bar bskal nyi shu la stong /
NK122(kho)002:3618: de nas chags pa la snod chags pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:3621: 'og tu rlung gi dkyil 'khor gyi steng du chu'i dkyil 'khor /
NK122(kho)002:3622: de'i steng du gser gyi sa gzhi /
NK122(kho)002:3623: de'i steng du ri rab gser ri bdun /
NK122(kho)002:3624: gling bzhi lcags ri bcas pa chags pa la bar bskal gcig gi yun thogs /
NK122(kho)002:3626: bsam gtan gnyis pa nas tshang chen gyi lha chags /
NK122(kho)002:3627: de nas rim pa bzhin du 'dod lha rigs drug /
NK122(kho)002:3630: de yang 'dzam bu gling pa'i mis mi dge ba bcu chung ngu spyad pas dud 'gror skyes /
NK122(kho)002:3632: cher spyang pas dmyal bar skyes /
NK122(kho)002:3633: de nas mtshams med kyang byas pas /
NK122(kho)002:3634: mnar med du sems can gcig skyes /
NK122(kho)002:3637: gnas pa'i 'go brtsam pa rnams dus mnyam mo //
NK122(kho)002:3638: chu'i bskal pas 'dzin pa'i bag chags thams cad bkru ba dang /
NK122(kho)002:3640: 'khru ces pa bshad pa'i gzhir drangs /
NK122(kho)002:3641: de'i khyad par gyi chos la gsum /
NK122(kho)002:3643: sangs rgyas kyi zhi gnas kyi ting 'dzin nam /
NK122(kho)002:3644: mnyam pa nyid kyi ye shes sam /
NK122(kho)002:3645: rat+na he ru ka nyid chu'i bskal par snang ba yis 'khru ba yin //
NK122(kho)002:3646: bdag med mi gnas chu'i bskal pas 'khru //
NK122(kho)002:3647: nga rgyal tshul gyis nga rgyal 'jom mdzad pa //
NK122(kho)002:3648: nga rgyal rdo rje rat+na he ru ka /
NK122(kho)002:3651: sems kyi rtog dpyod kyi 'dzin pa'i bag chags thams cad 'khru bar byed do //
NK122(kho)002:3655: bcud 'jig pa ni gong dang 'dra la /
NK122(kho)002:3657: bsam gtan gsum pa'i zhabs nas char shing rta'i 'phang
NK122(kho)002:3658: lo tsam babs nas snod kyi 'jig rten lan tsha
NK122(kho)002:3659: chur zhig pa bzhin du zhig go //
NK122(kho)002:3660: rlung gi bskal pas shes bya kun du bskyod pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:3662: bskyod ces pa bshad pa'i gzhir drangs /
NK122(kho)002:3663: de'i khyad par gyi chos la gsum gang gis bskyod na sangs rgyas kyi phrin las sam /
NK122(kho)002:3664: bya ba grub pa'i ye shes sam /
NK122(kho)002:3665: karma he ru ka nyid gang du yang thogs chags
NK122(kho)002:3666: med pa rlung gi bskal par snang ba yis bskyod
NK122(kho)002:3667: de / phrin las rgya mtshos 'gro ba'i don mdzad cing //
NK122(kho)002:3668: shes bya thogs med rlung gi bskal pas 'thor //
NK122(kho)002:3669: phrag dog tshul gyis phrag dog 'jom mdzad pa //
NK122(kho)002:3670: phrag dog rdo rje karma he ru ka /
NK122(kho)002:3673: shes bya'i dngos po gang snang ba thams cad thogs
NK122(kho)002:3674: pa med par kun tu bskyod cing gtor bar byed
NK122(kho)002:3675: do // tshul ci ltar du bskyod na /
NK122(kho)002:3678: bcud 'jig pa gong dang 'dra ba la /
NK122(kho)002:3679: khyad par du bsam gtan gsum pa man chad 'jig dgos so //
NK122(kho)002:3681: bsam gtan bzhi pa'i zhabs nas rlung langs nas 'jig
NK122(kho)002:3682: rten gyi khams thams cad ras bal rlung gis gtor
NK122(kho)002:3684: stong pa'i bskal pas mtshan 'dzin 'joms pa'o //
NK122(kho)002:3686: stong ces pa bshad pa'i gzhir drang /
NK122(kho)002:3687: de'i khyad par gyi chos la gsum gang gis stong na /
NK122(kho)002:3688: sangs rgyas kyi thugs shes rab ste chos dbyings ye shes sam /
NK122(kho)002:3689: yang na bud+d+ha he ru ka nyid nam mkha'i bskal bar snang ba yis stong pa yin te /
NK122(kho)002:3690: 'gro rnams ci ltar 'dul cing gshegs mdzad pa //
NK122(kho)002:3691: shes rab nam mkha'i bskal pas nas rbud stong //
NK122(kho)002:3692: gti mug tshul gyis gti mug 'joms mdzad pa //
NK122(kho)002:3693: gti mug rdo rje bud+d+ha he ru ka /
NK122(kho)002:3696: dngos por skyes pa'i mtshan ma'i rgas rgud ste /
NK122(kho)002:3697: skye rgas na 'chi thams cad stong par byed pa'o //
NK122(kho)002:3698: de la dgos ched ci yod na /
NK122(kho)002:3699: sngar gyi las ngan pa'i dri ma dag nas /
NK122(kho)002:3700: phyis nas 'jig rten chags nas sangs rgyas kyi gdul
NK122(kho)002:3701: byar gyur nas don dam nges pa'i theg pa'i snod
NK122(kho)002:3702: du rung ba'o // yun ji srid du stong na /
NK122(kho)002:3703: 'jig pa lan drug cu rtsa bzhi'i 'og tu bar bskal nyi shu'i yun du stong pas so //
NK122(kho)002:3704: de yang me'i bdun tshan brgyad cu'i bdun tshan gcig /
NK122(kho)002:3705: rlung gcig dang drug cu rtsa bzhi la 'jig chags kyi 'khor lo chen po gcig zhes bya ste /
NK122(kho)002:3708: de ltar chu bdun thal nas kyang //
NK122(kho)002:3709: me'i bdun no de nas ni //
NK122(kho)002:3710: mjug tu rlung gis sdud par byed //
NK122(kho)002:3712: de yang bsam gtan dang po na rtog dpyod me lta bu yod pas mes 'jig /
NK122(kho)002:3714: dga' bde chu lta bu yod pas chus 'jig /
NK122(kho)002:3716: dbug 'byung rngub rlung lta bu yod pas rlung gis 'jig pa yin te /
NK122(kho)002:3717: bsam gtan de dang chos mthun phyir //
NK122(kho)002:3718: me chu rlung gis 'jig par byed //
NK122(kho)002:3721: tshor ba bde sdug gnyis la sogs pa bsam gtan
NK122(kho)002:3722: gyi skyon brgyad dang bral bas me chu rlung gsum
NK122(kho)002:3723: gyis mi 'jig /'o na ye mi 'jig pa e
NK122(kho)002:3724: yin na / de ma yin te /
NK122(kho)002:3726: mi rtag de yi gzhal med khang //
NK122(kho)002:3729: lha re re skye ba na /
NK122(kho)002:3730: gzhal yas khang dang sa gzhi dang bcas pa 'byung zhing /
NK122(kho)002:3731: lha de 'chi ba dang gzhal yas khang sa gzhi dang bcas pa dus gcig tu 'jig go //
NK122(kho)002:3732: de yang stong gsum gyi stong chen po'i 'jig rten gyi khams 'di ni /
NK122(kho)002:3734: chags dus gcig chags pa yin na de /
NK122(kho)002:3735: gling bzhi pa dang nyi zla dang //
NK122(kho)002:3736: ri rab dang ni 'dod lha dang //
NK122(kho)002:3737: tshangs pa'i 'jig rten stong la ni //
NK122(kho)002:3738: stong ni spyi phud yin par 'dod //
NK122(kho)002:3739: de stong la ni stong gnyis pa //
NK122(kho)002:3740: bar ma'i 'jig rten khams yin no //
NK122(kho)002:3741: de stong la ni stong gsum pa //
NK122(kho)002:3746: dus gang gi tshe gdul bya gang la ci ltar snang ba dang /
NK122(kho)002:3748: snyigs ma lngar gyur pa'i skabs rnams su ni 'di lta ste /
NK122(kho)002:3753: de yang dus kyi snyigs ma ni /
NK122(kho)002:3754: dus ngan rtsod pa'i dus dang ldan no //
NK122(kho)002:3756: tshe lo brgya pa man chad do //
NK122(kho)002:3757: las kyi snyigs ma ni mi dge ba bcu la longs spyod pa'o //
NK122(kho)002:3758: sems can gyi snyigs ma ni /
NK122(kho)002:3759: de'i dus skyes pa'i sems can rnams so //
NK122(kho)002:3760: nyon mongs pa'i snyigs ma ni /
NK122(kho)002:3761: nyon mongs pa skye sla la 'jig dka' ba yin te /
NK122(kho)002:3763: de'i tshe 'dul ba rnam gnyis ni mdo sngags gnyis yin /
NK122(kho)002:3764: yang na 'khor lo rgyun gyi theg pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:3765: don dam nges pa'i theg pa gnyis yin pa nub pas na /
NK122(kho)002:3766: bstan pa dung phyis pa bzhin du gyur pa'i dus na /
NK122(kho)002:3767: nad mug mtshon gsum gyi bskal pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:3768: sogs kyi sgras me bdun chu gcig gi bskal pa rnams bsdu ba yin /
NK122(kho)002:3769: de yang sangs rgyas kyi thugs rjes po de nyid kyi mdzad par bstan pa ste /
NK122(kho)002:3770: sems can gyis las ngan pa sna tshogs spyod pa de'i las rgyun gcod dgos pa'i phyir /
NK122(kho)002:3771: dper na lcags rgong dang 'dra bar 'dul dka' nyon
NK122(kho)002:3772: mongs pa'i dbang du song ba'i gdul bya dmu rgod
NK122(kho)002:3773: la / lcags la bzhu btul byed pa dang 'dra
NK122(kho)002:3774: ba'i gnyen po nad mug mtshon gsum 'jig chags stong
NK122(kho)002:3776: de la dgos ched ci yod na /
NK122(kho)002:3777: sdug bsngal rnams kyi rnam par snang nas /
NK122(kho)002:3778: gdul bya'i las ngan pa'i rgyun yongs su spyod par
NK122(kho)002:3779: byed nas don dam nges pa'i theg pa'i snod du
NK122(kho)002:3781: de nyid gsang sngags thun mong ma yin pa'i thugs
NK122(kho)002:3782: rje thabs kyi theg pa tha ma'i tha mar bstan
NK122(kho)002:3788: theg pa 'og ma pa rnams kyi nad mug mtshon
NK122(kho)002:3789: gsum gyi bskal pa la sogs de dag sangs rgyas
NK122(kho)002:3790: kyi mdzad pa yin pa la /
NK122(kho)002:3791: yin par ma shes nas blo phyogs gcig tu zhen pa dag na re /
NK122(kho)002:3792: ston pa sangs rgyas ni 'das nas bstan pa'i chos
NK122(kho)002:3793: ni nub pa'o zhes bstan pas 'dul ba'i thabs med
NK122(kho)002:3797: theg pa chen po ba rnams kyi dus de dag
NK122(kho)002:3798: la gsang sngags kyi thugs rje la shar nub med
NK122(kho)002:3799: pas sangs rgyas dang chos la 'byung 'jig dang dar
NK122(kho)002:3800: rgud med cing ston pa ma 'das bstan pa ni
NK122(kho)002:3801: nub ste me chu rlung gsum nad mug mtshon gsum
NK122(kho)002:3802: gyi bskal pa de nyid ston pa dang bstan pa
NK122(kho)002:3805: sangs rgyas mya ngan yongs mi 'da' //
NK122(kho)002:3806: chos kyang nub par mi 'gyur te //
NK122(kho)002:3807: ma rig smin mdzad 'dul ba'i phyir //
NK122(kho)002:3808: byung nas mya ngan 'da' bar stoon //
NK122(kho)002:3811: 'khor ba ji srid yod par du //
NK122(kho)002:3812: bstan pa'i snying po nyi ma shar //
NK122(kho)002:3814: mi nub rgyun mi chad par bskor //
NK122(kho)002:3816: snyigs ma lnga'i dus 'dir sangs rgyas kyi thugs rje'i
NK122(kho)002:3817: phrin las nad mug mtshon la sogs pa'i bskal par
NK122(kho)002:3818: snang nas gdul bya drag po rnams ngang ngam shugs
NK122(kho)002:3820: 'on kyang sangs rgyas kyi 'dul ba'i thabs dang theg pa gang dag la /
NK122(kho)002:3821: spyir bsam gyis mi khyab pa gcig yod pa la /
NK122(kho)002:3822: 'khor lo rgyun gyi theg pa tha ma yin par bstan pa la /
NK122(kho)002:3823: cho 'phrul mngon 'byung gi theg pa ni /
NK122(kho)002:3824: de bas kyang gdul bya ches 'dul bar dka' ba
NK122(kho)002:3825: rnams kyi ngor shin tu rtsub par snang bas na
NK122(kho)002:3826: tha ma yin par mdo dgongs 'dus las bshad pa
NK122(kho)002:3827: yin no // cho 'phrul mngon 'byung gi theg pa
NK122(kho)002:3828: 'di yang don la chos nyid rang byung gi ye
NK122(kho)002:3829: yin no // shes yin la / ma rtogs pa'i
NK122(kho)002:3830: sems can gyis dngos po a 'thas su zhen cing
NK122(kho)002:3831: phyin ci log gi gdul bya rnams la /
NK122(kho)002:3832: dbyings ma 'gag pa de nyid kyi ngang las ye
NK122(kho)002:3833: shes chen po'i cho 'phrul ston cing 'dul ba'i thabs
NK122(kho)002:3834: yin te / dgongs 'dus kyi cho 'phrul mngon 'byung gi theg pa'i zhabs bsdu ba'i skabs na /
NK122(kho)002:3835: lang ka'i bdag po de ltar na //
NK122(kho)002:3836: 'di kun gsang ba dam pa yi //
NK122(kho)002:3837: dbyings las gar yang ma g.yos te //
NK122(kho)002:3838: stong pa kho na'i dbyings nyid las //
NK122(kho)002:3839: stong pa'i chos rnams 'byung bar zad //
NK122(kho)002:3840: stong nyid gsang ba de kho na //
NK122(kho)002:3841: theg chen gsang ba de nyid do //
NK122(kho)002:3843: don dam nges pa'i theg pa la lnga ste /
NK122(kho)002:3846: lung gis mdor bstan pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:3848: dang po lung de nyid kyis mthar dbyung zhing don bsdu ba'o //
NK122(kho)002:3851: 'khor lo rgyun dang don dam nges //
NK122(kho)002:3854: gong ma 'khor lo rgyun gyi theg pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:3855: 'og ma cho 'phrul mngon 'byung gi theg pa gnyis
NK122(kho)002:3856: kyi don rgyas par bshad pa gong du song nas
NK122(kho)002:3857: 'dir bar ma don dam nges pa'i theg pa rgyas
NK122(kho)002:3858: par bshad cing gsal bar bstan pa ni 'di lta
NK122(kho)002:3860: srid pa ste khams gsum 'khor bas bsdus pa'i chos rnams ni /
NK122(kho)002:3861: gzung 'dzin gnyis kyis nga bdag tu 'dzin pas sdug bsngal ste /
NK122(kho)002:3862: de las thar bar 'dod pa'i gang zag las 'phro dang /
NK122(kho)002:3864: lam 'gyur med don dam nges pa'i theg pa de
NK122(kho)002:3865: yang spang bya'i gnyen po'i thabs kyi 'dul thabs kyis
NK122(kho)002:3866: / nyon mongs pa srid pa khams gsum 'khor ba'i chos sdug bsngal ba rnams /
NK122(kho)002:3867: dper na skra shad kyi 'khor lo bzhin rab tu
NK122(kho)002:3868: bsal bar byas te zag pa med pa'i dbyings 'phags
NK122(kho)002:3869: pa'i lam la bkod pa rnams la /
NK122(kho)002:3870: 'di la ming ci btags na don dam nges pa'i theg pa zhes bya bar brjod pa ste /
NK122(kho)002:3871: don dam nges pa'i theg pa de la'ang rnam pa gnyis yin te /
NK122(kho)002:3872: zhar las byung ba 'jig rten pa'i lta ba phyal
NK122(kho)002:3873: ba dang rgyang 'phen pa gnyis mu rtug pa dang
NK122(kho)002:3874: mu stegs gnyis dang bzhi'i 'dod pa bstan pa de
NK122(kho)002:3875: dang 'jig rten la 'das pa'i lta ba theg pa
NK122(kho)002:3876: rim pa dgu'i 'dod pa bstan pa'o //
NK122(kho)002:3877: lung gis mdor bstan pa ni /
NK122(kho)002:3879: de skad du'ang gsang ba'i snying po'i rgyud le'u bcu gsum las kyang /
NK122(kho)002:3880: don dam nges pa'i theg pa'i gzhung bsrang ba ni 'di lta ste /
NK122(kho)002:3881: ma rtogs pa phyal ba dang rgyang 'phen gnyis yin
NK122(kho)002:3882: pa dang log par rtog pa mu rtug dang mu
NK122(kho)002:3883: stegs gnyis phyogs tsam rtogs pa nyan rang gnyis /
NK122(kho)002:3884: gsang sngags la ltos na yang dag nyid ma rtogs te dbu ma dang sems tsam gnyis yin /
NK122(kho)002:3885: 'dul ba ni lus ngag yid gsum gyi spyod pa
NK122(kho)002:3886: gtsor byed pas kri ya dang u pa gnyis yin
NK122(kho)002:3887: / dgongs pa ni ting 'dzin gtsor byed pas na yo ga yin /
NK122(kho)002:3888: gsang ba dang zhes pa ni lta ba zab mo
NK122(kho)002:3889: dang spyod pa barlanga po gtsor byed pas ma h+aa
NK122(kho)002:3890: yo ga yin / rang bzhin bcos bslad dang bral ba a nu yo ga yin /
NK122(kho)002:3891: gsang ba'i don rnams zhes pa ni a ti yo ga yin /
NK122(kho)002:3892: de rnams yin pa'i rgyu mtshan zhib tu ngo sprad
NK122(kho)002:3893: rgyu yod kyang yi ge mang gis dogs pa'i phyir
NK122(kho)002:3894: ma bris / bla ma'i zhal las shes par bya'o //
NK122(kho)002:3895: te zhes pa'i don ni da res 'dir bstan bya lhag ma can gyi tshig yin /
NK122(kho)002:3896: lung de la rtsa tshig gis mdor bstan pa 'og nas rgyas par 'grel 'dod pa'o //
NK122(kho)002:3897: bye brag rgyas par bshad pa la gnyis te /
NK122(kho)002:3899: don dam nges pa'i theg pa nang pa rnams so //
NK122(kho)002:3905: zhes de ltar lung las gsungs pa'i phyir na bye brag tu phye ste rgyas par bshad na /
NK122(kho)002:3906: ma rtogs pa la phyal ba dang rgyang 'phen gnyis yin te /
NK122(kho)002:3907: log par rtog pa la mu rtug pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:3909: bzhi po 'di dag srid pa ste khams gsum 'khor
NK122(kho)002:3910: ba'i chos yin pas 'jig rten pa zhes bya ste
NK122(kho)002:3911: / don dam nges pa'i theg pa yin par mi brjod ste /
NK122(kho)002:3913: de'i zhar las byung ba'i lta ba'o //
NK122(kho)002:3914: rgyas par bshad pa de la gnyis te /
NK122(kho)002:3919: shin tu rgyas par bshad pa'o //
NK122(kho)002:3920: rgyas par bshad pa la gnyis te /
NK122(kho)002:3924: ma rtogs pa phyal ba dang rgyang 'phen gnyis kyi 'dod pa ni 'di lta ste /
NK122(kho)002:3925: dang po phyal ba pa'i 'dod pa ni khams gsum
NK122(kho)002:3926: gyi sems can 'di dag rnams la rgyu dge ba
NK122(kho)002:3927: la 'bras bu mtho ris kyi bde ba dang mi
NK122(kho)002:3928: dge ba'i chos rnams las ngan song gsum gyi sdug
NK122(kho)002:3929: bsngal dag yod pa dang med pa gang du'ang mi
NK122(kho)002:3931: de bzhin du dus gsum gyis bsdus pa'i skye ba
NK122(kho)002:3932: snga ma dang phyi ma dag kyang yod pa dang
NK122(kho)002:3933: med par yang mi rtog ste /
NK122(kho)002:3934: so so'i skye bo dud 'gro ba glang lta bu ste shin tu dman pa'o //
NK122(kho)002:3935: 'on kyang tshe 'di la dang po skye bar shes
NK122(kho)002:3936: bar du 'tsho ba'i zas tshol mkhas brten pa'i gnas
NK122(kho)002:3937: dang las 'gul shes pa can yin ste /
NK122(kho)002:3938: lta ba dang grub mtha' 'di yin med pas phyal pa zhes bya'o //
NK122(kho)002:3941: rgyang 'phen gyi lta ba phal cher phyal ba pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:3942: dge sdig dang las rgyu 'bras ngo ma shes pas der mtshungs la /
NK122(kho)002:3943: dge sdig mi shes kyang tshe 'di yi phan bsod dang /
NK122(kho)002:3944: khyad par du khe grags dang btsan phyug kho na don du gnyer zhing tshe 'di bsgrub pa'i phyir /
NK122(kho)002:3945: mchod sbyin phra mo gtong ba dang /
NK122(kho)002:3946: las kyi gtsang sbra la sogs spyad par byed cing /
NK122(kho)002:3947: 'jig rten pa'i lha'i gsang tshig gi lo ma can gyi gsang sngags te /
NK122(kho)002:3949: mo bon dang phan pa'i phyir sa bdag mchod pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:3950: phyug pa'i ched du g.yang blan pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:3951: rigs brgyud 'phel ba'i ched du sel byed pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:3952: sde btsug pa dang de rnams yin no //
NK122(kho)002:3953: de yang rang gi shes na byed /
NK122(kho)002:3954: gzhan la bcol na tshe 'di'i 'bras bu sgrub pa'i brten sa btsal ba'o //
NK122(kho)002:3955: de'i don gyis tshe 'di la btsan pa ni khe drag pa'o //
NK122(kho)002:3956: phyug pa ni nor mang zhing longs spyod che ba /
NK122(kho)002:3957: 'phan pa ni mi nor gnyis ka dar zhing tshe 'di la ci bsam 'grub pa'o //
NK122(kho)002:3958: de lta bu'i mthu stobs 'dod pa'i phyir tshe 'di'i
NK122(kho)002:3959: bde ba la dmigs pa dang de'i ched du spyod
NK122(kho)002:3960: pa'i khyad par can des ni thar pa yang dag
NK122(kho)002:3961: pa'i don las gol ba dang /
NK122(kho)002:3962: tshe 'di'i phan bsod tsam sgrub pa ma gtogs pa
NK122(kho)002:3963: thar pa la rgyang ring ba'i phyir rgyang 'phen pa
NK122(kho)002:3965: shin tu rgyas pa la gnyis te /
NK122(kho)002:3966: phyal ba shin tu rgyas pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:3978: phyal ba la dman rigs dang /
NK122(kho)002:3985: dman rigs ni blo shin tu dman pa thar lam
NK122(kho)002:3986: ston pa'i rkyen dge ba'i bshes gnyen dang mi 'phrad
NK122(kho)002:3987: / gal te 'phrad kyang blo 'jug pa'i skal ba gtan nas med de /
NK122(kho)002:3988: dper na shes rigs med pa'i dud 'gro ba glang dang mtshungs so //
NK122(kho)002:3991: log lta can phal cher rigs ma nges pa ni
NK122(kho)002:3992: skal pa cung zad yod kyang rkyen dge ba'i bshes
NK122(kho)002:3993: gnyen bla ma dam pa dang ma 'dzom pas /
NK122(kho)002:3994: dal ba brgyad rang 'byor dang bcas pa yod kyang gzhan 'byor lnga med pa dang mtshungs so //
NK122(kho)002:3995: de la dal 'byor bco brgyad ni /
NK122(kho)002:3996: de yang dal ba ni mi khom pa'i gnas brgyad spangs pa yin te /
NK122(kho)002:3998: mi khom brgyad spangs de yis dal ba rtag tu rnyed //
NK122(kho)002:4000: de la mi khom pa brgyad ni /
NK122(kho)002:4003: mi ma yin gyi 'gro ba dang bzhi /
NK122(kho)002:4005: log lta can de phyi pa mu stegs pa lta
NK122(kho)002:4006: bu sangs rgyas kyi bstan pa med pa mun pa'i
NK122(kho)002:4008: glen cing lkug pa dang bzhi ste brgyad do //
NK122(kho)002:4010: dmyal ba yi dwags dud 'gro dang //
NK122(kho)002:4011: kla klo tshe ring lha dang ni //
NK122(kho)002:4012: log lta sangs rgyas kyis stong pa //
NK122(kho)002:4013: lkug pa 'di dag mi khoms brgyad //
NK122(kho)002:4018: mi nyid dbus skyes dbang po tshang //
NK122(kho)002:4019: las mtha' ma log gnas la dad //
NK122(kho)002:4022: yul dbus su skyes pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:4024: sangs rgyas kyi bstan pa dar ba'i gnas la dad pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:4025: log lta ma skyes pas las kyi mtha' ma log pa'o //
NK122(kho)002:4027: sangs rgyas 'jig rten du byon pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:4029: bstan pa yun ring du gnas pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:4030: rang nyid de'i bstan pa la zhugs pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:4031: gzhan gyi phyir snying brtse ba yod pa rnams yin no //
NK122(kho)002:4032: rang 'byor lnga dang mi khoms pa brgyad spangs pa ngo bo gcig ste /
NK122(kho)002:4034: mi ma yin gyi 'gro ba spangs pa ngo bo gcig la /
NK122(kho)002:4036: zhing stong par ma skyes pa ngo bo gcig la /
NK122(kho)002:4037: yul dbus su skyes pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:4038: kla klor ma skyes pa ngo bo gcig la /
NK122(kho)002:4040: ma tshang ba spangs pa ngo bo gcig /
NK122(kho)002:4041: las kyi mtha' ma log pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:4042: log lta spangs pa ngo bo gcig pas /
NK122(kho)002:4043: dal 'byor ngo bo gcig yin no //
NK122(kho)002:4044: 'on kyang dal ba ni bral ba'i cha yin la /
NK122(kho)002:4045: 'byor pa ni ldan pa'i cha yin pas /
NK122(kho)002:4046: ldog pa tha dad pa yin no //
NK122(kho)002:4047: de lta bu'i dal 'byor rnyed par dka' ste /
NK122(kho)002:4048: gang las rnyed par dka' na mi khom pa'i gnas las rnyed par dka' ste /
NK122(kho)002:4050: ngan song las ni mi nyid shin tu thob dka' gsungs //
NK122(kho)002:4052: rgyu gang gis rnyed par dka' na /
NK122(kho)002:4053: dge ba phun sum tshogs pa'i rgyu las byung ba yin la /
NK122(kho)002:4054: mi khom pa'i gnas na dge ba spyod pa'i skabs med pas /
NK122(kho)002:4055: 'bras bu dal 'byor rnyed par dka' ba yin no //
NK122(kho)002:4056: rgyang 'phen shin tu rgyas pa la gnyis te /
NK122(kho)002:4060: mdo'i chos skad la rgyang 'phen la gnyis su phye ba yin te /
NK122(kho)002:4061: rigs chad dang 'du shes can gnyis yin no //
NK122(kho)002:4065: log par rtog pa mu rtug dang /
NK122(kho)002:4066: mu stegs gnyis dang bzhi'i bshad pa bas med la /
NK122(kho)002:4067: de bzhi'i nang tshan du dbye ba rgyas par phye
NK122(kho)002:4068: ba rnams mdo dgongs 'dus kyi chos skad yin par
NK122(kho)002:4075: rang bzhin gnas pa'i rigs khams bde gshegs snying po chad pa ma yin /
NK122(kho)002:4077: bde gshegs snying pos 'gro kun yongs la khyab zer ba dang 'gal /
NK122(kho)002:4078: 'dir ni mngon sum du rtogs pa rgyas 'gyur gyi rigs chad pa yin te /
NK122(kho)002:4079: 'khor ba spyi btsan la gtan du'ang sangs rgyas mi srid pa yod pa'i phyir /
NK122(kho)002:4080: gtan tshig de bas na rgyu rang bzhin la rtogs
NK122(kho)002:4081: pa'i shes rab dang blo chos la 'jug pa gtan
NK122(kho)002:4082: nas med / rkyen dge ba'i bshes gnyen dang yang mi 'phrad /
NK122(kho)002:4084: dper na byang chub kyi myu gu tshig pa'am /
NK122(kho)002:4085: dmus long gi sngon la kha dog dkar dmar bstan pa dang 'dra ste /
NK122(kho)002:4086: lam la 'jug pa'i skal ba med de /
NK122(kho)002:4088: chos kyi dbyings kyi kun la khyab gyur kyang //
NK122(kho)002:4089: rang rig rtogs pa'i skal dang mi ldan na //
NK122(kho)002:4090: ci ltar dmus long mdun du mdog bstan bzhin //
NK122(kho)002:4091: 'di ni skal med rigs chad pa yin no //
NK122(kho)002:4098: 'du shes can la'ang rnam pa bzhi ste /
NK122(kho)002:4103: mos pa'i 'du shes can nyid dang bzhi yod do //
NK122(kho)002:4106: ya nga ba'i las can dang /
NK122(kho)002:4109: rgyu la ya nga ba'i nyon mongs pa dug gsum
NK122(kho)002:4110: gyis kun nas bslang zhing srog gcod pa'i mchod sbyin
NK122(kho)002:4111: gtong ba la sogs pa mi dge ba'i rnam smin
NK122(kho)002:4113: 'bras bu ya nga ba ni ngan song gsum gyi nang nas kyang /
NK122(kho)002:4114: tsha ba dang rab tu tsha ba dang mnar med
NK122(kho)002:4115: pa'i sdug bsngal gting zab par 'phen par byed pas
NK122(kho)002:4117: las rgyu 'bras la mkhas pa shes rab dang ldan
NK122(kho)002:4118: pa'i skyes bus bltas na skyi g.ya' bas ya nga
NK122(kho)002:4119: can zhes grags pa yin no //
NK122(kho)002:4122: g.yeng ba'i 'du shes can rnams kyis tshe gcig po
NK122(kho)002:4123: 'di nyid kyi ched phyir du khe dang grags pas
NK122(kho)002:4125: tshe 'di yi che btsan grags pa sgrub pa'i phyir
NK122(kho)002:4126: nga rgyal dang zhe sdang gi sgo nas dmag 'dren
NK122(kho)002:4129: shag shing gnyen gsum la sogs pa g.yeng ba'i bya blag sna tshogs byed pa'o //
NK122(kho)002:4132: zhen pa'i 'du shes can gyi mtshan nyid ni /
NK122(kho)002:4133: zas dang nor la zhen pa dang rigs dang rgyud la zhen pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:4134: gnyen dang chung ma la zhen pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:4135: de'i ched phyir du brtson 'grus dang ldan pa'i sgo
NK122(kho)002:4136: nas 'jig rten gyi lha dbang phyug chen po dang
NK122(kho)002:4138: phra men la sogs pa'i nor lha'i rigs la sogs
NK122(kho)002:4139: pa rnams la blo brtan bca' nas bsgom bsnyen mchod
NK122(kho)002:4140: bstod byed pa'o // gzhan yang 'jig rten pa'i /
NK122(kho)002:4143: sgyu ma gsum la brten nas pha rol po gzhan
NK122(kho)002:4144: gyi mig 'phrul par byed nas nor dang rdzas sgrub
NK122(kho)002:4145: par byed cing gang zag phal pa gzhan gyi 'du
NK122(kho)002:4146: shes bsgyur bar byed cing mi mgo bskor nas tshe
NK122(kho)002:4147: phyi ma yal bar dor ba'o //
NK122(kho)002:4148: mos pa'i 'du shes can nyid do //
NK122(kho)002:4150: bzhi pa mos pa'i 'du shes can gyi mtshan nyid ni /
NK122(kho)002:4151: lta ba la gtad so med pas phyal bar gnas pa la /
NK122(kho)002:4152: 'on kyang dkon mchog gsum la skur bar mi byed pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:4153: sdig pa'i las la ya nga zhing las mi dge ba mi byed pa de ni /
NK122(kho)002:4154: cung zad dkar po'i sa bon dang ldan pa yin te /
NK122(kho)002:4155: de la brgyud nas sbyangs pa'i las yod pa'o //
NK122(kho)002:4156: dper na khyim bdag dpal skyes kyi gtam rgyud lta bu yin no //
NK122(kho)002:4157: log par rtog pa la gnyis te /
NK122(kho)002:4162: log rtog can la'ang gnyis yod de /
NK122(kho)002:4163: lta ba phyin ci log la mur bzung nas shes par bya ba'i yul la rtug pa'i phyir /
NK122(kho)002:4164: mu rtug pa zhes bya ba dang rtag chad gnyis
NK122(kho)002:4165: la mur bzung nas phyin ci log gi lta ba
NK122(kho)002:4166: la stegs bcas pa'i phyir na mu stegs pa zhes
NK122(kho)002:4167: bya ba dang gnyis yin no //
NK122(kho)002:4175: mu rtug gi nges tshig go //
NK122(kho)002:4178: mu rtug pa rang la yang rnam pa gnyis yod
NK122(kho)002:4179: de ston byed kyi mkhan po slob dpon med par
NK122(kho)002:4180: rang bzhin gyis log pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:4181: gzhan gyis rkyen gyis log pa dang gnyis so //
NK122(kho)002:4184: rang bzhin gyis log pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:4186: dang po rang bzhin gyis log par de yang mi
NK122(kho)002:4187: dge ba bskul pa'i skyon med kyang sngon gyi las
NK122(kho)002:4188: mi dge ba byed pa'i rgyu mthun gyi sbyangs pas
NK122(kho)002:4189: yang dag pa'i lta ba las log par 'dzin pa
NK122(kho)002:4190: ste / dge sdig gi las rgyu 'bras dang tshe
NK122(kho)002:4191: snga phyir snang ba de dag thams cad gdod ma
NK122(kho)002:4193: da ltar gyi snang ba 'di ni glo bur ba
NK122(kho)002:4194: sho mang spang la rdol ba ltar rgyu rkyen med
NK122(kho)002:4195: par rang shugs kyis snang bar 'dod la /
NK122(kho)002:4196: de bzhin du phyi snod kyi 'jig rten nang bcud
NK122(kho)002:4197: kyi sems can kun la yang rgyun med par de
NK122(kho)002:4198: ltar rtog pa'o // rkyen gyis log pa'o //
NK122(kho)002:4200: gnyis pa rkyen gyis log pa ni /
NK122(kho)002:4201: mu stegs kyi ston pa drug gsum bco brgyad rnams yin te /
NK122(kho)002:4202: de yang rtog ge pa drug /
NK122(kho)002:4204: snyoms par 'jug pa drug dang bco brgyad do //
NK122(kho)002:4205: de yang grangs su sbyar na /
NK122(kho)002:4207: la sogs kyi sgras ston pa gzhan bsdu ba ni /
NK122(kho)002:4208: kun tu rgyu gnag lhas kyi bu dang /
NK122(kho)002:4209: yang dag rgyal ba can dang /
NK122(kho)002:4210: mi pham skra'i lwa ba can dang /
NK122(kho)002:4211: ka ta yi'i bu nog can dang /
NK122(kho)002:4212: gcer bu pa gnyen gyi bu ste rtog ge ba drug dang /
NK122(kho)002:4219: bram ze'i rjes su sgrogs pa drug dang /
NK122(kho)002:4222: kun tu rgyu rab bzang dang /
NK122(kho)002:4224: drang srong nyon mongs med dang /
NK122(kho)002:4225: lteng rgyas 'od srungs te snyoms par 'jug pa drug dang bco brgyad do //
NK122(kho)002:4226: mu stegs kyi ston pa 'di rnams ni /
NK122(kho)002:4227: sngon sangs rgyas 'od srung gi bstan pa rgas ka'i dus kyi mu stegs pa rnams yin no //
NK122(kho)002:4228: mu stegs kyi ston pa drug gsum bco brgyad po
NK122(kho)002:4229: 'di dag gi rjes su 'brang nas lta ba ngan
NK122(kho)002:4230: pa chad lta nag 'byams yongs su 'dzin pa ste
NK122(kho)002:4231: / de yang rgyu dkar po dge ba dang /
NK122(kho)002:4232: nag po mi dge ba la rnam smin gyi 'bras
NK122(kho)002:4233: bu med par smra zhing da lta'i snang ba rgyu
NK122(kho)002:4234: rkyen med par glo bur du skyes la /
NK122(kho)002:4235: shi nas kyang glo bur du thim ste /
NK122(kho)002:4236: phyi ma med pa'i chad par lta ba'o //
NK122(kho)002:4237: phur bus bstan pa'i mdo las /
NK122(kho)002:4238: bzang mo ma shi bar du bde bar mdzod /
NK122(kho)002:4239: shi nas de'i spyod yul min //
NK122(kho)002:4240: lus kyang thal ba bzhin song nas //
NK122(kho)002:4241: slar skye ba lta ga la yod //
NK122(kho)002:4243: skye ba phyi ma yod zer ba rdzun ste mi bden /
NK122(kho)002:4244: skye ba phyis len par brjod pa ni /
NK122(kho)002:4245: dper na thang po che la spyang ku'i rjes bcad pa dang mtshungs te /
NK122(kho)002:4246: rtsar phyin pa su yang med zer nas //
NK122(kho)002:4247: mang ston pas ni mang bstan pa //
NK122(kho)002:4248: spyang ku dag gi rjes bcad 'dra //
NK122(kho)002:4250: mang ston ces pa ni sangs rgyas yin la /
NK122(kho)002:4251: mang bstan zhes pa ni las rgyu 'bras tshe snga phyi yod zer ba rdzun yin /
NK122(kho)002:4252: ma mthong smra ba spyang ku'i rjes dang 'dra /
NK122(kho)002:4254: sngon 'tsho ba ma rnyed pa'i mi g.yo can gcig gis grong khyer gcig gi srang mdo na /
NK122(kho)002:4255: spyang ku'i rjes chen po mang du bris nas mi
NK122(kho)002:4256: sde rnams la srin po spyang ku'i lus can zhes
NK122(kho)002:4257: bya ba 'ong nas mi kun za bar byed do
NK122(kho)002:4258: // de bzlog pa'i rim gro la zas nor rnams
NK122(kho)002:4259: sgo rgyab tu bor la zhag bdun la phyi rol
NK122(kho)002:4260: du ma lta bar nang du gab par gyis shig
NK122(kho)002:4261: ces smras nas gzhan gyis de bzhin du byas pa'i
NK122(kho)002:4262: rjes la kho zas nor thams cad phyogs gzhan du
NK122(kho)002:4264: sa phyogs de na spyang ku bas spyang ki'i rjes kyang yod pa ma yin pa ltar /
NK122(kho)002:4265: dge sbyong goo ta mas bsnyen bkur 'dod nas las rgyu 'bras dang tshe snga phyi yod do zhes /
NK122(kho)002:4266: khyim bdag la sogs pa 'khor rnams skrag par byas nas /
NK122(kho)002:4267: bsnyen bkur len par byed pa yin no //
NK122(kho)002:4268: las rgyu 'bras tshe snga phyi yod pa ma yin zhes brjod do //
NK122(kho)002:4269: sems ni 'byung ba'i dngas ma yin par 'dod do //
NK122(kho)002:4270: gtan tshig de'i phyir na yang skye ba snga ma
NK122(kho)002:4271: dang phyi ma med par smra ba de nyid rang
NK122(kho)002:4272: gi grub mtha' yin par 'dod do //
NK122(kho)002:4273: mu rtug gi nges tshig gi /
NK122(kho)002:4275: mu rtug pa de'i sgra don ni /
NK122(kho)002:4276: phyi ma med phyir mu rtug ste /
NK122(kho)002:4278: tshe snga phyi las rgyu 'bras thams cad med par 'dod pa ni /
NK122(kho)002:4279: log lta'i nang nas chad lta nag 'byams su smra ba yin /
NK122(kho)002:4280: dper na sa brkos pa brag la thug pa bzhin
NK122(kho)002:4281: du slar brkos pas mi thub pas tshe snga phyi
NK122(kho)002:4282: las rgyu 'bras mtho ris dang ngan song thams cad
NK122(kho)002:4283: kyang / 'dir snang ba ma gtogs pa gzhan med do zer nas phyogs gcig par blta ba'o //
NK122(kho)002:4284: mu stegs pa la gnyis te /
NK122(kho)002:4289: mu stegs pa'i lta ba ni mdo'i chos skad du
NK122(kho)002:4290: bye brag nang tshan bzhi ru shes par bya ste
NK122(kho)002:4291: / gang zhe na phra men spyod pa'i mu stegs pa ni /
NK122(kho)002:4292: mtho ris bzhed phyir mi dge ba bsgrub nas mi 'tshams pa'i bya ba byed pa'o //
NK122(kho)002:4293: dper na mgo lus mi mtshungs pas phra men ma zer ba lta bu'o //
NK122(kho)002:4294: dang zhes pa ni 'og ma sdud pa'i tshig go //
NK122(kho)002:4295: rten log 'chal ba'i mu stegs ni phya dang dbang
NK122(kho)002:4296: phyug la rten bcas nas srog gi mchod sbyin byed
NK122(kho)002:4297: pa'o // rtags tsam 'dzin pa'i mu stegs ni /
NK122(kho)002:4298: sangs rgyas kyi bstan pa rgas pa'i dus la /
NK122(kho)002:4299: nang du chos lugs bzhin mi spyod /
NK122(kho)002:4300: phyi na tshul spyod gzab pa la zer ro //
NK122(kho)002:4301: dang zhes pa ni lung phyogs brten pa'i mu stegs sdud 'dod pa'o //
NK122(kho)002:4302: mu stegs 'di ni theg pa rim dgu'i lung phyogs phra mo tsam cig 'dzin par byed /
NK122(kho)002:4303: lta ba rtag chad kyi mthar song ba'i mu stegs dgu yin no //
NK122(kho)002:4304: gong du bshad pa'i bye brag bzhi po 'di dag
NK122(kho)002:4305: gis las rgyu 'bras dang tshe snga phyi yod par
NK122(kho)002:4306: 'dod pa dang / ngan song gsum gyi 'jigs pa
NK122(kho)002:4307: las thar bar 'dod pa dang mtho ris kyi bde
NK122(kho)002:4308: 'bras rnams thob par 'dod kyang thar pa la bdag
NK122(kho)002:4309: med rtogs dgos pa la lta ba log pa rtag
NK122(kho)002:4310: chad du song nas lta ba phyin ci log dang
NK122(kho)002:4311: 'dod pa dang / / spyod pa ni srog gi
NK122(kho)002:4312: mchod sbyin la sogs pa byed pas lta spyod ya
NK122(kho)002:4314: bu sangs rgyas pa'i sku thob snyam pa'i zhe 'dod
NK122(kho)002:4316: kun tu tshol ba'i lam du zhugs nas 'bras bu thob par re ba'o //
NK122(kho)002:4317: rgyas par bshad pa la gsum ste /
NK122(kho)002:4319: bsam gtan las gol ba 'bras bu dang bcas pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:4320: kha cig lam tshol ba la zhugs pa brgyud nas nang pa'i lam gyi rgyud gyur pa'o //
NK122(kho)002:4325: lung gi phyogs tsam brtan pa'o //
NK122(kho)002:4326: dang po 'phra men spyod pa ni /
NK122(kho)002:4328: 'phra men spyod pa'i mu stegs pa'i mtshan nyid ni 'di lta ste /
NK122(kho)002:4329: 'bras bu thar ba 'dod cing lta ba gang zag gi bdag tu lta ba yin /
NK122(kho)002:4330: mtho ris bzhed pa'i phyir srog gcod pa la sogs pa'i mchod sbyin gyis mi dge ba bsgrub pa'o //
NK122(kho)002:4331: khyad par du phyin ci log pa bzhi la gnas te /
NK122(kho)002:4333: lus mi gtsang ba la gtsang ba /
NK122(kho)002:4334: tshor ba sdug bsngal ba la bde ba /
NK122(kho)002:4335: sems 'dus byas mi rtag pa la rtag pa /
NK122(kho)002:4336: chos bdag med pa la bdag tu blta zhing /
NK122(kho)002:4337: de bzhin du snod bcud 'di dag kun la'ang dngos por smra ba yin no //
NK122(kho)002:4338: don la 'phra men spyod pa 'di rtag par lta ba yin /
NK122(kho)002:4339: 'dod pa thar ba 'dod pa dang lta ba bdag
NK122(kho)002:4340: lta spyod pa srog gi mchod sbyin byed pa rnams
NK122(kho)002:4342: rgyu 'bras bsnol mar song ba'i phyir /
NK122(kho)002:4343: 'phra men spyod pa'i mu stegs zhes de la bya'o //
NK122(kho)002:4344: rten log 'chal ba la bzhi ste /
NK122(kho)002:4346: byang chub sems dpa' la log par rtog cing 'dzin pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:4348: rten log 'chal ba'i mu stegs pa'i mtshan nyid ni /
NK122(kho)002:4349: rgyas par bshad cing gsal bar bstan pa ni 'di lta ste /
NK122(kho)002:4350: tshangs pa dang la sogs kyi sgras dbang phyug dang
NK122(kho)002:4351: khyab 'jug dang brgya byin la sogs pa'i lha chen
NK122(kho)002:4352: dag ni bsod nams bsags pa dang lam sbyangs pa'i
NK122(kho)002:4354: sbyang stobs che bas 'jig rten la mnga' dbang brnyes shing dbang bsgyur ba'i phyir dang /
NK122(kho)002:4355: byang chub sems dpa' mthu chen po thob pa ni
NK122(kho)002:4356: sa lnga pa man chad dam kha cig gis sa
NK122(kho)002:4358: mthong lam yan chad nam yang yin pas /
NK122(kho)002:4359: 'gro ba'i don la byang chub sems dpa' de rnams
NK122(kho)002:4360: 'jig rten pa kun gyi gtso bor gyur pa'i 'jig
NK122(kho)002:4361: rten gyi lha mthu bo che'i tshul 'dzin pas bzhugs
NK122(kho)002:4362: pa ste / log lta can gyis mu stegs pas ma shes te /
NK122(kho)002:4363: 'di dag ni ph+y+wa dang dbang phyug yin zhes ming
NK122(kho)002:4364: du btags nas 'jig rten gyi lha mthu bo che
NK122(kho)002:4365: de dag byang chub sems dpa' 'a ma 'gro don
NK122(kho)002:4366: la bzhugs pa ma go nas de dag rang rgyud
NK122(kho)002:4367: du ye nas grub zin yin par smra zhing 'jig
NK122(kho)002:4368: rten thams cad kyi byed pa po bskos pa po
NK122(kho)002:4369: yin te / 'di bas lhag pa ni med ces bskur 'os dang mchod pa'i gnas byed pa'o //
NK122(kho)002:4370: 'bras bu la re bas log par spyod pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:4372: ph+y+wa dang dbang phyug de'i go 'phang thob par 'dod pa'i phyir me lnga bsten dang dbyu gu dang /
NK122(kho)002:4374: sngon mi gcig gis ba stor nas 'brog dgon pa
NK122(kho)002:4375: gcig tu 'khyams nas phyin pa la kho 'khyag pa'i
NK122(kho)002:4376: dbang gis / phyogs bzhir me dpung bzhi byas /
NK122(kho)002:4377: steng du nyi ma shar nas nyal ba la /
NK122(kho)002:4378: kho la nad tsha ba drag po gcig phog nas kho shi /
NK122(kho)002:4379: de'i rnam shes sum cu rtsa gsum na lha'i bur skyes pa de /
NK122(kho)002:4380: mu stegs kyi ston pas zag bcas kyi mngon shes kyis shes nas /
NK122(kho)002:4381: khos kyang me lnga brten pa'i dka' thub byas nas
NK122(kho)002:4382: de'i go 'phang thob 'dod pa'i ched du de ltar
NK122(kho)002:4383: du byas so // sngon drang srong sgom chen gcig
NK122(kho)002:4384: gis grong khyer du ldom bu la song ba'i tshe
NK122(kho)002:4385: kha t+wam rtse gsum cig 'chang nas mgur byas pa
NK122(kho)002:4386: du byas so // la / byis pa phru gu zhig phyam kha nas brul ba'i /
NK122(kho)002:4387: kha t+wam gi rtse la phog nas bsad pa de yang sum cu rtsa gsum na lha'i bur skyes /
NK122(kho)002:4388: de'i go 'phang thob pa'i don du dbyug gu rtse gsum dang rtse gcig pa'i dka' thub byas so //
NK122(kho)002:4389: khyi'i dka' thub zhes pa ni /
NK122(kho)002:4390: sngon khyi gcig lcags thag gis bskor nas shi ba de yang lha dbang phyug chen po la skyes /
NK122(kho)002:4391: khos kyang de ltar du dka' thub byas so //
NK122(kho)002:4392: sogs kyis sgras ba lang gi dka' thub dang /
NK122(kho)002:4394: rkang mig pa la sogs pa'i dka' thub lus sun
NK122(kho)002:4395: byung ba log pa'i brtul shugs mi 'dra ba sna
NK122(kho)002:4396: tshogs byed do // 'di rnams kyi gtam rgyud ni yi ge mang dogs pa'i phyir ma bris so //
NK122(kho)002:4397: rten logs 'chol ba'i mu stegs grangs can pa 'di
NK122(kho)002:4398: rnams la zag bcas kyi mngon shes yod pa'i rgyu
NK122(kho)002:4399: mtshan ni / dug gsum cha mnyam pa yin te /
NK122(kho)002:4400: gtso bo bem po la thim pa'i phyir /
NK122(kho)002:4401: re zhig gang zag gi bdag mngon 'gyur dag pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:4402: lo ma dang ldum bu tsam la brten te /
NK122(kho)002:4403: ri brag gam gtsang sa la gnas bca' ba dang /
NK122(kho)002:4404: srog gcod pa ma gtogs pa'i mi dge ba dgu po dang /
NK122(kho)002:4405: gsang ba'i tshig tsam la brten nas sgrub pa'i stobs kyis /
NK122(kho)002:4406: zag bcas kyi mngon shes 'char ste /
NK122(kho)002:4407: ngan song mtho ris su 'pho ba dang /
NK122(kho)002:4408: mtho ris ngan song du 'pho ba mthong /
NK122(kho)002:4409: de dag dkar nag gi las kyi 'phen pa ni mi shes pas /
NK122(kho)002:4410: 'di la byed po po gcig yod zhes rtogs ste /
NK122(kho)002:4411: slob dpon dga' rab la dris pas 'jig rten na dbang su che ba yod byas so //
NK122(kho)002:4412: des kyang 'jig rten na dbang che ba ni /
NK122(kho)002:4416: brgya byin la sogs pa yod do //
NK122(kho)002:4418: de dag gi go 'phang thob par 'dod pa'i ched
NK122(kho)002:4419: du me lnga bsten pa la sogs pa'i brtul shugs
NK122(kho)002:4420: sna tshogs spyod pa yin no //
NK122(kho)002:4421: rgyu 'bras log par lta ba dang /
NK122(kho)002:4423: lta ba ni dug gsum cha mnyam pa yin /
NK122(kho)002:4424: dug gsum ni rdul las gyur pa 'dod chags dang /
NK122(kho)002:4425: mun pa las gyur pa gti mug dang /
NK122(kho)002:4426: snying stobs las gyur pa zhe sdang dag gi bye brag las /
NK122(kho)002:4427: de gsum po cha mnyam na gtso bo bem po la thim pas skye ba mi len te /
NK122(kho)002:4428: mthar thug gi 'bras bu yin par smra /
NK122(kho)002:4429: cha mi mnyam na rgyu sems can du 'gro bar 'dod pa yin te /
NK122(kho)002:4430: de yang de gsum cha mnyam na bdag dag ste /
NK122(kho)002:4431: cha mi mnyam pa'i dbang gis bdag dag par ma nus pas /
NK122(kho)002:4432: slar khams gsum sems can du snang ba ni /
NK122(kho)002:4433: snying stobs shas che na dmyal ba /
NK122(kho)002:4434: mun pa shas che na byol song /
NK122(kho)002:4435: rdul shas che na yi dwags /
NK122(kho)002:4438: mun pa chung bas lha min du snang ste /
NK122(kho)002:4440: don la dug gsum cha mnyam pa 'di /
NK122(kho)002:4441: ma dag pa kun gyi lhan cig skyes pa'i ma
NK122(kho)002:4442: rig pa gti mug lung ma bstan pa yin la
NK122(kho)002:4443: / mu stegs grangs can pa des 'di'i ngo bo
NK122(kho)002:4444: la gzung 'dzin mngon 'gyur mi snang snyam nas mthar
NK122(kho)002:4445: thug gi 'bras bu chos sku yin par 'dod pa'o
NK122(kho)002:4447: grangs can pa'i ston pa zhes kyang bya /
NK122(kho)002:4448: drang srong ser skya'i rjes su 'brang ba chos thams
NK122(kho)002:4449: cad de tsam nyi shu rtsa lngar 'dod pa dang
NK122(kho)002:4450: / de shes pas grol ba'i tshul lo //
NK122(kho)002:4451: dang po la dbye ba'i dngos po dang /
NK122(kho)002:4456: dbang po bcu gcig /'byung ba lnga /
NK122(kho)002:4457: de tsam lnga ste nyer bzhi /
NK122(kho)002:4458: bdag rtag pa shes rig gi skyes bu ste nyer lnga'o //
NK122(kho)002:4462: snying stobs gsum cha mnyam pa'o //
NK122(kho)002:4463: de gsum cha mi mnyam pa las rnam 'gyur te /
NK122(kho)002:4464: de la chen po zhes bya ba ni /
NK122(kho)002:4465: shel gyi khang pa ltar gzugs brnyan 'char ba'i gzhi yin te /
NK122(kho)002:4466: phyi nas gzugs sgra la sogs pa rnam 'gyur gyi gzugs brnyan 'char la /
NK122(kho)002:4467: nang nas gtso bo'i gzugs brnyan 'char ba'o //
NK122(kho)002:4469: bdag yul la longs spyod ces smra ba'o //
NK122(kho)002:4470: rdul mun pa snying stobs gsum las gyur pa la /
NK122(kho)002:4472: rdul zhe sdang las gyur pa dbang po bcu gcig ste /
NK122(kho)002:4483: chu so ste las dbang lnga dang /
NK122(kho)002:4484: thun mong du gyur pa'i yid do //
NK122(kho)002:4485: snying stobs las gyur pa bcu ste /
NK122(kho)002:4486: sa chu me rlung nam mkha' ste /
NK122(kho)002:4488: gzugs sgra dri ro reg bya dang /
NK122(kho)002:4490: mun pa las gyur pa ni de gnyis kyi grogs
NK122(kho)002:4491: byed pa las 'bras bu logs su mi bskyed par
NK122(kho)002:4492: 'dod / de yang rnam 'gyur gyi chos rnams gtso bo'i rang bzhin gcig tu yod pas /
NK122(kho)002:4493: rgyu la 'bras bu gnas zhes bya ste /
NK122(kho)002:4494: rgyu 'jim pa las 'bras bu bum pa grub /
NK122(kho)002:4495: rtsa mchog la glang grub zer ro //
NK122(kho)002:4496: de yang med pa la mi 'byung ba yin pa
NK122(kho)002:4497: la rgyu rkyen gyis 'bras bu 'byung gi 'dug pa'i
NK122(kho)002:4498: phyir / de'ang rnam 'gyur gyi dngos po rnams gtso bo'i rang bzhin du yod pa la /
NK122(kho)002:4499: de mi gsal ba gsal bar byed pas rang las rang skye zhes bya'o //
NK122(kho)002:4502: gtso bo'i rang bzhin du thim ste mi gsal bar 'gyur ba'o //
NK122(kho)002:4503: de'ang dbang phyug nag po'i rgyud las /
NK122(kho)002:4504: rang bzhin las chen de la nga rgyal ste //
NK122(kho)002:4505: de las tshogs ni rnam pa bcu drug byung //
NK122(kho)002:4506: de tsam lnga las 'byung ba rnam lnga byung //
NK122(kho)002:4508: rnam 'gyur gyi chos nyi shu rtsa gcig la longs spyod pa ni /
NK122(kho)002:4509: bdag rtag pa shes rig gi skyes bu yin /
NK122(kho)002:4514: de yang 'gro ba'i spyod yul du ma gyur pas dngos su mi snang zhes bya'o //
NK122(kho)002:4515: slob dpon dga' rab kyi zhal nas //
NK122(kho)002:4516: la la yon tan gsum rang bzhin //
NK122(kho)002:4521: shes bya'i sgo nas rnam par bzhag pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:4522: rang bzhin dang rnam 'gyur gyis dang /
NK122(kho)002:4524: don dam kun rdzob kyis so //
NK122(kho)002:4526: bdag ni shes pa kho na la //
NK122(kho)002:4527: gzhan rnams shes par bya ba'o //
NK122(kho)002:4530: gtso bo ni rang bzhin kho na'o //
NK122(kho)002:4532: de tsam lnga ste bdun ni /
NK122(kho)002:4535: 'byung ba lnga ste bcu drug ni rnam 'gyur ro //
NK122(kho)002:4536: bdag shes rig gi skyes bu ni /
NK122(kho)002:4538: de la dbang phyug chen po'i gzhung las /
NK122(kho)002:4539: gtso bo rang bzhin nyid dang ni //
NK122(kho)002:4540: chen po bdun sogs rang bzhin dang //
NK122(kho)002:4542: skyes bu rang bzhin 'gyur ba min //
NK122(kho)002:4545: gtso bo ni rgyu yin la /
NK122(kho)002:4547: bdag ni gnyis ka ma yin cing longs spyod pa'o //
NK122(kho)002:4549: bdag dang gtso bo don dam dang /
NK122(kho)002:4552: yon tan gsum gyi rang bzhin mchog /
NK122(kho)002:4553: mthong ba'i lam du 'gyur ma yin //
NK122(kho)002:4554: mthong ba'i lam du gang gyur pa //
NK122(kho)002:4555: sgyu ma bzhin du shin tu gsog /
NK122(kho)002:4558: de tsam nyi shu rtsa lnga'i don shes na grol bar 'dod pa ste /
NK122(kho)002:4559: de tsam nyi shu lnga shes na //
NK122(kho)002:4560: ral pa'am spyi bo cod pan nam //
NK122(kho)002:4561: cha lugs gang ltar gnas kyang rung //
NK122(kho)002:4564: nang pa'i gsang sngags phyi nang la gol ba dang /
NK122(kho)002:4565: chos thams cad sems nyid rang snang las byung ba /
NK122(kho)002:4566: chos dang rgyu 'bras gnyis su med cing /
NK122(kho)002:4567: rang rig mtha' dbus phyi nang med par bstan pa
NK122(kho)002:4568: ma go bar thams cad sems las byung ba dang
NK122(kho)002:4571: rig pa ye shes yin pa'i lung phyogs re la
NK122(kho)002:4572: dam par bzung nas gong ltar log par go ba
NK122(kho)002:4573: ni zhar byung gi mu stegs pa'o //
NK122(kho)002:4574: rten log 'chal ba'i nges tshig go //
NK122(kho)002:4576: dkon mchog rin chen rnam gsum la /
NK122(kho)002:4578: rten log pa ni 'jig rten gyi ph+y+wa dang dbang phyug la byas nas /
NK122(kho)002:4579: dngos por brtag pa'i 'jig rten gyi lhar skyabs tshol
NK122(kho)002:4580: ste rten 'cha' bas de dag mchod par bya ba'i
NK122(kho)002:4581: phyir / skye 'gro du ma'i srog gcod pa'i mchod sbyin ste /
NK122(kho)002:4582: 'chal ba'i spyod pa sna tshogs byed pa'o //
NK122(kho)002:4583: de la 'dir gsang sngags pas lha la brten nas rig pa'i rtsal spyod /
NK122(kho)002:4585: gnyis med rang grol du rtogs par bya ba'i thabs la /
NK122(kho)002:4586: de ltar ma go bar lha rang rgyud dngos por bzung nas /
NK122(kho)002:4587: gong ltar gol pa yang yod do //
NK122(kho)002:4588: de yang mu stegs pa des thob bya'i 'bras bu mtho ris kyi thar pa mi thob ste /
NK122(kho)002:4589: ngan song gsum gyi sdug bsngal can du phal cher gzhol ba /
NK122(kho)002:4590: de la ni rten log 'chal ba'i mtshan nyid bya ba yin no //
NK122(kho)002:4591: rtags tsam 'dzin pa la drug ste /
NK122(kho)002:4593: gol gzhi gzugs brnyan gyi chos dang /
NK122(kho)002:4595: rtags tsam 'dzin pa mu stegs pa'i mtshan nyid ni 'di ltar yin te /
NK122(kho)002:4596: sprul pa'i sku snga ma sangs rgyas 'od srungs 'das
NK122(kho)002:4597: pa de'i bstan pa'i snyigs mar bab cing gyur pa'i
NK122(kho)002:4598: tshe / bstan pa de'i gzugs brnyan gyi chos la /
NK122(kho)002:4599: de yang rang dgar zhugs pas lta ba sna tshogs byung ba dang /
NK122(kho)002:4601: bla ma dang slob dpon mi bsten par rang dgar
NK122(kho)002:4602: 'jug 'dod g.yo can rlom bcas kyi blo cung zad
NK122(kho)002:4603: yod pa'i phyir thos bsam sgom gsum gyi shes rab
NK122(kho)002:4604: gsum la ma sbyangs pas ste /
NK122(kho)002:4605: de yang thos pas phyi'i sgro 'dog ma bcad /
NK122(kho)002:4606: bsam pas nang gi 'khrul pa'i rtsa ba ma bcad /
NK122(kho)002:4607: bsgom pas bde bar gshegs pa'i dgongs pa ma lon pa'o //
NK122(kho)002:4608: bstan pa yi zab don gyi chos la rang bzo'i rtog dpyod byas nas /
NK122(kho)002:4610: don dam bden pa gnyis kyi brjod bya'i don de rtog dpyod kyis ma phig pas /
NK122(kho)002:4611: zab mo'i bka' la rang gi zhe 'dod kyis zhen phyogs su lung drangs shes pa'o //
NK122(kho)002:4613: ring byed kyi bu lhag spyod dang sgyu rtsal shes
NK122(kho)002:4614: kyi bu ring phur la sogs pa'i mu stegs kyi
NK122(kho)002:4615: ston pa drug gsum bco brgyad zhes bya ba lta
NK122(kho)002:4616: ba dang grub mtha' log par smra ba mang du
NK122(kho)002:4617: byung ngo // bsdus na rtag chad gnyis su 'dus pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:4620: la la rgyu 'bras 'gog pa yis zhes pa ni /
NK122(kho)002:4621: las rgyu 'bras tshe snga phyi thams cad 'gog nas med pa ste /
NK122(kho)002:4622: nyi tshe'i stong pa chad lta kho nar bltas so //
NK122(kho)002:4623: la las yod par rnam par brtag pa yis 'bras
NK122(kho)002:4624: bu rtag par rtog pa'i blta bas rang rgyud dngos
NK122(kho)002:4625: po mtshan mar smra ba ste 'di rtag lta ba'i
NK122(kho)002:4626: 'dod pa'o // log rtog gi dpyod pas bka'i don mi phig pa'i phyir /
NK122(kho)002:4627: lta ba ngan pa 'dzin pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:4629: de dag gis bka'i don ci'i phyir ma rtogs zhe
NK122(kho)002:4630: na bde bar gshegs pa'i bstan pa'i gsung rab 'di
NK122(kho)002:4631: rnams ni rgya mtsho ltar dgongs pa'i gting zab cing
NK122(kho)002:4632: sa gzhi ltar spyod pa rgya che /
NK122(kho)002:4633: dgongs pa sna tshogs ston pas na gang zag gis
NK122(kho)002:4634: mi rig ste dpag dka' bas rang gis yin snyam
NK122(kho)002:4635: gyi dpyod pas bka' zab mo'i don ma phig ste
NK122(kho)002:4636: log pa'i lta ba rtag chad sna tshogs 'dzin pa'o
NK122(kho)002:4637: // rtags tsam 'dzin pa'i nges tshig dang /
NK122(kho)002:4639: rtags tsam 'dzin pa'i mu stegs pa de'i sems ni log pa'i lam du zhugs te /
NK122(kho)002:4640: rtag chad kyi don la gnas shing nyon mongs pa rang khar spyod par byed pa'o //
NK122(kho)002:4641: chos gos rnam gsum la sogs pa lus kyis sangs rgyas kyi tshul rtags 'dzin pas /
NK122(kho)002:4642: rtags tsam 'dzin pa'i mu stegs pa zhes de la bya /
NK122(kho)002:4643: bstan pa 'jig pa'i tshe rtags tsam 'dzin pa rang gi phyogs la yod pa 'o //
NK122(kho)002:4645: sprul sku sh+aakya seng+ge'i bstan pa rgas te 'jig la nye bas /
NK122(kho)002:4646: snyigs ma lnga'i dus deng sang la bab ste /
NK122(kho)002:4647: gang gis rtags tsam 'dzin pa'i 'gro ba de /
NK122(kho)002:4648: deng sang nang pa sangs rgyas pa'i nang na shin tu mang bar gsungs so //
NK122(kho)002:4649: de yang lang kar gshegs pa las /
NK122(kho)002:4650: nga yi bstan pa sum 'byin pa //
NK122(kho)002:4651: ngur smrig gi ni go bgos shing //
NK122(kho)002:4652: 'bras bu yod dang med smra ba //
NK122(kho)002:4653: byis sba'i gzugs can rang bzhin 'byung //
NK122(kho)002:4654: 'bras bu med smra'i lta ngan gyis //
NK122(kho)002:4655: skye bo mang po brlag par byed //
NK122(kho)002:4657: lung gi phyogs tsam 'dzin pa la gsum ste /
NK122(kho)002:4658: bka' las gol tshul spyir bstan pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:4659: bye brag bzhis mdor bstan pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:4663: bde bar gshegs pa'i gsung sde snod gsum dang rgyud
NK122(kho)002:4664: sde bzhi'i lung gi phyogs phra ba tsam cig 'dzin
NK122(kho)002:4665: par byed cing lta ba rtag chad kyi mthar song
NK122(kho)002:4666: ba'i mu stegs pa de dag gi mtshan nyid rgyas
NK122(kho)002:4667: par bshad cing gsal bar bstan pa ni 'di lta
NK122(kho)002:4668: ste / rgyal ba sangs rgyas kyi bka'i sgra'i rjes
NK122(kho)002:4669: su 'brang pa'i zhor byung gi theg pa yin pa'i
NK122(kho)002:4670: ste / phyir / phyogs ni cung zad mthun pa
NK122(kho)002:4671: tsam gyi lta ba log pa ste theg pa dgu'i
NK122(kho)002:4672: grangs dang mthun pa tsam las don nor bar song
NK122(kho)002:4673: ste / phyir / nas / rang gi 'dod pa'i
NK122(kho)002:4674: zhen phyogs kyis 'khrul pa'i lam du zhugs nas de'i
NK122(kho)002:4675: nga rgyal gyis snyems pas de las bzlog par dka'
NK122(kho)002:4676: ste / phyir / nas / ba'o // gnyis pa mdor bstan pa ni /
NK122(kho)002:4678: lung gi phyogs tsam 'dzin pa'i mu stegs pa de
NK122(kho)002:4679: la yang mdo skad kyis bye brag rnam pa bzhi
NK122(kho)002:4681: nyan rang gnyis la gol ba phyi rol pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:4682: byang sems la gol ba yang dag pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:4683: phyi rgyud gsum la gol ba gsang sngags pa dang
NK122(kho)002:4684: nang pa rnam gsum la gol ba gsang chen pa
NK122(kho)002:4685: dang bzhi ste / 'di dag re re la'ang bye brag gsum gsum du phye ste /
NK122(kho)002:4686: theg pa dgu la gol ba'i mu stegs dgu yin no //
NK122(kho)002:4688: gang zag gsum gol gzhi gsum las cha mthun log par rtogs pa phyi rol pa rgyas pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:4694: phyi rol pa la'ang rnam pa gsum ste /
NK122(kho)002:4696: 'dir bshad gzhi cig drang na go bde ba yin pas /
NK122(kho)002:4697: log par song ces pa bshad pa'i gzhir drangs /
NK122(kho)002:4698: de'i khyad par gyi chos la gsum /
NK122(kho)002:4700: mu stegs pa bye brag pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:4702: rang snang phyogs gcig pa zhes bya ba de gsum log par song /
NK122(kho)002:4703: gang las log par song na /
NK122(kho)002:4704: nyan thos bye brag pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:4705: mdo sde pa dang rang sangs rgyas kyi lta ba
NK122(kho)002:4706: las log par song tshul ci ltar du log par
NK122(kho)002:4707: song na cha mthun tsam las log par song ba'o
NK122(kho)002:4708: // 'di dag gi don rgyas par bshad cing gsal bar bstan pa la /
NK122(kho)002:4709: mu stegs bye brag pa'i lta ba ni /
NK122(kho)002:4710: yul sems gnyis la 'brel ba med pas bye brag tu smra ba yin /
NK122(kho)002:4711: phyi bzung ba'i yul rdul phra rab sil bu dus gsum rdzas yod du rtag par 'dod /
NK122(kho)002:4712: nang 'dzin pa'i sems skad cig cha shas dang bral ba la gol nas /
NK122(kho)002:4713: bdag rtag pa shes rig gi skyes bu zhes bya ba zhig 'dod do //
NK122(kho)002:4714: tha snyad pa'i lta ba ni /
NK122(kho)002:4715: gzhal bya gzhal byed kyis 'brel ba'i phyir nyan thos mdo sde pa las gol ste /
NK122(kho)002:4716: phyi bzung ba'i yul ni rdul 'dus pa'i rang bzhin po ti'i gras kha ltar rtag par 'dod /
NK122(kho)002:4717: nang gi sems ni bye brag pa dang mthun no //
NK122(kho)002:4720: dka' thub bye brag pa rnams dang /
NK122(kho)002:4721: lus ba glang gi lci bas byug cing 'dag chal gyis khrus byed pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:4722: rdzas can gyi gser dngul la sogs pa la gcod pa dang reg par mi byed do //
NK122(kho)002:4724: bdag de dag par bya ba'i phyir //
NK122(kho)002:4725: shes pa yul la mi spro zhing //
NK122(kho)002:4726: de nyid la ni brtan pa'o //
NK122(kho)002:4727: rang snang phyogs gcig pa ni /
NK122(kho)002:4728: rang sangs rgyas kyi lta ba phyi'i yul ma grub
NK122(kho)002:4729: cing nang 'dzin pa'i sems skad cig rang gsal de
NK122(kho)002:4730: las gol ste / phyi yul la rtog dpyod mi byed nas stong pa phyang chad du 'dod do //
NK122(kho)002:4731: nang 'dzin pa'i sems rig pa rdzas grub dkar la 'tsher ba /
NK122(kho)002:4733: spyod pa ni gong ma gnyis dang mthun /
NK122(kho)002:4734: khyad par du gcig pur gnas pa'o //
NK122(kho)002:4735: yang dag pa la gnyis te /
NK122(kho)002:4737: gang zag gsum gol gzhi gsum las cha mthun log par rtog pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:4739: gong gi phyi rol pa las lhag par 'dod pas na yang dag pa zhes bya'o //
NK122(kho)002:4740: de yang rnam pa gsum ste /
NK122(kho)002:4741: log ces pa bshad pa'i gzhir drangs /
NK122(kho)002:4742: de'i khyad par gyi chos la bzhi ste /
NK122(kho)002:4744: mu stegs phra ba pa dang za ba pa dang rgya che yang pa gsum po 'di dag log /
NK122(kho)002:4746: sems tsam rnam bden pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:4747: rnam rdzun pa dang dbu ma chen po'i lta ba las log par song /
NK122(kho)002:4748: tshul ci ltar du song na /
NK122(kho)002:4749: spyod pa phyogs mthun tsam du zhugs /
NK122(kho)002:4750: lta ba cha mthun tsam gyis log par song /
NK122(kho)002:4752: phra ba ni rnam bden pa las gol ba yin te /
NK122(kho)002:4753: sems nang gi bdag rtag pas yul byed pa byed mkhan gyi ngo bor bden par 'dod /
NK122(kho)002:4754: gzhan yang yul du snang ba shing la sogs pa rnams la sems yod pa yin te /
NK122(kho)002:4755: lpags pa bshus na skam pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:4757: mtshan mo lo 'dab 'khum zhing 'dug pa'i phyir ces zer ro //
NK122(kho)002:4759: rnam rdzun pa las gol ba yin te /
NK122(kho)002:4760: phyi yul gyi rnam pa rdzun te chad lta la shor ba'o //
NK122(kho)002:4761: nang 'dzin pa'i sems rang rig rang gsal dkar la
NK122(kho)002:4762: 'tsher ba snum la 'dril ba sems can gyi lus
NK122(kho)002:4763: dang sbyar ba / che ba sran rdog tsam /
NK122(kho)002:4765: yang chung rdul phran tsam du yod par 'dod /
NK122(kho)002:4767: dbu ma chen po'i lta ba las gol ba yin te /
NK122(kho)002:4768: 'gro ba sems can gyi shes rgyud bdag chen po gcig yin gyis /
NK122(kho)002:4769: de yang rig pa mu mtha' med cing dngos po yod med las grol ba /
NK122(kho)002:4770: 'gro ba kun la gnyis su med par khyab pa'i bdag rtag pa chen po gcig yin la /
NK122(kho)002:4771: sems rgyud tha dad par snang ba ni /
NK122(kho)002:4772: srog lus du ma 'khrul ba'i dbang gis bdag gzhan tha dad du bzung ba'o //
NK122(kho)002:4773: de yang dper na phyi'i nam mkha' chen po de /
NK122(kho)002:4774: bum pa la sogs snod tha dad pa'i rkyen gyis /
NK122(kho)002:4775: nam mkha' chung ngur bkol ling du chad la /
NK122(kho)002:4776: de yang bum pa chags nas nam mkha' chen por thim pa'o //
NK122(kho)002:4777: de bzhin du rnal 'byor pas lam bgrod pas bdag
NK122(kho)002:4778: tha dad du 'dzin pa zad pas srog gi dbang
NK122(kho)002:4780: dngos po yod med las grol ba'i bdag gcig tu thim nas thar bar 'dod pa'o //
NK122(kho)002:4781: 'di'i 'dod pa ni 'og rgyal thob pa'i skabs su sbyor /
NK122(kho)002:4782: de ni cha mthun tsam gyi lta ba log lugs yin /
NK122(kho)002:4784: sems can la byams snying rje cung zhig bsgom nas /
NK122(kho)002:4785: sems can la gnod 'tshe spang ba'o //
NK122(kho)002:4786: bdag nyid ma spangs pa'i skyon no //
NK122(kho)002:4788: mu stegs de rnams kyi lta ba ci tsam zab pa'i tshig brjod kyang /
NK122(kho)002:4789: phra ba chos kyi bdag dang /
NK122(kho)002:4790: rags pa gang zag gi bdag 'dzin gnyis po ma
NK122(kho)002:4791: spangs pas bsgom pa bsam gtan nor ba'i lam du
NK122(kho)002:4792: zhugs te mtho ris thob ste thar pa byang chub
NK122(kho)002:4793: mi thob pa'o // rtsa ba drug po 'di las
NK122(kho)002:4794: gyes pa'i rgyu'i theg pa rnams dang cha mthun tsam
NK122(kho)002:4795: mi thob pa'o // gyi / log pa'i lta ba du ma sna tshogs 'byung bar bshad do //
NK122(kho)002:4798: gang zag gsum gyis phyi rgyud gsum la cha mthun log par rtog pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:4800: 'di ni gsang sngags las gol bas gsang sngags pa zhes bya'o //
NK122(kho)002:4802: log ces pa bshad pa'i gzhir drangs /
NK122(kho)002:4805: mu stegs rig byed pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:4807: rig sbyor ba dang gsum log /
NK122(kho)002:4809: bya ba spyod pa rnal 'byor las log /
NK122(kho)002:4810: tshul ci ltar du log na /
NK122(kho)002:4811: lta ba spyod pa bsam gtan dag bya spyod rnal
NK122(kho)002:4812: 'byor gsum dang cha tsam mthun ste don las log
NK122(kho)002:4814: de la rig byed pa'i lta ba ni kri ya lha drug bskyed pa las gol te /
NK122(kho)002:4816: rgyu rkyen las 'das pa'i ye grub rtag pa chen po de ni tshangs pa yin te /
NK122(kho)002:4817: 'jig rten 'di dag med pa'i dus na /
NK122(kho)002:4818: tshangs pa chen pos sprul pa'i sgo nga zhig byung /
NK122(kho)002:4819: de bcag pa'i nang nas stong gsum gyi stong chen
NK122(kho)002:4820: po'i 'jig rten gyi khams phyi nang snod bcud thams
NK122(kho)002:4821: cad byung bar 'dod pa'i rtag lta chen po gcig
NK122(kho)002:4822: tu 'dod do // rig spyod pa ni /
NK122(kho)002:4823: spyod pa'i rgyud las gol te /
NK122(kho)002:4824: 'jig rten 'di dag khyab 'jug gis byas pa'i rtag pa gcig tu 'dod do //
NK122(kho)002:4825: de yang mdzad pa bcur snang bas kun la khyab ste /
NK122(kho)002:4826: gser gyi ru sbal du snang bas /
NK122(kho)002:4827: snod bcud rten dang brten pa'i gzhi byas /
NK122(kho)002:4828: phag tu snang bas 'jig rten gyi mi gtsang ba'i ljan ljin thams cad dag par byas /
NK122(kho)002:4829: rma byar snang nas sman gyi nus pa bskyed pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:4830: dug gi nus pa sel bar byas /
NK122(kho)002:4831: ne tsor snang bas bem rig thams cad kyi grags
NK122(kho)002:4832: pa sgra'i nus pa dang bye brag thams cad byas
NK122(kho)002:4833: so // mdung thung du snang nas bsad cing med pa'i las thams cad byas /
NK122(kho)002:4834: skyes bur snang ba sh+aakya thub pa nyid kyang yin /
NK122(kho)002:4835: gzhan yang mun par snang ba dang /
NK122(kho)002:4836: seng ger snang bas kha nas 'od zer spros zhing nyi zla gsal bar thams cad byas /
NK122(kho)002:4837: tho ba mtshon cha'i mdzad pas lha ma yin gyi g.yul ngo bzlog par byas /
NK122(kho)002:4838: rtag pa chen po 'dis ni kun la khyab ste /
NK122(kho)002:4839: 'di thob par bya ba'i phyir de nyid kyi bzlas sgom mchod bstod la brtson par bya'o //
NK122(kho)002:4840: gzhan yang khyab 'jug gi sprul pa bcu ni /
NK122(kho)002:4842: nya dang ru sbal phag rgod dang //
NK122(kho)002:4844: ra ma gnyis dang nag pa dang //
NK122(kho)002:4845: sangs rgyas kar ko tse dang bcu //
NK122(kho)002:4847: 'di rnams kyi gtam rgyud rgyas par bshad rgyu yod kyang /
NK122(kho)002:4848: don chung bas ma bris so //
NK122(kho)002:4849: rig sbyor ba'i lta ba ni /
NK122(kho)002:4850: rgyu rkyen dang bral ba'i ye grub chen po de ni /
NK122(kho)002:4852: kha cig dga' rab dbang phyug yin te /
NK122(kho)002:4853: snod bcud 'di dag des byas so //
NK122(kho)002:4854: de yang lo thog skye 'khrungs dang /
NK122(kho)002:4860: nam mkhas go skabs 'byed por byed pa'o //
NK122(kho)002:4862: rig byed kyi smrang bzhi 'don zhing khrus dang /
NK122(kho)002:4864: dka' thub dka' spyad la brtson pa'o //
NK122(kho)002:4865: lta ba spyod pa de ltar byas kyang 'khor ba las mi 'da' 'o //
NK122(kho)002:4867: bdag tu 'dzin pa la zhen cing de'i dbang gis
NK122(kho)002:4868: gzung 'dzin gyi 'khrul pa'i mtha' la zhen pa rnams
NK122(kho)002:4869: kyi bde gshegs sprul sku'i rnams rigs lnga thub drug
NK122(kho)002:4870: rigs gsum mgon po skur snang ba las /
NK122(kho)002:4872: thams cad kyi byed pa po ph+y+wa dang dbang phyug dag tu 'khrul nas /
NK122(kho)002:4873: de thob pa'i thabs la rig byed kyis smra ba bzhi 'dod pa'o //
NK122(kho)002:4875: nges brjod kyi rig byed dang /
NK122(kho)002:4876: snyan ngag gi rigs byed dang /
NK122(kho)002:4877: mchod sbyin gyi rig byed dang /
NK122(kho)002:4878: srid srung gi rig byed dang bzhi'o //
NK122(kho)002:4880: dus tshig gza' skar khrus gtsang sbra la brtson pa'o //
NK122(kho)002:4881: de ltar dka' thub dka' spyad ci bsgrub kyang /
NK122(kho)002:4882: skyon ni bdag 'dzin la zhen pa'i mun pa ma dngas pas bdag med ma rtogs pa'i phyir /
NK122(kho)002:4883: 'khor ba nyid du skye ba mang por brgyud de thar pa mi thob pa'o //
