NK122(kho)002:8139: goms pa mthar thug pa mthar lam yin no //
NK122(kho)002:8140: de lta bu'i bskal pa grangs med gsum nas rim gyis 'jug pa yun gyi tshad yin no //
NK122(kho)002:8141: 'di rnams kyi spyi don rgyas par bshad na /
NK122(kho)002:8142: dang po grangs med ngos bzung ba ni /
NK122(kho)002:8143: bskal phran brgyad cu la bskal chen gcig zer ro //
NK122(kho)002:8144: de la mdo phal po che dang /
NK122(kho)002:8145: rgya cher rol pa la sogs pa rnams su bshad
NK122(kho)002:8146: lugs mang du yod kyang 'dir mdo sil bu nas
NK122(kho)002:8148: grangs kyi gnas gzhan drug bcu tshun chad la grangs can du byas nas /
NK122(kho)002:8149: de phan chad la so so'i skye bo phal pas
NK122(kho)002:8150: grangs brtsi bar mi nus pa'i phyir grangs med du
NK122(kho)002:8152: de dag kyang gong bzhin gyis bskal pa chen po gcig nas bcu la /
NK122(kho)002:8154: zhes pa nas bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i bar yin te /
NK122(kho)002:8156: gcig bcu brgya stong khri 'bum dang //
NK122(kho)002:8157: bye ba sa ya dung phyur dang //
NK122(kho)002:8158: dgu po rkyang par shes par bya //
NK122(kho)002:8159: ther 'bum khrag khrig rab bkram dang //
NK122(kho)002:8160: gtam dkrigs mi 'khrug khyad phyin dang //
NK122(kho)002:8161: dpang rten ded 'dren mtha' snang dang //
NK122(kho)002:8162: rgyu rig 'ong mdzes dbang po dang //
NK122(kho)002:8164: rgya rtags stobs 'khor brda shes dang //
NK122(kho)002:8165: rnam byung rnam nyid stobs mig rnams //
NK122(kho)002:8166: nyi shu gnyis te chen po dang //
NK122(kho)002:8167: zung re brtsis pas bzhi bcu bzhi //
NK122(kho)002:8168: grangs med skye mched dpag tu med //
NK122(kho)002:8169: dpag yas gzhal med gzhal mi lang //
NK122(kho)002:8170: bsam med bsam gyis mi khyab pa'o //
NK122(kho)002:8171: de la brgyad re drug cu gcig /
NK122(kho)002:8172: zhes bya ba'i bar du yin te /
NK122(kho)002:8173: de la mdzod kyi 'grel pa rnams nas grangs kyi
NK122(kho)002:8174: gnas gzhan brgyad mdo las ma rnyed do zer yang
NK122(kho)002:8175: / don gyi drug cu rtsa gcig gi bar gsungs
NK122(kho)002:8176: 'dug pa'i phyir 'dir ming 'dogs brgyad bsnan pa yin
NK122(kho)002:8177: / no // mkhas pa 'ga' zhig gis tshad med bzhis kha bkang pa yang 'dug /
NK122(kho)002:8178: de lta bu'i bskal pa grangs med gsum gyi nang
NK122(kho)002:8179: du thub pa'i dbang po sangs rgyas par 'dod do
NK122(kho)002:8180: // gzhan bskal pa grangs med bdun dang /
NK122(kho)002:8181: sum cu rtsa gsum la sogs pa mdo du ma'i 'dod pa snang ngo //
NK122(kho)002:8182: sems bskyed pa la theg chung lugs dang /
NK122(kho)002:8186: glang po che 'dul sbyangs mkhan gyi gtam rgyud lta bu yin pas gzhan du shes par bya'o //
NK122(kho)002:8187: theg chen sems bskyed lugs mi 'dra ba mdo du ma'i 'dod pa yod de /
NK122(kho)002:8188: de la 'dir rje btsun byams pa mgon po dang /
NK122(kho)002:8189: bskal pa bzang po'i mdo yi rjes su 'brang bar bya'o //
NK122(kho)002:8190: kun rdzob sems bskyed kyi mtshan nyid ni /
NK122(kho)002:8191: sems can thams cad kyi don du dmigs pa /
NK122(kho)002:8192: yang dag par rdzogs pa'i byang chub 'dod pa /
NK122(kho)002:8193: sangs rgyas yon tan can du shes pa'i 'du shes gsum ldan gcig dgos te /
NK122(kho)002:8195: sems bskyed pas ni gzhan don phyir //
NK122(kho)002:8196: yang dag rdzogs pa'i byang chub 'dod //
NK122(kho)002:8198: de la dang po sems bskyed snga shos ni /
NK122(kho)002:8200: sngon tshe nga ni dman par gyur pa'i tshe //
NK122(kho)002:8201: de bzhin gshegs pa sh+aakya thub de la //
NK122(kho)002:8202: 'byam gong zhig ni dbul ba byas nas kyang //
NK122(kho)002:8203: dang por byang chub tu ni sems bskyed do //
NK122(kho)002:8205: de dag gi tshul yang bskal pa grangs snying rje pad+ma dkar po ltar na /
NK122(kho)002:8206: bskal pa mi 'dzin pa zhes bya bar 'jig rten
NK122(kho)002:8207: gyi khams pad+ma can zhes bya ba la 'khor los
NK122(kho)002:8208: bsgyur ba rtsibs kyi mu khyud zhes bya ba byon
NK122(kho)002:8209: / de'i tshe bdag cag gi ston pa 'di rgyal
NK122(kho)002:8210: po'i blon po bram ze rgya mtsho'i rdul zhes bya
NK122(kho)002:8211: / bar gyur to // des sras rgya mtsho snyems
NK122(kho)002:8212: bral dang lha dang mi'i gdul bya dpag tu med
NK122(kho)002:8213: / bar gyur to // pa bskul ste / sangs
NK122(kho)002:8214: rgyas kyi drung na phyag 'tshal bas de rnams sangs
NK122(kho)002:8216: bram ze khyod ma 'ongs pa'i dus na tshe lo brgya pa'i dus su /
NK122(kho)002:8217: de bzhin gshegs pa sh+aakya thub pa zhes bya bar 'gyur ro //
NK122(kho)002:8219: yang dris len bsab mdo dang /
NK122(kho)002:8220: mdo sde 'dzang blun nas dmyal ba'i yul du gyad stobs po cher skyes nas sems bskyed lugs dang /
NK122(kho)002:8221: de la sogs pa theg pa che chung gi 'dod pa mang du snang ngo //
NK122(kho)002:8222: phung po gsum pa'i mdo ltar na ston pa 'di tshong dpon gyi bu mngon dgar skyes pa na /
NK122(kho)002:8223: de bzhin gshegs can la sems bskyed par bshad do //
NK122(kho)002:8225: med pa gsum 'das pa'i gong rol du /
NK122(kho)002:8226: bskal pa'i ming ni bzang po /
NK122(kho)002:8227: 'jig rten gyi khams mi mjed ces bya ba na /
NK122(kho)002:8228: de bzhin gshegs pa sh+aakya thub pa zhes bya ba tshe lo brgya pa'i dus su byon /
NK122(kho)002:8229: de'i yab zas gtsang ma yum sgyu ma lha mdzes ma /
NK122(kho)002:8230: mchog zung ni sh+aa ri'i bu dang /
NK122(kho)002:8232: rim gro pa ni kun dga' bo //
NK122(kho)002:8235: bstan pa lo brgya phrag bcu /
NK122(kho)002:8236: sku gdung ni rgyas par gyur to //
NK122(kho)002:8237: de'i tshe bdag cag gi ston pa 'di ni /
NK122(kho)002:8238: rdza mkhan gyi bu khye'u snang byed zhes bya bar gyur to //
NK122(kho)002:8239: des thub pa chen po de la ut+pala lnga /
NK122(kho)002:8244: thugs bskyed nas smon lam btab ste /
NK122(kho)002:8245: de bzhin gshegs pa khyed sku ci 'dra dang //
NK122(kho)002:8246: 'khor dang sku tshe'i tshad dang zhing khams dang //
NK122(kho)002:8247: khyed kyi mtshan mchog bzang po ci 'dra ba //
NK122(kho)002:8248: de 'dra kho nar bdag kyang 'gyur bar shog /
NK122(kho)002:8250: smon lam gyi nus pas phyis de lta bu nyid du grub bo //
NK122(kho)002:8251: des grangs med gsum du tshogs ci ltar bsags lugs la gnyis /
NK122(kho)002:8252: dang po theg chung gi 'dod pa ltar na /
NK122(kho)002:8254: sangs rgyas sh+aakya thub pa nas //
NK122(kho)002:8256: bdun khri dang ni lnga stong gi //
NK122(kho)002:8257: sangs rgyas rnams ni ngas mchod do //
NK122(kho)002:8258: grangs med gcig ni 'das pas na //
NK122(kho)002:8259: rgyal ba ngas ni mchod byas te //
NK122(kho)002:8260: sangs rgyas nyid ni 'dod pa'i phyir //
NK122(kho)002:8261: nga la skyo ba'i sems med do //
NK122(kho)002:8264: sangs rgyas mar me mdzad pa nas //
NK122(kho)002:8265: dbang po'i rgyal mtshan thug gi bar //
NK122(kho)002:8266: lnga khri drug stong tshang pa yi //
NK122(kho)002:8267: sangs rgyas rnams ni ngas mchod do //
NK122(kho)002:8268: grangs med gnyis pa tshang bar ni //
NK122(kho)002:8269: nga la skyo ba'i sems med do //
NK122(kho)002:8272: grangs med pa ni gsum pa la'ang /
NK122(kho)002:8273: sangs rgyas legs mdzad nas bzung ste //
NK122(kho)002:8274: sangs rgyas 'od srung bar dag tu //
NK122(kho)002:8275: bdun khri bdun stong nga yis mchod //
NK122(kho)002:8277: tshigs su bcad pa kho nas don go bar zad do //
NK122(kho)002:8278: yang nyan thos bye brag tu smra ba'i 'dod pa ltar ni /
NK122(kho)002:8279: mdzod kyi gnas bzhi pa las //
NK122(kho)002:8280: rnam gzigs mar me rin chen gtsug /
NK122(kho)002:8281: grangs med gsum gyi tha mar byung //
NK122(kho)002:8282: dang po sh+aakya thub pa yin //
NK122(kho)002:8283: ces pas grangs med pa dang po'i tha ma la rin chen gtsug tor can dang /
NK122(kho)002:8284: gnyis pa'i tha mar mar me mdzad dang /
NK122(kho)002:8285: gsum pa'i tha ma la rnam par gzigs dang /
NK122(kho)002:8286: de dag thams cad kyi dang po ni sh+aakya thub pa chen po yin no //
NK122(kho)002:8288: yang 'phags pa byang chub sems dpa'i sde snod kyi lugs bzhin theg chen ltar na /
NK122(kho)002:8289: sangs rgyas 'od 'phro'i phung po chen po la ston
NK122(kho)002:8290: pa 'di gzhon nu brtson 'grus spyod yul du gyur
NK122(kho)002:8291: pa'i tshe / sangs rgyas nyan thos dang bcas pa
NK122(kho)002:8292: la lo bye ba phrag dgu bcu rtsa drug la
NK122(kho)002:8294: de nas grangs med pa bcu gcig na de bzhin
NK122(kho)002:8295: gshegs pa dkon mchog yan lag zhes bya ba kha
NK122(kho)002:8296: cig gis 'di rin chen gtsug tor can yin zer
NK122(kho)002:8297: ro // nyan thos bye ba phrag brgyad cu dang bcas pa 'jig rten du byon /
NK122(kho)002:8298: de'i dus su grong khyer 'dzam bu'i chu bo gser
NK122(kho)002:8299: zhes bya ba zhig tu rgyal po mdzes par snang
NK122(kho)002:8300: ba zhes bya ba gcig kyang byung bar gyur to
NK122(kho)002:8301: // de'i ring la ston pa 'di rgyal po de'i
NK122(kho)002:8302: blon po tshong dpon shes rab bzang po zhes bya
NK122(kho)002:8303: // bar gyur to // de bzhin gshegs pa des
NK122(kho)002:8304: tshong dpon de byang chub kyi snod du rung bar
NK122(kho)002:8305: gzigs nas chos gsungs pas de la dad ste lo
NK122(kho)002:8306: stong du bsnyen bkur byas so //
NK122(kho)002:8307: de nas grangs med gnyis pa na /
NK122(kho)002:8308: de bzhin gshegs pa mar me mdzad 'jig rten du byon //
NK122(kho)002:8309: de'i tshe ston pa 'di bram ze rin po che'i
NK122(kho)002:8310: slob ma khye'u sprin chen po zhes bya bar gyur
NK122(kho)002:8311: to // 'khor lo bsgyur ba'i rgyal po dgra thul
NK122(kho)002:8312: gyis tshongs 'dus pad+ma can zhes bya ba'i phyogs zhig
NK122(kho)002:8313: tu sangs rgyas dang mjal nas /
NK122(kho)002:8314: bram ze'i khye'u khyod da ste bskal pa grangs med
NK122(kho)002:8315: pa gcig nas sangs rgyas sh+aakya thub pa zhes bya
NK122(kho)002:8317: mi skye ba'i chos la bzod pa thob cing de'i
NK122(kho)002:8318: tshe ting nge 'dzin gyi sgo bye ba khrag khrig
NK122(kho)002:8319: dpag tu med pa mngon du byas so //
NK122(kho)002:8324: mar me mdzad kyis lung bstan pa'i mdo kun mthun cing /
NK122(kho)002:8326: bdag ni sngon tshe pha rol phyin pa'i mchog 'di dang /
NK122(kho)002:8327: mthun par smra gyur de tshe sngon gyi skyes mchog gis /
NK122(kho)002:8328: ma 'ongs pa yi dus na sangs rgyas 'gyur ro zhes /
NK122(kho)002:8329: nga lung bstan par gyur te rgyal bas de skad gsungs /
NK122(kho)002:8331: de nas grangs med pa gcig na bskal pa bzang
NK122(kho)002:8332: po 'di nyid la skye dgu rnams tshe lo nyi
NK122(kho)002:8333: khri pa'i dus su sangs rgyas 'od srungs 'jig rten
NK122(kho)002:8334: na byon / de'i tshe ston pa 'di bram ze'i khye'u bla ma zhes bya ba yin /
NK122(kho)002:8335: mdo kha cig na bram ze'i khye'u 'od zer phreng bar 'dogs pa yang 'dug /
NK122(kho)002:8336: de tshe 'phos pas dga' ldan du lha rnams kyi ston pa dam pa tog dkar por gyur to //
NK122(kho)002:8337: dam pa tog dkar sa bcu pa'i byang sems yin
NK122(kho)002:8338: pa de 'dzam bu'i gling du mdzad pa bcu gnyis
NK122(kho)002:8340: bskal pa grangs med gsum gyis lam gcod lugs ni /
NK122(kho)002:8341: tshogs sbyor gnyis la grangs med gcig /
NK122(kho)002:8342: ma dag pa sa bdun la grangs med gcig /
NK122(kho)002:8343: dag pa sa gsum la grangs med gcig thog /'bras bu'o //
NK122(kho)002:8345: sa bcu lam lnga mthar phyin nas spang bya sgrib pa'i phung po gnas su dag /
NK122(kho)002:8346: rtogs bya sgrib med kyi ye shes mngon du gyur pa ni /
NK122(kho)002:8347: bcu gcig kun tu 'od kyi sa /
NK122(kho)002:8350: ma rig gnyid las sangs phyir dang //
NK122(kho)002:8351: shes bya la yang blo rgyas phyir //
NK122(kho)002:8352: sangs rgyas pad+mo ltar sangs rgyas //
NK122(kho)002:8353: de phyir sangs rgyas mtshan gsol to //
NK122(kho)002:8356: rang bzhin gyis gnas pa'i rigs gnas su gyur pa rang don chos sku dang /
NK122(kho)002:8357: rgyas gyur gyi rigs gnas su gyur pa gzhan don gzugs sku rnam pa gnyis te /
NK122(kho)002:8358: sku gsum lhun gyis grub pa ni rgyu mtshan nyid
NK122(kho)002:8359: kyi theg pa'i lugs la spangs rtogs mthar phyin gyi
NK122(kho)002:8362: rigs 'di gnyis las sangs rgyas kyi //
NK122(kho)002:8363: sku gsum thob par 'dod pa yin //
NK122(kho)002:8364: dang po'i sku ni dang po la //
NK122(kho)002:8365: gnyis pa la ni phyi ma gnyis //
NK122(kho)002:8367: nges par bya ba'i phyir lung gis don bsdu ba'o //
NK122(kho)002:8369: dgongs pa 'dus pa'i lung las kyang ni 'di skad du /
NK122(kho)002:8370: don dam pa yul med ma skyes phyogs thams cad
NK122(kho)002:8371: dang bral bar 'dod pa ni gnas lugs rtogs pa'i
NK122(kho)002:8372: lta ba'o // sgom pa dang spyod pa ni /
NK122(kho)002:8373: bdag med rtogs pa'i ngang nas byams snying rje dga'
NK122(kho)002:8374: ba btang snyoms bzhi sgom pa'i dus su rnam par
NK122(kho)002:8376: sa bcu dang rnam thar gsum bde blag tu bskrun
NK122(kho)002:8377: te bsgrubs nas rtogs bya chos kyi dbyings rang bzhin
NK122(kho)002:8378: gyis rnam par dag pa rtogs pa las /
NK122(kho)002:8379: dngos po med pa ngo bo nyid kyi sku dang /
NK122(kho)002:8380: de nyid rtogs par byed pa'i ye shes chos sku dang nges pa lnga ldan longs sku dang /
NK122(kho)002:8381: ma nges lnga ldan sprul pa'i sku dang /
NK122(kho)002:8382: sku bzhi thob pa yin te /
NK122(kho)002:8384: ngo bo nyid longs rdzogs bcas dang //
NK122(kho)002:8385: de bzhin gzhan pa sprul pa ni //
NK122(kho)002:8386: chos sku mdzad pa dang bcas pa //
NK122(kho)002:8387: rnam pa bzhir ni yang dag brjod //
NK122(kho)002:8389: zhes gsung lung gis bgrod pa dang gsal /
NK122(kho)002:8391: 'di rnams kyi spyi don bshad na /
NK122(kho)002:8392: rgyu rigs gnyis la brten nas /
NK122(kho)002:8394: 'bras bu sku gsum ye shes lnga thob par bshad do //
NK122(kho)002:8395: de yang phung khams skye mched nyer len zag bcas rnams lcags kyi khams dang 'dra ba la /
NK122(kho)002:8396: rdo rje lta bu'i ting nge 'dzin ni gser 'gyur gyi rtsi dang 'dra bas /
NK122(kho)002:8397: zag med sangs rgyas kyi sku gser lta bur bsgyur ba yin te /
NK122(kho)002:8399: gser 'gyur rtsi yis rnam pa mchog lta bur //
NK122(kho)002:8400: mi gtsang lus 'di blang nas rgyal ba'i sku //
NK122(kho)002:8401: rin chen rin thang med par bsgyur bas na //
NK122(kho)002:8403: de ltar 'bras bu sangs rgyas la sku gcig tu bshad pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:8407: de la sku gcig ni 'gro ba sems can gyi dus su sems rgyud gcig yin pas /
NK122(kho)002:8408: 'bras bu'i dus su sangs rgyas chos kyi sku gcig yin cing /
NK122(kho)002:8409: de'i cho 'phrul sangs rgyas kyi sku thams cad snang ba yin te /
NK122(kho)002:8411: ci ltar sems ni gcig pu la //
NK122(kho)002:8412: rnam pa sna tshogs sems brjod pa //
NK122(kho)002:8413: de bzhin sangs rgyas sku gcig la //
NK122(kho)002:8414: sangs rgyas thams cad brjod pa yin //
NK122(kho)002:8416: gnyis su brjod pa ni rgyu rigs gnyis las lam
NK122(kho)002:8417: la tshogs gnyis kyis 'bras bu rang don chos sku
NK122(kho)002:8418: dang gzhan don gzugs sku thob par bshad de /
NK122(kho)002:8420: rang don gzhan don don dam sku dang ni //
NK122(kho)002:8421: de la brten pa kun rdzob sku nyid do //
NK122(kho)002:8422: dang po'i sku ni stobs la sogs //
NK122(kho)002:8423: bral ba'i yon tan rnams dang ldan //
NK122(kho)002:8424: gnyis pa skyes bu chen po'i mtshan //
NK122(kho)002:8425: sum cu rtsa gnyis dag dang ldan //
NK122(kho)002:8427: sku gsum du dbye ba ni /
NK122(kho)002:8428: dbyings rang bzhin gyis rnam par dag pa la /
NK122(kho)002:8429: spang bya glo bur gyi dri ma dang bral ba /
NK122(kho)002:8430: yon tan thams cad kyi bdag nyid du gnas pa ni chos sku /
NK122(kho)002:8432: sa bcu'i byang chub sems dpa' rnams kyi ston pa nges pa lnga dang ldan pa yin te /
NK122(kho)002:8433: gnas nges pa ni 'og min stug po bkod pa /
NK122(kho)002:8434: sku nges pa mtshan dang dpe byad 'bar ba /
NK122(kho)002:8435: 'khor nges pa sa bcu'i byang sems /
NK122(kho)002:8436: chos nges pa theg pa chen po /
NK122(kho)002:8437: dus nges pa rgyun chad med pa dang ldan pa ni longs sku'o //
NK122(kho)002:8438: sprul sku ni gdul bya'i me long la phrin las kyi gzugs brnyan sna tshogs shar ba ste /
NK122(kho)002:8439: mchog gi sprul pa sangs rgyas stong lta bu'o //
NK122(kho)002:8440: bzo'i sprul pa karma bi shwa /
NK122(kho)002:8441: skye ba'i sprul pa ru ru sha sha stag dang
NK122(kho)002:8442: ri bong la sogs pa sna tshogs su snang ba'o
NK122(kho)002:8443: // de la dang po ni rang don rten yin la /
NK122(kho)002:8444: gnyis pa ni gzhan don brten pa yin te /
NK122(kho)002:8446: sku gsum dag gis sangs rgyas kyi //
NK122(kho)002:8447: sku bsdus pa ni shes bya ste //
NK122(kho)002:8448: sku gsum dag gi rang bzhin gyi //
NK122(kho)002:8449: don 'di rten dang bcas par bstan //
NK122(kho)002:8452: rtogs bya chos kyi dbyings dri ma dang bral ba ni ngo bo nyid kyi sku /
NK122(kho)002:8453: rtogs pa'i ye shes chos sku /
NK122(kho)002:8455: de yang mngon rtogs rgyan las /
NK122(kho)002:8456: ngo bo nyid longs rdzogs bcas dang //
NK122(kho)002:8457: de bzhin gzhan pa sprul pa ni //
NK122(kho)002:8458: chos sku mdzad pa dang bcas pa //
NK122(kho)002:8459: rnam pa bzhir ni yang dag brjod //
NK122(kho)002:8461: sku'i dbye ba de ltar yin /
NK122(kho)002:8462: gsung gi dbye ba la gsung dbyangs yan lag drug cu dang /
NK122(kho)002:8463: thugs kyi dbye ba la ye shes lnga /
NK122(kho)002:8464: yon tan gyi dbye ba la stobs bcu mi 'jigs pa bzhi /
NK122(kho)002:8465: ma 'dres pa'i chos bco brgyad la sogs pa rnams dang /
NK122(kho)002:8466: phrin las la sku gsung thugs kyi dbye bas cho
NK122(kho)002:8467: 'phrul gsum la sogs pa rnams gzhan du shes par
NK122(kho)002:8468: bya'o // 'dir spyi don gyi bshad pa mang drags
NK122(kho)002:8469: na ha cang thal drags red pa'i don gyis ma
NK122(kho)002:8470: bya'o // bshad do // 'bras bu gsang sngags rdo rje'i theg pa la gnyis te /
NK122(kho)002:8476: rgyud sde bzhir 'jog pa'i rgyu mtshan /
NK122(kho)002:8479: mtshan nyid gsang sngags lha yis phye //
NK122(kho)002:8480: gsang sngags phyi nang rdzas kyis phye //
NK122(kho)002:8482: rtogs par bya ba'i lta ba la ma rmongs pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:8483: mchog thun mong gi dngos grub bsgrub pa'i thabs mang ba dang /
NK122(kho)002:8484: dka' ba med par byang chub bsgrub pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:8485: 'bras bu myur du 'grub pas dbang po rno ba dang bzhi yin te /
NK122(kho)002:8487: su si ti ka ra legs par grub pa'i rgyud las /
NK122(kho)002:8488: don gcig na yang ma rmongs dang //
NK122(kho)002:8489: thabs mang dka' ba med pa dang //
NK122(kho)002:8490: dbang po rnon pos dbang byas pas //
NK122(kho)002:8491: sngags kyi theg pa khyad par 'phags //
NK122(kho)002:8493: mtshan nyid kyi lugs la kun rdzob 'di nyid spang bya yin la /
NK122(kho)002:8494: gsang sngags kyi lugs la kun rdzob de nyid lha
NK122(kho)002:8495: dang lha mo'i dkyil 'khor du 'dod pas dpag par
NK122(kho)002:8496: shes par bya'o // gsang sngags bla med kyi lugs
NK122(kho)002:8497: la 'bras bu'i ngo bo nyid lam du khyer bar
NK122(kho)002:8498: shes par bya'o // 'dod de / dang po de
NK122(kho)002:8499: bzhin nyid spros pa'i mtshan ma thams cad bral bar
NK122(kho)002:8501: kun tu snang gi ting nge 'dzin 'gag med du snying rje'i rtsal kha 'phyo ba 'di longs sku /
NK122(kho)002:8502: de gnyis ye nas chu dang chu'i rlan bzhin dbyer
NK122(kho)002:8503: med ro gcig tu yi ge'am phyag rgya gcig pa
NK122(kho)002:8504: rgyu'i ting nge 'dzin sgom pa ni sprul sku /
NK122(kho)002:8505: de ltar sku gsum lam du khyer ba 'bras bu'i ngo bor 'dod de /
NK122(kho)002:8507: 'di ni gsang chen nges pa yi //
NK122(kho)002:8508: 'bras bu lam du khyer ba yin //
NK122(kho)002:8511: bde skyob gnyis kyi sgo nas dbye ba yang yod /
NK122(kho)002:8512: myur skyob bskal pa grangs med mi dgos par tshe gcig lus gcig gis sangs rgyas thob pa'o //
NK122(kho)002:8513: bde skyob ni nyon mongs pa dang 'dod yon spangs
NK122(kho)002:8514: ma dgos par gnas lugs kyi don dang dbyer med
NK122(kho)002:8515: du lam du khyer ba la bya ste /
NK122(kho)002:8517: lam gyi nang na nye lam bde rdzogs can //
NK122(kho)002:8518: thabs kyi nang na ma nor dam pa'i mchog /
NK122(kho)002:8520: gzhan yang kun rdzob don dam gnyis dbyer med ro
NK122(kho)002:8521: gcig tu rtogs pa gsang sngags kyi khyad chos yin
NK122(kho)002:8523: bden gnyis ye nas dbyer med pa //
NK122(kho)002:8524: gsang sngags spyi yi lta ba yin //
NK122(kho)002:8527: rnam par byang dang sdug bsngal dag /
NK122(kho)002:8528: kun rdzob tu yang dbyer med pas //
NK122(kho)002:8529: lta ba mtho dman de tsam mo //
NK122(kho)002:8535: rnal 'byor bla med kyi rgyud dang bzhi'o //
NK122(kho)002:8537: rdo rje rnam par 'joms pa la sogs pa bya ba spyi'i rgyud /
NK122(kho)002:8538: rigs gsum mgon po'i rgyud drug gsum bco brgyad la sogs pa khyad par gyi rgyud dang /
NK122(kho)002:8539: gtsug tor rnam rgyal gdugs dkar la sogs pa cho ga zhib mo'i rgyud dang /
NK122(kho)002:8540: gzung grwa lnga la sogs pa gzung gi rtog pa brjod pa'i rgyud do //
NK122(kho)002:8541: gnyis pa spyod pa'i rgyud ni /
NK122(kho)002:8542: rnam snang mngon byang gi rgyud dang /
NK122(kho)002:8543: rdo rje sa 'og gi rgyud dang /
NK122(kho)002:8544: khams gsum rnam rgyal gyi rgyud la sogs pa'o //
NK122(kho)002:8545: gsum pa rnal 'byor gyi rgyud ni /
NK122(kho)002:8546: rtsa rgyud de nyid 'dus pa la sogs pa yo ga'i rgyud rnams so //
NK122(kho)002:8547: bzhi pa rnal 'byor bla med kyi rgyud la gsum ste /
NK122(kho)002:8549: gshin rje'i gshed kyi skor la sogs pa rnams pha rgyud yin no //
NK122(kho)002:8553: dgyes pa rdo rje la sogs pa rnams ma rgyud yin /
NK122(kho)002:8555: 'jam dpal mtshan brgyad la sogs pa rnams gnyis med kyi rgyud yin no //
NK122(kho)002:8556: gsang sngags rnying ma'i rgyud rnams gnyis med kyi rgyud yin par 'dod /
NK122(kho)002:8558: mchog rkyen rgyud ni rnam gsum ste //
NK122(kho)002:8559: gsang ba'i snying po nyid lta bu //
NK122(kho)002:8565: rgyud sde bzhi'i dbye ba zhib tu yod pa rnams gzhan du shes par bya'o //
NK122(kho)002:8566: rgyud sde bzhir 'jog pa'i rgyu mtshan ni /
NK122(kho)002:8568: lha rigs bzhi dang mi rigs bzhi'i //
NK122(kho)002:8569: 'dod pa bzhi la dgongs nas ni //
NK122(kho)002:8570: rgyud sde rnam pa bzhir bshad do //
NK122(kho)002:8571: ces pas lha rigs bzhi la dgongs pa ni /
NK122(kho)002:8575: sum cu rtsa gsum pa dang bzhi'i 'dod pa la dgongs nas gsungs te /
NK122(kho)002:8576: gzhan 'phrul gyi 'dod chags bltas pas tshims pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:8577: 'phrul dga' ba'i dgod pas tshims pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:8578: dga' ldan pa'i lag pa bcang pas tshim pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:8579: sum cu rtsa gsum pa'i 'khyud pas tshims pa ste /
NK122(kho)002:8580: bde mchog le'u nyi shu rtsa gcig pa nas //
NK122(kho)002:8581: bltas dang dgod dang lag bcang dang //
NK122(kho)002:8582: 'khyud dang gnyis gnyis spyod la sogs //
NK122(kho)002:8583: rgyud rnams kun gyi dam pa yin //
NK122(kho)002:8585: de yang bya ba'i rgyud las lha yab yum ci ltar du sgom na /
NK122(kho)002:8587: g.yon du lha mo gos dkar mo //
NK122(kho)002:8588: cung zad blta ba bri bar bya //
NK122(kho)002:8590: spyod pa'i rgyud kyi lha yab yum sgom pa ni /
NK122(kho)002:8592: mgon po ral pa'i thor tshugs can //
NK122(kho)002:8593: de yi g.yon du lha mo ni //
NK122(kho)002:8594: zhal ni cung zad 'dzum pa bri //
NK122(kho)002:8596: rnal 'byor gyi rgyud kyi yab yum ni /
NK122(kho)002:8598: bcom ldan 'das kyi g.yon phyogs su //
NK122(kho)002:8599: lha mo sgrol ma sgra gcan 'dzin //
NK122(kho)002:8602: bla med kyi lha yab yum sgom tshul ni /
NK122(kho)002:8604: chags can rnams ni drang ba'i phyir //
NK122(kho)002:8605: rdo rje sems dpa' khros nas ni //
NK122(kho)002:8606: dpa' bo rdo rje sems ma ni //
NK122(kho)002:8607: dbus su yang ni rol par mdzad //
NK122(kho)002:8609: mi rigs bzhi la dgongs pa yang //
NK122(kho)002:8610: bram ze khrus dang gtsang sbra la dga' bas bya ba'i rgyud /
NK122(kho)002:8611: rje rigs nor sred che bas spyod pa'i rgyud la nor sgrub thabs du ma yod pas so //
NK122(kho)002:8612: rgyal rigs rgyal po'i cha 'dzin pas rnal 'byor yo ga /
NK122(kho)002:8613: dmangs rigs dang nag po gdol pa'i rigs gnyis spyod ngan pas bla med kyi rgyud bshad do //
NK122(kho)002:8614: rdo rje sa 'og gi rgyud las /
NK122(kho)002:8615: bram ze'i rigs dang rgyal rigs dang //
NK122(kho)002:8616: rje rigs gdol pa 'jug pa'i sgo //
NK122(kho)002:8617: bde gshegs sku gsung thugs phrin las //
NK122(kho)002:8618: so so'i rgyud sde bzhin du bshad //
NK122(kho)002:8620: dus bzhi la dgongs nas rgyud sde bzhir gsungs pa ni /
NK122(kho)002:8621: da res kyi bskal pa bzang po 'di mar 'grib
NK122(kho)002:8622: kyi dus la 'khor ba 'jigs tshe lo bzhi khri'i
NK122(kho)002:8623: dus su byon nas kri ya'i chos gsungs /
NK122(kho)002:8624: 'di 'og ma la ltos na tshe bsod nams phun sum tshogs pas rdzogs ldan dang po zhes bya'o //
NK122(kho)002:8625: tshe lo sum khri'i dus su gser thub byon nas
NK122(kho)002:8626: spyod rgyud gsungs pa dang gdul bya rnams kyis tshe
NK122(kho)002:8627: lo sum khri thub pas gsum ldan gnyis pa /
NK122(kho)002:8628: nyi khri'i dus su 'od srungs byon nas rnal 'byor gyi rgyud gsungs pa la gnyis ldan gsum pa /
NK122(kho)002:8629: bzhi pa tshe lo brgya pa'i dus su sh+aakya thub
NK122(kho)002:8630: pa byon nas mtshan nyid sde gsum dang bya spyod
NK122(kho)002:8631: rnal 'byor gsum gsungs pa'i steng du gsang sngags bla
NK122(kho)002:8633: de'i dus kyi gdul bya rnams rtsod pa chags sdang
NK122(kho)002:8634: sna tshogs byed pas rtsod ldan bzhi pa zhes bya'o
NK122(kho)002:8635: // lha rnams thams cad yang dag par 'dus pa'i rgyud las /
NK122(kho)002:8636: rdzogs ldan dang po bya ba'i rgyud //
NK122(kho)002:8637: gsum ldan gnyis pa spyod pa'i rgyud //
NK122(kho)002:8638: gnyis ldan gsum pa rnal 'byor rgyud //
NK122(kho)002:8639: rtsod ldan bzhi pa bla med rgyud //
NK122(kho)002:8642: rdzogs ldan ni tshe lo brgyad khrir phyin pa la zer /
NK122(kho)002:8646: stobs la sogs pa rdzogs par yod pa'i phyir /
NK122(kho)002:8648: 'di ni mi rigs pa yin no //
NK122(kho)002:8649: tshe lo brgyad khrir phyin pa'i dus su chags pa'i rting rdzogs /
NK122(kho)002:8651: las mi dge ba sna tshogs spyod pas /
NK122(kho)002:8652: mnar med du sems can gcig skye ba dang dus mnyam /
NK122(kho)002:8653: de'i dus su 'od 'grib pa sa nas nyi zla shar dgos pa'o //
NK122(kho)002:8654: de lta bu yin na tshe lo brgyad khri'i dus su 'khor ba 'jig byon dgos /
NK122(kho)002:8655: 'dod na snying rje pad+ma dkar po las //
NK122(kho)002:8656: tshe lo brgyad khri'i dus su rnam par gzigs //
NK122(kho)002:8657: bdun khri'i dus su gtsug tor can //
NK122(kho)002:8658: drug khri'i dus su thams cad skyob byon zer ba dang 'gal /
NK122(kho)002:8659: gzhan yang dus 'khor rtsa rgyud dang /
NK122(kho)002:8660: pha rgyud gsang ba 'dus pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:8662: mdo dgongs 'dus kyi byung tshul bcu gnyis kyi nang nas bshad pa bzhin shes dgos /
NK122(kho)002:8663: 'dir yi ge mang gi dogs pa'i phyir de rnams zhib tu ma bris so //
NK122(kho)002:8664: blo rab 'bring tha ma bzhi la dgongs nas rgyud sde bzhi gsungs pa ni /
NK122(kho)002:8666: dman pa rnams la bya ba'i rgyud //
NK122(kho)002:8667: bya min rnal 'byor de ltag la //
NK122(kho)002:8668: sems can mchog la rnal 'byor rgyud //
NK122(kho)002:8669: rnal 'byor bla med de ltag go //
NK122(kho)002:8671: kha cig gis rigs can bzhi la dgongs nas rgyud sde bzhir bshad /
NK122(kho)002:8677: ma h+aa de ba dang bzhi'o //
NK122(kho)002:8679: nyon mongs pa dug gsum dang /
NK122(kho)002:8680: dug gsum cha mnyam pa'i ma rig pa dang bzhi la dgongs nas rgyud sde bzhir bshad /
NK122(kho)002:8682: 'di rnams shes byed kyi lung ni ma mthong /
NK122(kho)002:8683: 'on kyang rnam mkhyen sangs rgyas kyis gdul bya gang
NK122(kho)002:8684: la gang 'dul gyi don du chos gsungs pa yin
NK122(kho)002:8685: pas 'gal bar nam yang mi sems so //
NK122(kho)002:8686: bzhi pa gsang sngags kyi rgyud sde bzhi'i gzhung tshad ni /
NK122(kho)002:8687: ye shes rdo rje kun las btus pa'i rgyud las /
NK122(kho)002:8688: bya ba'i rgyud la stong phrag bzhi /
NK122(kho)002:8689: spyod pa'i rgyud la stong phrag drug /
NK122(kho)002:8690: rnal 'byor rgyud la stong phrag brgyad /
NK122(kho)002:8691: bla med rgyud la stong phrag bcu gnyis yod par bshad do //
NK122(kho)002:8694: gzhung gi ming tha dad pa rnams kyi grangs yin no //
NK122(kho)002:8696: bya ba'i rgyad la stong phrag bzhi yod zer kyang /
NK122(kho)002:8697: don yod zhags pa kho na la stong phrag brgyad yod pa la zhes zer ro //
NK122(kho)002:8698: de bzhin du de nyid 'dus pa stong phrag brgya pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:8699: dgyes pa rdo rje 'bum lnga dang /
NK122(kho)002:8700: 'jam dpal sgyu 'phrul dra ba la le'u khri drug stong yod par gsungs pa'i phyir ro //
NK122(kho)002:8701: de rnams kyis spyi don gyi bshad pa de song nas /
NK122(kho)002:8703: dka' thub rig byed kyi theg pa la gsum ste /
NK122(kho)002:8706: gdul thabs kyi sgo nas mdor bstan pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:8709: khrus dang gtsang sbra la sogs dag spyod kyi sgo nas /
NK122(kho)002:8710: dka' thub dang dka' spyad kyis don rig par byed
NK122(kho)002:8711: pa'i theg pa de yang gdul bya yul gyis phye
NK122(kho)002:8712: ba de rnam pa gsum nyid de /
NK122(kho)002:8714: lus ngag yid gsum gyi bya ba gtso bor byed pas bya ba'i rgyud dang /
NK122(kho)002:8715: lus ngag gi bya ba'i steng nas ting nge 'dzin
NK122(kho)002:8716: nyams su blang zhing spyod pas spyod pa'i rgyud dang
NK122(kho)002:8717: / nang gi ting nge 'dzin gtso bor byed pa rnal 'byor gyi rgyud do //
NK122(kho)002:8718: gdul bya'i blo'i bye brag gis /
NK122(kho)002:8720: dka' thub rig byed kyi theg pa /
NK122(kho)002:8721: dbang bsgyur thabs kyi theg pa dang gsum yod pa las /
NK122(kho)002:8722: dka' thub rig byed kyi theg pa blo 'bring gi chos yin pas 'bring po ces bya'o //
NK122(kho)002:8723: de nyid la'ang rnam pa gsum ste /
NK122(kho)002:8724: tha ma 'bring dang mchog tu snang /
NK122(kho)002:8726: ci ltar gdul bar byed pa'i thabs kyang de bzhin du bye brag gsum yin no //
NK122(kho)002:8727: rgyas par bshad pa la gsum ste /
NK122(kho)002:8735: bya ba'i rgyud kyi theg pa de la yang /
NK122(kho)002:8739: nyams su len pa'i spyod pa'i khyad par dang /
NK122(kho)002:8741: grub pa'i lam gyi yun dang /
NK122(kho)002:8742: thob bya'i 'bras bu dag dang bdun du bzhed pa'o //
NK122(kho)002:8743: rgyas par bshad pa la bdun ste /
NK122(kho)002:8755: de la dang po a ti man chad gsang sngags spyi'i 'jug sgo ni /
NK122(kho)002:8756: kun rdzob bden pa lha'i dkyil 'khor du shar ba'i dus de nyid la /
NK122(kho)002:8757: don dam bden pa skye med kyi gnas lugs las
NK122(kho)002:8758: ma g.yos par rtogs pa ni bden gnyis dbyer med
NK122(kho)002:8762: khyad par bya ba'i 'jug sgo ni 'di ltar yin te /
NK122(kho)002:8763: 'di gong 'og gi 'bru sdeb yod pa shes par bya'o //
NK122(kho)002:8767: mi gtsang ba spyod pa gsum spangs la /
NK122(kho)002:8770: dkar gsum mngar gsum za ste /
NK122(kho)002:8771: rigs gsum mgon po'i sku rdo rje lta bu'i rang bzhin du 'jug /
NK122(kho)002:8773: phra ma tshig rtsub ngag 'chal bzhi spangs te rigs
NK122(kho)002:8774: gsum mgon po'i gsung rdo rje lta bu'i rang bzhin
NK122(kho)002:8775: du 'jug / yid kyi sgo nas brnab sems /
NK122(kho)002:8776: gnod sems logs lta gsum spangs te /
NK122(kho)002:8777: rigs gsum mgon po'i thugs rdo rje lta bu'i rang bzhin du 'jug /
NK122(kho)002:8778: de ltar lus ngag yid gsum rnam par dag pa
NK122(kho)002:8779: rigs gsum mgon po'i sku gsung thugs kyi rang bzhin
NK122(kho)002:8780: du 'jug pa'o // lta ba la gnyis te /
NK122(kho)002:8781: bya ba rang gzhung gi lta ba dang /
NK122(kho)002:8787: lta ba ni phyi snod kyi 'jig rten dang nang
NK122(kho)002:8788: bcud kyi sems can sgyu ma rmi lam tsam du
NK122(kho)002:8789: chos can dang dngos por snang ba 'di rnams don
NK122(kho)002:8791: sems nyid kyang gdod ma nas stong zhing skye ba
NK122(kho)002:8792: med pa don dam par spros pa'i mtha' yod med
NK122(kho)002:8793: rtag chad bzhi dang bral ba las kun rdzob sgyu
NK122(kho)002:8794: ma'i mtshan nyid du snang ba'o //
NK122(kho)002:8796: rang sems mtha' bzhi yongs bral ba //
NK122(kho)002:8797: rig phyir ye shes gzhan du min //
NK122(kho)002:8801: kun rdzob sgyu ma'i mtshan nyid ni /
NK122(kho)002:8802: 'khrul pa'i ngo la ci ltar snang yang de nyid
NK122(kho)002:8803: de bzhin gshegs pa rigs gsum mgon po'i ngo bo
NK122(kho)002:8804: nyid yin te / lha drug gi cho gas byin
NK122(kho)002:8805: gyis brlabs nas rigs gsum lha'i dkyil 'khor du snang
NK122(kho)002:8806: nyid yin te / bar 'dod pa / dper na /
NK122(kho)002:8808: 'jim pa las gzhan pa'i 'der so mi 'byung /
NK122(kho)002:8809: mkhar chu lugs sku ma yin yang 'khar chu las gzhan pa'i sku mi 'byung ba bzhin du /
NK122(kho)002:8810: dngos po 'di ltar snang ba thams cad rigs gsum mgon po'i dkyil 'khor ma yin kyang /
NK122(kho)002:8811: de bas gzhan pa'i rigs gsum mgon po'i sku mi 'byung ba bzhin te /
NK122(kho)002:8813: mthong ba'i dngos po mtho 'jam rtsub //
NK122(kho)002:8814: drug phyed rigs kyi dkyil 'khor du //
NK122(kho)002:8815: mthong ba rnam par dag cing bya //
NK122(kho)002:8817: dngos por snang ba 'di rnams kyang /
NK122(kho)002:8818: rigs gsum mgon po'i sku ma yin kyang /
NK122(kho)002:8819: lta spyod sgom gsum gyi sgo nas sems dag par byas na mkhar chu las sku snang ba bzhin /
NK122(kho)002:8820: 'khrul pa dag pa nyid 'bras bu'i ngo bor ye nas gnas par 'dod pa'o //
NK122(kho)002:8822: chu dang gsher ba ci lta ba bzhin yin no //
NK122(kho)002:8826: kun rdzob bden pa gnyis chu dang chab bram ltar
NK122(kho)002:8827: spang gnyen ro gcig pa ye nas dbyer med pa
NK122(kho)002:8828: ni gsang sngags spyi'i lta ba yin no //
NK122(kho)002:8831: dam tshig sems dpa' ci ltar bskyed pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:8833: bya ba'i rnal 'byor bsam gtan ni lus ngag yid
NK122(kho)002:8834: gsum sku gsung thugs su sgom dgos pa yin te
NK122(kho)002:8835: / lha drug gi sgo nas 'jug pa'i tshul 'di
NK122(kho)002:8836: nyid kyis rigs gsum mgon po'i lha'i dkyil 'khor du
NK122(kho)002:8837: / gsal ba yin / las zhes pa ni 'og
NK122(kho)002:8838: gi ye shes sems dpa' dang 'brel mtshams sbyar ba'i
NK122(kho)002:8839: / gsal ba yin / tshig yin / de yang lha drug la 'jug pa'i tshul ni /
NK122(kho)002:8840: dben pa'i gnas su sngon 'gro'i cho ga mtho dman
NK122(kho)002:8841: gnyis la tshogs bsags pa rnam gnyis sngon du song
NK122(kho)002:8842: nas lha drug gi tshul du dam tshig sems dpa'i
NK122(kho)002:8843: skur bsgom ste / dang por sbyangs pa'i sngags kyis
NK122(kho)002:8844: stong par byas te stong pa chos nyid kyi lha
NK122(kho)002:8845: skur bsgom ste / dang / don dam skye 'gags med pa'i ting nge 'dzin yin la /
NK122(kho)002:8846: kun rdzob tu stong pa'i ngang las sa bon gang
NK122(kho)002:8847: yin pa'i sgra grags pa sgra brnyan gyi lha dang
NK122(kho)002:8848: / yig 'bru dngos su byung ba gsung yig 'bru'i lha dang /
NK122(kho)002:8849: de'i zhabs su gdan nyi zla byung ba gdan gyi lha dang /
NK122(kho)002:8850: de'i sa bon la thugs phyag mtshan 'byung ba thugs phyag mtshan gyi lha dang /
NK122(kho)002:8851: de las rigs gsum gang yin gyi skur snang ba sku phyag rgya'i lha /
NK122(kho)002:8852: de'i sku gsung thugs byin gyis brlab pa ni /
NK122(kho)002:8853: dper na 'bangs gcig gis rgyal po gcig gdan drangs
NK122(kho)002:8854: nas bsnyen bskur gyi ched du gnas khang phyag dar
NK122(kho)002:8855: byas pa dang / rang nyid kyang rgyan gyis legs
NK122(kho)002:8856: par brgyan nas rgyal po mnyes pa'i phyir dang 'dra
NK122(kho)002:8857: byas pa dang / bar / ye shes sems dpa'
NK122(kho)002:8858: spyan drangs pa la dam tshig sems dpas dngos grub
NK122(kho)002:8859: la re ba'i phyir bsnyen bkur byed pa'i tshul lo
NK122(kho)002:8860: byas pa dang / bar / // ye shes sems dpa' ci ltar dgug pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:8862: ye shes sems dpa' de nyid rje dpon lta bu /
NK122(kho)002:8863: bdag dam tshig sems dpa' bran lta bus bkur 'os jo bo'i tshul nyid du sgom zhing /
NK122(kho)002:8864: mdun gyi nam mkha' la ye shes sems dpa'i gdan
NK122(kho)002:8865: khri'i 'og tu dam tshig sems dpa'i dbu'i gtsug tor
NK122(kho)002:8866: gyis ma reg pa tsam gyi tshul du spyan drangs
NK122(kho)002:8867: pa yin te / g.yu thang las /
NK122(kho)002:8868: mi grub phyir na 'jig rten chos //
NK122(kho)002:8869: mthun par bya phyir rje khol ltar //
NK122(kho)002:8871: de la tshogs bsags dang bsnyen pas mnyes par byas nas dngos grub blang ba'o //
NK122(kho)002:8873: mdun gyi ye shes sems dpa' de nyid la /
NK122(kho)002:8874: lus gus pa'i sgo nas phyag 'tshal pa /
NK122(kho)002:8875: la sogs kyi sgras phyi nang gi mchod pa 'bul /
NK122(kho)002:8876: tshe rabs thog med dus nas bsags pa'i sdig pa bshags /
NK122(kho)002:8877: dge ba la rjes su yi rang /
NK122(kho)002:8878: chos kyi 'khor lo bskor bar bskul /
NK122(kho)002:8879: mya ngan las mi 'da' bar gsol ba gdab /
NK122(kho)002:8880: rjes dge ba'i rtsa ba byang chub tu bsngo'o //
NK122(kho)002:8881: de lta bu'i yan lag bdun pas rgyu bsod nams
NK122(kho)002:8882: kyi tshul gyis tshogs yongs su bsags shing mchod bstod
NK122(kho)002:8883: dang bzlas brjod bsnyen pa rgyun mi bcad pa ni
NK122(kho)002:8884: / ting nge 'dzin gyi dmigs pa gsum /
NK122(kho)002:8885: bsnyen pa'i yan lag bzhi shes dgos /
NK122(kho)002:8886: de la dmigs pa gsum ni /
NK122(kho)002:8887: bdag dam tshig sems dpa' bran gyi tshul du dmigs pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:8888: ye shes sems dpa' rje'i tshul du dmigs pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:8889: ye shes sems dpa'i thugs kar byang chub mchog tu
NK122(kho)002:8890: sems bskyed pa mtha' phyin pa'i rtags su zla ba'i
NK122(kho)002:8891: dkyil 'khor yig 'bru dang bcas pa la dmigs pa'o
NK122(kho)002:8893: dbugs phyir rgyu ba'i dus su lha'i thugs kar dmigs /
NK122(kho)002:8894: tshur rgyu ba'i dus su bdag gi thugs kar dmigs /
NK122(kho)002:8895: sngags bzla ba'i dus su bsnyen pa'i skyon rnams spangs te /
NK122(kho)002:8900: mi tshig gis bar ma chod par bya zhing sngags kyi 'od zer phar 'phros lha'i thugs kar thim /
NK122(kho)002:8902: tshur 'dus bdag gi thugs kar thim pas /
NK122(kho)002:8903: dngos grub thob par bsam la /
NK122(kho)002:8904: ting nge 'dzin rgyun mi 'chad par 'gal me'i 'khor lo ltar bya'o //
NK122(kho)002:8906: bzlas brjod byed tshe mi dal mi myur zhing //
NK122(kho)002:8907: ha cang sgra cher ma yin shub bur min //
NK122(kho)002:8908: gug bskyed klad skor tshag shad zur phyin cing //
NK122(kho)002:8909: gsang sngags dag cing cho ga yongs su zlos //
NK122(kho)002:8911: bya rgyud kyi bzlas brjod 'di rnams la dngos grub 'grub par byed pa'i yan lag gsum yod de /
NK122(kho)002:8912: dam bca' grangs nges pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:8916: bzlas pa'i grangs dam bca' ba de nyid las mi 'ada'o //
NK122(kho)002:8918: bzlas brjod byed pa'i tshe glal ba dang /
NK122(kho)002:8921: mchil snab bor ba la sogs pa spang nas /
NK122(kho)002:8922: mi tshig gis bar chod par lta ci dgos te /
NK122(kho)002:8923: dper na brgya rtsa brgyad du dam bcas nas /
NK122(kho)002:8924: dgu bcu rtsa dgu nas mi tshig gis bar chod na gzhi nas bzla dgos so //
NK122(kho)002:8926: sngags kyi grangs dam bcas pa de nyid mthar phyin te 'byongs pa'o //
NK122(kho)002:8927: rjes su dngos grub blang ste /
NK122(kho)002:8928: gtang rag gi mchod bstod bya /
NK122(kho)002:8929: bzod gsol gshegs su gsol ba dang /
NK122(kho)002:8932: mi dmigs pa'i rgyas gdab pa ni bya ba'i rgyud kyi ting nge 'dzin gyi rim pa yin no //
NK122(kho)002:8935: bya ba'i rgyud kyi spyod pa ni /
NK122(kho)002:8936: lus ngag yid gsum sku gsung thugs su dag pa gsum gyis mtha' bzung nas /
NK122(kho)002:8937: phyi nang gsang gsum gyi khrus dang gtsang sbra la sogs bde bar spyod de /
NK122(kho)002:8938: bsgrub pa'i dbu 'dzin pa'i dus su zhag grangs bzang po nya dang tshes brgyad la sogs pa /
NK122(kho)002:8939: dus tshig bzang po ra ba bzhi /
NK122(kho)002:8940: gza' bzang po pa sangs dang /
NK122(kho)002:8944: rgyu skar bzang po mgo dang /
NK122(kho)002:8945: rgyal la sogs pa rnams yin no //
NK122(kho)002:8946: gtsang ma'i yo byad la sogs pa zhes pa ni /
NK122(kho)002:8947: dag gtsang gi yo byad cha rkyen nyer lnga ste dkar gsum /
NK122(kho)002:8948: mngar gsum la sogs pa ma smad pa /
NK122(kho)002:8951: ro bag la sogs pas ma gos pa'i rten 'brel
NK122(kho)002:8952: de dag 'dzom pa las mchog thun mong dngos grub
NK122(kho)002:8957: rdo dang skyes bu'i lag pa'i rtsol ba rnams 'dus
NK122(kho)002:8958: pa las me thon pa dang 'dra ba yin no
NK122(kho)002:8963: bya ba'i rgyud kyis bsrung ba'i tshul khrims ni /
NK122(kho)002:8965: so sor thar pa rigs bdun dang /
NK122(kho)002:8966: bar byang chub sems dpa'i bslab bya smon 'jug gnyis
NK122(kho)002:8967: la sogs pa spyi'i sdom brtson mi bshig cing brtson
NK122(kho)002:8969: khyad par gyi dam tshig go //
NK122(kho)002:8971: lus ngag yid gsum dam tshig dag zhes pa ni /
NK122(kho)002:8972: lus kyi dag pa mi dge ba gsum spangs /
NK122(kho)002:8973: gos dag pa gon cing lus dag pa'i lhar mos /
NK122(kho)002:8974: ngag gi mi dge ba bzhi spangs sngags dang bstod pa brjod /
NK122(kho)002:8975: yid kyi mi dge ba gsum spangs /
NK122(kho)002:8977: bying rmugs la sogs pa'i skyon spangs /
NK122(kho)002:8978: de lta bu'i ngang las mi 'da' bar byed cing
NK122(kho)002:8979: yan lag gi dam tshig dang bcas pa bsrung dgos
NK122(kho)002:8981: bdun yod de dkon mchog gsum mi spang ba dang /
NK122(kho)002:8982: byang chub kyi sems mi spangs ba dang /
NK122(kho)002:8983: rdo rje slob dpon gtsug gi nor bu ltar bkur ba dang /
NK122(kho)002:8984: lta spyod mthun pa'i grogs la gdung sems rgyun mi bcad pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:8985: yi dam gyi lha rgyun du bsgom zhing bzlas brjod dag par bya ba dang /
NK122(kho)002:8986: sha chang sgog btsong la sogs pa'i dri ngan pa'i kha zas mi za ba dang /
NK122(kho)002:8987: sku gsung thugs kyi phyag rgya'i gzugs brnyan dang /
NK122(kho)002:8988: lha la phul ba'i rnying pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:8989: lha'i grib ma mi 'gom pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:8991: bya rgyud kyi lugs la spyod pa'i gtso bo nye reg 'thor 'thung la bya ste /
NK122(kho)002:8992: chu phud ma nyams pa'i nang du dri bzang sbyar la mdun du bzhag /
NK122(kho)002:8993: lag pa g.yon pa'i theb srin sprad pa'i bar du rdo rje 'dzin la /
NK122(kho)002:8994: theb srin la nyi zla'i dkyil 'khor bsam la de'i
NK122(kho)002:8995: steng du yi ge a dkar po gcig bsam pa'i
NK122(kho)002:8996: 'phro 'du las dri chab de nyid a'i rang bzhin
NK122(kho)002:8998: de nas dri chab lag mthil g.yas g.yon du thig le zlum por byug ste /
NK122(kho)002:8999: zla ba'i dal du bsam la lag mthil kha sprad
NK122(kho)002:9000: pa'i bar du a dkar po yung 'bru tsam gyis
NK122(kho)002:9001: gang bar bsam / de bdag gi mgo la byug
NK122(kho)002:9002: pas lus skye ba med pa chos kyi dbyings su
NK122(kho)002:9003: gang bar bsam / byin gyis brlabs / lce la bzhag pas kyang de bzhin du byin gyis rlabs /
NK122(kho)002:9004: thugs kar byug pas kyang de bzhin du brlabs /
NK122(kho)002:9005: de nas rnal 'byor pa rnams la reg nas kyang /
NK122(kho)002:9006: skye med chos kyi dbyings su byin gyis rlabs pa ni nye reg ces bya'o //
NK122(kho)002:9007: de phyogs bcur gtor bas stong gsum thams cad byin gyis rlabs pa la 'thor ces bya'o //
NK122(kho)002:9008: de nas lhag ma bdag gis kyang btung /
NK122(kho)002:9009: rnal 'byor pa gzhan gyi lus bkru ba la sogs pa byed nas /
NK122(kho)002:9010: nang gi bag chags dag par dmigs pa la ni 'thung zhes bya'o //
NK122(kho)002:9011: de lta bu'i bya rgyud kyi bsrung sdom bye brag tshul gyis gnas pa yin no //
NK122(kho)002:9016: bya ba'i rnal 'byor 'grub pa'i yun ni /
NK122(kho)002:9017: blo mtho na mi tshe bdun gyi nang du zag bcas kyi 'bras bu thob par 'dod de /
NK122(kho)002:9019: dag spyod gtsang sbra can de mi tshe bdun /
NK122(kho)002:9021: tha ma yang ring mthar mi tshe bcu drug gis zag bcas kyi 'bras bu thob par 'dod de /
NK122(kho)002:9022: mi rigs khyad par can rgyal rigs dang bram ze
NK122(kho)002:9023: gtsang ma dang 'dod pa'i lha brgya byin la sogs
NK122(kho)002:9024: pa dang / gzugs kyi khams la yod pa'i tshangs
NK122(kho)002:9025: pa la sogs pa rnams kyi gtsang ma'i lus 'dzin
NK122(kho)002:9026: pa dang / cing / nang dgongs pa gsang sngags
NK122(kho)002:9027: kyi theg pa chen po bsgrub par 'gyur ba yin
NK122(kho)002:9028: pa dang / cing / no // zag med kyi yun no //
NK122(kho)002:9030: bcu drug mtha' la zag pa dang bral nas rang
NK122(kho)002:9031: gi yi dam lha'i sku nyid kyi phyag rgya chen
NK122(kho)002:9033: 'og min dga' ldan la sogs pa'i rnam dag zhing du rab snang ste /
NK122(kho)002:9034: zag med kyi yun la brgya phrag bcu drug tshun
NK122(kho)002:9035: chad kyi nang du rdo rje 'dzin pa'i sa dang
NK122(kho)002:9040: rdo rje 'dzin pa'i sa non pa yin te /
NK122(kho)002:9041: de'i ngo bo chos sku dang /
NK122(kho)002:9045: bde ba chen po'i sku dang /
NK122(kho)002:9046: sku lnga lhun gyis 'grub par 'gyur ro //
NK122(kho)002:9049: dgongs pa 'dus pa'i lung las kyang ni 'di skad du zhes pa nas /
NK122(kho)002:9050: zhes gsungs lung gis bgrod dang sla /
NK122(kho)002:9051: zhes pa'i bar ni go sla'o //
NK122(kho)002:9052: spyod pa'i rnal 'byor la gsum ste /
NK122(kho)002:9057: spyod pa'i rnal 'byor la bye brag gi 'jug sgo
NK122(kho)002:9058: la sogs pa bdun du dbye ba ni gong dang
NK122(kho)002:9059: 'dra'o // dbang po 'bring ni dka' thub rig byed kyi theg pa'i gdul bya /
NK122(kho)002:9060: de la gsum yod pa las u pa ya 'di
NK122(kho)002:9061: nyid kyis gdul bya'i gang zag 'bring gi 'bring du
NK122(kho)002:9062: gyur pa yin pa shes par bya'o //
NK122(kho)002:9063: rgyas par bshad pa la bdun las lngar bsdus pa ste /
NK122(kho)002:9067: dam tshig gsum bya ba dang mtshungs pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:9069: u pa ya ni bya pho rog gi mig dang 'dra ste /
NK122(kho)002:9070: dper na pho rog gi mig ya bas yar nam mkha' la blta /
NK122(kho)002:9071: ya bas mar sa la blta ba bzhin /
NK122(kho)002:9073: lta ba yo ga'i rjes su snyeg 'jug sgo spyod pa dang dam tshig gsum /
NK122(kho)002:9074: kri ya dang mthun par bshad de //
NK122(kho)002:9075: 'jug sgo spyod dang dam tshig gsum //
NK122(kho)002:9076: bya ba'i rnal 'byor dag dang mtshungs //
NK122(kho)002:9078: lta ba rnal 'byor dang mthun pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:9084: bsam gtan rnam par snang mdzad kyi ting nge 'dzin las /
NK122(kho)002:9085: de nyid bzhi'i tshul dag gis /
NK122(kho)002:9087: bdag gi de kho na nyid /
NK122(kho)002:9089: ting nge 'dzin gyi de kho na nyid /
NK122(kho)002:9091: sngags kyi de kho na nyid dang bzhi'o //
NK122(kho)002:9093: lha dam tshig bsgom pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:9094: gnyis pa ye shes pa spyan drangs nas smin mtshams kyi thad sor bzhugs pa /
NK122(kho)002:9095: gsum pa bdag dang mdun gyi ye shes sems dpa'i /
NK122(kho)002:9098: bzhi pa dbugs dang sprad nas dbugs phyir rgyu ba'i
NK122(kho)002:9099: dus su ye shes sems dpa'i thugs dam gyi rgyud
NK122(kho)002:9100: bskul / tshur rgyu ba'i dus su dngos grub stsol bar bsam zhing bzlas pa'i skyon bcu spangs ba'o //
NK122(kho)002:9101: dang po bsnyen nas bsgrub pa'i yan lag rdzogs par gyur nas 'bras bu thob pa'o //
NK122(kho)002:9106: dbang po tha mas zag bcas pa la mi tshe bdun thogs /
NK122(kho)002:9107: dbang po rab la mi tshe lnga'i nang du 'grub pa yang bshad do //
NK122(kho)002:9108: lta spyod gong 'og can te mi tshe lnga /
NK122(kho)002:9110: skye ba gong gi kri ya'i skabs dang 'dra ba las zag med kyi yun no //
NK122(kho)002:9112: de mthar lus kyi zag pa /
NK122(kho)002:9114: skye gnas kyi zag pa gsum zad par gyur nas /
NK122(kho)002:9115: phyag rgya chen po'i rig 'dzin thob par 'gyur ro //
NK122(kho)002:9116: de lta bu'i bsam gtan gyi lam la rnam par gnas te /
NK122(kho)002:9117: zag med la brgya phrag bcu drug tshun chad kyi yun thog /
NK122(kho)002:9118: de nas mthar thug gi 'bras bu thob pa'o //
NK122(kho)002:9121: rigs bzhi rdo rje 'chang gis zhes pa ni /
NK122(kho)002:9122: rigs gsum dbyer med pa la rigs bzhi rdo rje 'chang gi sa zer /
NK122(kho)002:9124: de bzhin gshegs pa'i rigs dang /
NK122(kho)002:9125: chos dbyings ye shes spyir khar btang nas rigs bzhi bshad pa yang 'dug /
NK122(kho)002:9126: gang yin na'ang u pa ya'i gang zag des chos
NK122(kho)002:9127: lugs bzhin nyams su blangs na mthar thug gi 'bras
NK122(kho)002:9128: bu thob par gdon mi za'o //
NK122(kho)002:9129: lung gis zhabs bsdu ba ni go sla'o //
NK122(kho)002:9130: theg pa rim pa dgu yod kyang /
NK122(kho)002:9131: rang sa ma zin pa gnyis yod pas /
NK122(kho)002:9132: rgyud gsang ba snying po'i nang du /
NK122(kho)002:9133: theg pa dgu la spyi lung bdun du bshad de /
NK122(kho)002:9134: phyogs rtogs zhes smos pa nyan thos la bzhag gis
NK122(kho)002:9135: rang sangs rgyas la rtogs pa lhag po yod kyang
NK122(kho)002:9137: u pa la lta spyod gong 'og gi rjes su
NK122(kho)002:9138: 'brangs pas rang sa ma zin pas rang sangs rgyas
NK122(kho)002:9139: dang de gnyis spyi lung du mi brtsi ba'i dbang
NK122(kho)002:9141: shin tu gsang ba'i man ngag gi le'u las kyang /
NK122(kho)002:9143: dgongs pa zhes pa yo gar bstan pa'o //
NK122(kho)002:9144: rnal 'byor theg pa la gsum ste /
NK122(kho)002:9147: rnal 'byor zhes pa ni yul ma skyes pa chos
NK122(kho)002:9148: kyi dbyings don dam pa'i rnal ma la nang 'dzin
NK122(kho)002:9149: sems bdag med pa rang rig pa'i ye shes kyi
NK122(kho)002:9150: blo 'byor bas rnal 'byor zhes bya ste /
NK122(kho)002:9152: rnal 'byor thabs kyi ma yin la //
NK122(kho)002:9153: rnal 'byor shes rab kyis kyang min //
NK122(kho)002:9154: thabs dang shes rab dbyer med na //
NK122(kho)002:9155: rnal 'byor zhes ni de la bya //
NK122(kho)002:9157: theg pa zhes pa ni 'degs par byed pa'i don gyis na'o //
NK122(kho)002:9158: rnam pa bdun zhes pa ni /
NK122(kho)002:9159: 'jug sgo la sogs bdun du dbye bar shes par bya'o //
NK122(kho)002:9160: rgyas par bshad pa la bdun ste /
NK122(kho)002:9164: rnal 'byor rnam gnyis te dbyings dang ye shes dbyer
NK122(kho)002:9165: med gtan la phab pa ni 'jug pa'i sgo yin
NK122(kho)002:9168: phyi rol gyi yul nang 'dzin pa'i sems dang gnas
NK122(kho)002:9169: 'di dag kun ni phyi gzung ba'i yul dngos por
NK122(kho)002:9170: ma skyes pa'i chos kyi dbyings dang /
NK122(kho)002:9171: nang 'dzin pa'i sems bdag med de ye shes kyi ngang du rtogs pa'i phyir /
NK122(kho)002:9172: de nyid chu dang chu'i rlabs bzhin /
NK122(kho)002:9173: ye nas dbyer med par rtogs pa na rnal 'byor yo ga zhes bya ba'i lta ba yin /
NK122(kho)002:9174: gzhan yang rnal 'byor yo ga'i lta ba gtan la
NK122(kho)002:9175: dbab tshul bye brag rgya chen po yod pa yo
NK122(kho)002:9176: ga'i rgyud gzhung gzhan du brtsal bar bya'o //
NK122(kho)002:9179: mngon par byang chub rnam lnga yis /
NK122(kho)002:9181: gong gi don de nyid rtogs shing /
NK122(kho)002:9182: kun rdzob tu phung po khams dang skye mched 'di
NK122(kho)002:9183: nyid rigs lnga rdo rje dbyings kyi dkyil 'khor du
NK122(kho)002:9184: 'dod / dper na lugs ma lugs sgrom nas ma phyung ba'am /
NK122(kho)002:9185: tsha tsha skos phor nas ma phyung ba bzhin du
NK122(kho)002:9186: 'di ltar kun rdzob tu snang 'di lha'i ngo bor
NK122(kho)002:9187: 'dod de / de nyid mngon byang lnga'i sgo nas rang gi lha'i skur bskyed de /
NK122(kho)002:9189: stong pa chos nyid la mngon par byang chub pa /
NK122(kho)002:9197: mchod pa'i cho 'phrul dang bzhi yis rgyud sbyangs nas /
NK122(kho)002:9198: ye shes dam tshig dbyer med par bstim pa ni rnal 'byor theg pa'i ting 'dzin yin no //
NK122(kho)002:9201: rnal 'byor theg pa'i spyod pa ni /
NK122(kho)002:9202: phyi yo byad la gtsor mi 'dzin cing yal bar
NK122(kho)002:9203: dor ba lta bu ma yin cing sems kyi spyod
NK122(kho)002:9204: pa ting 'dzin gyi cho 'phrul du sgom pa yin
NK122(kho)002:9205: te / ngag gi spyod pa sngags dang tshigs su bcad pa'i dbyangs kyi bye brag dang /
NK122(kho)002:9206: lus kyi spyod pa gar stabs dang phyag rgya sna
NK122(kho)002:9207: tshogs byed pa la sogs pas rang gzhan gyi don
NK122(kho)002:9208: byed pa'o // de dag 'dzom pas 'bras bu 'grub
NK122(kho)002:9209: pa la kri ya ltar rdzas dang yo byad gtsor
NK122(kho)002:9210: byed pa'o // ma gsungs kyang / 'byor pa'i tshogs pa mchog tu bshad do //
NK122(kho)002:9215: spyir bsrung ba'i tshul khrims kyi bye brag ni /
NK122(kho)002:9216: 'og ma mtshan nyid theg pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:9217: bya spyod rgyud kyi theg pa'i bsrung bya rnams dang
NK122(kho)002:9218: ldan bzhin du rang gzhung gi dam tshig dgu ste
NK122(kho)002:9222: slob dpon dang grogs tshangs pa mtshungs pa la /
NK122(kho)002:9223: gdung sems rgyun mi chad pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:9224: mchod pa'i yo byad phud mi nyams zhing gtsang mar bya ba dang /
NK122(kho)002:9225: nyon mongs pa rang rgyud pa dang lhan cig mi gnas pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:9226: 'chad pa'i dbang ma thob par chos mi bshad pa dang bzhi'o //
NK122(kho)002:9227: khyad par rigs lnga'i dam tshig go //
NK122(kho)002:9229: khyad par rigs lnga'i dam tshig 'di dag ni yo ga'i lugs la mchog tu bshad pa'o //
NK122(kho)002:9230: de yang phyi nyan thos kyi sdom pa /
NK122(kho)002:9231: bar byang chub sems dpa'i sdom pa /
NK122(kho)002:9232: nang gsang sngags kyi sdom pa gsum mi spang pa ni bde gshegs rigs kyi dam tshig go /
NK122(kho)002:9233: bla ma rdo rje slob dpon rtag tu bkur ba dang /
NK122(kho)002:9234: thabs shes rab gnyis kyi ngo bo rdo rje dril
NK122(kho)002:9235: bu dang ldan zhing 'chang ba ni rdo rje rigs
NK122(kho)002:9238: zang zing gi sbyin pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:9239: mi 'jigs pa byams pa'i sbyin pa gsum dang ldan pa ni rin chen rigs kyi dam tshig go //
NK122(kho)002:9242: gsang ba sngags kyi theg pa ste /
NK122(kho)002:9243: 'di gsum la nyan bsam byed pa ni /
NK122(kho)002:9244: pad+ma rigs kyi dam tshig go //
NK122(kho)002:9245: yar 'phags tshogs rtag tu mchod pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:9246: mar sems can la sbyin pa byed pa ni /
NK122(kho)002:9247: las kyi rigs kyi dam tshig go //
NK122(kho)002:9248: gong gi de dag rnams rnal 'byor yo ga'i bsrung ba'i dam tshig yin no //
NK122(kho)002:9249: rigs lnga'i sdom bzung 'di rnams la chos mthun gyi
NK122(kho)002:9250: sgo nas zhib tu bshad rgyu yod kyang yi ge
NK122(kho)002:9251: mang gis dogs pa'i phyir ma bris so //
NK122(kho)002:9254: mi tshe gsum gyi nang rol du /
NK122(kho)002:9256: de ni zag bcas kyi yun yin pas go sla'o //
NK122(kho)002:9257: las dang nyon mongs kun byang nas //
NK122(kho)002:9258: khams gsum 'jigs sogs zag pa bral //
NK122(kho)002:9259: de tshe bcu drug tshun chad kyis //
NK122(kho)002:9260: phra rags shes bya'i sgrib byang nas //
NK122(kho)002:9262: 'bras bu sangs rgyas thob pa'i zag med kyi yun yin no //
NK122(kho)002:9263: 'di yang go sla bas ma 'grel lo //
NK122(kho)002:9266: stug po bkod pa'i sa non ste //
NK122(kho)002:9267: rdzogs sangs rgyas su nges par 'gyur //
NK122(kho)002:9269: yo ga'i theg pa'i lugs kyis 'bras bu'i mthar thug sangs rgyas la sbyor tshul ni /
NK122(kho)002:9270: yun ring na lo stong drug brgyar shes bya'i sgrib
NK122(kho)002:9271: pa mthar zad nas 'og min stug po bkod pa'i
NK122(kho)002:9272: sa non cing / sku lnga lhun grub tu sangs rgyas so //
NK122(kho)002:9274: gtsang ma'i rigs dag spangs pa yi //
NK122(kho)002:9275: 'og min zhes bya'i nyams dga' der //
NK122(kho)002:9276: yang dag sangs rgyas der sangs rgyas //
NK122(kho)002:9279: zhing khams 'di ni 'jig med yin te /
NK122(kho)002:9280: 'og min stug po nyams dga' der //
NK122(kho)002:9281: sdug po zhing khams 'jig med pa //
NK122(kho)002:9282: de na sangs rgyas rnams kyi chos //
NK122(kho)002:9285: kha cig bde ba can la sogs pa yang longs
NK122(kho)002:9286: sku'i zhing khams su 'dod pa ni gyi na ste
NK122(kho)002:9287: / longs sprul gnyis kyi bye brag ma shes par rang dgar smra ba yin te /
NK122(kho)002:9288: zhing der nges pa lnga ldan med pa'i phyir ro //
NK122(kho)002:9289: longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku ni /
NK122(kho)002:9290: 'byung ba'i rdul las grub pa'i gong bu ni ma yin te /
NK122(kho)002:9291: ye shes kyi ngo bo'i sku snang la rang bzhin med cing mtshan nyid yongs su rdzogs pa /
NK122(kho)002:9292: mtshan dang dpe byad kyis mdzes pa /
NK122(kho)002:9293: sku'i mthar sus kyang rtogs par mi nus shing 'khor
NK122(kho)002:9294: ba ci srid gnas kyi bar du rgyun mi chad
NK122(kho)002:9295: par bzhugs so // lung gis zhabs bsdu ba'o //
NK122(kho)002:9297: dgongs pa 'dus pa'i lung las kyang ni 'di skad gsungs /
NK122(kho)002:9298: dbyings skye ba med pa'i sems nyid de bslab bya'i
NK122(kho)002:9299: yul mngon byang lnga las rtsal rdzogs te bsgom bya'i
NK122(kho)002:9300: yul de nyid rig pa'i ye shes kyis mngon sum
NK122(kho)002:9301: du mthong nas mngon byang lnga'i mtshan ma de nyid
NK122(kho)002:9302: mtshan med kyi gnas lugs der ni mngon sum du
NK122(kho)002:9303: byas nas mi tshe gsum gyi nang du phyag rgya
NK122(kho)002:9305: de nas zag med kyi yun la lo stong drug
NK122(kho)002:9306: brgya la blo sbyangs nas 'bras bu rnal 'byor stug
NK122(kho)002:9307: po bkod pa'i sa thob bo //
NK122(kho)002:9308: zhes gsungs lung gi bgrod dang gsal zhes pa ni go sla'o //
NK122(kho)002:9309: dbang bsgyur thabs kyi theg pa la gnyis te /
NK122(kho)002:9313: gsang sngags phyi nang gi shan phye ba dang /
NK122(kho)002:9314: dbang bsgyur thabs kyi theg pa'i sgra don dang /
NK122(kho)002:9316: shan 'byed pa la lta ba dang /
NK122(kho)002:9318: dang po ni don dam mtha' bral dang /
NK122(kho)002:9319: kun rdzob dag ma dag gnyis su 'dzin pa ni phyi pa yin te /
NK122(kho)002:9321: don dam du ni dbyer med de //
NK122(kho)002:9322: kun rdzob tu ni thams cad la //
NK122(kho)002:9323: dag dang ma dag gnyis kar 'dzin //
NK122(kho)002:9326: don dam rang byung gi ye shes la /
NK122(kho)002:9327: kun rdzob tu 'khor 'das gnyis med lha'i dkyil 'khor du 'dod pa yin te /
NK122(kho)002:9329: thabs kyi theg pa chen po ni //
NK122(kho)002:9330: rnam par byang dang sdug bsngal dag /
NK122(kho)002:9331: kun rdzob tu yang dbyer med de //
NK122(kho)002:9332: lta ba mtho dman de tsam mo //
NK122(kho)002:9335: khrus dang gtsang sbra la sogs dag gtsang gi spyod pa ni phyi pa yin te /
NK122(kho)002:9337: khrus dang gtsang sbra spyod pa 'bad //
NK122(kho)002:9339: gsang sngags nang pas ni bzang ngan gnyis med kyi lta ba rtogs nas /
NK122(kho)002:9340: sbyor sgrol la sogs pa rnams la spyod pa ni nang pa yin te /
NK122(kho)002:9342: sbyor sgrol ma byin len pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:9343: rdzun smra ngag barlanga spyod pa lnga //
NK122(kho)002:9345: sgom pa'i ting nge 'dzin la gnyis /
NK122(kho)002:9346: mtshan bcas dang mtshan med do //
NK122(kho)002:9347: mtshan med ni yo ga bas chos nyid mtha' brgyad
NK122(kho)002:9348: dang bral ba'i ting nge 'dzin gtsor byed pas bdag
NK122(kho)002:9349: nyid chen po ma rtogs pas phyi pa yin la
NK122(kho)002:9350: / nang pas rig pa rang gsal yul bral gyi
NK122(kho)002:9351: ting nge 'dzin zhe 'dod phra ba'ang mi mnga' bar
NK122(kho)002:9352: rang rig gi ngo bo yin pas na nang pa'o
NK122(kho)002:9353: / // mtshan bcas la lha'i sku mngon byang lnga las /
NK122(kho)002:9354: bskyed pa ni phyi pa yin la /
NK122(kho)002:9355: cho 'phrul bzhi'i bskyed pa ni nang pa'o //
NK122(kho)002:9356: yab rkyang du sgom pa phyi pa yin la /
NK122(kho)002:9357: yab yum zhal sbyor du sgom pa ni nang pa'o //
NK122(kho)002:9358: 'khor thugs ka nas spro ba ni phyi pa yin la /
NK122(kho)002:9359: gsang gnas nas spro ba ni nang pa'o //
NK122(kho)002:9360: zhi ba gtso che ba ni phyi pa yin la /
NK122(kho)002:9361: zhi khro gnyis ka sgom pa ni nang pa'o //
NK122(kho)002:9362: rgyan cha zhi ba'i rgyan cha dang ldan pa ni phyi pa yin la /
NK122(kho)002:9363: dpal chas rnams dang ldan pa ni nang pa'o //
NK122(kho)002:9364: rdzogs rim khyad sna rtse dang /
NK122(kho)002:9366: smin mtshams kyi thig le tsam la brten pa ni phyi pa yin la /
NK122(kho)002:9367: 'khor lo bzhi dang chags lam gyi thabs rnams ni nang pa'o //
NK122(kho)002:9369: cha rkyen nyer lnga la sogs pa dag gtsang la spyod pa ni phyi pa yin la /
NK122(kho)002:9370: spyod pa'i dngos po nyi shu la spyod pa ni nang pa'o //
NK122(kho)002:9374: 'dod yon lnga dang dag gtsang gi mchod pa rnams la gtsor byed pa phyi pa yin la /
NK122(kho)002:9375: phyi'i mchod pa de rnams kyi steng du /
NK122(kho)002:9376: nang gi mchod pa gtor ma dang /
NK122(kho)002:9378: dug gsum gyi mchod pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:9379: gsang ba sbyor sgrol gyi mchod pa nyams su len pa ni nang pa'o //
NK122(kho)002:9380: dngos grub len tshul yang ye shes pa mnyes pas
NK122(kho)002:9381: bdag dag pa dngos grub kyi snod du rung bar
NK122(kho)002:9383: bsnyen bsgrub rnam bzhi'i sgo nas dngos grub blang ba rang las shar bar blta ba ni nang pa'o //
NK122(kho)002:9384: dbang yang rdo rje slob dpon gyi dbang man chad len pa phyi pa yin la /
NK122(kho)002:9385: zab mo'i dbang gsum len pa ni nang pa'o //
NK122(kho)002:9387: 'khor 'das gnyis kyis bsdus pa'i chos thams cad yul
NK122(kho)002:9388: med rang snang sku dang ye shes su dbang bsgyur
NK122(kho)002:9389: bas na dbang bsgyur ces bya'o //
NK122(kho)002:9390: dper na rma byas dug la dbang bsgyur nas bkrags mdangs phun sum tshogs pa lta bu'o //
NK122(kho)002:9393: thabs mkhas che dang mang yas yangs //
NK122(kho)002:9394: bsgyur dang rlab che cir yang ston //
NK122(kho)002:9396: 'og ma'i spang bya nyon mongs pa nyid la spyad
NK122(kho)002:9397: kyang spyad bya spyad byed med cing 'bras bu'i ngo
NK122(kho)002:9398: bor gsal bas na thabs mkhas shing rgya che /
NK122(kho)002:9400: zhi rgyas dbang drag lhun gyis grub pas gzhan don rtsol med du snang bas thabs mang /
NK122(kho)002:9402: thabs mkhas bsam gyis mi khyab par snang ba'o //
NK122(kho)002:9404: 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad la blang dor med cing ci yang mi shong ba med pa'o //
NK122(kho)002:9405: gsum pa dbye ba ni gsum yin te /
NK122(kho)002:9409: ma h+aa yo ga 'di la rgya gar na tan+t+ra sde bco brgyad du yod pa las /
NK122(kho)002:9413: de dag gi man ngag phra mo drug cu rtsa bzhi dang bcas pa /
NK122(kho)002:9414: rgya gar gyi mkhas pa chen po bi ma mi
NK122(kho)002:9415: tras zhu chen gyi lo ts+aa ba rin chen mchog
NK122(kho)002:9416: la gsungs so // de ni gzhung 'di nyid brtsams
NK122(kho)002:9417: mkhan gyi dam pa bde bar gshegs par grags so
NK122(kho)002:9418: la gsungs so // // de yang sgyu 'phrul sde brgyad gang zhe na /
NK122(kho)002:9419: sems dang ye shes rang snang du ston pa sgyu
NK122(kho)002:9420: 'phrul rtsa ba'i rgyud gsang ba'i snying po dang gcig
NK122(kho)002:9421: / rol pa mngon par brjod pa lha mo sgyu 'phrul dang gnyis /
NK122(kho)002:9422: dkyil 'khor rdzogs par ston pa sgyu 'phrul brgyad pa dang gsum /
NK122(kho)002:9423: phrin las rdzogs par bstan pa sgyu 'phrul bzhi bcu pa dang bzhi /
NK122(kho)002:9424: dbang gtso bor ston pa sgyu 'phrul bla ma dang lnga /
NK122(kho)002:9425: yon tan mthar phyin pa sgyu 'phrul brgyad cu pa dang drug /
NK122(kho)002:9426: sde snod yongs la khyab par ston pa sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba chen po dang bdun /
NK122(kho)002:9427: dam tshig mchog tu ston pa sgyu 'phrul le'u lag dang brgyad do //
NK122(kho)002:9429: grol lam rim gyis dang cig char ston pa ye shes snying po dang /
NK122(kho)002:9431: thabs lam rim gyis dang cig char ston pa sgyu 'phrul thal pa dang rgya mtsho gnyis dang bzhi'o //
NK122(kho)002:9432: man ngag phra mo drug cu rtsa bzhi ni logs su shes par bya'o //
NK122(kho)002:9433: 'dir tshig tshogs mang gis dogs pa'i phyir ma bkod do //
NK122(kho)002:9434: de rnams kyis spyi don gyi bshad pa de song nas /
NK122(kho)002:9436: dbang bsgyur thabs kyi theg pa la gnyis te /
NK122(kho)002:9437: gang zag dang theg pa'i sgo nas mdor bstan pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:9438: yan lag rgyas par bshad pa'o //
NK122(kho)002:9440: dbang bsgyur thabs kyis theg pa yang //
NK122(kho)002:9441: gdul bya'i blo shed khyad par gyis //
NK122(kho)002:9442: rnam pa gsum du snang ba de //
NK122(kho)002:9443: bskyed dang rdzogs dang shin tu rdzogs //
NK122(kho)002:9444: 'di rnams ni go sla ba yin no //
NK122(kho)002:9445: rgyas par bshad pa la gsum ste /
NK122(kho)002:9446: bskyed pa ma h+aa yo ga dang /
NK122(kho)002:9447: rdzogs pa a nu yo ga dang /
NK122(kho)002:9448: rdzogs pa chen po a ti yo ga'o //
NK122(kho)002:9455: tha ma bskyed pa'i rnal 'byor yang //
NK122(kho)002:9456: bdun du nges par snang ba ste //
NK122(kho)002:9458: rgyas par bshad pa la bdun ste /
NK122(kho)002:9460: gang zag dang 'jug sgo thun mong du bstan pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:9462: de la ma h+aa yo ga'i rten gyi gang zag
NK122(kho)002:9463: ni dbang bsgyur thabs kyi theg pa dbang po mchog
NK122(kho)002:9465: de'i nang na gsum yod pa'i tha ma ni ma h+aa yo ga yin /
NK122(kho)002:9466: de yang gong ma la ltos na 'di la lta spyod sgom pa ched 'dzin can zhes zer ro //
NK122(kho)002:9467: 'on kyang gsang sngags ma h+aa yo ga'i rten gyi
NK122(kho)002:9468: gang zag 'di nyid blo'i mtshan nyid bdun ldan cig
NK122(kho)002:9470: de yang blo mtho ba ni nam mkha' lta bu /
NK122(kho)002:9471: brtan pa ni ri rab lta bu /
NK122(kho)002:9473: rno ba ral gri lta bu /
NK122(kho)002:9474: rgya che ba sa gzhi lta bu /
NK122(kho)002:9475: yangs pa bar snang lta bu /
NK122(kho)002:9476: zab pa rgya mtsho lta bu dang bdun yin no //
NK122(kho)002:9478: mtho brtan myur rno rgya che dang //
NK122(kho)002:9479: zab yongs rgyu yi gang zag yin //
NK122(kho)002:9481: de yang rang bzhin gyis dbang rnon dang /
NK122(kho)002:9482: sbyangs pa'i dbang rnon gnyis bshad pa'o //
NK122(kho)002:9483: dang po ni sngar nges 'byung gi theg pa la
NK122(kho)002:9484: blo ma sbyangs kyang ma h+aa la 'jug nus pa'o
NK122(kho)002:9485: // phyi ma ni sngar nges 'byung gi theg pa
NK122(kho)002:9486: la sbyangs nas ma h+aa la 'jug nus pa yin
NK122(kho)002:9488: de yang rang bzhin sbyangs pa yis //
NK122(kho)002:9489: snod du gyur pa nye ring phyir //
NK122(kho)002:9490: rim dang gcig char bzhi cha yis //
NK122(kho)002:9493: 'jug sgo ni ma h+aa yo ga'i lugs la /
NK122(kho)002:9494: thabs 'gag pa med pa dang shes rab mi dmigs
NK122(kho)002:9495: pa gnyis dbyer med pa'i sgor zhugs pas lam gyi
NK122(kho)002:9496: gnad 'gag thams cad chod cing mi 'gyur ba'o //
NK122(kho)002:9497: de yang lam la thabs shes rab gnyis ka dgos so //
NK122(kho)002:9499: thabs shes lag pa bkru ba yin te /
NK122(kho)002:9500: lag pa bkru ba'i dus su gcig la brten nas gcig gi dri ma bkru nas dag pa'o //
NK122(kho)002:9501: de bzhin du thabs la brten nas shes rab stong zhen gyi dri ma dag /
NK122(kho)002:9502: shes rab la brten nas thabs dngos 'dzin gyi dri ma dag pa'i go ba blang bar bya'o //
NK122(kho)002:9505: lha yab yum bsgom pa 'bras bu dbyings ye shes gnyis so //
NK122(kho)002:9506: gsang sngags kyi lam la gnad che ba thabs shes
NK122(kho)002:9507: gnyis yin pas zhib tu ngo sprad rgyu yod pa
NK122(kho)002:9508: gsang sngags la mnga' brnyes pa'i bla ma rnams kyi
NK122(kho)002:9510: 'di rje btsun gong ma rnams kyi gsung sgros kyis rtogs dgos pa'i phyir 'dir ma bkod do //
NK122(kho)002:9511: de la thog mar 'jug sgo ni mtshan nyid dang
NK122(kho)002:9512: ldan pa'i bla ma la smin lam dbang bzhi yongs
NK122(kho)002:9513: su rdzogs par blang dgos te /
NK122(kho)002:9515: slob dpon mnyes par ma byas shing //
NK122(kho)002:9516: dbang rnams thob par ma byas par //
NK122(kho)002:9517: nyan pa la sogs rtsom pa rnams //
NK122(kho)002:9520: de la thog mar dbang bzhis chos sgo phye lugs ni /
NK122(kho)002:9521: phyi bum pa'i dbang gis phung khams skye mched rgyal
NK122(kho)002:9522: ba'i dkyil 'khor du ngo sprad nas bskyed rim sgom
NK122(kho)002:9524: nang gsang ba'i dbang gis rtsa gnas kyi yi ge
NK122(kho)002:9525: sbyangs na sems rtog med du ngo sprad de thabs
NK122(kho)002:9526: lam steng sgo rtsa thig rlung gsum sgom pa'i chos
NK122(kho)002:9527: sgo phye / shes rab ye shes kyi dbang gis
NK122(kho)002:9528: gsang ba'i dkyil 'khor du bcug nas bde stong gnyis
NK122(kho)002:9530: thabs lam 'og sgo bde ba bcud 'dus sam /
NK122(kho)002:9531: mkhas gsang byin gyis brlabs pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:9532: lha yab yum 'khril sbyor sgom pa'i chos sgo phye /
NK122(kho)002:9533: dbang bzhi pa bskur bas sems kyi ngo bo sku
NK122(kho)002:9534: lnga lhun grub kyi sangs rgyas su ngo sprad pas
NK122(kho)002:9535: zhi rdzogs phyag gsum gyi sgo nas sems kyi gnas
NK122(kho)002:9536: lugs ci bzhin pa ngo sprad pa'i chos sgo phye
NK122(kho)002:9537: ba'o // 'di rnams kyi don rgyas par shes 'dod na /
NK122(kho)002:9538: dbang bzhi ngo sprad kyi stong thun kho bos byas nas yod pa der gzigs mdzod /
NK122(kho)002:9539: de nas thabs grol gnyis la 'jug dgos te /
NK122(kho)002:9540: grol lam bskyed rdzogs gnyis kyi sgo nas 'jug pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:9541: thabs kyi sgo nas 'jug pa la thabs lam steng
NK122(kho)002:9542: sgo la 'jug na rtsa thig rlung gsum la blo
NK122(kho)002:9543: sbyang ba dang / thabs lam 'og sgo la 'jug
NK122(kho)002:9544: pa shes rab yum la bsten pa la sogs pa'i
NK122(kho)002:9545: bye brag nang tshan mi 'dra ba kun /
NK122(kho)002:9546: gong gi 'jug sgo de dag kun kyang thabs dang shes rab dbyer med pa'i sgo nas 'jug pa'o //
NK122(kho)002:9547: gong gi de lta bu rnams ni gsang sngags gnyis
NK122(kho)002:9548: med kyi don rnal ma la rang rig pa'i ye
NK122(kho)002:9550: yo ga man chad las dpag pas chen po zhes bya'o //
NK122(kho)002:9551: de lta bu ma h+aa yo ga zhes bya'i 'jug pa'i sgo yin no //
NK122(kho)002:9552: theg pa 'di'i lugs kyi lta ba gtan tshig gis gtan la 'bebs par byed pa la /
NK122(kho)002:9553: sngon byung dngos po lnga'i gtan tshig /
NK122(kho)002:9556: tshig la dpyad du yod pas go ba dang /
NK122(kho)002:9557: dpyad du med pas go ba gnyis /
NK122(kho)002:9558: dpyad du yod pas go ba la tshig don mthun pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:9560: tshig don mi mthun pa la yang kun yin gang yin gyi gtan tshig dang /
NK122(kho)002:9561: mi spangs mi ldan gyi gtan tshig go //
NK122(kho)002:9562: tshig don mthun pa'i gtan tshig la /
NK122(kho)002:9563: tshad ma bka' gzhung gi gtan tshig /
NK122(kho)002:9564: sgra mthun don dpag gi gtan tshig /
NK122(kho)002:9565: gcig dang du bral gyi gtan tshig /
NK122(kho)002:9566: bdag nyid chen po'i gtan tshig go //
NK122(kho)002:9567: tshad ma bka' gzhung gi gtan tshig la /
NK122(kho)002:9571: 'di rnams kyi don rgyas par gsang sngags ma h+aa
NK122(kho)002:9572: yo ga'i lta ba gtan tshig gis rgyas par gtan
NK122(kho)002:9573: la phab pa ni lam rim le'u gnyis pa ltar
NK122(kho)002:9574: shes par bya'o // de yang gzhung lugs 'di'i nang
NK122(kho)002:9575: du bkod pa de dag gtan tshig de rnams kyi
NK122(kho)002:9576: nang nas gang yin snyam na /
NK122(kho)002:9577: dag mnyam gyi gtan tshig dang /
NK122(kho)002:9578: bden gsum dbyer med kyi gtan tshig gnyis yin par shes par bya'o //
NK122(kho)002:9580: gsang ba snying po'i lung la dpang po mdzad nas //
NK122(kho)002:9581: snod bcud rgyud rnams dag rtogs shing //
NK122(kho)002:9582: mnyam gnyis lhag pa'i mnyam gnyis kyis //
NK122(kho)002:9584: snod 'byung ba lnga yum lngar dag /
NK122(kho)002:9585: bcud phung po lnga yab lngar dag /
NK122(kho)002:9586: rgyud rnam shes tshogs brgyad ye shes lngar dag pa ste /
NK122(kho)002:9587: phung po dang khams dang skye mched rnams lha dang
NK122(kho)002:9588: lha mo'i dkyil 'khor du dag pa la dgongs pa'o
NK122(kho)002:9589: // de rnams spyi don gyis bshad pa yin la /
NK122(kho)002:9590: gzhung don bshad na lta ba la gsum ste /
NK122(kho)002:9592: rtog tshogs thabs ma 'gag pa rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor
NK122(kho)002:9593: du kun tu bzang po'i rol par bstan pa dang
NK122(kho)002:9595: phyi snod 'byung ba lnga nang bcud phung po lnga
NK122(kho)002:9596: la sogs pa'i 'jig rten gyi chos 'di rnams ye'am
NK122(kho)002:9597: thog ma med pa'i dus nas rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor
NK122(kho)002:9598: yin te / phung po chen po lnga nyid bde gshegs rigs lnga yin te /
NK122(kho)002:9601: sgra don dbye ba dang gsum /
NK122(kho)002:9603: gzugs kyi mtshan nyid gzhig cing gzhom du rung ba'am skye rung zhing /
NK122(kho)002:9605: rnam shes yul gcod cing rig par byed pa /
NK122(kho)002:9606: tshor ba nyams su myong ba /
NK122(kho)002:9608: 'du byed yang nas yang du mngon par 'du byed pa'o //
NK122(kho)002:9610: phung po'i bye brag rnams phyogs gcig tu 'dus pa la phung po zhes bya'o //
NK122(kho)002:9611: dbye ba la gzugs can bco lnga /
NK122(kho)002:9612: de yang rgyu'i gzugs bzhi ni sa chu me rlung bzhi'o //
NK122(kho)002:9616: rnam par rig byed ma yin pa'i gzugs dang bco lnga'o //
NK122(kho)002:9617: gzugs 'di bcos slad dang bral ba rnam par snang mdzad do //
NK122(kho)002:9618: rnam shes kyi dbye ba la /
NK122(kho)002:9623: 'di gzhi gdod ma nas bcos slad dang bral ba mi bskyod pa'o //
NK122(kho)002:9625: bzang ngan bar gsum gyis phye bas bco brgyad do //
NK122(kho)002:9626: 'di gnas su dag nas rin chen 'byung ldan du gyur pa'o //
NK122(kho)002:9628: rgya che chung zab pa gsum yod pa ni snang ba mtha' yas /
NK122(kho)002:9629: 'du byed la lnga bcu rtsa gcig yod kyang /
NK122(kho)002:9630: tshor 'du gnyis gong du song nas /
NK122(kho)002:9631: da bzhi bcu rtsa dgu ngos bzung na /
NK122(kho)002:9632: reg pa dbang yul rnam shes /
NK122(kho)002:9633: yid la byed pa sems gtod pa /
NK122(kho)002:9634: sems dpa' dang ni gsum ni kun 'agro'o //
NK122(kho)002:9635: las mos gzhan du mi g.yo /
NK122(kho)002:9646: ste yul so sor nges pa lnga'o //
NK122(kho)002:9653: 'dod chags med pa'i dge ba'i rtsa ba /
NK122(kho)002:9655: zhe sdang med pa'i dge ba'i rtsa ba /
NK122(kho)002:9657: gti mug med pa'i chos don shes /
NK122(kho)002:9661: shin lus sems las su rung /
NK122(kho)002:9668: mi 'tshe ba ste dge ba bcu gcig dang /
NK122(kho)002:9678: don dang mi mthun pa log lta the tshom dmigs pa la som nyid /
NK122(kho)002:9679: ste rtsa ba'i nyon mongs pa drug /
NK122(kho)002:9705: mi dge ba la goms pa /
NK122(kho)002:9709: yon tan can la mi gus /
NK122(kho)002:9718: shes bzhin mi gtsang ba'i phung po la sogs la gtsang ba ltar zhen pa /
NK122(kho)002:9719: ma yin pa ste nye ba'i nyon mongs pa nyi shu'o //
NK122(kho)002:9726: dpyod pa ste sems zhib pa /
NK122(kho)002:9727: gzhan du 'gyur ba bzhi dang zhe dagu'o //
NK122(kho)002:9728: 'di rnams gzhi gdod ma nas rnam par dag pa don yod grub pa'o //
NK122(kho)002:9729: 'byung lnga shes rab dbyings phyug lnga /
NK122(kho)002:9735: nam mkha' dbyings kyi dbang phyug ma dang lnga /
NK122(kho)002:9736: gong gi snod bcud de dag thams cad dbyer med
NK122(kho)002:9737: pa'i khyad par las rtog tshogs khams dang skye mched
NK122(kho)002:9738: thams cad sems dpa' dang sems ma yin te /
NK122(kho)002:9739: de yang mig gi rnam par shes pa sa'i snying po /
NK122(kho)002:9740: rna ba'i rnam par shes pa spyan ras gzigs /
NK122(kho)002:9741: sna'i rnam par shes pa nam mkha'i snying po /
NK122(kho)002:9742: lce'i rnam par shes pa phyag na rdo rje /
NK122(kho)002:9747: mig gi dbang po byams pa /
NK122(kho)002:9748: rna ba'i dbang po sgrib sel /
NK122(kho)002:9749: sna'i dbang po kun tu bzang po /
NK122(kho)002:9754: phyis 'byung ba dri chab ma dang bzhi'o //
NK122(kho)002:9755: rtag chad mthar lta reg pa'i tshogs /
NK122(kho)002:9757: rtag par lta ba mi pham ma /
NK122(kho)002:9758: chad par lta ba khro gnyer ma /
NK122(kho)002:9759: bdag tu lta ba ral gcig ma /
NK122(kho)002:9760: mtshan mar lta ba ro langs ma dang bzhi'o //
NK122(kho)002:9762: lus kyi dbang po sku gshin rje gshed /
NK122(kho)002:9763: rnam par shes pa thugs stobs po che /
NK122(kho)002:9764: gsang ba'i yul gsung rta mgrin /
NK122(kho)002:9765: gsum 'dus kyi reg pa phrin las bdud rtsi 'khyil ba dang bzhi'o //
NK122(kho)002:9766: rtog tshogs de dag khro bo khro mo'i ngang du gsal ces bya'o //
NK122(kho)002:9767: gong gi tshogs zhes pas ni /
NK122(kho)002:9768: nyon mongs pa drug thub pa drug dang /
NK122(kho)002:9769: yid byed pa po kun tu bzang po dang /
NK122(kho)002:9770: chos bya ba mo kun tu bzang mo rnams sdud pa yin no //
NK122(kho)002:9771: rtog tshogs bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis rgyal ba bzhi bcu
NK122(kho)002:9772: rtsa gnyis su shar ba 'di rnams thams cad rang
NK122(kho)002:9773: rig pa'i ye shes kyi cho 'phrul las kun tu
NK122(kho)002:9774: bzang po'i rol pa 'gag pa med par snang ba
NK122(kho)002:9775: ni / kun rdzob bden pa'i gnas lugs sprul sku sangs rgyas su gnas pa yin te /
NK122(kho)002:9777: rdo rje phung po'i yan lag ni //
NK122(kho)002:9778: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas lnga ru grags //
NK122(kho)002:9779: skye mched khams rnams ma lus kun //
NK122(kho)002:9780: byang chub sems dpa'i dkyil 'khor nyid //
NK122(kho)002:9781: sa chu spyan dang ma ma ki //
NK122(kho)002:9782: me rlung gos dkar sgrol ma ste //
NK122(kho)002:9783: nam mkha' dbyings kyi dbang phyug ma //
NK122(kho)002:9784: srid gsum ye nas sangs rgyas zhing //
NK122(kho)002:9786: rtog tshogs kyi chos 'di rnams la chos mthun rgyu mtshan zhib mo'i sgo nas ngo sprad rgyu dang /
NK122(kho)002:9787: gnas su dag nas lhar gyur pa'i dus su /
NK122(kho)002:9788: sku mdog zhal phyag rgyan cha lugs phyag mtshan bzhugs
NK122(kho)002:9789: tshul rnams rgyas par ngo sprad rgyu yod kyang yi
NK122(kho)002:9790: ge mang gis dogs pa'i phyir ma bris so //
NK122(kho)002:9792: ngo sprod dus ga dar byed mdzod /
NK122(kho)002:9793: shes rab mi dmigs pa kun tu bzang mo'i mkha' dbyings su 'dus ma byas pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:9795: lha dang lha mor snang ba de nyid snang dus
NK122(kho)002:9796: na ngo bo 'dus ma byas rgyu rkyen las ma
NK122(kho)002:9797: skyes pa chos nyid stong pa kun tu bzang mo'i
NK122(kho)002:9798: dbyings 'di ni don dam bden pa chos skur sangs
NK122(kho)002:9801: gzhi rtsa med pa'i sems nyid ni //
NK122(kho)002:9802: pho mo ma yin ma ning min //
NK122(kho)002:9803: mtshan nyid ma yin rigs brgyud min //
NK122(kho)002:9804: kha dog ma yin dbyibs ma yin //
NK122(kho)002:9805: gnas su ma yin gang yang min //
NK122(kho)002:9807: dbyer med byang sems bde ba chen po ma 'dres yongs rdzogs kyi lta ba'o //
NK122(kho)002:9809: de ltar ma skyes pa don dam dang /
NK122(kho)002:9810: kun rdzob ma 'gags pa rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor du
NK122(kho)002:9811: snang ba chu dang gzugs brnyan ltar dbyer med pa
NK122(kho)002:9812: de ni byang sems bde ba chen po de bzhin
NK122(kho)002:9813: nyid yin te / dbyer med bden pa 'di longs skur sangs rgyas pa'o //
NK122(kho)002:9816: 'dus byas snang ba rdo rje nyid //
NK122(kho)002:9817: yin phyir ngo bo tha dad min //
NK122(kho)002:9819: 'di ni rnal 'byor chen po'i lta ba yin no //
NK122(kho)002:9830: gcig ni blo mchog skal ldan rnams //
NK122(kho)002:9831: nges par tshud nas der gnas pa //
NK122(kho)002:9832: gnyis su med pa'i byang chub sems //
NK122(kho)002:9833: sems sgom rnam gsum dus gcig rdzogs //
NK122(kho)002:9835: rim gyis pas lam thar chags su bgrod nas sangs rgyas par 'dod de /
NK122(kho)002:9836: dang po tshogs lam rnal 'byor bzhi ni /
NK122(kho)002:9838: nges pa zhi ba'i dkyil 'khor thams cad kun /
NK122(kho)002:9839: bskyed pa rnam bzhi rim gyis bskyed dgos pa yin te /
NK122(kho)002:9840: lta ba rtogs nas dang po de bzhin nyid kyi
NK122(kho)002:9841: ting nge 'dzin ni rnam pa mchog ldan gyi stong
NK122(kho)002:9842: pa nyid bsgom par bzhed de /
NK122(kho)002:9844: don dam kun gyi rgyu yin phyir //
NK122(kho)002:9845: lhag pa'i rgyu de dang por sgom //
NK122(kho)002:9849: rgya mtsho'i 'jing gi pha bong ltar //
NK122(kho)002:9850: bskal par lam la rtsol byas kyang //
NK122(kho)002:9851: don med snying po skam pa yin //
NK122(kho)002:9853: stong pa de'i don ma rtogs pa'i sems can rnams
NK122(kho)002:9854: la kun tu snang ba'i ting nge 'dzin gyis snying
NK122(kho)002:9855: rje chen po'i rnal 'byor sgom pa yin te /
NK122(kho)002:9857: yongs la snyoms pa'i snying rje gsum //
NK122(kho)002:9860: de yi ma lus chos so cog /
NK122(kho)002:9861: snying po yod pa ma yin te //
NK122(kho)002:9862: sgyu ma mig yor sprul pa ltar //
NK122(kho)002:9863: snying rje chu zla 'ja' tshon bzhin //
NK122(kho)002:9864: bdag dang 'gro ba ngo bo gcig /
NK122(kho)002:9866: de'i rjes su snang stong gnyis med lhag pa'i lha dgu nyid dang bcu sgom dgos pa yin te /
NK122(kho)002:9868: sku gcig rdo rje dril 'bar sgom //
NK122(kho)002:9869: de bzhin nyid du gyur pa dang //
NK122(kho)002:9870: dbu gsum phyag drug nyid du sgom //
NK122(kho)002:9871: gnas gcig ye shes sems dpa' sgom //
NK122(kho)002:9872: spyi mgrin tsit+ta gnas gsum du //
NK122(kho)002:9873: byin rlabs rdo rje gsum bsgom bya //
NK122(kho)002:9874: dbu yi gnas lngar yi ge lnga //
NK122(kho)002:9875: ye shes lnga dbang rdzogs par brgyan //
NK122(kho)002:9877: phyag rgya spros pa la bzhi ste /
NK122(kho)002:9880: zhal phyag rnam grangs spro ba'o //
NK122(kho)002:9881: gzhan rnams logs su shes la /
NK122(kho)002:9883: zhi ba'i dkyil 'khor bsdus pa la bco brgyad /
NK122(kho)002:9884: 'bring po la bzhi bcu zhe gnyis /
NK122(kho)002:9885: rgyas pa la brgyad cu rtsa gnyis yin te /
NK122(kho)002:9887: dang po bco brgyad bzhi bcu gnyis //
NK122(kho)002:9888: rgyas pa'i dkyil 'khor rim par slob //
NK122(kho)002:9890: khro bo'i dkyil 'khor bsdus pa la lnga bcu rtsa brgyad /
NK122(kho)002:9891: 'bring po la drug cu rtsa brgyad /
NK122(kho)002:9892: rgyas pa la brgyad cu rtsa brgyad yod do //
NK122(kho)002:9893: de lta bu'i dkyil 'khor rgyas 'bring bsdus gsum la /
NK122(kho)002:9894: cho 'phrul rnam bzhis gzhung bsrang ba yin te /
NK122(kho)002:9898: mchod pa 'bul ba'i cho 'phrul rnams so //
NK122(kho)002:9899: phyag rgya bzhis gzer gdab dgos te /
NK122(kho)002:9902: thugs dam tshig gi phyag rgya /
NK122(kho)002:9903: 'phro 'du phrin las kyi phyag rgya dang bzhi'o //
NK122(kho)002:9904: 'di rnams kyi don rgyas par bshad rgyu yod kyang yi ges 'jigs pa'i phyir ma bris so //
