NK122(kho)002:9905: dam tshig pa dang ye shes dbyer med du rtogs pa las mi g.yo ba'o //
NK122(kho)002:9907: dus bzhi'i rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor dang /
NK122(kho)002:9909: bsam yas rang bzhin lhun gyis grub pa'i dkyil 'khor la bya'o //
NK122(kho)002:9910: rig pa rang snang gi dkyil 'khor ni sgom pa'i ting nge 'dzin la bya'o //
NK122(kho)002:9911: rtogs pa'i ye shes la gnas te /
NK122(kho)002:9912: de gnyis dper na chu la chu bzhag pa bzhin dbyer med pa'i sku /
NK122(kho)002:9913: ma skyes pa chos nyid shes rab las ma g.yos
NK122(kho)002:9914: par thabs ma 'gags pa rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor du
NK122(kho)002:9915: snang ba de nyid thabs dang shes rab ye nas
NK122(kho)002:9916: dbyer med pa de ni rnal 'byor chen po'i bsam
NK122(kho)002:9917: gtan yin no // spyod pa la gnyis te /
NK122(kho)002:9921: rnal 'byor chen po'i nyams su len pa'i spyod pa ni /
NK122(kho)002:9922: bsnyen bsgrub bzhi dang phrin las bzhi yin no //
NK122(kho)002:9923: de la bsnyen bsgrub yan lag bzhi ni /
NK122(kho)002:9926: dkyil 'khor gcig la brten pa'i bsnyen bsgrub bzhi /
NK122(kho)002:9927: 'di rnams kyi don ni gong na yod bzhin shes par bya'o //
NK122(kho)002:9931: 'bras bu la phrin las bzhi yod pa las /
NK122(kho)002:9932: 'dir da res lam gyi phrin las bzhi /
NK122(kho)002:9933: de la dbye na phyi'i phrin las /
NK122(kho)002:9936: de kho na nyid kyi phrin las so //
NK122(kho)002:9937: 'di rnams sgyu 'phrul ma h+aa yo ga'i spyod pa'i
NK122(kho)002:9938: gtso bo yin pas nyams su len pa yang gal
NK122(kho)002:9939: che / 'di rnams kyi don rgyas par 'dod na
NK122(kho)002:9940: sgyu 'phrul thugs thig gi nang na yod pa bzhin
NK122(kho)002:9941: che / shes par bya'o // 'dir tshig tshogs mang dogs pa'i phyir ro //
NK122(kho)002:9942: spyod pa lnga la sogs pa thabs kyis zin par nyams su blangs bar bya'o //
NK122(kho)002:9944: sbyor sgrol dang la sogs kyi sgras ma byin len pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:9946: ngag barlanga po la sogs spyod pa'i chos 'di bdag
NK122(kho)002:9947: dang gzhan gyi don bsgrub pa'i phyir nyams su blang
NK122(kho)002:9948: ngo // de yang mkhas rtogs kyi gdeng dang ldan
NK122(kho)002:9949: pa ting nge 'dzin dang snying rje dang ldan pa
NK122(kho)002:9950: des thabs kyi zin te nyams su blang bar bya'o
NK122(kho)002:9951: ngo // // des ni bdag gzhan grol bar 'gyur ro //
NK122(kho)002:9952: dam tshig la ga nyis te /
NK122(kho)002:9954: yan lag gi dam tshig go //
NK122(kho)002:9956: rnal 'byor chen po'i dam tshig ni /
NK122(kho)002:9957: byang chub kyi sems la gnyis dang sogs kyi sgras /
NK122(kho)002:9958: sku gsung thugs dang rtsa ba bzhi yi nang tshan
NK122(kho)002:9959: dam tshig nyi shu rtsa dgu'i dbye ba shes par
NK122(kho)002:9960: bya'o // yan lag gi dam tshig la gnyis te /
NK122(kho)002:9962: khyad par gyi yan lag dang /
NK122(kho)002:9964: sbyor sgrol ma byin len pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:9965: rdzun smra ngag barlanga la sogs pa'i spyod pa lnga dang /
NK122(kho)002:9966: 'di'i nang tshan dbye na brgyad cu gya gsum yod do //
NK122(kho)002:9967: mi spangs ba la yang dag pa'i dug lnga la /
NK122(kho)002:9968: lta spyod gnyis gnyis su phye bas bcu /
NK122(kho)002:9969: log pa'i dug lnga dang bco lnga'o //
NK122(kho)002:9970: dang du blangs pa'i dam tshig la sum cu yod pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:9971: bsgrub par bya ba'i dam tshig la bzhi bcu zhe lnga yod pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:9972: shes par bya ba lnga sogs dang zhes pa 'di la dbye na bdun cu yod do //
NK122(kho)002:9973: thun mong gi dam tshig la bdag don nyi shu rtsa gcig dang /
NK122(kho)002:9974: gzhan don bzhi bcu zhe bzhi yod do //
NK122(kho)002:9975: thun mong ma yin pa'i dam tshig gong du bshad pa rnams dang /
NK122(kho)002:9976: 'og nas mdo bzhi brjod bya'i don rnams yin /
NK122(kho)002:9977: bye brag sna tshogs zhes pa nyams rgyu nyi shu dang /
NK122(kho)002:9978: mdo gsum gyi bsrung bya rnams bsdus pa'o //
NK122(kho)002:9979: de rnams la sum brgya drug cu yod pas rgyas pa ni gsal bkra las shes par bya'o //
NK122(kho)002:9980: dam bca' ba 'di rnams dus thams cad du 'da' nyams med par dang du blang ngo //
NK122(kho)002:9985: tshogs lam rnal 'byor bzhi gong du song nas 'dir
NK122(kho)002:9986: sbyor lam bar chad med par tshom bu tshogs bsgrub
NK122(kho)002:9987: pa ni phun sum tshogs pa lngas gzhi bzung /
NK122(kho)002:9988: bsnyen bsgrub bzhis gzhung bsrang lugs lam rim le'u bdun pa ltar shes par bya'o //
NK122(kho)002:9989: 'dir tshom bu tshogs bsgrub pa'i mthar dbang po rab gcig mi tshe gcig la mngon par 'grub ste /
NK122(kho)002:9990: dad brtson shes rab gsum gyi rtsal mchog dang ldan
NK122(kho)002:9991: pa'i skyes bu des ni blo rab zla ba drug
NK122(kho)002:9994: tha ma bcu drug gis lhag mar bcas pa'i lus
NK122(kho)002:9995: nyid kyis dag bya las dang nyon mongs pa kun
NK122(kho)002:9996: bral nas tshe dbang rig 'dzin thob pa'o //
NK122(kho)002:9998: lus khams skye gnas zag pa zad //
NK122(kho)002:9999: rdo rje'i rigs gyur tshe yi rigs //
NK122(kho)002:10000: mthong ba'i chos la mya ngan 'das //
NK122(kho)002:10001: lus ma bor bar sangs rgyas so //
NK122(kho)002:10003: blo dman gyis rnam smin rig 'dzin thob lugs ni /
NK122(kho)002:10004: dper na khyung sgong rgya seng+ge mngal rgya /
NK122(kho)002:10005: rnal 'byor pa lus rgya zer ba ltar /
NK122(kho)002:10006: tsha tsha skos phor nas ma byung ba bzhin du /
NK122(kho)002:10007: lus lha mir snang yang sems nyid yi dam gyi lhar smin pas rnam smin ces bya'o //
NK122(kho)002:10009: ka la ping ka mi 'jigs bzhin //
NK122(kho)002:10010: bral nas snang byed de rnam smin //
NK122(kho)002:10012: rig 'dzin 'di gnyis ni mthong lam pa yin no //
NK122(kho)002:10014: sgom lam phyag rgya chen po'i rig 'dzin dang /
NK122(kho)002:10015: mthar lam lhun grub rig 'dzin gnyis sdud pa'o //
NK122(kho)002:10016: de la phyag rgya chen po'i rig 'dzin te /
NK122(kho)002:10018: mthar lam lhun grub rig 'dzin ni /
NK122(kho)002:10019: sku lnga lhun gyis grub pa'i rig 'dzin yin cing /
NK122(kho)002:10020: sangs rgyas kyi sa la dus matha'i skad cig mas sbyor ba yin te /
NK122(kho)002:10022: sku lnga lhun gyis grub pa'i phyir //
NK122(kho)002:10023: sangs rgyas nyid dang spyod yul gcig /
NK122(kho)002:10024: mi g.yo ba la mi rtog pas //
NK122(kho)002:10025: da rung mngon par mi rgya ste //
NK122(kho)002:10026: dus matha'i skad cig nyid kyis gshegs //
NK122(kho)002:10028: de lta bu'i rig 'dzin thob bo //
NK122(kho)002:10030: phyag rgya chen po'i rig 'dzin la sogs pa rig pa 'dzin pa'i tshe de nyid kyis /
NK122(kho)002:10032: bde gshegs zhing rnams sbyong byed cing //
NK122(kho)002:10033: skye shi med pa'i sa bzung nas //
NK122(kho)002:10034: longs spyod rdzogs dang sprul pa yi //
NK122(kho)002:10035: tshul gyis 'gro rnams rgyud sbyangs te //
NK122(kho)002:10036: sems can sdug bsngal gnas las sgrol //
NK122(kho)002:10039: rgyal ba rgya mtsho'i tshogs rnams kyi nye ba'i sras su gyur pa'i byang chub sems dpa' yin cing /
NK122(kho)002:10040: byang chub sems dpa' kun gyi spun du 'gyur /
NK122(kho)002:10041: 'jig rten gyi lha chen po la sogs pa kun gyi rje bor lhag go //
NK122(kho)002:10043: brgya phrag bcu drug tshun chad du zhes pa ni
NK122(kho)002:10044: lo stong drug brgya'i nang du shes bya phra ba'i
NK122(kho)002:10045: sgrib pa bag la nyal byang bar gyur nas 'bras
NK122(kho)002:10047: mthar thug gi 'bras bu lam gyi rtsol ba zad pa mthar phyin pa la /
NK122(kho)002:10048: rnal 'byor rtsal chen rdzogs pa'i sa zhes bya'o //
NK122(kho)002:10049: de'i dus na stong pa chen po'i rnal 'byor mthar phyin pas chos sku thob /
NK122(kho)002:10050: snying rje chen po'i rnal 'byor mthar phyin pas sprul sku /
NK122(kho)002:10051: phyag rgya gcig pa mthar phyin pas longs sku /
NK122(kho)002:10052: phyag rgya spros pa mthar phyin pas mngon par byang chub pa'i sku /
NK122(kho)002:10053: sku bzhi ye nas dbyer med cing 'jig dang bral ba'i gnas lugs 'gyur med ni rdo rje'i sku'o //
NK122(kho)002:10054: de lta bu'i sku lnga lhun gyis 'grub par 'gyur ro //
NK122(kho)002:10057: dgongs pa 'dus pa'i lung las kyang ni 'di skad du /
NK122(kho)002:10058: rab kyi dbang po tha mas bskyed pa'ang ma h+aa
NK122(kho)002:10059: yo ga ltar gang snang ba thams cad thabs ma
NK122(kho)002:10060: 'gag pa dang / shes rab mi dmigs pa gnyis
NK122(kho)002:10061: dbyer med pas rnam par dag pa'i don la dang
NK122(kho)002:10062: po thos bsam gyis lta ba de ltar rtogs /
NK122(kho)002:10063: tha ma spyod pas brten pa dam rdzas lnga la sogs pa'i rdzas nyi shu po de dag dang /
NK122(kho)002:10064: rig pa byang chub sems dang ye nas dbyer med par blangs pas /
NK122(kho)002:10065: mthar thug rgyal ba rigs lnga sku lnga ye shes lnga ru rdzogs sangs rgyas pa'o //
NK122(kho)002:10066: de ni 'bras bu rnal 'byor rtsal chen rdzogs pa'i sa zhes zer ro //
NK122(kho)002:10067: zhes gsungs lung gi bgrod dang gsal zhes pa ni gong dang 'bru gnon mthun no //
NK122(kho)002:10068: rjes su rnal 'byor la gsum ste /
NK122(kho)002:10069: snod theg pa'i sgo nas bstan pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:10071: lung gis don bsdus ste bstan pa'o //
NK122(kho)002:10073: dbang po rab kyi 'bring la 'og ma ma h+aa
NK122(kho)002:10074: yo ga ltar bskyed mi dgos par rdzogs pa'i tshul
NK122(kho)002:10075: du snang ba ni rnam grol rig pa'i tan+t+ra sde
NK122(kho)002:10076: ched byas rtsol bsgrub kyi mtha' la 'das pa'o //
NK122(kho)002:10077: de'ang 'og ma la ltos pa'i dbang gis 'jug sgo la sogs bye brag bdun bshad pa'o //
NK122(kho)002:10078: rgyas par bshad pa la bdun ste /
NK122(kho)002:10081: 'jug sgo thun mong du bstan pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:10083: dbang po rab kyi 'bring du gyur pa a nu yo ga'i lugs kyi 'jug sgo ni /
NK122(kho)002:10084: dbyings dang ye shes dbyer med pa 'jug pa'i sgo yin no //
NK122(kho)002:10087: chos can gyi ngos nas ma 'dres pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:10089: lung a nu yo ga rnal 'byor rdzogs pa'i rtogs pa'i lta ba ni /
NK122(kho)002:10090: ya gi bla med sangs rgyas man chad nas ma
NK122(kho)002:10091: gi na rag dmyal khams yan chad du phyi snod
NK122(kho)002:10092: kyi 'jig rten nang bcud kyi sems can phra ba
NK122(kho)002:10093: rdul phran / rag pa rab rib /
NK122(kho)002:10096: las dkar po dge ba nag po sdig pa gnas
NK122(kho)002:10097: mthon po 'og min dman pa dmyal ba bzang ba
NK122(kho)002:10098: mtho ris ngan pa ngan song gsum la sogs pa
NK122(kho)002:10099: rnams ma 'gag par bye brag rnam pa cir yang
NK122(kho)002:10100: snang ba de nyid gang gis shes na /
NK122(kho)002:10103: ma skyes ye shes rang rig nyid //
NK122(kho)002:10104: rtsal rdzogs rig pa rang snang bas //
NK122(kho)002:10105: grangs dag ma nges sku gsung thugs //
NK122(kho)002:10106: rang snang phyag rgya bsam mi khyab //
NK122(kho)002:10107: kun bzang rol phyir blang dor med //
NK122(kho)002:10109: snang tsam nyid na'ang ngo bo ma skyes pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:10112: ngo bo nyid kyis ma skyes pas mtshan mar mi dmigs /
NK122(kho)002:10114: matha'i spros pa thams cad dang bral zhing rig pas
NK122(kho)002:10115: bzung du med shing mtshan ma'i dngos po med pa
NK122(kho)002:10116: de ni dbyings kun tu bzang mo ste /
NK122(kho)002:10118: gang yang sems las gzhan min pas //
NK122(kho)002:10119: rang bzhin cir yang ma yin phyir //
NK122(kho)002:10120: rtog pa'i smra bsam yul las 'das //
NK122(kho)002:10121: kun tu bzang mo'i mkha' dbyings klong //
NK122(kho)002:10122: cir yang snang ba yum gyi dbyings //
NK122(kho)002:10124: dbyer med pas ye shes rol pa'i rgyan du rdzogs pa'o //
NK122(kho)002:10126: ma skyes ma bcos sems kyi dbyings mu mtha' thams cad dang bral ba /
NK122(kho)002:10127: de nyid rang snang 'gag pa med pa'i rang rtsal gyis 'khor ba'i chos thams cad dang /
NK122(kho)002:10128: 'das pa'i chos thams cad ma 'gag par rang snang
NK122(kho)002:10129: ba de nyid dbyings ye shes dbyer med sras bde
NK122(kho)002:10130: ba chen po / ye shes rol pa'i rgyan du
NK122(kho)002:10131: ye nas rdzogs par rtogs pa ni lta ba yin
NK122(kho)002:10132: ba chen po / no // g.yu thang las /
NK122(kho)002:10133: snang srid bzang mo'i mkha' dbyings las //
NK122(kho)002:10134: ma bskyed dkyil 'khor kun bzang shar //
NK122(kho)002:10135: shar ba nyid na shar ba med //
NK122(kho)002:10136: yab yum sras bcas bde chen po'o //
NK122(kho)002:10139: rang snang rol pa bsam yas kyang //
NK122(kho)002:10140: b+ha ga'i klong las g.yos pa med //
NK122(kho)002:10142: sangs ma rgyas pa gcig kyang med //
NK122(kho)002:10149: mtshan med ni lta ba'i ngang la lha sgom pa'i rtsol ba dang bral ba'o //
NK122(kho)002:10151: rnal 'byor chen po'i bsam gtan ni //
NK122(kho)002:10152: ci bzhin pa yi de nyid la //
NK122(kho)002:10153: ma bcos pa yi blo bzhag ste //
NK122(kho)002:10156: mtshan bcas ni ma h+aa bzhin ting nge 'dzin bzhi
NK122(kho)002:10157: po rim gyis ma bskyed de 'bar ba khro bo
NK122(kho)002:10159: des pa zhi ba bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis kyi rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor rnams /
NK122(kho)002:10160: dper na rnyog ma dngas pa'i mtsho la gza' skar skad cig gis shar ba bzhin /
NK122(kho)002:10161: rang rig pa'i rtsal gyi byin gyis rlabs kyis rim
NK122(kho)002:10162: gyis mi bskyed skad cig gis rdzogs pa'i tshul du
NK122(kho)002:10163: bsgom mo // spyod pa la gnyis te /
NK122(kho)002:10165: rnal 'byor chen po dang mthun par spyod pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:10167: 'og ma'i spyod pa mtshan bcas kyi rnam pa de dag las grol ba dang /
NK122(kho)002:10168: nang dgongs pa rig pa'i ye shes su spyod pa ni a nu rang gzhung gi lugs yin no //
NK122(kho)002:10170: rnal 'byor che dang bye brag med ces gsungs pas /
NK122(kho)002:10171: 'og ma rnal 'byor chen po ma h+aa yo ga'i
NK122(kho)002:10172: spyod pa rnams 'dir yar ldan gyi tshul mi spyod
NK122(kho)002:10174: lung gi brtul shugs nyi shu rtsa gsum mo //
NK122(kho)002:10176: khyad par gzhung gi dam tshig dgu yin te /
NK122(kho)002:10181: khro gtum spang ba ste bdud lnga bsal ba dang /
NK122(kho)002:10182: lta spyod sgom gsum bcos ma rang dgar zhugs pa'i dgra /
NK122(kho)002:10183: lta dman spyod rtsings 'chal ba'i dgra /
NK122(kho)002:10184: rtsa ba yan lag gi dam tshig nyams pa ltung ba'i dgra /
NK122(kho)002:10185: brtson med le lo 'bras bu 'phrog pa'i dgra ste dgra bzhi bzlog pa dang dagu'o //
NK122(kho)002:10186: gzhan yang bla ma'i gdan mi 'gong ba sogs bsgrub pa'i dam tshig nyi shu'o //
NK122(kho)002:10189: gsang sngags kyi brda skad smra ba dang gsum /
NK122(kho)002:10190: le lo gzhom pa ste spyod lam gyi dam tshig bzhi /
NK122(kho)002:10191: 'di rnams kyi don rgyas par dgongs 'dus kyi nang du zhib bo //
NK122(kho)002:10192: log sred can 'dul ba'i ched du brtul shugs nyi shu rtsa gsum po'i spyod pa ni /
NK122(kho)002:10195: rngam pa glog 'phreng gi lung las bshad pa de dag yin /
NK122(kho)002:10209: dpa' brtul zhing bcu bsgral ba'i spyod pa /
NK122(kho)002:10210: za byed gtum brtul shugs rang bzhin gyis /
NK122(kho)002:10212: mkha' lding rlabs su chod pas thams cad ma bltas par gsal /
NK122(kho)002:10214: gtum chen dom rnal 'byor lta ba brtul shugs dom
NK122(kho)002:10215: dred 'dra ba'i rnal 'byor pas de tshugs su byed
NK122(kho)002:10217: gsang don dam pa la gsang ba'i ye shes spel /
NK122(kho)002:10218: ba mi ldog rgya mtsho'i gser //
NK122(kho)002:10219: mun gti mug che ba'i las rang tshugs su byed /
NK122(kho)002:10220: ltar lkug pa'i blo tshul bka' la yang ris su
NK122(kho)002:10221: mi byed mthar phyin nas slob dpon brtsi bar sems
NK122(kho)002:10223: lhun po mi 'gyur brtan pa ting nge 'dzin gyis gang la yang spang len med /
NK122(kho)002:10224: brtul shugs de dag gis dbang du /
NK122(kho)002:10226: mkha' ltar yang dog kun mched lcam nang du shong yang che /
NK122(kho)002:10228: khro bo'i bzlas pa drag po gang la yang bab par 'joms /
NK122(kho)002:10229: gnam lcags me yi drag shul can //
NK122(kho)002:10230: drag shul chen po'i lag na rdo rje 'joms pa'i rang bzhin /
NK122(kho)002:10233: khu 'phrig lta bu'i zon bag can //
NK122(kho)002:10234: rab dang klong la mi lta bar chu dag la nges par rting la sran tshugs /
NK122(kho)002:10235: nges par glang chen chur zhugs brtan //
NK122(kho)002:10237: zla med seng ge gcig brjid pa //
NK122(kho)002:10243: phag ni brtul shugs gtsang sme med par kun la spyod /
NK122(kho)002:10244: gang la rtog med kun spyod nyid //
NK122(kho)002:10245: thogs med 'gyur spyod thogs med gsod pa la dga' brtson par byed /
NK122(kho)002:10247: yid ltar myur bar glog lce /
NK122(kho)002:10248: mgyogs glog ltar bar glog rtse /
NK122(kho)002:10251: gang gis gang gong la 'brad kha na ma tho ba la 'dzem /
NK122(kho)002:10253: sa thub bag rnal 'byor myes thub 'gro ba skyong ba gcig /
NK122(kho)002:10255: rgyal po rgyal sa zhi thub par skyong /
NK122(kho)002:10256: rnal 'byor brtul shugs chen po ni //
NK122(kho)002:10258: gnyis blang dor mi che 'khon chen bdag rtog med ye shes ma rig 'joms /
NK122(kho)002:10261: wa yi brtul shugs chen po yis //
NK122(kho)002:10262: spang pa'i skabs su sbyang bar bya //
NK122(kho)002:10263: cang shes brtul shugs chen po yis //
NK122(kho)002:10265: lus kyi rtsal gyis bya ba yi //
NK122(kho)002:10266: gyi ling brtul shugs chen pos bya //
NK122(kho)002:10267: glang chen myos pa'i brtul shugs kyis //
NK122(kho)002:10268: mi 'byed rmongs pa'i brtul shugs bya //
NK122(kho)002:10269: stag 'chong rngam pa'i brtul shugs kyis //
NK122(kho)002:10270: dpa' brtul chen po'i las can bya //
NK122(kho)002:10271: khyung chen mkha' lding brtul shugs kyis //
NK122(kho)002:10272: lta ba'i phyi rgya rlabs kyis bcad //
NK122(kho)002:10273: gtum thung dom gyi brtul shugs kyis //
NK122(kho)002:10274: re ba med pa las can bya //
NK122(kho)002:10275: rgya mtsho gser gyi brtul shugs kyis //
NK122(kho)002:10276: yid mthun mi ldog brtan par bya //
NK122(kho)002:10277: lkugs pa lta bu'i brtul shugs kyis //
NK122(kho)002:10278: gti mug bzhin du shes rab ldan //
NK122(kho)002:10279: ri rab lta bu'i brtul shugs kyis //
NK122(kho)002:10280: mi 'gyur rab tu brtan par bya //
NK122(kho)002:10281: nam mkha' lta bu'i brtul shugs kyis //
NK122(kho)002:10282: yangs dog kun dang bral bar bya //
NK122(kho)002:10283: gnam lcags lce yi brtul shugs kyis //
NK122(kho)002:10284: drag shul las la sbyor bar bya //
NK122(kho)002:10285: lag na rdo rje'i brtul shugs kyis //
NK122(kho)002:10286: mthu stobs dag la sbyor bar bya //
NK122(kho)002:10287: bya rog brtul shugs chen po yis //
NK122(kho)002:10288: tshor ba khu 'khrig spong bar bya //
NK122(kho)002:10289: glang chen chur 'jug brtul shugs kyis //
NK122(kho)002:10290: nges par nga rgyal bskyed par bya //
NK122(kho)002:10291: ri dwags seng ge'i brtul shugs kyis //
NK122(kho)002:10292: grogs ngan la sogs spang bar bya //
NK122(kho)002:10293: reg 'jam bya yi brtul shugs kyis //
NK122(kho)002:10294: 'grogs nas chags shing bde bar bya //
NK122(kho)002:10295: sgyu ma rgya mtsho'i brtul shugs kyis //
NK122(kho)002:10296: thabs la mkhas pa'i las can bya //
NK122(kho)002:10297: lce spyang ka yi brtul shugs kyis //
NK122(kho)002:10298: gtsang sme med par bza' bar bya //
NK122(kho)002:10299: thog med 'gyur spyod za byed wa //
NK122(kho)002:10300: thog med gsod la brtson par bya //
NK122(kho)002:10301: phag gi brtul shugs chen po yis //
NK122(kho)002:10302: gtsang sme med par spyod par bya //
NK122(kho)002:10303: bar snang glog gi brtul shugs kyis //
NK122(kho)002:10304: ci la myur sogs brtson par bya //
NK122(kho)002:10305: mkha' lding lta bu'i brtul shugs kyis //
NK122(kho)002:10306: kun la 'dzem pa'i spyod pa bya //
NK122(kho)002:10307: rgyal po 'khor spyod brtul shugs kyis //
NK122(kho)002:10308: sa thub 'khor dang ldan par spyod //
NK122(kho)002:10309: 'di la mchan gsal po mi 'dug ste /
NK122(kho)002:10310: rgyud kho rang gi nang du ci ltar yod pa bzhin bris so //
NK122(kho)002:10312: thabs 'jug bsre ba'i spyod pa ni /
NK122(kho)002:10313: log sred can 'dul ba'i ched du de dag dang cha mthun par spyod pa ste /
NK122(kho)002:10314: lung gi brtul shugs nyi shu rtsa gsum bshad pa'o //
NK122(kho)002:10315: wa dang ces pa wa gal la zin kyang srog
NK122(kho)002:10316: la mi lta bar lag pa bcad nas 'gro ba
NK122(kho)002:10317: ltar / rnal 'byor ba srog la bab kyang dam tshig bsrung bya la 'dzem /
NK122(kho)002:10318: de'i mi mthun phyogs brtul cing gnyen por dam tshig stobs zhugs pa'i thabs so //
NK122(kho)002:10320: cang shes kyi rtas thams cad shes shing myur mgyogs
NK122(kho)002:10321: kyis stong gsum yud tsam la bskor ba ltar shes
NK122(kho)002:10322: rab kyis shes bya spyi dang rang gi mtshan nyid
NK122(kho)002:10323: thams cad la thogs pa med pa'i brtul shugs so
NK122(kho)002:10325: gyi ling rtsal che bas cir yang 'gyur ba ltar /
NK122(kho)002:10326: lus gus pas gar dang phyag rgya 'phrul 'khor la brtson pas le lo gzhom pa'i brtul shugs so //
NK122(kho)002:10327: shin tu glang chen myos 'dra ba /
NK122(kho)002:10329: glang chen chang gis myos na dgra zun gang yang mi 'byed par gang snang 'joms pa ltar /
NK122(kho)002:10330: 'khor 'das mi 'byed dbyer med du shes pas lta spyod kyi dgra bzhi 'jom pa'i spyod pa'o //
NK122(kho)002:10331: dpa' brtul za byed gtum rngam 'khrug /
NK122(kho)002:10333: stag gis dmigs pa la dpa' zhing brtul pas za byed kyi sems rngam 'khrug dang ldan pa ltar /
NK122(kho)002:10334: rang bzhin gnas lugs rtogs pa'i ting nge 'dzin gyi brtul shugs kyis dpa' brtul stobs dang ldan cing /
NK122(kho)002:10335: spyod pa'i brtul shugs kyis zhing bcu bsgral ba'i thabs
NK122(kho)002:10336: gdul bya dang mthun par za byed gtum rngam 'khrug
NK122(kho)002:10337: pa'i tshul gyis ru tra bsgral nas gnas spar ba
NK122(kho)002:10339: mkha' lding khyung chen gang mi blta //
NK122(kho)002:10341: khyung mkha' la lding na rtsol ba med par gnam
NK122(kho)002:10342: 'phang rlabs kyis gcod cing ma bltas par thams cad
NK122(kho)002:10343: gsal ba ltar / lta bas dbyings ye shes dbyer
NK122(kho)002:10344: med par thag chod pas rtsol ba med pa'i spyod
NK122(kho)002:10345: gsal ba ltar / pa'o // gtum chen dom bu 'jigs 'dra ba /
NK122(kho)002:10347: dom gyis gang la dmigs pa la re ltos dang
NK122(kho)002:10348: the tshom med par 'jigs par byed cing 'dral ba
NK122(kho)002:10349: ltar rnal 'byor lta spyod kyi gdeng dang ldan pas
NK122(kho)002:10350: the tshom chod pas drag po'i las ci tshugs su
NK122(kho)002:10352: gsang thub mi ldog rgya mtsho'i gser /
NK122(kho)002:10354: rgya mtsho'i gting gi gser ltar zab don gsang thub
NK122(kho)002:10355: cing nyams su len pa la blo mi ldog par
NK122(kho)002:10357: mun ltar lkug pa'i blo tshul ldan /
NK122(kho)002:10358: lkugs pa gti mug can gyis sngags dang phyag rgya
NK122(kho)002:10359: dbyangs sogs so sor mi 'byed pa ltar 'khor 'das
NK122(kho)002:10360: la sogs gnyis can ris su mi 'byed pa'i mnyam
NK122(kho)002:10361: bzhag gis bdag med rtogs pa'i shes rab mthar phyin
NK122(kho)002:10363: lhun po mi 'gyur brtan pa che /
NK122(kho)002:10364: zhes pas ri rab mi g.yo ba ltar bla ma dang grogs la dad gus mi 'gyur ba dang /
NK122(kho)002:10365: ting nge 'dzin bying rgod kyis mi g.yo ba'i gnyen po brten pa'i thabs kyi brtul shugs so //
NK122(kho)002:10366: mkha' ltar yangs dog kun dang bral /
NK122(kho)002:10368: nam mkha' ni yangs la rgya che bas spong len
NK122(kho)002:10369: med par snod bcud bde sdug la sogs pa kun
NK122(kho)002:10370: shongs pa ltar / rnal 'byor mched lcam gyi nang du shongs yangs rgya che ba dang /
NK122(kho)002:10371: 'khor 'das dang theg pa gang yang bdag nyid chen
NK122(kho)002:10372: po'i lta spyod 'di'i nang du mi shongs pa med
NK122(kho)002:10373: par spyod pa'i brtul shugs so //
NK122(kho)002:10374: drag shul chen po'i brtul shugs bdag /
NK122(kho)002:10375: ces pas lag na rdo rjes log lta can thams cad 'joms pa ltar /
NK122(kho)002:10376: rnal 'byor pas khro bo bsgom nas /
NK122(kho)002:10377: dgra bgegs the tshom med par 'joms pa'i brtul shugs so //
NK122(kho)002:10378: khu 'phrig lta bu'i zon bag can /
NK122(kho)002:10379: ces pas bya rog gis dgra dang gcan gzan gnyis dus gcig tu mig gis bsrung ba ltar /
NK122(kho)002:10380: phyi nang gi dam tshig 'di dag spang len la rgyun du brtson pa'i thabs kyi brtul shugs so //
NK122(kho)002:10381: nges par glang chen chur 'jug ltar /
NK122(kho)002:10383: glang chen chu rab bde ba dang rba rlab la
NK122(kho)002:10384: sogs pa thams cad nges pa med par 'jug cing
NK122(kho)002:10385: gcod pa ltar / bdag nyid chen po'i lta spyod gdeng ldan nga rgyal gyis /
NK122(kho)002:10386: spangs gnyen gnyis med du spyod pa'am phrin las bzhis
NK122(kho)002:10387: gdul bya mi gdam par las mdzad pas brtul zhugs
NK122(kho)002:10388: so // zla med seng ge gcig brjid pa //
NK122(kho)002:10390: seng ge gcig pur 'dug pa ltar lta spyod mi
NK122(kho)002:10391: mthun pa'i grogs ngan spangs nas dgon par gcig pur
NK122(kho)002:10392: 'dug nas lta sgom skyong ba'i brtul zhugs so //
NK122(kho)002:10395: ngang pa pho mo mi 'bral bar rgyun du 'grogs nas bde ba ltar /
NK122(kho)002:10396: sems can thams cad la thugs brtse ba dang bcas
NK122(kho)002:10397: pas thar pa'i bde ba la bkod pa'i thabs dang
NK122(kho)002:10398: rtag tu mi 'bral bar 'grogs pa'i brtul zhugs so
NK122(kho)002:10399: // sgyu mas sgyu ma'i tshul 'drid pa //
NK122(kho)002:10401: sgyu ma mkhan gyis byas pa'i gzugs brnyan lta bur /
NK122(kho)002:10402: phung khams skye mched ye nas rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor sgyu ma lta bu yin pa la /
NK122(kho)002:10403: de ltar lta sgom gyis nyams su len cing ston pa ni /
NK122(kho)002:10404: thabs mkhas kyi 'drid pa'i brtul zhugs so //
NK122(kho)002:10405: gang la'ang rtog med kun spyod nyid //
NK122(kho)002:10407: phag gis gtsang sme med par thams cad bza' ba ltar /
NK122(kho)002:10408: dam rdzas lnga blang dor med par mnyam nyid du spyod pa'i brtul zhugs so //
NK122(kho)002:10409: thogs med 'gyur spyod za byed khwa //
NK122(kho)002:10411: ce spyang thogs pa med par gsod pa la dga' ba bzhin /
NK122(kho)002:10412: lta spyod goms pa'i thugs rjes thogs pa med par
NK122(kho)002:10413: log lta can gyi rnam rtog bsgral zhing rnam shes
NK122(kho)002:10414: zag med la bkod pa'i tshogs gnyis rdzogs pa'i brtul
NK122(kho)002:10415: zhugs so // yid ltar myur mgyogs glog ltar 'gyu //
NK122(kho)002:10416: zhes pa bar snang glog gis thams cad dus gcig la myur du gsal ba ltar /
NK122(kho)002:10417: lam nyams su blang pa'i rnal 'byor pas rang don
NK122(kho)002:10418: myur du 'grub cing gzhan don thugs rje myur du
NK122(kho)002:10419: 'byung bar brtson pa'i brtul zhugs so //
NK122(kho)002:10420: gang gis gang bsrung nam mkha' lding //
NK122(kho)002:10421: zhes pa bya rgod gang la 'brang yang srog gcod la 'dzem nas bsrung ba ltar /
NK122(kho)002:10422: gong gi barlanga spyod kyi brtul zhugs phal pa de
NK122(kho)002:10423: dag gzhan la 'tshe ba ltar snang yang theg pa
NK122(kho)002:10424: 'dir bdag nyid chen po'i tshul du spyad na dam
NK122(kho)002:10425: tshig sbyangs shing nyes pa dag pa'i brtul zhugs so
NK122(kho)002:10426: // sa thub bag ldan rgyal 'khor skyong //
NK122(kho)002:10428: rgyal po bag dang ldan pas rgyal sa non cing rang bas gces par 'khor skyong ba ltar /
NK122(kho)002:10429: theg pa 'di nyid lta ba dbyings ye shes dbyer
NK122(kho)002:10430: med pa'i bde ba chen po rtogs shing goms pa'i
NK122(kho)002:10432: brtul zhugs thams cad kyi rgyal sa non te rnal 'byor pa thams cad mnyes thub /
NK122(kho)002:10434: yang na dbyer med bde ba chen por rtogs pas
NK122(kho)002:10435: chos thams cad rang las mi gzhan par rtogs pa
NK122(kho)002:10436: ni 'khor skyongs shing nyes pa rang sar dag pa'i
NK122(kho)002:10437: brtul zhugs so / rnal 'byor brtul zhugs chen po ni //
NK122(kho)002:10438: bcu gnyis dang ni gsum blor ldan //
NK122(kho)002:10439: ces pas de dag ni bdag don dang gzhan don dang /
NK122(kho)002:10440: bdag gzhan gnyis ka'i don du go bar bya'o //
NK122(kho)002:10441: spyir blo rab cig char ba'i nyams su blang bya
NK122(kho)002:10442: yin cing log sred can dang cha mthun brtul zhugs
NK122(kho)002:10443: kyi thabs kyis thar pa la 'god pa'i thabs so
NK122(kho)002:10446: rnal 'byor gnyis ka'i sum brgya drug cu dang /
NK122(kho)002:10448: dam tshig bsrung ba'i thabs ni 'di lta ste /
NK122(kho)002:10449: ma h+aa dang a nu gnyis ka'i thun mong sum
NK122(kho)002:10450: brgya drug cu la sogs bsrung mtshams mtha' yas te
NK122(kho)002:10451: / khyad par du lung rang gzhung gi dam tshig la bdud lnga bsal ba dang /
NK122(kho)002:10452: dgra bzhi bzlog pa dang dgu /
NK122(kho)002:10453: bsgrub pa'i dam tshig nyi shu /
NK122(kho)002:10454: spyod lam rgyun gyi dam tshig la sogs pa bsrung ba'o //
NK122(kho)002:10455: 'di rnams kyi don stod spyod pa'i skabs su bris nas yod /
NK122(kho)002:10456: lung rang gi gong 'og gi dam tshig thams cad bsrung ba'o //
NK122(kho)002:10458: gong ma a ti'i dam tshig ni /
NK122(kho)002:10461: lhun gyis grub pa la sogs pa'i dam tshig thams cad bsrung ba dang /
NK122(kho)002:10462: 'og ma h+aa yo ga'i sum brgya drug cu bsrung
NK122(kho)002:10463: ba'i bye brag rnams ni a nu yo ga 'di
NK122(kho)002:10464: yis mi bsrung ba gcig kyang med pa'o //
NK122(kho)002:10469: dbang po rab kyis zla ba gcig /
NK122(kho)002:10471: 'bring gis lo bcu gnyis tha mas lo bcu drug
NK122(kho)002:10472: gis rgyun gyi khyad par gyis rim gyis pas 'dun
NK122(kho)002:10473: pa sems pa'i rnal 'byor tshogs lam pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:10474: rigs chen 'byed pa'i rnal 'byor sbyor lam pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:10475: dbugs chen 'byin pa'i rnal 'byor mthong lam pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:10476: lung chen thob pa'i rnal 'byor sgom lam pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:10477: rtsal chen rdzogs pa'i rnal 'byor mthar lam pa dang lnga rim gyis bgrod par 'dod do //
NK122(kho)002:10478: rnal 'byor 'di rnams la rab lnga phrag dang /
NK122(kho)002:10481: tha ma bzhi bcu'i phrag tu 'dod de /
NK122(kho)002:10483: gcig shos 'jug pa lnga dang bcu //
NK122(kho)002:10484: spros pas bzhi bcur 'gyur ba yin //
NK122(kho)002:10486: zag med la sbyor tshul yun dang bcas pa'o //
NK122(kho)002:10488: lam cig char ba 'di sbyor lam rigs chen 'byed
NK122(kho)002:10489: pa'i steng nas yi ge 'khor lo tshogs chen gyi
NK122(kho)002:10490: sa mngon sum du thob par 'gyur ro //
NK122(kho)002:10491: 'di ni 'bras bu'i mthar thug sangs rgyas kyi sa yin te /
NK122(kho)002:10492: sangs rgyas kyi sku dang ye shes ma 'dres par snang ba'i cha nas yi ge /
NK122(kho)002:10493: sku rigs rgyan gyi 'khor lo nyi shu rtsa lnga rgyun mi chad pas na 'khor lo /
NK122(kho)002:10494: sku dang ye shes 'gag med du shar bas bsod nams kyi tshogs /
NK122(kho)002:10495: sku dang ye shes shar ba'i dus de nyid na
NK122(kho)002:10496: me long gi gzugs brnyan ltar chos kyi dbyings las
NK122(kho)002:10497: ma g.yos pa ni ye shes kyi tshogs /
NK122(kho)002:10498: de'i dus su tshogs bsag pa gsog byed dang bral
NK122(kho)002:10499: nas chos sku'i dba' klong gcig tu gyur pa ni
NK122(kho)002:10501: blo rig pa de nyid kyi ngo bor shar ba ni mngon 'gyur zhes bya'o //
NK122(kho)002:10503: cig char pas sangs rgyas kyi sa thob pa'o //
NK122(kho)002:10504: thod rgal bas phyag rgya chen po'i rig pa 'dzin
NK122(kho)002:10505: pa lung chen thob pa'i rnal 'byor du sbyor ba
NK122(kho)002:10506: yin / de nas lam mthar phyin pa'i rtsal chen
NK122(kho)002:10507: rdzogs pa'i rnal 'byor mngon sum du gyur pa ni
NK122(kho)002:10511: de nas ring por mi thogs par /
NK122(kho)002:10513: sangs rgyas kyi sa thob pa la ring por mi
NK122(kho)002:10514: thogs par shes bya'i sgrib pa bag la nyal ba
NK122(kho)002:10515: dag nas / rgya chad phyogs lhung thams cad dang
NK122(kho)002:10516: bral ba gdal ba chen po chos nyid kyis sa
NK122(kho)002:10517: dag nas / zhes bya ba'am / ngan pa'i skyon mtshan dag nas /
NK122(kho)002:10518: dbyings ye shes dbyer med pas kun bzang dbye ba med pa'i sa /
NK122(kho)002:10519: thog pa med par mngon du gyur cing sku rigs
NK122(kho)002:10520: rgyan gyi 'khor lo nyi shu rtsa lnga lhun gyis
NK122(kho)002:10521: grub pa'o // lung gis zhabs bsdu ba'o //
NK122(kho)002:10523: dgongs pa 'dus pa'i lung las kyang ni 'di skad du gsungs /
NK122(kho)002:10524: gzhi ye nas 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad mnyam
NK122(kho)002:10525: pas na gzhi'i de nyid thos bsam gyis gtan la
NK122(kho)002:10526: phabs nas dbyings ye shes dbyer med mnyam pa'i don
NK122(kho)002:10527: mngon sum du lta bas rtogs shing mthong nas /
NK122(kho)002:10528: chos nyid mngon sum du rtogs pa'i mthong lam pa yin la /
NK122(kho)002:10529: de nas de nyid kyi don bsgom zhing lam mthar
NK122(kho)002:10530: phyin nas 'bras bu sangs rgyas pa'i dus su mnyam
NK122(kho)002:10531: rdzogs chen po rtogs bya'i yul dbyings skye med kyi
NK122(kho)002:10532: gnas lugs dang / rtogs byed kyi shes pa ye
NK122(kho)002:10533: shes gnyis ye nas dbyer med ro gcig tu gyur
NK122(kho)002:10534: gnas lugs dang / pa'o // de'i dus su ci
NK122(kho)002:10535: lta ba mkhyen pa'i ye shes kyis shes bya'i chos
NK122(kho)002:10536: kun skye med kyi gnas lugs su kun rig pa'o
NK122(kho)002:10537: gnas lugs dang / pa'o // // kun tu snang zhes pa ni /
NK122(kho)002:10538: ji snyed mkhyen pa'i ye shes kyis shes bya'i chos
NK122(kho)002:10539: thams cad lag mthil du skyu ru ra bzhag pa
NK122(kho)002:10540: bzhin mi mkhyen pa ci yang med pa'o //
NK122(kho)002:10542: dbyer med mkhyen pa'i ye shes kyis ji snyed mkhyen
NK122(kho)002:10543: pa'i dus de nyid na'ang ji lta ba'i rang rlab
NK122(kho)002:10545: thams cad bdal ba chos nyid sa //
NK122(kho)002:10546: zhes gsungs lung gi bgrod dang gsal /
NK122(kho)002:10548: rdzogs pa chen po 'chad par byed pa la /
NK122(kho)002:10553: mtshon bya don gnyis las dang po ni /
NK122(kho)002:10554: a ti'i bstan pa nam mkha' dang 'dra ste mtha' med par bstan pa'o //
NK122(kho)002:10555: de'ang phyogs tsam cig mtshon na /
NK122(kho)002:10560: la bzla rgyal po'i skor dang /
NK122(kho)002:10561: rang grol mngon sum du ston pa man ngag skor dang drug go //
NK122(kho)002:10562: dang po sems sde bco brgyad la rmad byung dang /
NK122(kho)002:10563: rig pa mchog gi dang bkra shis mi 'gyur gsal
NK122(kho)002:10564: bar gnas pa'i rgyud la sogs pa rgyud sde chen
NK122(kho)002:10566: snga 'gyur lnga dang phyi 'gyur bcu gsum la sogs dpag tu med pa yod par gsungs so //
NK122(kho)002:10567: klong sde'i skor la bzhi ste phyi rtsis rgya'i skor
NK122(kho)002:10568: la glang po che rab 'bog gi rgyud la sogs
NK122(kho)002:10569: pa gzer bu brgya dang brgyad cu /
NK122(kho)002:10570: nang gsang rgya'i skor la kun tu bzang mo rig
NK122(kho)002:10571: pa rang rtsal shar ba'i rgyud la sogs man ngag
NK122(kho)002:10573: gsang ba rgyud bu chung gi skor la /
NK122(kho)002:10574: rin chen bkod pa'i rgyud la sogs pa bsam gtan brgya dang brgyad cu /
NK122(kho)002:10575: dgongs pa gtad rgya'i skor la klong chen rab 'byams
NK122(kho)002:10576: rgyal po'i rgyud la sogs pa la bzla brgya dang
NK122(kho)002:10577: brgyad cu yod par gsungs so //
NK122(kho)002:10579: gong gi bshad lugs bzhi po de rnams yod par gsungs so //
NK122(kho)002:10580: rgyud sde'i skor la nam mkha' mtha' mnyam dang /
NK122(kho)002:10581: nya mo 'khor lo'i rgyud la sogs pa rgyud bzhi
NK122(kho)002:10582: bcu zhe gnyis man ngag dang bcas pa yod par
NK122(kho)002:10583: gsungs so // bram ze'i skor la /
NK122(kho)002:10584: bram ze rtsa ba'i rgyud drug /
NK122(kho)002:10585: man ngag gi rgyud sum cu so drug yod par gsungs so //
NK122(kho)002:10586: de la nam mkha' klong yangs kyi rgyud dang /
NK122(kho)002:10587: ye shes gting nas rdzogs pa'i rgyud dang /
NK122(kho)002:10588: kun tu bzang po ye shes klong yongs kyi rgyud dang /
NK122(kho)002:10589: rang byung bde ba 'khor lo'i rgyud dang /
NK122(kho)002:10590: nges don 'dus pa gter gyi rgyud dang /
NK122(kho)002:10591: 'khor ba rtsad nas gcod pa'i rgyud dang /
NK122(kho)002:10592: spyi rgyud ye shes nam mkha' dang mnyam pa'i rgyud la sogs pa'o //
NK122(kho)002:10593: la bzla rgyal po'i skor ni /
NK122(kho)002:10594: bkra shis dus tshod 'dzin pa khu byug rol pa'i rgyud dang /
NK122(kho)002:10595: yon tan rtsal chen rdzogs pa'i rgyud dang /
NK122(kho)002:10596: thig le sgron ma gsang ba bkod pa'i rgyud dang /
NK122(kho)002:10597: kun byed rgyal po dang rig pa nam mkha' dang
NK122(kho)002:10598: mnyam pa'i rgyud la sogs pa rtsa ba'i rgyud lnga
NK122(kho)002:10599: dang / yan lag gi rgyud sde brgya tham pa man ngag dang bcas pa yod par gsungs so //
NK122(kho)002:10601: gab pa mngon du byung ba gab pa 'khor lo'i skor dang /
NK122(kho)002:10602: rig pa gnad la 'beb pa sgom pa'i skor dang /
NK122(kho)002:10603: chos nyid ma bu sprad pa rdzong 'phrang gi skor dang /
NK122(kho)002:10604: rang grol mngon sum du ston pa rgyud tha ma'i skor dang /
NK122(kho)002:10605: de re re la'ang rgyud man chad dang bcas pa du ma yod par gsungs so //
NK122(kho)002:10606: de tshe re re'i khong nas kyang mu stegs la sogs pa'i log rtog bsal ba dang /
NK122(kho)002:10607: theg pa rim pa brgyad kyi shan phye ba dang /
NK122(kho)002:10608: rdzogs pa chen por la bzla ba dang /
NK122(kho)002:10609: rang grol mngon sum du ngo sprad pa la sogs
NK122(kho)002:10610: pa theg pa thams cad kyi 'dod lugs yongs su
NK122(kho)002:10612: de la sogs te ke'u tshang gi skor la /
NK122(kho)002:10616: gsang ba bla na med pa'i skor la sogs pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:10618: spros bral don gsal gyi skor dang /
NK122(kho)002:10620: rgyal po'i bla gter gyi skor dang /
NK122(kho)002:10621: kun 'gro'i skor la sogs pa brjod las 'das pa yod par gsungs so //
NK122(kho)002:10622: mtshon bya don la bzhi ste /
NK122(kho)002:10623: theg pa 'og ma bskyed rdzogs gnyis kyi don dang shan phye ba dang /
NK122(kho)002:10625: rdzogs pa chen po'i che ba'i yon tan dang /
NK122(kho)002:10626: rtogs shing grol ba'i thabs dang bzhi'o //
NK122(kho)002:10627: dang po shan phye ba ni /
NK122(kho)002:10628: ma h+aa yo gas snang ba sems kyi cho 'phrul dang /
NK122(kho)002:10629: a nus sems kyi rtsal du snang bar 'dod de /
NK122(kho)002:10630: a tis ni 'khor 'das gnyis kyis bsdus pa'i chos
NK122(kho)002:10631: thams cad rang byung gi ye shes rang snang ba'i
NK122(kho)002:10632: khyad par yod / 'og ma gnyis kyis sems la snang ba'i cho 'phrul dang rtsal du 'dod pas /
NK122(kho)002:10633: gzhi sems su lta zhing shugs kyis 'dzin pa'i cha dang ma bral ba'o //
NK122(kho)002:10634: a ti ni chos thams cad rang byung gi ye shes rgya chad phyogs lhung dang bral ba /
NK122(kho)002:10635: chos kun mnyam pa nyid du rang grol ba'o //
NK122(kho)002:10636: yang ma h+aas snang ba chos nyid du 'dod la /
NK122(kho)002:10637: brtag zhen gnyis chos nyid du mi 'dod pa'o //
NK122(kho)002:10638: a nus snang brtag gnyis chos nyid du 'dod la /
NK122(kho)002:10640: a tis chos kun rang byung gi ye shes mngon
NK122(kho)002:10641: du snang bas zhen pa bcos slad med par chos
NK122(kho)002:10642: nyid du 'dod cing chos nyid min pa'i chos gcig
NK122(kho)002:10643: kyang med pa'o // gnyis pa gol ba la bzhi ste /
NK122(kho)002:10644: a ti la skur pa btab pa'i nyes dmigs dang /
NK122(kho)002:10645: kha 'byams tshig gi lta bas gol ba dang /
NK122(kho)002:10646: ma rtogs pa'i bsgom pas gol ba dang /
NK122(kho)002:10647: a ti la ltos na a nu man chad gol ba'o //
NK122(kho)002:10648: dang po rdzogs pa chen po'i bstan pa nam mkha' dang 'dra zhing /
NK122(kho)002:10649: theg pa thams cad kyi yang rtse /
NK122(kho)002:10650: bstan pa thams cad kyi snying po 'di la /
NK122(kho)002:10651: blo chung phyogs 'dzin can rnams kyis bskur pa btab pas /
NK122(kho)002:10652: nam mkha' gnas kyi bar du dmyal bar 'gro bar gsungs te /
NK122(kho)002:10654: khyod kyis blo chung gzhan du spel mi bya //
NK122(kho)002:10655: gal te spel na gang zag de nyid kyis //
NK122(kho)002:10656: kun bzang dgongs pa 'di la gshe gyur na //
NK122(kho)002:10657: nam mkha' ci srid gnas kyi bar du ni //
NK122(kho)002:10658: shi ba'i 'og tu rdo rje'i dmyal bar 'gro //
NK122(kho)002:10660: gnyis pa kha 'byams tshig gi lta ba ni /
NK122(kho)002:10661: chos kun rang byung gi ye shes mngon sum du snang zhing ye nas sangs rgyas pa nyid /
NK122(kho)002:10662: blo che ba rnams kyis da ltar gyi snang ba
NK122(kho)002:10663: 'di nyid ma bcos ma bslad par rang byung gi
NK122(kho)002:10664: ye shes dang dbyer med du rtogs nas grol ba
NK122(kho)002:10665: de blo chung ba rnams kyi ma go nas /
NK122(kho)002:10666: 'khrul grol shan ma phyed par kha 'byams tshig gi lta ba la zhen nas /
NK122(kho)002:10667: snang ba 'di ltar sangs rgyas yin //
NK122(kho)002:10668: zhes dngos po rang gar smra ba ni gol ba yin par gsungs te /
NK122(kho)002:10670: nyams su ma blangs kha tshig gis //
NK122(kho)002:10671: chags sdang zil gyis mi non cing //
NK122(kho)002:10672: skye bo rang rgyud pa ru gol //
NK122(kho)002:10674: gsum pa don ma rtogs par bsgoms kyang gol bar gsungs te /
NK122(kho)002:10676: rang sems don nyid ma rtogs par //
NK122(kho)002:10677: sgom du 'gro ba snying re rje //
NK122(kho)002:10678: rkyal ma sbyangs par chur 'jug ltar //
NK122(kho)002:10679: de bzhin ma rtogs sus bsgom par //
NK122(kho)002:10682: bzhi pa a ti la ltos nas a nu man chad gol bar gsungs te /
NK122(kho)002:10683: de'ang chos kun rang byung gi ye shes rang snang
NK122(kho)002:10684: zhing ye nas 'dus ma byas pa'i ye shes su
NK122(kho)002:10686: nyan rang gis skyon du bzung nas spang zhing dgag pas gol ba dang /
NK122(kho)002:10687: dbu sems gnyis kyis sbyangs pas gol ba dang /
NK122(kho)002:10688: kri yog pa dang gsang sngags nang pa gnyis kyis
NK122(kho)002:10689: bsgyur cing dbang du byed pas rang byung ye shes
NK122(kho)002:10690: la bcos zhing gol bar gsungs te /
NK122(kho)002:10692: mdo sde dang ni kri ya dang //
NK122(kho)002:10693: u pa ya dang yo ga dang //
NK122(kho)002:10694: ma h+aa yo ga a nu drug /
NK122(kho)002:10695: rdzogs pa chen po'i gol sa ste //
NK122(kho)002:10697: gsum pa rdzogs pa chen po'i che ba'am yon tan la drug ste /
NK122(kho)002:10698: bka' rdzogs pa chen po lnga brgya'i tha ma la
NK122(kho)002:10699: byang phyogs kha ba can gyi zhing khams der dar
NK122(kho)002:10700: shing / sems can gyi sgron me byed par lung bstan pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:10701: bstan pa 'dzin cing 'chang ba'i yon tan dang /
NK122(kho)002:10704: gzhung bzhin bshad pa'i yon tan dang /
NK122(kho)002:10705: rtogs shing bsgom pa'i yon tan dang drug go //
NK122(kho)002:10707: bstan pa'i snying po bka' rdzogs pa chen po 'di /
NK122(kho)002:10708: lnga brgya'i tha ma la bod kha ba can gyi zhing khams 'dir dar bar gsungs te /
NK122(kho)002:10709: rang byung bde ba 'khor lo'i rgyud las //
NK122(kho)002:10710: sangs rgyas bstan pa 'jig kha'i tshe //
NK122(kho)002:10711: 'dzam gling bod kyi byang phyogs su //
NK122(kho)002:10712: sde snod chos kun nub gyur cing //
NK122(kho)002:10714: rang sems rtogs pa tsam gyis ni //
NK122(kho)002:10717: gnyis pa dam pa'i chos 'di la mos pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:10719: bris na yang rgyal ba kun gyi bu bzhin du skyong bar bshad de /
NK122(kho)002:10721: klog dang bris dang 'dzin pa dag /
NK122(kho)002:10722: kun kyang bu bzhin skyong bar byed //
NK122(kho)002:10724: gsum pa 'di la mos par byed pa ni sangs
NK122(kho)002:10725: rgyas rnams dang mnyam zhing sangs rgyas par gsungs te
NK122(kho)002:10726: / 'di la mos pa'i gang zag ni //
NK122(kho)002:10727: sangs rgyas rnams dang skal pa mnyam //
NK122(kho)002:10729: bzhi pa gzhung 'di nyan cing spyod na'ang sangs rgyas par gsungs te /
NK122(kho)002:10732: dus gsum sangs rgyas dgongs pa thob //
NK122(kho)002:10734: lnga pa gzhung bzhin spyod pa'i yon tan ni /
NK122(kho)002:10736: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi //
NK122(kho)002:10737: phyag rgya gsang chen snying po 'di //
NK122(kho)002:10738: rtogs nas smra bar gang byed pa //
NK122(kho)002:10739: de nyid nga yin dbang yang rdzogs //
NK122(kho)002:10741: drug pa rtogs shing bsgom pa'i yon tan la gnyis te /
NK122(kho)002:10742: rtogs nas bsgom na yang sangs rgyas pa'i yon tan ni /
NK122(kho)002:10744: dbang po rab kyi don du ni //
NK122(kho)002:10745: bstan pa tsam gyis rtogs pa'i chos //
NK122(kho)002:10746: thig le nyag gcig chos kyi sku //
NK122(kho)002:10747: shes pa tsam gyis sangs rgyas nges //
NK122(kho)002:10749: rtogs shing goms par byed pa'i yon tan la bcu bzhi ste /
NK122(kho)002:10750: gol sa thams cad dus gcig tu chod pa'i yon tan dang /
NK122(kho)002:10751: sgrib pa thams cad dus gcig la dag pa'i yon tan dang /
NK122(kho)002:10752: tshogs gnyis dus gcig la rdzogs pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:10753: mkha' 'gro chos skyong thams cad bka' nyan pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:10754: mchod pa thams cad kyi mchog yin pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:10756: sdom pa gsum rdzogs pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:10757: shes rab gsum rdzogs pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:10758: dge ba bcu rdzogs pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:10759: pha rol tu phyin pa drug rdzogs pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:10760: tshad med pa bzhi rdzogs pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:10761: gsang sngags kyi bsgrub pa ma lus pa rdzogs pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:10762: sa dang lam dus gcig la rdzogs pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:10763: 'bras bu sku lnga la sogs pa sangs rgyas kyi yon tan ma lus pa rdzogs pa'o //
NK122(kho)002:10764: 'di rnams kyi don rgyas par gsang sgron le'u bcu gsum pa yon tan yar ldan gyi le'u dang /
NK122(kho)002:10765: rtogs ldan shag rdor gyis theg spyi'i chen mor bkod 'dug pas der gzigs mdzod /
NK122(kho)002:10766: bzhi pa rtogs shing grol bar byed pa'i thabs ni /
NK122(kho)002:10767: spyir rdzogs chen gyi lugs la /
NK122(kho)002:10768: lta ba gtan la dbab par byed pa la che ba lnga dang /
NK122(kho)002:10771: bdag nyid chen po'i gtan tshig la sogs pa rnams
NK122(kho)002:10772: kyis gtan la phab nas lta ba rtogs par byed
NK122(kho)002:10778: yang rab rab dang 'bring dang tha ma grol //
NK122(kho)002:10780: dbang po yang rab gcig shes bya gcig chod rtogs grol lam thar pa dus mnyam pa ni /
NK122(kho)002:10782: slob tshul rim gyis ma yin kyang //
NK122(kho)002:10783: ma bgrod cig char 'jug pa'i sa //
NK122(kho)002:10785: rab rtogs pa'i don la gnas pa tsam gyis grol ba ni /
NK122(kho)002:10787: dbang po rab kyi sgom pa la //
NK122(kho)002:10788: mnyam dang mi mnyam med pa'i phyir //
NK122(kho)002:10789: 'bral med don la rtsol mi dgos //
NK122(kho)002:10790: sprin med nam mkha' ji bzhin no //
NK122(kho)002:10792: 'bring rtogs pa'i don la gnyug bsring nas nyams su blangs pas grol ba la /
NK122(kho)002:10795: nyams rtogs brtan pa gsum du 'dus /
NK122(kho)002:10796: tha ma gdams ngag gis ngo sprad de /
NK122(kho)002:10797: nyams rim pa ltar skyes nas grol ba'o //
NK122(kho)002:10798: de yang bram ze skor gyi lugs la /
NK122(kho)002:10799: dang por gnas pa'i ting nge 'dzin /
NK122(kho)002:10800: gnyis pa ni mi g.yo ba /
NK122(kho)002:10801: gsum pa mnyam pa nyid du 'gyur /
NK122(kho)002:10802: bzhi pa ye shes lhun gyis grub pa dang bzhi'i sgo nas lam bgrod nas grol bar gsungs /
NK122(kho)002:10803: rdzogs chen klong sde'i lugs la /
NK122(kho)002:10804: chos nyid mngon sum nyams gong 'phel /
NK122(kho)002:10806: chos nyid zad sar skyol ba dang bzhi'i sgo nas grol bar gsungs /
NK122(kho)002:10807: de la sogs pa rdzogs chen rang gzhung nas lam
NK122(kho)002:10808: bgrod tshul mi 'dra ba 'ga' zhig yod pa don
NK122(kho)002:10809: la gnad gcig par shes par bya'o //
NK122(kho)002:10810: da ni gzhung don bshad par bya ste /
NK122(kho)002:10811: rdzogs pa chen po la gnyis /
NK122(kho)002:10813: bye brag tu phye ste rgyas par bshad pa'o //
NK122(kho)002:10816: theg pa'i che ba'am don dbyer med pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:10818: theg pa gsum mam dgu kun gyi spyi dpal ni rdzogs pa chen po yin te /
NK122(kho)002:10819: 'di ni theg pa thams cad kyi yang rtse /
NK122(kho)002:10820: rgyud thams cad kyi rgyal po /
NK122(kho)002:10821: lung thams cad kyi spyi rje /
NK122(kho)002:10822: man ngag thams cad kyi nying khu /
NK122(kho)002:10823: chos thams cad kyi rtsa ba /
NK122(kho)002:10824: bstan pa thams cad kyi sgron me /
NK122(kho)002:10825: dus gsum sangs rgyas thams cad kyi dgongs pa'i bcud
NK122(kho)002:10826: 'dus pa dam chos rdzogs pa chen po 'di yin
NK122(kho)002:10827: no // gtan tshig de bas na /
NK122(kho)002:10828: shin tu rnal 'byor theg pa'i blo zhes bya'o //
NK122(kho)002:10829: 'di nyid kyi don la theg pa 'og ma bzhin byed rtsol mi dgos pas bya bral /
NK122(kho)002:10830: yon tan thams cad lhun gyis grub pas rdzogs pa
NK122(kho)002:10831: de lta bu'i don la blo gnas pas rnal 'byor
NK122(kho)002:10832: gzhi lam 'bras gsum dbyer med cing 'brel pas na
NK122(kho)002:10833: rgyud ces bya'o // de lta bu'i rang byung ye
NK122(kho)002:10834: shes lhun gyis grub pa'i phyir na tshig gi tha
NK122(kho)002:10835: snyad 'jug sgo la sogs pa'i bye brag ma mchis
NK122(kho)002:10836: rgyud ces bya'o // te / 'on kyang theg pa
NK122(kho)002:10837: 'og ma la ltos pa'i don gyis 'jug sgo la
NK122(kho)002:10839: 'og ma ltos nas yon tan rgyud la skye tshul gyi ngos nas dbye ba'o //
NK122(kho)002:10841: theg pa 'og ma kun gyi ldog phyogs kyis /
NK122(kho)002:10842: 'jug sgo la sogs bdun du dbye ba yin /
NK122(kho)002:10843: 'di nyid kyi ngo bo la chos kun rang byung gi ye shes su /
NK122(kho)002:10844: lhun gyis grub pas 'jug sgo la sogs pa'i tha snyad bdun po ka nas dag pa'o //
NK122(kho)002:10846: lta ba rtogs pa gcig pu'i ngos nas rdzogs par shes par bya'o //
NK122(kho)002:10848: ma h+aa rdzogs chen gcig yod pa mkha' 'gro snying thig lta bu /
NK122(kho)002:10849: thog mar bskyed rim bshad cing mthar rdzogs chen la ngo sprad pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:10850: gsang snying le'u bcu gsum pa'i u rgyan pad+ma lta
NK122(kho)002:10851: phreng gi nang du rdzogs chen gyi dgongs pa bstan
NK122(kho)002:10852: pa dang / rtogs pa bzhi dag pa gsum gyi sgo nas ngo sprad pa lta bu yin /
NK122(kho)002:10853: 'di'i lugs kyis rang bzhin rdzogs pa chen po nyid kyi chos skad de lta bu smra'o //
NK122(kho)002:10855: mdo dgongs 'dus kyi byung tshul bcu gnyis kyi nang nas bshad pa 'di nyid yin /
NK122(kho)002:10857: rdzogs chen spyir chibs pa zhes pa ni /
NK122(kho)002:10858: gtan tshig bzhi'i gtan la phab pa yin /
NK122(kho)002:10859: rdzogs chen gyi rdzogs chen ni /
NK122(kho)002:10861: zhe sdang rang byung chen po dang /
NK122(kho)002:10862: 'dod chags rang byung chen po dang /
NK122(kho)002:10863: gti mug rang byung chen po dang /
NK122(kho)002:10864: de la sogs pa shes bya srid tshad thams cad rang byung ye shes su gtan la phab pa'o //
NK122(kho)002:10865: 'di'i chos skad la thig le drug dang /
NK122(kho)002:10868: lung las ma byung ba'i gtan tshig dang /
NK122(kho)002:10869: rgyu las ma byung ba'i 'bras bu dang /
NK122(kho)002:10870: sems las ma byung ba'i sangs rgyas te /
NK122(kho)002:10871: 'di rnams rdzogs chen rang gzhung gi chos skad yin par shes par bya'o //
NK122(kho)002:10872: gzhan yang rtogs ldan shag rdor pas /
NK122(kho)002:10873: theg spyi'i nang du che ba lnga'i gtan la phab pa ni 'di lta ste /
NK122(kho)002:10874: a ti 'dus ma byas kyi ye shes che ba lngar sangs rgyas pa ni /
NK122(kho)002:10876: ma spangs mi gnas mi ltos rag ma lus //
NK122(kho)002:10877: tha snyad kun dang bral ba'i 'bras bu che //
NK122(kho)002:10878: rang bzhin lhun grub 'dus ma byas pas na //
NK122(kho)002:10879: 'bras bu'i rgyal po khyad par dpag ste che //
NK122(kho)002:10881: chos sku sems nyid rang snang ba yin pas /
NK122(kho)002:10882: de nyid spangs gar yang ma spangs par mngon par sangs rgyas pa'i che ba /
NK122(kho)002:10883: skye bo mu stegs pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:10885: rang rgyal las grol zhing dpag pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:10886: ltos ci la yang mi ltos te de nyid yin pa sangs rgyas pa'i che ba /
NK122(kho)002:10887: dbu ma sems tsam kri yog sde gsum las grol zhing dpag pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:10888: rag gar yang ma lus pa bdag nyid chen por sangs rgyas pa'i che ba /
NK122(kho)002:10889: ma h+aa yo ga las grol zhing dpag pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:10890: gnas ci la yang mi gnas par chos dbyings su sangs rgyas pa'i che ba /
NK122(kho)002:10891: a nu yo ga las grol zhing dpag pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:10892: thams cad nas thams cad du sangs rgyas pas sangs ma rgyas pa med pa'i che ba /
NK122(kho)002:10893: a ti'i rgyud lung man ngag las grol zhing dpag pa'o //
NK122(kho)002:10895: che ba lnga yi byang chub sems //
NK122(kho)002:10896: sems nyid che ba lngas dpag ste //
NK122(kho)002:10898: mngon par sangs rgyas che ba ni //
NK122(kho)002:10899: 'dus ma byas pa'i byang chub sems //
NK122(kho)002:10900: snang srid thams cad khyad par 'phags //
NK122(kho)002:10901: rdzogs pa chen po'i che bar bshad //
NK122(kho)002:10903: de yi sangs rgyas che ba ni //
NK122(kho)002:10904: ma nor ba yi byang chub sems //
NK122(kho)002:10905: gtan tshig kun las khyad par 'phags //
NK122(kho)002:10906: yo ga dag gi che bar bshad //
NK122(kho)002:10908: bdag nyid sangs rgyas che ba ni /
NK122(kho)002:10909: lhun gyis grub pa'i byang chub sems //
NK122(kho)002:10910: rtsol zhing bsgrub las khyad par 'phags //
NK122(kho)002:10911: ma h+aa yo ga'i che bar bshad //
NK122(kho)002:10913: chos dbyings sangs rgyas che ba ni //
NK122(kho)002:10914: thams cad 'byung ba'i byang chub sems //
NK122(kho)002:10916: a nu yo ga'i che bar bshad //
NK122(kho)002:10918: sangs rgyas thams cad che ba ni //
NK122(kho)002:10919: sgro skur 'das pa'i byang chub sems //
NK122(kho)002:10920: bsam dpyod kun las khyad par 'phags //
NK122(kho)002:10921: la zlos pa yi che bar bshad //
NK122(kho)002:10924: sems nyid klong chen yangs pa ru //
NK122(kho)002:10926: che ba lnga ru mngon sangs rgyas //
NK122(kho)002:10928: 'di rnams ni rdzogs chen mthar thug gi 'dod pa yin par shes par bya'o //
NK122(kho)002:10929: rgyas par bshad pa la brgyad de /
NK122(kho)002:10942: bskal pa dpag tu med pa'i sngon rol du dge
NK122(kho)002:10943: ba'i bshes gnyen bsten cing theg pa 'og ma'i don
NK122(kho)002:10944: blo la sbyangs pa'i skyes bu rtogs pa'i skal ba
NK122(kho)002:10945: dang ldan pa'i gsang sngags kyi rigs can de ni
NK122(kho)002:10946: dbang po rab kyi yang rab cig char ba'i rnal
NK122(kho)002:10947: 'byor pa sa bcu'i dbang phyug dang skal ba mnyam
NK122(kho)002:10948: pa de ni / 'di tshe gcig la mngon par rdzogs par nus par 'dod /
NK122(kho)002:10949: de lta bu de rdzogs chen la 'jug pa'i rten gyi gang zag yin no //
NK122(kho)002:10950: lung gis gsal bar bshad pa'o //
NK122(kho)002:10952: nam mkha' che'i lung las kyang ni 'di skad du
NK122(kho)002:10953: chos nyid kyi klong brjod pa thams cad dang bral
NK122(kho)002:10954: ba rdzogs pa chen po'i don 'di la gnas pa'i
NK122(kho)002:10955: rnal 'byor pa de ni yon tan gyi bgo skal
NK122(kho)002:10956: rgyas pas skal pa bzang ba'o //
NK122(kho)002:10958: dang zhes pa ni 'og nas rtse mo byung rgyal gyi lung sdud pa'o //
NK122(kho)002:10959: bskal pa dpag tu med pa'i sngon rol du theg
NK122(kho)002:10960: pa brgyad po la sbyangs pa'i skyes bu skal ldan
NK122(kho)002:10962: rdzogs pa chen po shin tu rnal 'byor gyi don
NK122(kho)002:10963: de ni bla ma'i man ngag snyan nas snyan du
NK122(kho)002:10964: brgyud pa khung nas khung du brgyud pa /
NK122(kho)002:10965: thugs nas thugs su brgyud par byed cing 'di lta
NK122(kho)002:10966: bu'i man ngag gang zag ci 'dra gcig gis nyams
NK122(kho)002:10967: su blang na lus srog la mi blta ba'i dad
NK122(kho)002:10968: pa can rgyal ba'i thugs kyi sras dang 'dra ba
NK122(kho)002:10970: zhes rtse mo byung rgyal las de ltar gsungs pa'o //
NK122(kho)002:10971: dang zhes pa ni gong du rdzogs chen rnams kyi lung song nas /
NK122(kho)002:10972: 'dir gsang ba'i snying po'i lung sdud pa'o //
NK122(kho)002:10973: bskal pa chen po'i grangs rgyal ba'i zhing gi rdul
NK122(kho)002:10974: phra rab de snyed gcig tu theg pa 'og ma'i
NK122(kho)002:10975: don la shin tu sbyangs pa la rab tu gnas
NK122(kho)002:10976: shing / gsang sngags kyi dkyil 'khor ma lus pa
NK122(kho)002:10977: kun bsnyen pa'i 'bras bu gsang chen rdzogs pa chen
NK122(kho)002:10981: don 'di dag gsungs pa'i phyir na lung de dag
NK122(kho)002:10982: gis gzhung 'dir bgrod cing drongs dang the tshom med
NK122(kho)002:10985: theg pa'i yang rtse rdzogs pa chen por 'jug pa'i sgo ni /
NK122(kho)002:10986: ya ki bla med sangs rgyas man chad nas ma
NK122(kho)002:10987: ki mnar med dmyal ba yan chad du 'khor 'das
NK122(kho)002:10988: gnyis su snang ba'i phyi nang gi chos 'di rnams
NK122(kho)002:10989: thams cad ma 'dres la yongs su rdzogs pas na
NK122(kho)002:10990: / rgya chad phyogs lhung thams cad dang bral ba
NK122(kho)002:10991: ni dbang po yang rab rdzogs chen gyi 'jug sgo
NK122(kho)002:10992: / yin no // 'di la ma 'dres yongs rdzogs rgyas par ngo sprod na /
NK122(kho)002:10993: chos kun rang byung gi ye shes la lhag ma med par yongs su rdzogs pa'o //
NK122(kho)002:10994: de'i rgyu mtshan ni rang byung ye shes su ma gyur pa'i chos gcig kyang med pas /
NK122(kho)002:10995: rang byung ye shes nyid 'khrul grol la sogs pa
NK122(kho)002:10996: tha snyad kyi snang ba gang yang ma 'dres la
NK122(kho)002:10997: / de nyid mu mtha' med cing kun la gnyis
NK122(kho)002:10998: su med par khyab pas yul med du yongs su
NK122(kho)002:10999: / rdzogs pa'o // de yang rig pa la mu mtha' med cing rgya chad phyogs lhung med pas /
NK122(kho)002:11000: rig pa gcig gi steng du yang thams cad ma 'dres par gsal lo //
NK122(kho)002:11001: des na 'dres pa'ang med la tha dad pa'ang med de ma 'dres la yongs su rdzogs pa'o //
NK122(kho)002:11002: de yang ma 'dres pa'i dus de nyid na /
NK122(kho)002:11003: thams cad dbyer med yul med du yongs su rdzogs
NK122(kho)002:11004: la yongs rdzogs kyi dus de nyid na'ang ma 'dres
NK122(kho)002:11006: des na ma 'dres pas yongs rdzogs kyi sgo ma bkag /
NK122(kho)002:11007: yongs rdzogs kyis ma 'dres pa'i sgo ma bkag par ma 'dres pa la yongs su rdzogs pa'o //
NK122(kho)002:11009: mnyam nyid gcig pa'i klong dkyil nas //
NK122(kho)002:11010: mnyam nyid klong phran mtha' yas shar //
NK122(kho)002:11012: cir yang min no gang yang 'dra //
NK122(kho)002:11013: dbyings la bzang ngan dbye ba med //
NK122(kho)002:11016: rnam mkhyen la dmyal ba'i sdug bsngal rdzogs sam ma rdzogs /
NK122(kho)002:11019: rdzogs chen gyi dam bca' bud /
NK122(kho)002:11020: rdzogs na dmyal ba sdug bsngal zhing nyam thag par thal zer na /
NK122(kho)002:11021: sangs rgyas kyi ngos na dmyal ba'i sdug bsngal log na ma lus par rdzogs dgos /
NK122(kho)002:11022: dmyal ba tsha grang gi rtog pa spangs ma dgos
NK122(kho)002:11023: par chos kun rang byung ye shes su rtogs pas
NK122(kho)002:11024: sdug bsngal gyi sa la med pa'o //
NK122(kho)002:11025: yang dmyal ba la sangs rgyas kyi dgongs pa rdzogs sam ma rdzogs /
NK122(kho)002:11028: rdzogs na sangs rgyas la mkhyen pa'i ye shes brtse
NK122(kho)002:11029: ba'i thugs rje mdzad pa'i phrin las yod pa bzhin
NK122(kho)002:11030: du dmyal ba la yang mkhyen brtse nus ldan yod
NK122(kho)002:11032: dmyal ba la sangs rgyas kyi dgongs pa rdzogs dgos te /
NK122(kho)002:11033: lcags sreg gi sa gzhi'i rtog pa rang bcos slad
NK122(kho)002:11034: dang bral ba sangs rgyas kyi dgongs pa yin pa'i
NK122(kho)002:11035: phyir / mkhyen brtse nus ldan shugs ldan du yod la /
NK122(kho)002:11036: nus ldan du ma shes pa ni rang ngo rang gi ma shes pa'o //
NK122(kho)002:11037: 'di lta bu'i don gyi shes bya'i gting mtha' rig
NK122(kho)002:11038: na 'gal ba dang gol sa dang 'khrul pa med
NK122(kho)002:11039: pa'o // lta ba la gnyis te /
NK122(kho)002:11043: bya bral rdzogs pa'i rnal 'byor gyi lta ba ni
NK122(kho)002:11044: 'khor 'das kyi chos kun snang tshul du ma 'dres
NK122(kho)002:11045: la chos nyid mnyam pa nyid kyi ngang du yongs
NK122(kho)002:11047: 'di yang gtan la 'beb pa'i tshul brjod pa mtha' yas pa gcig bshad de /
NK122(kho)002:11048: che ba lnga'i sgo nas gtan la dbab pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:11049: thig le drug gi sgo nas gtan la dbab pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:11050: bdag nyid chen po'i sgo nas gtan la dbab pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:11051: rgyud lung man ngag gi sgo nas gtan la phab pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:11052: gtan tshig bzhi'i sgo nas gtan la dbab pa'o //
NK122(kho)002:11053: 'di rnams rgyas par nam mkha' che'i gsang 'grel dang /
NK122(kho)002:11054: rdo la gser zhun gyi 'grel pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:11055: lta ba che lnga'i 'grel pa de rnams kyi nang na yod do //
NK122(kho)002:11056: shes 'dod na de rnams la gzigs mdzod //
NK122(kho)002:11057: 'dir yi ge mang ba'i phyir ma bris so //
NK122(kho)002:11059: theg pa spyi bcing gi skabs 'dir phyogs mtshon phran tsam cig bzung ba te /
NK122(kho)002:11060: de gang zhe na 'dir ni bsgrub pa'i gtam tshig bzhir bshad de /
NK122(kho)002:11061: de yang dngos po mtshan ma gzugs dbyibs kha dog gang du yang ma grub cing /
NK122(kho)002:11062: dri ma ka nas dag pa'i gnas lugs ni rang bzhin skye ba med pa'i gtan tshig dang /
NK122(kho)002:11063: de nyid 'gag pa med pa las 'khor 'das snang
NK122(kho)002:11064: srid kyis bsdus pa'i chos thams cad kyi rgya mtsho
NK122(kho)002:11065: la gza' skar 'char ba lta bu ni kun bzang
NK122(kho)002:11066: rol pa 'gags pa med pa'i gtan tshig dang /
NK122(kho)002:11069: chu dang chu'i rlabs bzhin du ye nas dbyer med
NK122(kho)002:11070: pa ni mtshan nyid dbye ba med pa'i gtan tshig
NK122(kho)002:11071: dang / ma skyes mi 'gag dbyer med spyod yul dang bral ba /
NK122(kho)002:11074: rig pa nyid de'i ngo bor shar ba ni ngo bo rang grol gyi gtan tshig ste /
NK122(kho)002:11075: rdzogs chen rgyud kyi snying po las /
NK122(kho)002:11076: rang bzhin skye med gtan tshig gis //
NK122(kho)002:11077: lhun gyis grub par yid ches bya //
NK122(kho)002:11078: rol pa 'gag med gtan tshig gis //
NK122(kho)002:11079: cir yang 'char bar yid ches bya //
NK122(kho)002:11080: mtshan nyid dbyer med gtan tshig gis //
NK122(kho)002:11081: chos rnams gcig par yid ches bya //
NK122(kho)002:11082: ngo bo rang grol gtan tshig gis //
NK122(kho)002:11083: rtsol ba med par yid ches bya //
NK122(kho)002:11085: de ltar gtan tshig bzhi ru rgyal ba kun tu bzang pos bshad do //
NK122(kho)002:11086: gang gi gtan tshig bzhi po de nyid /
NK122(kho)002:11090: ngo bo nyid kyi sku dang bzhi la ngo sprad do //
NK122(kho)002:11091: gtan tshig bzhi po 'di ni shin tu gnad che ba yin pas /
NK122(kho)002:11093: dgongs gzhi dgos ched kyi sgo nas ngo sprad pa yin pas /
NK122(kho)002:11095: rang bzhin skye med gtan tshig 'di ltar snang ba'i
NK122(kho)002:11096: chos kun gyi ngo bo gzugs dbyibs kha dog mtshan
NK122(kho)002:11097: mar ma grub pa'i dri bral ka dag cig la
NK122(kho)002:11098: zer / de'i dgongs gzhi ni skye med kyi ngang
NK122(kho)002:11099: la dngos po mtshan ma'i sel med pa gcig la
NK122(kho)002:11100: zer / dgongs / dgos ched a 'thas ther gzugs pa gcig las grol ba'o //
NK122(kho)002:11101: rol pa 'gag med kyi gtan tshig ni /
NK122(kho)002:11102: dper na chu nyid las ma g.yos bzhin du /
NK122(kho)002:11103: gnyer ma dang rlabs sna tshogs su shar yang chu rang yin pa bzhin du /
NK122(kho)002:11104: skye med kho rang gi rang gzugs 'khor 'das phyi
NK122(kho)002:11105: nang gi chos thams cad du shar ba la zer
NK122(kho)002:11106: / de'i dgongs gzhi 'gags med kyi ngo la snang ba sna tshogs su shar ba gcig la dgongs /
NK122(kho)002:11107: dgos ched ni stong zhen nam chad lta las grol ba'o //
NK122(kho)002:11108: mtshan nyid dbyer med ni chu las gnyer ma dang
NK122(kho)002:11109: rlabs ci byung na yang chu rang sa yin pa
NK122(kho)002:11110: bzhin du / 'khor 'das snang ba sna tshogs su
NK122(kho)002:11111: shar yang ngo bo chos sku skye med kyi gnas
NK122(kho)002:11112: lugs las skad cig kyang ma g.yos pa'o //
NK122(kho)002:11113: de'i dgongs gzhi snang stong gnyis med gcig yin pa la dgongs /
NK122(kho)002:11114: dgos ched ni snang stong tha dad ni kyi 'dzin pa las grol ba'o //
NK122(kho)002:11115: rig pa rang grol gyi gtan tshig ni /
NK122(kho)002:11116: rig pa nyid lta ba'i ngo bor shar nas /
NK122(kho)002:11117: ma skyes ma 'gags dbyer med gsum spyod yul dang bral ba'o //
NK122(kho)002:11119: rig pa nyid lta ba'i ngo bo yin pa la
NK122(kho)002:11120: dgongs dgos ched ma skyes mi 'gags yul med du
NK122(kho)002:11121: shar ba'o // des chos kun rang byung ma 'dres yongs rdzogs par rtogs pa'o //
NK122(kho)002:11122: rgyas par bshad pa la bzhi ste /
NK122(kho)002:11123: rang bzhin skye med kyi gtan tshig dang /
NK122(kho)002:11124: rol pa 'gag med kyi gtan tshig /
NK122(kho)002:11125: mtshan nyid dbye med kyi gtan tshig /
NK122(kho)002:11126: ngo bo rang grol gyi gtan tshig go //
NK122(kho)002:11129: gdams par bya ba'i gzhi ma 'gags par snang ba'ang yin pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:11131: rang bzhin skye ba med pa'i gtan tshig rgyas par
NK122(kho)002:11132: bshad cing gsal bar bstan pa ni 'di lta ste
NK122(kho)002:11133: / ma rtogs pa 'khor ba rtogs pa 'das pa
NK122(kho)002:11134: shes bya snang srid kyis bsdus pa'i phyi snod kyi
NK122(kho)002:11135: 'jig rten nang bcud kyi sems can dang las dkar
NK122(kho)002:11136: po dge ba nag po sdig pa bzang ba mtho
NK122(kho)002:11137: ris ngan pa ngan song la sogs pa rnams med
NK122(kho)002:11138: bzhin du nan gyis brtag pa'i zhen brtag gnyis snang
NK122(kho)002:11140: 'gro ba drug gi las snang so so'i mthun snang
NK122(kho)002:11141: gi cha la 'gag pa med par rang snang ste
NK122(kho)002:11142: / snang tsam nyid na bya rtsol dang bral ba chos dbyings ma skyes par bstan pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:11144: 'di ltar so sor snang ba'i dus de nyid na
NK122(kho)002:11145: chos nyid skye ba med pa'i ngang las ma g.yos
NK122(kho)002:11146: par sems can sgrim pos ma bcos sangs rgyas sgam
NK122(kho)002:11147: pos ma byas shing gnyen po gang yang med pa
NK122(kho)002:11148: chos can dang chos nyid la sogs pa'i bye brag
NK122(kho)002:11149: tha snyad thams cad dang spyod yul ngang gis bral
NK122(kho)002:11150: ba'o // de'i tshe na rgya chad phyogs lhung gi
NK122(kho)002:11151: mi mtha' med pa'i ye shes kyi dba' klong gcig
NK122(kho)002:11152: ba'o // tu gyur pa'o // de'i mtshan nyid ni /
NK122(kho)002:11153: mtha' dbus med pas gdal ba che //
NK122(kho)002:11154: 'od bsdu med par thams cad khyab //
NK122(kho)002:11156: skye med mtshon pa'i ming dang /
NK122(kho)002:11158: de'i bla dwags ni ming gi rnam grangs yin pa'o //
NK122(kho)002:11159: de dag gi bye brag ni 'di lta ste /
NK122(kho)002:11160: spros pa dang bral zhing mi 'gyur bas chos nyid ces bya'o //
NK122(kho)002:11161: dngos po mtshan mar ma grub pas ma skyes pa
NK122(kho)002:11162: ces kyang bya thams cad kyi 'byung gnas su gyur
NK122(kho)002:11163: pas chos kyi dbyings zhes kyang bya /
NK122(kho)002:11164: rgya chad phyogs lhung thams cad dang bral bas mu med ces kyang bya /
NK122(kho)002:11165: gnas lugs kyi don 'di'i kun la khyab pas gdal ba chen po'i klong zhes bya /
NK122(kho)002:11166: ma bcos ma bslad pas ye ci bzhin pa'i dkyil 'khor dang /
NK122(kho)002:11167: chos thams cad kyi gnas lugs yin pas rnal ma don gyi kun gzhi dang /
NK122(kho)002:11168: stong pa skye med kyi gnas lugs chos dbyings ka
NK122(kho)002:11169: dag 'di shes bya'i mchog tu gyur pa yin pas
NK122(kho)002:11170: shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa zhes bya'o
NK122(kho)002:11171: // de la sogs pa skye med kyi bla dwags bsam mtha' yas pa'o //
NK122(kho)002:11174: 'khor ba thams cad dang 'das pa thams cad skye
NK122(kho)002:11175: med kyi gnas lugs der gcig kyang de la phyogs
NK122(kho)002:11177: ris su chad pa gnyis su mi mnga' ba'i phyir /
NK122(kho)002:11178: rang bzhin skye med kyi gtan tshig ces brjod do //
NK122(kho)002:11180: rang bzhin skye med gtan tshig ni //
NK122(kho)002:11181: gzhi la snang ba med pa yis //
NK122(kho)002:11182: chos rnams thams cad spros dang bral //
NK122(kho)002:11183: de phyir rang bzhin skye ba med ces so //
NK122(kho)002:11184: rol pa 'gag med la gsum ste /
NK122(kho)002:11187: shin tu rgyas par bshad pa'o //
NK122(kho)002:11190: ma 'gags par snang ba dngos dang /
NK122(kho)002:11192: rol pa 'gag med gtan tshig ni //
NK122(kho)002:11194: snod bcud bde sdug rgyu 'bras dang //
NK122(kho)002:11195: gnyis par snang ba'i chos 'di rnams //
NK122(kho)002:11197: so sor rang rtsal 'gag pa med par shar ba
NK122(kho)002:11198: de ni so so'i ming ji ltar btags pas chags
NK122(kho)002:11199: / ci ltar btags pa ltar snang /
NK122(kho)002:11200: gang ltar bsgrub kyang bsam pa ltar 'grub ste /
NK122(kho)002:11201: de lta bu brtag pa'i zhen blos btags pa bzhin no //
NK122(kho)002:11202: de nyid kun tu bzang po rol pa'i rgyan du bstan pa'o //
NK122(kho)002:11204: de dag gang yang spangs len med cing 'gag pa
NK122(kho)002:11205: med pa'i phyir kun bzang rol pa'i rgyan ces bya
NK122(kho)002:11206: ba yin no // rgyas pa la gnyis te /
NK122(kho)002:11208: 'gag pa med pa rang bzhin lhun gyis grub pa'i
NK122(kho)002:11209: dkyil 'khor de 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad du
NK122(kho)002:11211: rol pa 'gags pa med pas lhun grub tu bstan te /
NK122(kho)002:11212: dngos po dang mthun par snang ba dang /
NK122(kho)002:11213: 'phral gyi 'bad rtsol la mi nyams par sems nyid
NK122(kho)002:11214: ye nas sangs rgyas lhun gyis grub pa'i dkyil 'khor
NK122(kho)002:11215: thams cad de theg pa dgu kun gyis gzhal bya
NK122(kho)002:11216: yin pa dang / mu stegs kyis log par brtag pas 'khrul gzhi byas pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:11217: 'jig rten pas bden par 'dzin pas 'jig rten pa'i zhen phyogs rnams dang /
NK122(kho)002:11218: thams cad rang snang 'gag med kyi gnas lugs 'di
NK122(kho)002:11219: yin pas ngo ma shes pas 'khrul pa thams cad
NK122(kho)002:11221: ye shes rang snang lhun gyis grub pa de rtogs ma rtogs kyis 'ching grol du bstan pa'o //
NK122(kho)002:11223: phyi rol gyi yul 'gag med du snang ba 'di
NK122(kho)002:11224: rtogs na grol la ma rtogs dus na 'ching bar
NK122(kho)002:11225: bshad / mu stegs pas log par brtag pas shin tu'ang 'ching bar sangs rgyas kyis gsungs so //
NK122(kho)002:11226: theg pa 'og ma pas gnas lugs 'gyur med kyi
NK122(kho)002:11227: don ma rtogs par the tshom gyi lus pa 'di
NK122(kho)002:11228: yang sangs rgyas pa la thag ring ngo //
NK122(kho)002:11229: shin tu rgyas pa la gnyis te /
NK122(kho)002:11230: 'jig rten pa la snang tshul dang /
NK122(kho)002:11234: so so'i skye bo phal pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:11236: de la 'jig rten thun mong pas zhes pa ni /
NK122(kho)002:11237: so so'i skye bo lam la ma zhugs pa rnams
NK122(kho)002:11238: kyis rol pa 'gag med kyi snang ba 'di la
NK122(kho)002:11239: / 'byung chen nus pa nyid du brtan te /
NK122(kho)002:11244: rlung la rlung yin snyam nas zhen pas yul gyis 'ching ba yin no //
NK122(kho)002:11245: mu stegs pa la snang tshul lo //
NK122(kho)002:11247: mu stegs rtag par lta bas ni snod bcud thams
NK122(kho)002:11248: cad phya dang dbang phyug khyab 'jug la sogs pas
NK122(kho)002:11249: byas pa yin zer zhing gdos po rang kha mar
NK122(kho)002:11250: 'dzin pa'o // de nyid rang gi grub mtha' nyid du 'dod do //
NK122(kho)002:11252: rgyu'i theg pa la snang tshul dang gsang sngags la snang tshul lo //
NK122(kho)002:11257: nyan thos rnams kyis phyi bzung ba'i yul rdul phran cha med du gtan la dbab /
NK122(kho)002:11258: nang 'dzin pa'i sems skad cig cha shas dang bral
NK122(kho)002:11259: bar gtan la dbab ste rags pa gang zag gi
NK122(kho)002:11260: bdag med par the tshom bcad pas khams gsum 'khor
NK122(kho)002:11261: ba 'di las cung zad cig grol ba yin no
NK122(kho)002:11265: phyi gzung ba'i yul rdul phran de dang nang 'dzin pa'i sems gnyis /
NK122(kho)002:11266: phyi nang rten 'brel bcu gnyis su brtags pa yis gtan la phab nas /
NK122(kho)002:11267: bdag med phyed dang gnyis rtogs pas srid pa khams gsum 'khor ba'i chos las 'das par 'gyur ro //
NK122(kho)002:11268: byang chub sems dpa'i theg pa la gnyis te /
NK122(kho)002:11272: byang chub sems dpa' rnams kyis ni /
NK122(kho)002:11273: la las 'khrul ba'i gzhi sems tsam ste /
NK122(kho)002:11274: phyi rol gyi yul snang ba sna tshogs 'di nang gi sems su smra ba'o //
NK122(kho)002:11277: dbu ma pa la las shes pa skad cig ma
NK122(kho)002:11278: de dus gsum gyi chas gzhig pa las stong par
NK122(kho)002:11279: smra ba'o // phyi rol gyi yul 'di sgyu ma'i dpe brgyad ltar gtan la phab nas /
NK122(kho)002:11280: kun rdzob bden par ming btags te sems can mi
NK122(kho)002:11281: bslu ba'i tshul gyis byams snying rje'i sgo nas gzhan
NK122(kho)002:11282: don spyod pa'o // gsang sngags la snang tshul lo //
NK122(kho)002:11287: rang snang 'gag med kyi snang ba la gsang sngags theg pas lha ru 'dod pa'o //
NK122(kho)002:11288: de'ang bye brag gsang sngags phyi nang rnam pa gnyis te /
NK122(kho)002:11293: la las dag pa lha ru 'dod /
NK122(kho)002:11297: rnal 'byor gsum gyis 'dod pa bshad par bya'o //
NK122(kho)002:11300: la las de nyid lha ru 'dod /
NK122(kho)002:11302: ma h+aa dang a nu gnyis kyi 'dod pa bstan pa'o //
NK122(kho)002:11303: 'di rnams go sla bas rgyas par ma bshad do //
NK122(kho)002:11304: don la rdzogs pa chen po'i lugs la /
NK122(kho)002:11305: 'khor 'das snang srid kyis bsdus pa'i chos thams cad
NK122(kho)002:11306: 'gag med kyi snang ba ma 'dres pa'i gnas lugs
NK122(kho)002:11307: ye shes kyi klong chen gcig tu 'dod pa la
NK122(kho)002:11308: / de ltar ma rtogs nas 'gro ba rigs drug gi 'khrul gzugs drug /
NK122(kho)002:11309: mu stegs rtag chad kyi snang tshul gnyis /
NK122(kho)002:11310: theg pa brgyad kyis 'dod lugs brgyad bshad pa'o //
NK122(kho)002:11311: rdzogs pa chen po la snang tshul lo //
NK122(kho)002:11313: bya bral lhun gyis grub pa ni rdzogs pa chen po'i 'dod pa ste /
NK122(kho)002:11314: sems kyi gnas lugs rgya chad phyogs lhung dang bral zhing /
NK122(kho)002:11315: dngos po kha dog gzugs dbyibs phyogs lhung can ma grub pas rang bzhin ci yang ma yin la /
NK122(kho)002:11316: de nyid rig pa'i rtsal ye shes kyi 'char sgo
NK122(kho)002:11317: dper na rgya mtsho dngas pa la gzugs brnyan bkag
NK122(kho)002:11318: pas mi khegs pa bzhin du rol pa cir yang
NK122(kho)002:11319: mi 'gag pas phyi nang gi chos thams cad du
NK122(kho)002:11320: shar ba'o // 'o na sangs rgyas dgongs pa gzung 'dzin can du thal zhe na /
NK122(kho)002:11322: zhes pas sangs rgyas kyi dgongs pa rgya chad phyogs
NK122(kho)002:11323: lhung zhen 'dzin gyi dri ma ka nas dag pa'o
NK122(kho)002:11325: rol pa gang yang ma 'gags pas //
NK122(kho)002:11327: de phyir rol pa 'gags pa med //
NK122(kho)002:11328: sangs rgyas kun gyi che bar bshad //
NK122(kho)002:11331: sems nyid yod med kun ngo bo //
NK122(kho)002:11332: de phyir nam mkha' yod med ces //
NK122(kho)002:11333: blun po rnams ni rtsod byed cing //
NK122(kho)002:11334: mkhas pas nam mkha'i rang bzhin la //
NK122(kho)002:11337: nam mkha' yod par mi 'dzin te nam mkha'i ngo
NK122(kho)002:11338: bo la dngos po gzugs dbyibs ma grub pa'i phyir
NK122(kho)002:11340: gsal stong go skabs 'byed pa'i snang ba 'di yin pa'i phyir /
NK122(kho)002:11342: sems nyid kyi ngo bo la dngos po gzugs dbyibs
NK122(kho)002:11343: kha dog gang du yang ma grub pa'i phyir yod
NK122(kho)002:11345: de nyid la phyi nang gi chos thams cad 'char ba /
NK122(kho)002:11346: gsal cha che la 'dzin cha chung ba yin pas na med pa'i phyogs ltung dang bral ba'o //
NK122(kho)002:11347: gong gi phyogs lhung bral ba 'jug sgo yin /
NK122(kho)002:11348: zhes pas 'di lta bu'i sgo nas 'jug dgos so //
NK122(kho)002:11349: da rung 'di la sha chod rus chod du ngo sprad rgyu yod kyang /
NK122(kho)002:11350: snyan rgyud zhal gyi gdams pa rje btsun gong ma
NK122(kho)002:11351: rnams kyi thugs dam khrid ces bya ba la shes
NK122(kho)002:11352: par bya'o // mtshan nyid dbyer med kyi gtan tshig la gsum ste /
NK122(kho)002:11354: dpe'i sgo nas rgyas par bshad pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:11356: mtshan nyid dbyer med kyi gtan tshig ni dper na
NK122(kho)002:11357: chu nyid rlabs su shar ba'am yang na nam mkha'i
NK122(kho)002:11358: khams nas lho sprin nyid du snang yang /
NK122(kho)002:11359: snang tsam nyid na'ang nam mkha'i ngang du thim pas
NK122(kho)002:11360: stong pa ltar don la 'khor 'das kyi chos thams
NK122(kho)002:11361: cad kyang rol pa 'gag pa med pa'i dus na'ang
NK122(kho)002:11362: skye med kyi dbyings las skad cig kyang g.yos pa
NK122(kho)002:11363: med / de ltar rol pa 'gag pa med pa
NK122(kho)002:11364: rten 'brel gyi nus mthu yis so so'i bsam pa
NK122(kho)002:11365: ltar don byed pa'i rgyu dang rkyen snang ba sna
NK122(kho)002:11367: de tsam nyid na'ang rang bzhin nyid las nyams pa med pa'o //
NK122(kho)002:11368: de nyid lung gis gsal bar bya ba dang /
NK122(kho)002:11370: kun byed rgyal po'i lung las kyang ni 'di skad du /
NK122(kho)002:11371: rang bzhin gcig tu ma nges pas //
NK122(kho)002:11372: ci ltar bltas pa de ltar snang //
NK122(kho)002:11375: med pa'i rgyu las yod gsal ba //
NK122(kho)002:11376: snang nyid rang bzhin sgyu ma 'dra //
NK122(kho)002:11379: rgyu rkyen med pa las re zhig 'gag med gsal
NK122(kho)002:11380: ba ltar snang ba 'di thams cad snang ba'i dus
NK122(kho)002:11381: de nyid na'ang / rang bzhin ma grub ste /
NK122(kho)002:11382: sgyu ma mkhan gyi rta glang dang 'dra'o //
NK122(kho)002:11384: ci ltar nam mkha'i sprin bzhin du //
NK122(kho)002:11385: sna tshogs rnam pa cir snang yang //
NK122(kho)002:11386: de dus rang bzhin nyams pa med //
NK122(kho)002:11387: de sogs sna tshogs lung gis gsal zhes pa ni go sla'o //
NK122(kho)002:11388: ming gi rnam grangs nyid rang chas su gnas /
NK122(kho)002:11389: ngo bo'i rgyu ni rtogs byed kyi shes rab rang la yod /
NK122(kho)002:11391: bdag po'i rkyen ni mtshan nyid dang ldan pa'i bla ma la /
NK122(kho)002:11392: lhan cig skyes pa'i rkyen rang rig shes rab /
NK122(kho)002:11393: dmigs pa'i rkyen spyod yul thams cad rang byung gi ye shes /
NK122(kho)002:11394: de ma thag pa'i rkyen de dag thams cad 'dzom ba'i skad cig ma'o //
NK122(kho)002:11396: dmigs pa'i rkyen slob dpon dang glegs bam /
NK122(kho)002:11397: bdag po'i rkyen tshogs drug skyon med pa'o //
NK122(kho)002:11398: 'jug pa'i rkyen shes pa dngas pa /
NK122(kho)002:11399: de ma thag pa'i rkyen de dag thams cad 'dzom pa'o //
NK122(kho)002:11400: rtogs pa skye ba'i gdam ngag dngos //
NK122(kho)002:11402: gtan tshig gsum blo gdal bas /
NK122(kho)002:11404: rtogs pa skye thabs kyi gdams ngag dngos la /
NK122(kho)002:11405: rang bzhin skye med kyi gtan tshig /
NK122(kho)002:11406: rol pa 'gag med kyi gtan tshig mtshan nyid dbyer
NK122(kho)002:11407: med kyi gtan tshig gsum la blo gdal bas chos
NK122(kho)002:11408: kun mnyam pa nyid yul du ma byas par rig
NK122(kho)002:11409: pa nyid dbyings kyi ngo bor shar ba'o //
NK122(kho)002:11410: rtogs pa skye tshul la gnyis te /
NK122(kho)002:11412: rtogs pa'i yon tan gyi mi mthun pa'i phyogs rang sar dag pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:11414: srid pa'i chos rnams rang sar grol //
NK122(kho)002:11416: dper na nam mkha'i mthongs su nyi ma shar ba'i dus su /
NK122(kho)002:11417: mun pa thams cad thal gyis 'dir song gi khung med de /
NK122(kho)002:11418: rang sar dag cing grol ba'o //
NK122(kho)002:11419: dpe de bzhin du gtan tshig gsum po la blo
NK122(kho)002:11420: bdal nas chos kun mnyam pa nyid kyi don rtogs
NK122(kho)002:11421: pa'i dus su / srid pa'i chos thams cad rang
NK122(kho)002:11422: sar dag cing nyon mongs pa lnga dang khams gsum
NK122(kho)002:11423: 'khor ba'i sdug bsngal thams cad shugs kyis zhi zhing
NK122(kho)002:11425: rnam shes yul sems gnas su dag zhes pa ni /
NK122(kho)002:11426: rnam par shes pa'i tshogs brgyad ye shes lnga'i ngo bor dag pa'o //
NK122(kho)002:11427: de yang rnam shes tshogs brgyad dang /
NK122(kho)002:11428: gsang sngags kyi lugs la tshogs dgu ngo sprod dgos te /
NK122(kho)002:11429: rnal mngon gyi kun gzhi gding ches sbyor ba don gyi kun gzhi bsogs rkyen /
NK122(kho)002:11431: yid kyi shes pa col chung sgo lnga lam bstan pa'o //
NK122(kho)002:11435: chu dang bram ltar ngo bo gcig tu rtogs pa ni bden gnyis dbyer med ces kyang bya /
NK122(kho)002:11436: kun rdzob byang chub sems dang don dam byang chub
NK122(kho)002:11437: sems gnyis chu dang chu'i rlabs bzhin dbyer med du
NK122(kho)002:11438: rtogs pa ni byang chub sems dbyer med ces kyang
NK122(kho)002:11439: bya / ma skyes mi 'gag dbyer med kyi don de nyid rang rig la lhun gyis grub pas /
NK122(kho)002:11440: dper na mar la snum lhun gyis grub /
NK122(kho)002:11441: chu la gsher lhun gyis grub pa lta bu yin pa ni dbyer med lhun grub zhes kyang bya /
NK122(kho)002:11443: bden pa dbyer med ro gcig tu rtogs shing theg
NK122(kho)002:11444: pa 'og ma'i zung 'jug las dpag pas na zung
NK122(kho)002:11446: chos kun ma 'dres yongs rdzogs su rtogs pas na /
NK122(kho)002:11447: mnyam rdzogs chen po zhes kyang bya /
NK122(kho)002:11448: de la sogs pa grub matha'i bye brag gi ming ni bka' rdzogs pa chen po zhes kyang bya /
NK122(kho)002:11449: shin tu rnal 'byor zhes kyang bya /
NK122(kho)002:11450: gzhan yang sna tshogs ming gi rnam grangs bla dwags bsam mtha' yas pa yod pa shes par bya'o //
NK122(kho)002:11451: rig pa rang grol gyi gtan tshig la bzhi ste /
NK122(kho)002:11453: rtogs byed rten gyi gang zag gi mtshan nyid dang /
NK122(kho)002:11455: rig pa rang grol gyi gtan tshig ni /
NK122(kho)002:11456: gang zhig rten gyi gang zag skyes bu skal ldan can ni /
NK122(kho)002:11457: gong du bshad pa dang mthun pa gcig dgos so //
NK122(kho)002:11458: rtogs pa'i rgyu rkyen phun sum tshogs pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:11460: ma nor dam pa'i gsung ni rgyud lung la brten
NK122(kho)002:11461: nas shin tu rnal 'byor gyi theg pa la shes
NK122(kho)002:11462: rab gsum gyis rgyud sbyangs te /
NK122(kho)002:11463: dang po thos pa'i shes rab kyis tshig gi rtsa ba bcad /
NK122(kho)002:11464: bsam pa'i shes rab kyis nyon mongs pa'i chab rom bzhu /
