NK122(kho)002:11465: sgom pa'i shes rab kyis nyon mongs pa rang sar grol ba'o //
NK122(kho)002:11466: rgyu rkyen drug la me ltar g.yos //
NK122(kho)002:11468: rgyu gnyis rkyen bzhi dang drug gi sgo nas rdzogs chen gyi don rtogs te /
NK122(kho)002:11473: de'ang rnal mngon gyi kun gzhi ni chos dbyings ye shes su ngo sprad /
NK122(kho)002:11474: sbyor ba don gyi kun gzhi me long ye shes su /
NK122(kho)002:11475: nyon yid mnyam nyid ye shes /
NK122(kho)002:11476: yid kyi shes pa so sor rtog pa'i ye shes su /
NK122(kho)002:11477: sgo lnga bya ba grub pa'i ye shes su ngo sprad do //
NK122(kho)002:11478: 'di rnams la rnam shes tshogs brgyad kyi byed las /
NK122(kho)002:11479: ye shes lnga yin pa'i rgyu mtshan /
NK122(kho)002:11481: gnas su dag ma dag gi sa mtshams zhib tu ngo sprad rgyu yang /
NK122(kho)002:11482: gsang sgrogs su 'gro dogs pas don gyis 'dir ma bkod /
NK122(kho)002:11483: bla ma mkhas rtogs gdengs ldan rnams kyi zhal las shes par bya'o //
NK122(kho)002:11484: rtogs pa'i ye shes shar tshul lo //
NK122(kho)002:11486: gong du bshad pa bzhin gtan tshig gsum la blo gdal bas ni /
NK122(kho)002:11487: rgyu las ma byung rkyen gyis ma bskyed par rang
NK122(kho)002:11488: byung sgrib g.yog dang bral bas ye shes chen po'i
NK122(kho)002:11489: klong du shar ba yin no //
NK122(kho)002:11490: snang stong gang la'ang rten cha bral //
NK122(kho)002:11492: mnyam nyid kyi gnas lugs rtogs pa'i dus su /
NK122(kho)002:11493: snang ba dang stong pa gang la yang rten bca' ba ma yin /
NK122(kho)002:11494: dper na bya nam mkha' la lding ba'i dus su gshog rtse phyogs gang du'ang gtad pa ma yin /
NK122(kho)002:11495: de bzhin du rig pa nyid rgya chad phyogs lhung thams cad dang bral ba yin pas na /
NK122(kho)002:11496: phyogs lhung bral ba'i lta ba 'char zhes zer ro //
NK122(kho)002:11497: gnas lugs zab mo'i don rtogs pas rtogs ldan zhes kyang bya /
NK122(kho)002:11498: bya rtsol thams cad dang bral bas bya bral zhes kyang bya /
NK122(kho)002:11499: de lta bu'i don rnal ma la rang rig pa'i blo 'byor bas rnal 'byor pa zhes kyang bya /
NK122(kho)002:11500: spyod lam rnam bzhir rtse gcig tu dril bas sgom chen pa zhes kyang bya /
NK122(kho)002:11501: de lta bu'i nyams len dam pa khong du chud pas gang zag dam pa zhes kyang bya /
NK122(kho)002:11503: rgya chad phyogs lhung med pa'i phyir //
NK122(kho)002:11504: nam mkha'i dbyings ltar spros dang bral //
NK122(kho)002:11506: ngo bo nyid du blo grol bas //
NK122(kho)002:11507: gtan tshig nges par yid ches don //
NK122(kho)002:11508: lus ngag rtsol ba med pa'i phyir //
NK122(kho)002:11509: rang byung blo la 'ching grol med //
NK122(kho)002:11510: de phyir de bzhin nyid du gnas //
NK122(kho)002:11512: gzung 'dzin skyon gyis ma gos par //
NK122(kho)002:11513: rnam grol blo ni rang sar grol //
NK122(kho)002:11514: de phyir nges don ye shes klong //
NK122(kho)002:11515: rgyu dang rkyen las ma byung bas //
NK122(kho)002:11516: rang byung ngo bo nyid kyi sku //
NK122(kho)002:11517: de nyid rtogs pas chos skur grol //
NK122(kho)002:11518: yang dag sangs rgyas 'di las med //
NK122(kho)002:11522: lta bsgom dbyer med kyi ting nge 'dzin rang gi ngo bo dang /
NK122(kho)002:11524: bya bral rdzogs pa'i bsam gtan ni /
NK122(kho)002:11525: chos kun rang byung ye shes bde chen gyi klong du rang blo bdal ba ni /
NK122(kho)002:11526: shes bya dang shes byed bsgrub bya dang sgrub byed
NK122(kho)002:11527: dmigs bya dang dmigs byed la sogs pa'i rten cha
NK122(kho)002:11528: thams cad dang bral nas rang rig yul bral gyi
NK122(kho)002:11529: ye shes chen po ni rdzogs pa chen po'i sgom
NK122(kho)002:11530: bsam gtan kun gyi ngo bor byung ba yin no
NK122(kho)002:11533: kun byed rgyal po'i lung las kyang ni 'di skad du /
NK122(kho)002:11534: snang ba med pa'i chos nyid ni //
NK122(kho)002:11535: ma brtsal bzhag na sgom pa yin //
NK122(kho)002:11536: zhes sogs gsungs pas mngon du 'byin /
NK122(kho)002:11538: bsam gtan 'di ni blo rab kyi sgom du byung /
NK122(kho)002:11539: spyir rdzogs chen gyi lugs la /
NK122(kho)002:11540: lta ba rtogs nas grol lugs bzhi yod de /
NK122(kho)002:11542: yang rab rab dang 'bring dang tha ma grol /
NK122(kho)002:11544: rtogs ldan shag rdor gyis springs yig rig pa'i 'od zer gyi nang du 'di skad bkod 'dug /
NK122(kho)002:11545: nyams len yang rab rab 'bring tha ma ste //
NK122(kho)002:11546: yang rab shes bya ci ltar gnas pa'i don //
NK122(kho)002:11547: yul med rang grol chos nyid mngon du rtogs //
NK122(kho)002:11548: 'khor ba spangs med snang srid chos skur shar //
NK122(kho)002:11549: skad cig gcig la mthar phyin rdzogs sangs rgyas //
NK122(kho)002:11550: che ba'i yon tan rgya mtsho gzhi nas rdzogs //
NK122(kho)002:11551: rim med cig char grol bar rgyal bas gsungs //
NK122(kho)002:11552: rab kyi blo ldan rnal 'byor sgom pa ni //
NK122(kho)002:11553: rtogs pa'i don la bzhag thabs skyon bcos dang //
NK122(kho)002:11554: ngo bo rtogs tshad nyams kyi rim pa ste //
NK122(kho)002:11555: dang por rang snang yul med mngon rtogs pas //
NK122(kho)002:11556: blta bya lta byed ngang gis dag pa'i phyir //
NK122(kho)002:11557: bsgom mkhan gang gis sgom rgyu ci zhig bsgom //
NK122(kho)002:11558: bsgom bya sgom byed med pa'i sgom pa ni //
NK122(kho)002:11559: chos nyid mkha' la rig pa'i nyi shar cing //
NK122(kho)002:11560: rang rig 'od gsal mkha' ltar dag pa'o //
NK122(kho)002:11561: gnyis med rang sar grol ba'i lta ba la //
NK122(kho)002:11562: ma yengs dran pas zin pa'i man ngag ste //
NK122(kho)002:11563: rtogs pa'i ngang la rgyun du 'bral med par //
NK122(kho)002:11564: rig pa rtse gcig gnas pa sgom pa yin //
NK122(kho)002:11565: 'bring po'i blo can gom byed nyams len ni //
NK122(kho)002:11566: rtogs thabs lta ba gong bzhin mthun gyur kyang //
NK122(kho)002:11567: mngon du ma rtogs don spyi tsam go la //
NK122(kho)002:11568: rdzogs chen bstan pa nam mkha' lta bu'o //
NK122(kho)002:11569: thabs sgo dpag med lha rlung bde ba dang //
NK122(kho)002:11570: gang snang gang skyes spyod yul sna tshogs la //
NK122(kho)002:11571: blo dang mthun par khrid byas ngo sprad cing //
NK122(kho)002:11572: rtogs pa'i don la bzhag thabs skyon bcos dang //
NK122(kho)002:11573: thun dang goms tshad rkyen bsal gol sa bcad //
NK122(kho)002:11574: nyams kyi bog 'don rtogs tshad nyams rim sogs //
NK122(kho)002:11575: rang rang skabs bzhin rim par don sbyar nas //
NK122(kho)002:11576: rang gnas ye shes mngon du mthar phyin byed //
NK122(kho)002:11577: tha ma blo zhan nyams len goms byed nas //
NK122(kho)002:11578: chos nyid mngon sum rtogs par mi ldan na //
NK122(kho)002:11579: rang rang blo dang sbyar ba'i chos bstan te //
NK122(kho)002:11580: rim 'jug theg brgyad don la khrid byas nas //
NK122(kho)002:11581: skabs su rdzogs chen che ba'i spro ba bskyed //
NK122(kho)002:11582: mthun 'jug thabs kyi rdzogs chen don la drangs //
NK122(kho)002:11583: dus la bab na snying po'i don bstan la //
NK122(kho)002:11584: rdzogs chen don la rim gyis bslab byas te //
NK122(kho)002:11586: chos rje dam pa yab sras kyis ni /
NK122(kho)002:11587: 'di'i gang zag tha ma de nyams len rim gyis pa'i gang zag la bzhed do //
NK122(kho)002:11590: kun tu bzang po'i spyod pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:11592: bya bral rdzogs pa'i spyod pa ni /
NK122(kho)002:11593: lus ngag yid gsum gyi spyod yul thams cad sangs
NK122(kho)002:11594: rgyas kyi sku gsung thugs mi zad pa rgyan gyi
NK122(kho)002:11595: 'khor lo la longs spyod pa'i dus su /
NK122(kho)002:11596: ched du bya ba'i spyod pa dang bral ba'i rig
NK122(kho)002:11597: pa 'char ba de ni ngan pa'i skyon rtsa ba
NK122(kho)002:11598: nas dag pas kun tu bzang po'i spyod pa yin
NK122(kho)002:11599: / blang dor med pa'i spyod pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:11601: nyon mongs pa dug gsum dug lnga la sogs pa
NK122(kho)002:11602: rnams 'gag pa med par rang byung gi ye shes
NK122(kho)002:11603: nyid du gsal ba ni nyon mongs pa spang du
NK122(kho)002:11604: med / rig pa ye shes klong du med pa'i spyod pa yin /
NK122(kho)002:11606: ma rig pa nyid spang du med //
NK122(kho)002:11607: rig pa ye shes bsgrub tu med //
NK122(kho)002:11609: rgyan dang cha lugs ldan pa'i spyod pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:11611: 'dod pa'i yon tan de gzugs sgra dri ro reg bya lnga po 'di dag dang /
NK122(kho)002:11612: rang byung ye shes gnyis dbyer med gcig tu longs spyod pa la kun bzang rgyan /
NK122(kho)002:11614: 'di dag bdag nyid chen po'i gtan tshig gis chos
NK122(kho)002:11615: dbyings spros pa'i mtshan ma thams cad dag pa'i ngo
NK122(kho)002:11616: bor shar ba ni rgyan dang cha lugs ldan pa'i
NK122(kho)002:11618: 'di mthar phyin 'bras bu'i dus su longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku /
NK122(kho)002:11619: dbu rgyan do shal la sogs pa rgyan cha lugs can du 'gyur ro //
NK122(kho)002:11620: bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i spyod pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:11622: bla med theg pa man chad nas //
NK122(kho)002:11623: 'jig rten gyi spyod thams cad kun //
NK122(kho)002:11624: ched kyi dgag bsgrub gang yang med //
NK122(kho)002:11625: rang byung ye shes nyid du gsal //
NK122(kho)002:11626: bsam gyis mi khyab spyod pa yin //
NK122(kho)002:11629: dper na nam mkha'i ngang du 'byung ba bzhi ci shar na yang /
NK122(kho)002:11630: nam mkha'i ngo bo la spangs blang dang dgag bsgrub med pa bzhin du /
NK122(kho)002:11632: 'jig rten gyi bya spyod yan chad la ched du
NK122(kho)002:11633: spangs blang dang dgag sgrub med cing chos kun rang
NK122(kho)002:11634: byung gi ye shes chen po'i klong du longs spyod
NK122(kho)002:11635: pa'o // 'di lta bu'i bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i don la longs spyod dgos te /
NK122(kho)002:11636: slob dpon sangs rgyas gsang bas /
NK122(kho)002:11637: bsam gyis mi khyab ma mthong bar //
NK122(kho)002:11639: blun po mun sprul blo can de //
NK122(kho)002:11640: long ba'i grong khyer chen por 'gro //
NK122(kho)002:11642: bdag nyid chen po'i spyod pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:11644: thog ma dang tha ma dang dus gsum dang /
NK122(kho)002:11645: phyi snod kyi 'jig rten dang nang bcud kyi sems
NK122(kho)002:11646: can 'di rnams lhun grub rang byung ye shes kyi
NK122(kho)002:11647: rtsal du ma gyur pa ni gang yang med do
NK122(kho)002:11648: // de lta bu ni bdag nyid chen po'i spyod pa yin no //
NK122(kho)002:11649: spyod pa'i rgyal po byar med bstan pa'o //
NK122(kho)002:11651: spyod pa'i khyad par ci byung yang //
NK122(kho)002:11652: dgag sgrub ched 'dzin bral ba ni //
NK122(kho)002:11653: spyod pa'i rgyal po byar med yin //
NK122(kho)002:11655: 'on kyang spyod pa'i skabs 'dir sa mig drug yod pa ni /
NK122(kho)002:11656: mtshon tshul ma 'dres par dgos ched drug gis shes par bya'o //
NK122(kho)002:11659: shin tu rnal 'byor gyi dam tshig dgongs pa'i ngo bo dang /
NK122(kho)002:11661: bya bral rdzogs pa'i dam tshig ni spyod lam thams cad du chos nyid ngang la 'da' nyams med /
NK122(kho)002:11662: rig pa ye shes la 'da' nyams med /
NK122(kho)002:11663: ma bcos pa'i ting 'dzin la 'da' nyams med /
NK122(kho)002:11664: 'di lta bu'i dgongs pa ting nge 'dzin la ye shes la ye shes rgyun chad med pa ni /
NK122(kho)002:11665: dper na chu gsher ba las mi 'da'/
NK122(kho)002:11667: dung dkar ba las mi 'da' ba bzhin no //
NK122(kho)002:11668: gdul bya'i don byed pa las mi 'da' ba'i dam tshig go //
NK122(kho)002:11670: spang blang med pa'i spyod pa yis nang pa gsang sngags bla med theg pa'i dam tshig dang /
NK122(kho)002:11671: bar byang chub sems dpa' sdom pa'i spyod pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:11672: phyi nyan thos kyi gdul khrims la sogs pa sdom pa'i bye brag mtha' yas pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:11673: 'jig rten pa la sogs pa thun mong bya spyod
NK122(kho)002:11674: thams cad kun ni thabs kyi spyod pas 'gro don
NK122(kho)002:11675: byed dgos pas ched du dgag pa gcig kyang med
NK122(kho)002:11676: de / dgongs pa rang ngo la ched du 'dzin pa thams cad yongs su bral ba'o //
NK122(kho)002:11677: de ni bla med rdzogs pa chen po'i theg pa'i dam tshig go //
NK122(kho)002:11678: gzhan yang rdzogs chen rang gzhung gi dam tshig la /
NK122(kho)002:11679: lhag pa'i dam tshig rnam bzhir bshad de /
NK122(kho)002:11685: bsrung du med pa'i bsrung ba chen po'o //
NK122(kho)002:11688: ngo bo bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i dus dang /
NK122(kho)002:11690: bla med theg pa'i grub yun ni //
NK122(kho)002:11691: chos kun ye nas sangs rgyas pa //
NK122(kho)002:11692: ngo bo dus zhes bshad pa yin //
NK122(kho)002:11694: rdzogs chen gyi lugs la sangs rgyas pa'i yun la ci thog zhe na /
NK122(kho)002:11695: shes bya 'khor 'das kyis bsdus pa'i chos blo'i yul
NK122(kho)002:11696: du gyur tshad kun ye nas sangs rgyas pa yin
NK122(kho)002:11697: te / dngos po'i ngo bor snang ba'i dus de
NK122(kho)002:11698: nyid nas bzo bcos ma byas pa de ka sangs
NK122(kho)002:11699: rgyas yin par khas blang pa'o //
NK122(kho)002:11700: gtan tshig de bas na rtogs grol thar pa dus mnyam ste /
NK122(kho)002:11701: rngon pa rnyi dang sangs rgyas /
NK122(kho)002:11702: shan pa gri dang sangs rgyas /
NK122(kho)002:11703: thod pa bor chog gi gdams ngag yin zer ba'i don yang de bzhin no //
NK122(kho)002:11704: 'di blo rab la dgongs te srid pa tsam mo //
NK122(kho)002:11705: rdzogs chen la rten gyi gang zag bzhi yod pa gong du bshad pa bzhin no //
NK122(kho)002:11706: lta ba ngos 'phrod nas mthong lam g.yo ba'i dus dang /
NK122(kho)002:11708: rang bzhin skye med kyi gtan tshig /
NK122(kho)002:11709: rol pa 'gag med kyi gtan tshig /
NK122(kho)002:11710: mtshan nyid dbyer med kyi gtan tshig gsum la blo gdal na /
NK122(kho)002:11711: rig pa rang sar grol ba'i tshe /
NK122(kho)002:11712: de'i dus na dbyer med kyi don mnyam pa nyid
NK122(kho)002:11713: kyi gnas lugs ci bzhin pa rtogs pas thams cad
NK122(kho)002:11714: mkhyen pa'i ye shes kyi 'go bo zug pa yin
NK122(kho)002:11715: pas na sa chen dang po rab dga' nye bar
NK122(kho)002:11716: non / de ni g.yo ba'i nyams zhes bya ba yin no //
NK122(kho)002:11717: de nyid nyams su blangs pas sgom lam rig pa la dbang thob pa'i dus dang /
NK122(kho)002:11719: de nyid nyams su blang ba'i tshe //
NK122(kho)002:11720: sa chen gnyis pa non pa ste //
NK122(kho)002:11721: thos pa'i nyams zhes grags pa yin //
NK122(kho)002:11722: 'di ni sa bcad dang gzhung gnyis kyi steng nas go bar zad do //
NK122(kho)002:11723: goms pa mthar phyin pas rtsol bral mthar lam bstan pa'i dus dang /
NK122(kho)002:11725: ma btsal lhun grub kyi sa la gnas pa'i tshe
NK122(kho)002:11726: phyogs bcur bzhugs shing dus bzhi gshegs pa'i rgyal ba
NK122(kho)002:11727: rgya mtsho ste / bde gshegs ma lus thams cad dang /
NK122(kho)002:11728: sku gsung dang thugs rdo rje'i bdag nyid ltar dbyer
NK122(kho)002:11729: med cing brtan pa thob pa ni mthar phyin pa'i
NK122(kho)002:11731: sa lam bgrod sbyangs med par rdzogs pa'i yon tan gyi bdag nyid du bstan pa'o //
NK122(kho)002:11733: sa rnams kun gyi yang thog ste chos kun rang
NK122(kho)002:11734: byung gi ye shes la 'khor 'das gnyis su med
NK122(kho)002:11735: pas / lam bgrod du med cing lam lnga dus
NK122(kho)002:11736: gcig la rdzogs pa dang sa la sbyong du med
NK122(kho)002:11737: pas / pas / sa rnams dus gcig la non pa'o //
NK122(kho)002:11739: bgrod pa'i lam gyis tha ma non /
NK122(kho)002:11741: lam bgrod pa'i tha ma 'bras bu thob pa'o //
NK122(kho)002:11742: shes bya'i chos thams cad ma 'dres la yongs su rdzogs pas na /
NK122(kho)002:11743: rdzogs pa chen po'i lugs la rdzogs pa spyir chibs kyi sa zhes bya'o //
NK122(kho)002:11748: lam gyi bya ba thams cad mthar phyin pa'i 'bras bu'i mchog 'di la 'bras bu'i ngo bo dang /
NK122(kho)002:11751: bye brag dang snang tshul dang lnga bstan pa ni 'di lta ste /
NK122(kho)002:11752: rgyas par bshad pa la lnga ste /
NK122(kho)002:11755: ngo bo sku gsum lhun grub yin /
NK122(kho)002:11759: rnam grangs sku gsung thugs yon tan //
NK122(kho)002:11760: phrin las re re'ang lnga lnga ste //
NK122(kho)002:11762: ngo bo nyid kyi sku dang /
NK122(kho)002:11768: rig pa byin rlabs kyi gsung /
NK122(kho)002:11772: grags stong rdo rje'i gsung ngo //
NK122(kho)002:11784: rgyan cha yon tan can no //
NK122(kho)002:11790: lhun gyis grub pa'i phrin las dang lnga'o //
NK122(kho)002:11792: snang ba'i rgyan du stong pa che //
NK122(kho)002:11793: stong pa'i rgyan du snang ba che //
NK122(kho)002:11795: sku rigs rgyan 'khor nyi shu rtsa lngar snang ba des stong pa'i mtha' sel ba yin /
NK122(kho)002:11796: shar ba'i dus de nyid na rang byung ye shes
NK122(kho)002:11797: las ma g.yos pas snang ba dngos 'dzin gyi mtha'
NK122(kho)002:11800: gong gi sku rigs rgyan 'khor nyi shu rtsa lnga rgyun mi chad pa la bya'o //
NK122(kho)002:11801: nyi shu rtsa lnga zhes pa ni gong gi sku rigs rgyan 'khor nyi shu rtsa lnga la bya'o //
NK122(kho)002:11802: gzhan yang mthar phyin 'bras bu'i dbye ba la bye
NK122(kho)002:11803: brag rnam grangs bsam gyis mi khyab pa yod par
NK122(kho)002:11804: shes par bya'o // sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin
NK122(kho)002:11805: las lnga 'di rnams kyi don cung zhig bkrol na
NK122(kho)002:11806: shes par bya'o // / mdo lam rim la //
NK122(kho)002:11807: ngo bo nyid dang gsang ba dang //
NK122(kho)002:11808: chos dang longs spyod sprul pa'o //
NK122(kho)002:11810: mi mthun gnyen po med pas gnas lugs ci bzhin
NK122(kho)002:11811: pa nyid mngon du gyur pas na ngo bo nyid
NK122(kho)002:11812: kyi sku dang / chos dbyings skye ba med cing
NK122(kho)002:11813: rnam par dag pa nyid sgrib g.yogs thams cad dang
NK122(kho)002:11815: sku mtshan dang dpe byad kyis brgyan cing dgongs pa
NK122(kho)002:11816: bde ba chen por longs spyod pas longs spyod rdzogs
NK122(kho)002:11817: pa'i sku dang / thugs rje'i rnam 'phrul bsam gyis
NK122(kho)002:11818: mi khyab pas dag ma dag gi sems can la
NK122(kho)002:11819: gang la gang 'dul du sprul pas na sprul pa'i
NK122(kho)002:11820: pa'i sku dang / sku dang / bde stong gnyis
NK122(kho)002:11821: med la longs spyod cing gsang ba dam pas na
NK122(kho)002:11822: pa'i sku dang / sku dang / gsang ba'i sku'o // mdo dgongs 'dus las /
NK122(kho)002:11823: sprul pa ni ma byung ma myong rgyun du 'byung ba'o //
NK122(kho)002:11824: rdzogs longs spyod pa ni smin pa phun sum tshogs pa la bya'o //
NK122(kho)002:11825: chos kyi sku ni yongs su rnam par dag pa la bya'o //
NK122(kho)002:11826: ngo bo nyid kyi sku ni ci bzhin pa de nyid la bya'o //
NK122(kho)002:11827: gsang ba'i sku ni bde stong gnyis med kyi ye shes la bya'o //
NK122(kho)002:11829: ngo bo nyid kyi gsung ni ma brjod par ngo bo nyid kyis go ba'o //
NK122(kho)002:11830: chos sku'i gsung rang gsal byin brlabs kyis mtshon pa'o //
NK122(kho)002:11832: gsang ba brda yis mtshon pa'o //
NK122(kho)002:11833: longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku'i gsung ni /
NK122(kho)002:11836: tshangs pa dbyangs kyi sgo nas tshig gis mtshon pa'o //
NK122(kho)002:11838: gang ngo bo nyid med pa'i gsung ni nam mkha' lta bu'o //
NK122(kho)002:11839: rnam par dag pa'i gsung ni nyi ma'i snying po lta bu'o //
NK122(kho)002:11840: yongs su smin pa'i gsung ni me long lta bu'o //
NK122(kho)002:11841: gsang ba dam pa'i gsung ni seng ge lta bu'o //
NK122(kho)002:11842: rmad du byung ba'i gsung ni gsung gcig la yan lag bsam gyis mi khyab pa'o //
NK122(kho)002:11844: gsum pa thugs ye shes lnga ni /
NK122(kho)002:11846: chos kyi dbyings kyi ye shes ni /
NK122(kho)002:11847: chos kun mtshan ma med par rang gsal ba'o //
NK122(kho)002:11848: me long lta bu'i ye shes ni /
NK122(kho)002:11849: chos dbyings sgrib pa med cing rtog pa med par rang gsal ba'o //
NK122(kho)002:11850: mnyam pa nyid kyi ye shes ni /
NK122(kho)002:11851: bzang ngan che chung med par mnyam pa nyid du gsal ba'o //
NK122(kho)002:11852: so sor rtog pa'i ye shes ni /
NK122(kho)002:11853: chos kun bye brag ma 'dres par gsal ba'o //
NK122(kho)002:11854: bya ba grub pa'i ye shes ni /
NK122(kho)002:11855: rtsol bsgrub med cing bya ba med pas dgos 'dod 'byung ba'o //
NK122(kho)002:11857: kha cig tu ni chos kyi dbyings kyi ye shes zhes bya'o //
NK122(kho)002:11858: kha cig tu ni rnam dag gsal ba'i ye shes ces bya'o //
NK122(kho)002:11859: kha cig tu ni mnyam nyid kyi ye shes zhes bya'o //
NK122(kho)002:11860: kha cig tu ni so sor rtog pa'i ye shes zhes bya'o //
NK122(kho)002:11861: kha cig tu ni bya ba grub pa'i ye shes zhes bya'o //
NK122(kho)002:11864: stong nyid thugs ni nam mkha' bzhin //
NK122(kho)002:11865: me long lta bu'i ye shes dang //
NK122(kho)002:11866: chen po lta bu'i ye shes dang //
NK122(kho)002:11867: sna tshogs bkod pa'i ye shes dang //
NK122(kho)002:11868: yid bzhin nor bu'i ye shes so //
NK122(kho)002:11870: bzhi pa yon tan lnga ni /
NK122(kho)002:11871: bde ba chen po la sogs zhing khams yon tan can dang /
NK122(kho)002:11872: rin chen sna lnga las grub cing mdzes par brgyan pa'i gzhal yas khang yon tan can dang /
NK122(kho)002:11873: thugs rje'i 'od zer snang ba'i rtags su 'od zer
NK122(kho)002:11874: rnam lnga la sogs pa 'od zer yon tan can
NK122(kho)002:11875: dang / mi 'jigs pa seng ge'i khri dang /
NK122(kho)002:11877: nyi zla pad+ma la sogs pa'i gdan khri yon tan can dang /
NK122(kho)002:11878: mtshan dang dpe byad du ldan pa dang rin po
NK122(kho)002:11879: che'i rgyan cha sna tshogs dang ldan pa ni rgyan
NK122(kho)002:11882: zhing khams gzhal yas 'od zer dang /
NK122(kho)002:11883: gdan khri rgyan rnams zad 'phel med //
NK122(kho)002:11885: lnga pa phrin las lnga ni /
NK122(kho)002:11886: zhi ba rgyas pa dbang drag po /
NK122(kho)002:11887: lhun gyis grub pa'i phrin las kyis gang la gang 'dul du ci ltar 'tshams par don mdzad pa'o //
NK122(kho)002:11889: tshad med phrin las zhi drag dang //
NK122(kho)002:11890: dbang rgyas lhun gyis grub pa'o //
NK122(kho)002:11894: lam bgrod pa mthar phyin nas /
NK122(kho)002:11895: bdag don dam pa chos sku dang /
NK122(kho)002:11896: gzhan don dam pa gzugs sku gnyis kyi don dang bcas pa ni /
NK122(kho)002:11897: de phyin chad phyir ldog pa med pas na /
NK122(kho)002:11898: mthar phyin pa'i 'bras bu zhes bya'o //
NK122(kho)002:11899: theg pa thams cad kyis bsgrub pa'i don kun gyi
NK122(kho)002:11900: mchog rdzogs pa chen po 'di yin pa'i phyir mthar
NK122(kho)002:11902: de ltar 'bras bu'i nges tshig rgyal ba kun tu bzang pos gsungs so //
NK122(kho)002:11903: bye brag so so'i thob tshul bstan pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:11905: bye brag theg pa so so'i thob tshul te /
NK122(kho)002:11909: dbu ma la sogs theg pa 'og ma 'ga' zhig
NK122(kho)002:11910: gis sangs rgyas pa'i dus su chu la chu thim
NK122(kho)002:11911: pa'am / mar la mar bzhag pa bzhin du ye shes gcig tu 'dres par 'dod do //
NK122(kho)002:11914: sems tsam la sogs pa 'ga' zhig gis sangs rgyas
NK122(kho)002:11915: pa'i dus su shing gi me dpung ltar sbyangs pa'i
NK122(kho)002:11917: spyir me dpung gcig yin kyang bye brag tu shing
NK122(kho)002:11918: sna re re la me re re 'bar ba dpe
NK122(kho)002:11919: de bzhin du / spyir sangs rgyas thams cad kyi
NK122(kho)002:11920: dgongs pa ye shes kyi klong du gcig kyang bye
NK122(kho)002:11921: brag tu shes rgyud ma 'dres par so sor yod
NK122(kho)002:11922: de bzhin du / par 'dod do // 'di gnyis
NK122(kho)002:11923: ni gsang sngags kyi 'bras bu la ltos na drangs
NK122(kho)002:11925: rgya gar gyi mkhas pa chen po slob dpon sangs rgyas gsang bas /
NK122(kho)002:11926: don dam gcig pu ma yin phyir //
NK122(kho)002:11927: chu la chu ltar thim pa'ang min //
NK122(kho)002:11928: shing gi me dpung ltar brjod pa //
NK122(kho)002:11929: drangs ba tsam ste de nyid min //
NK122(kho)002:11932: lhun grub ye shes rang 'char ba //
NK122(kho)002:11934: gzhi ye shes rang la gnas pa /
NK122(kho)002:11935: lam rang la gnas pa rtogs shing goms par byed pa /
NK122(kho)002:11936: 'bras bu lhun grub ye shes shar ba'i dus su /
NK122(kho)002:11937: sku rigs rgyan 'khor nyi shu rtsa lnga la sogs
NK122(kho)002:11938: pa ma 'gag par cir yang 'char bas gcig pa'i
NK122(kho)002:11939: mtha' dang bral / shar ba'i dus de nyid na'ang rang byung gi ye shes las ma g.yos pas /
NK122(kho)002:11940: du ma dang bral ba yin te /
NK122(kho)002:11942: gcig dang du ma bral ba yi //
NK122(kho)002:11943: mtha' dang dbus med de bzhin nyid //
NK122(kho)002:11944: sangs rgyas kyis kyang mi gzigs te //
NK122(kho)002:11945: rang byung ye shes gnas med snang //
NK122(kho)002:11947: de rnams ni mthar phyin 'bras bu'i thob tshul yin te /
NK122(kho)002:11948: rdzogs chen gyi lugs la ma 'dres yongs su rdzogs
NK122(kho)002:11949: pa'i phyir ngo bo la so sor dbye ba med
NK122(kho)002:11952: de bzhin gshegs la snang tshul dang /
NK122(kho)002:11954: snang tshul nye bar bstan pa ni //
NK122(kho)002:11955: gnyis med ye shes rang byung ba //
NK122(kho)002:11956: de bzhin gshegs la snang ba dang //
NK122(kho)002:11958: spyir lam bgrod pa mthar phyin nas 'bras bu sangs
NK122(kho)002:11959: rgyas pa na nang gi gzung 'dzin gyi dri ma
NK122(kho)002:11960: ka nas dag pas phyi rol gyi dngos po sangs
NK122(kho)002:11961: rgyas chos sku 'ba' zhig tu rtogs pa'o //
NK122(kho)002:11962: byang chub sems dpa' la snang tshul dang /
NK122(kho)002:11964: ston pa longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku'i mdzad pa rgya chen rnams ni gong gi ngo la snang na /
NK122(kho)002:11965: phyag rgya chen po'i rig 'dzin byang chub sems dpa'i tshogs /
NK122(kho)002:11967: dag sa gsum la gnas pa'i byang chub sems dpa' dang /
NK122(kho)002:11968: khyad par du sa bcu'i byang chub sems dpa' rtogs
NK122(kho)002:11969: pa dang ting nge 'dzin gyis rgyud smin pa rnams
NK122(kho)002:11971: de'ang yang dag pa'i don du na sangs rgyas kyis
NK122(kho)002:11972: sangs rgyas de chos sku 'ba' zhig tu mthong la
NK122(kho)002:11973: / 'dir sa bcu'i dbang phyug gi rgyud thog na shes bya'i sgrib pa cha phra mo yod pas /
NK122(kho)002:11974: sangs rgyas longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku mtshan dpes spras
NK122(kho)002:11975: pa 'di sa bcu'i dbang phyug gi rgyud thog na
NK122(kho)002:11977: 'gro drug la snang tshul dpe dang bcas pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:11979: 'gro drug mos pa bsam yas pa //
NK122(kho)002:11981: 'gro drug so so'i mthun snang la /
NK122(kho)002:11982: sprul pa'i sku bsam yas su snang lugs ni //
NK122(kho)002:11983: dngas pa'i mtsho la gza' skar bzhin //
NK122(kho)002:11985: dper na rgya mtsho dngas pa'i nang na gza' skar shar ba'am /
NK122(kho)002:11986: chu ldeeng tha dag gi nang du zla ba'i dkyil
NK122(kho)002:11987: 'khor gcig las ma g.yos bzhin zla ba du ma
NK122(kho)002:11988: 'char ba'o // dpe de bzhin du kun tu bzang
NK122(kho)002:11989: po'i dgongs pa chos nyid las ma g.yos par 'dzam
NK122(kho)002:11990: gling bye ba phrag brgyar thub pa bye ba phrag
NK122(kho)002:11992: lha 'dul ba la tshangs pa dang brgya byin /
NK122(kho)002:11993: lha ma yin 'dul ba la thag bzang ris /
NK122(kho)002:11995: byol song la seng ge yi dam brtan /
NK122(kho)002:11997: dmyal ba la gshin rje chos rgyal /
NK122(kho)002:11998: lto 'phye la lto 'phye'i rgyal po sbrul mgo dgu pa /
NK122(kho)002:11999: mi'am ci la mi'am ci'i rgyal po ljon pa skyes /
NK122(kho)002:12000: dri za la dri za'i rgyal po zur phud lnga pa /
NK122(kho)002:12001: bya 'dul ba la ngang pa gser ldan la sogs pa sna tshogs su snang ba'o //
NK122(kho)002:12002: gong gi de dag ni sprul pa'i sku yin par bshad do //
NK122(kho)002:12003: de yang tshigs su bcad pa'i mdo las /
NK122(kho)002:12004: lha rnams la ni brgya byin gzugs //
NK122(kho)002:12005: lha ma yin la thag bzang ris //
NK122(kho)002:12006: mi rnams la ni 'jig rten du //
NK122(kho)002:12007: 'khor los sgyur rgyal lta bu'i tshul //
NK122(kho)002:12008: gcan gzan la ni seng ge'i gzugs //
NK122(kho)002:12009: yi dwags la ni kha 'bar ma //
NK122(kho)002:12010: dmyal ba la ni gshed pos 'dul //
NK122(kho)002:12013: mos pas spyod pa'i sa man chad kyi spyod yul yin te /
NK122(kho)002:12014: gdul bya rnams kyis skye 'chi med pa'i don ci
NK122(kho)002:12015: bzhin pa ma rtogs pas sangs rgyas rang yang skye
NK122(kho)002:12017: sangs rgyas rang la bzang ngan byung ba'i rgyu mtshan ci yin na /
NK122(kho)002:12018: dper na nam mkha'i mthongs su zla ba dkar po shar yang ram khu'i nang du zla ba sngo /
NK122(kho)002:12019: skag khu'i nang du zla ba dmar ba bzhin du /
NK122(kho)002:12020: bzang ngan shar ba ni sangs rgyas kyi skyon min /
NK122(kho)002:12021: gdul bya'i skyon yin par shes par bya'o //
NK122(kho)002:12022: snang tshul ci ltar snang yang /
NK122(kho)002:12023: ngo bo nyid la dbye ba med pa dpe dang bcas pa'o //
NK122(kho)002:12027: sprul pa'i sku gsum snang tshul tha dad kyang /
NK122(kho)002:12030: gsal ba gnyis nyi ma'i 'od la gcig pa ltar /
NK122(kho)002:12031: gzugs sku gnyis kyi mdzad pa ci ltar snang yang
NK122(kho)002:12032: ngo bo chos sku de nyid kyi ngang la dbye
NK122(kho)002:12033: ba med do // spyir rnam mkhyen sangs rgyas kyis gdul bya'i don mdzad lugs la /
NK122(kho)002:12034: rten can gyis don mdzad pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:12035: rten med kyis don mdzad pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:12036: gnas lugs ngo bo nyid kyis don mdzad pa dang gsum mo //
NK122(kho)002:12037: 'di'i don rgyas pa g.yung ston rin po ches 'bras bu'i skabs su 'di 'dra gcig bkod 'dug /
NK122(kho)002:12038: rten can gyis don byed par 'dod pa bram ze'i mchod sdong bsgrub pa lta bu /
NK122(kho)002:12039: rten med kyis don byed par 'dod pa drang srong gis dmod pa bsgrub pa lta bu /
NK122(kho)002:12040: gnas lugs ngo bo nyid kyis don byed par 'dod
NK122(kho)002:12041: pa yid bzhin gyi nor bu rin po che lta
NK122(kho)002:12044: dper na rigs sngags grub pa'i bram ze zhig gis rin po che'i mchod sdong bsgrubs nas bzhag pas /
NK122(kho)002:12045: bram ze kho rang tshe'i dus byas kyang /
NK122(kho)002:12046: kho'i rjes 'jug rnams kyi 'dod pa rin po che'i
NK122(kho)002:12047: mchod sdong gis skong bar byed pa bzhin du byang
NK122(kho)002:12048: chub sems dpa'i spyod pa rlab po che yongs su
NK122(kho)002:12049: rdzogs par byas nas mi gnas pa'i mya ngan las
NK122(kho)002:12050: 'das kyang / tshogs gnyis rdzogs pa'i 'bras bu sku
NK122(kho)002:12051: dang ye shes kyis gdul bya rnams kyi don byed
NK122(kho)002:12053: rgya gar na slob dpon seng ge bzang po dang /
NK122(kho)002:12054: bod na zhang shes rab bla ma la sogs pa rnams kyi bzhed pa yin no //
NK122(kho)002:12056: dper na dmod pa grub pa'i drang srong zhig gis
NK122(kho)002:12057: dmod pa bsgrub nas bzhag pas drang srong kho rang
NK122(kho)002:12058: tshe'i dus byas kyang gzhan snang du kho'i dmod pa
NK122(kho)002:12059: ci lta bar grub bzhin du /
NK122(kho)002:12060: byang chub sems dpa'i spyod pa spyad pa'i dus su
NK122(kho)002:12061: smon lam rgya chen po btab pa'i mthus gdul bya
NK122(kho)002:12062: rnams kyi snang ngor de bzhin gshegs pa'i sku gsung
NK122(kho)002:12063: thugs kyi mdzad pa gdul bya gang la gang 'dul
NK122(kho)002:12064: de la de ltar ston pa snang bar zad kyis
NK122(kho)002:12065: / byang chub sems dpa' mngon par rdzogs par sangs
NK122(kho)002:12066: rgyas pa'i dus na yul yul can gyi gzung 'dzin
NK122(kho)002:12067: bag la nyal ba gnyen po rdo rje lta bu'i
NK122(kho)002:12069: rig pa rgyun chad pa'i phyir /
NK122(kho)002:12070: ye shes kyang med par 'dod pa ni rgya gar na slob dpon chen po klu grub dang /
NK122(kho)002:12071: bod na rong zom chos kyi bzang po la sogs pa'i bzhed pa yin no //
NK122(kho)002:12073: dper na yid bzhin gyi nor bu rin po che /
NK122(kho)002:12074: rgyal mtshan gyi rtse mo la btags nas mchod na
NK122(kho)002:12075: 'gro ba rang rang gis bsod nams dang 'tshams pa'i
NK122(kho)002:12076: dgos 'dod 'byung mod kyang rin po che la rtsol
NK122(kho)002:12077: rtog dang nye ring med pa bzhin du /
NK122(kho)002:12078: rang gi sems kyi chos nyid dbyings shin tu dri ma med pa'i chos sku de /
NK122(kho)002:12079: glo bur gyi dri mas bsgribs pa /
NK122(kho)002:12080: lam lnga sa bcu mthar phyin pas dag nas ngo
NK122(kho)002:12081: bo nyid kyi sku mngon du byas pa zab mo
NK122(kho)002:12082: chos sku'i yon tan gyi cha la gzugs sku gnyis
NK122(kho)002:12083: kyi phrin las kyis gdul bya gang la gang 'dul
NK122(kho)002:12084: de la der ston gyis skur snang nas gdul bya'i
NK122(kho)002:12086: rgya gar na mkhas pa sh+r+ai sing ha dang /
NK122(kho)002:12087: bod na zur chung shes rab grags pa la sogs pa'i bzhed pa yin no //
NK122(kho)002:12088: dang po'i lung de nyid kyis mthar dbyung zhing don bsdu ba'o //
NK122(kho)002:12090: don dam nges pa'i theg pa la gsang ba snying
NK122(kho)002:12091: po'i lung gis rtsa tshig byas shing mthar phyin pa'i
NK122(kho)002:12093: ma rtogs pa dang log par rtog /
NK122(kho)002:12094: phyogs rtogs yang dag nyid ma rtogs //
NK122(kho)002:12095: 'dul ba dgongs pa gsang ba dang //
NK122(kho)002:12096: rang bzhin gsang ba'i don rnams zhes //
NK122(kho)002:12097: rgyud las gsungs pa de ltar yin //
NK122(kho)002:12101: brtsam pa'i gzhi brgyud tshul dang bcas pa'i sgo nas rang bzhin gsal ba dang /
NK122(kho)002:12103: chos sku kun tu bzang po /
NK122(kho)002:12104: longs sku rnam par snang mdzad /
NK122(kho)002:12105: sprul sku sh+aakya thub pa la sogs pa mtha' gnyis
NK122(kho)002:12106: dang bdud bzhi las rgyal ba dgongs pa zab cing
NK122(kho)002:12107: grangs mang ba / rgya mtsho lta bu'i sangs rgyas dkon mchog /
NK122(kho)002:12108: de dag gis bstan pa dam pa'i chos /
NK122(kho)002:12109: brjod bya theg pa dgu la sogs pa /
NK122(kho)002:12110: brjod byed sde snod gsum dang rgyud sde bzhi'am drug gi chos /
NK122(kho)002:12111: dgongs pa zab cing rgya che la grangs mang ba
NK122(kho)002:12112: rgya mtsho lta bu ci snyed gsungs pa rnams te
NK122(kho)002:12114: sku lnga'i bdag nyid rgyal ba kun tu bzang po'i
NK122(kho)002:12115: thugs las skyes shing rgyal tshab dam par gyur pa
NK122(kho)002:12116: gsang bdag phyag na rdo rje dang /
NK122(kho)002:12117: rgyal ba sh+aakya thub pa'i rgyal tshab dam pa dbang bskur ba'i byams pa mgon po dang /
NK122(kho)002:12118: rgyal ba rnams kyi thugs kyi sras gsang sngags phyi
NK122(kho)002:12119: nang sde drug gi rig 'dzin dang sa bcu la
NK122(kho)002:12120: gnas pa'i smin pa rgya mtsho ste dge 'dun dkon
NK122(kho)002:12121: mchog gis bstan pa dam chos sde snod gsum dang
NK122(kho)002:12122: / rgyud sde drug gi chos tshig tshogs su snang ba rnams ni brjod byed kyi tshig yin la /
NK122(kho)002:12123: theg pa so so'i gzhi lam 'bras gsum gyi don
NK122(kho)002:12124: ston pa rnams ni brjod bya'i don yin te gdul
NK122(kho)002:12125: bya rnams kyis rtogs pa ni dgos pa yin /
NK122(kho)002:12126: gnas skabs theg pa rang gi 'phags lam thob cing /
NK122(kho)002:12127: mthar thug rang rang gi 'bras bu thob pa ni
NK122(kho)002:12128: nying dgos dang bzhi rim pa ltar 'brel ba yin
NK122(kho)002:12129: te / rjod byed tshig gis brjod bya'i don ston /
NK122(kho)002:12130: don de gdul bya rnams kyis rtogs nas nyams su
NK122(kho)002:12131: blangs pas gnas skabs dang mthar thug gi 'bras bu
NK122(kho)002:12132: la sbyor bar byed pas na 'brel ba'o //
NK122(kho)002:12133: de bzhi'i tshul gyis bde bar gshegs pa rnams la dgongs pas brgyud pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:12134: rig 'dzin rnams la rig pas brgyud pa /
NK122(kho)002:12135: gang zag rnams kyi rna ba ste snyan nas snyan du brgyud pa /
NK122(kho)002:12136: de ltar brgyud pa'i rgyud gzhung rgya che ba rgya
NK122(kho)002:12137: mtsho lta bu'i tshul las brtsam tshul dpe dang bcas
NK122(kho)002:12138: pa'i sgo nas nyams su myong ba dang 'brel zhing
NK122(kho)002:12139: / rtsom pa po rtogs ldan du bsgrub pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:12141: dper na bya ngang pa'i rgyal po gser ldan gyi
NK122(kho)002:12142: mchu la skyur rtsi yod pas rgya mtsho chen po'i
NK122(kho)002:12143: nang nas 'o ma'i bcud blangs pa ci lta ba
NK122(kho)002:12144: bzhin / slob dpon chen po dam pa bde bar
NK122(kho)002:12145: gshegs pa'i thugs kyis dgongs pas theg pa'i bye brag
NK122(kho)002:12146: phyogs te theg pa rim pa dgu dang /
NK122(kho)002:12147: phyogs min mu stegs dgu zhar byung dang bcas pa
NK122(kho)002:12148: rnams mdo rgyud rgya mtsho ltar rgya che la grangs
NK122(kho)002:12149: mang ba rnams su don 'thor zhing sdud dka' bar
NK122(kho)002:12150: gnas pa la / gzhung 'dir rgya che ba rnams
NK122(kho)002:12151: mdor bsdus mi gsal ba rnams gsal bar byas don
NK122(kho)002:12152: ma nor bar nges par bsgrub pa'i theg pa spyi
NK122(kho)002:12154: gong gi dgongs 'grel bzhi'i skabs la /
NK122(kho)002:12155: mdo dgongs 'dus nas bshad srol 'di dang mi 'dra
NK122(kho)002:12156: ba zhig byung snang snyam pa zhig kho bo la
NK122(kho)002:12157: yod / dge ba'i rtsa ba thams cad mkhyen pa
NK122(kho)002:12158: la bsngosa pas brtsams pa pos don chen po mdzad
NK122(kho)002:12160: bstan bcos 'di nyid brtsams pa'i dge ba'i rtsa ba rnams 'gro kun yongs la bsngo /
NK122(kho)002:12161: bsngo zhes pa bshad pa'i gzhir drangs /
NK122(kho)002:12162: de'i khyad par gyi chos la drug /
NK122(kho)002:12164: rgyal ba sras bcas rnams kyi rjes su 'brangs nas /
NK122(kho)002:12165: sngon byung du slob dpon chen po dam pas /
NK122(kho)002:12166: rjes 'jug tu 'chad nyan pa rnams kyis bsngo ba yin te /
NK122(kho)002:12167: shin tu rgyas pa'i sde snod kyi bsngo ba bstan pa'i le'u las /
NK122(kho)002:12168: 'jam dpal dpa' bos ci ltar mkhyen pa dang //
NK122(kho)002:12169: kun tu bzang po de yang de bzhin te //
NK122(kho)002:12170: de dag kun gyi rjes su bdag slob cing //
NK122(kho)002:12171: dge ba 'di dag thams cad rab tu bsngo //
NK122(kho)002:12175: 'chad nyan byas pa'i dge rtsas mtshon nas /
NK122(kho)002:12176: bdag gzhan gyis dus gsum du bsags pa'i dge ba thams cad bsngo ba yin te /
NK122(kho)002:12177: rdo rje rgyal mtshan gyi bsngo ba'i le'u las /
NK122(kho)002:12178: 'gro kun dge ba ci snyed yod pa dang //
NK122(kho)002:12179: byas dang byed 'gyur de bzhin byed pa dag /
NK122(kho)002:12182: sangs rgyas kyi sar bsngo ba yin te /
NK122(kho)002:12184: dge ba'i rtsa ba de dag thams cad kyang bla na med pa'i sangs rgyas ma gtogs pa /
NK122(kho)002:12185: nyan thos dang rang sangs rgyas sar bsngora mi 'jug pa'o //
NK122(kho)002:12187: gang la bsngo ba dang dgos ched ci'i phyir bsngo na /
NK122(kho)002:12188: 'gro kun yongs la sangs rgyas thob pa'i ched du'o //
NK122(kho)002:12190: dngos sam yang na brgyud kyang rung //
NK122(kho)002:12191: sems can don las gzhan mi spyad //
NK122(kho)002:12192: sems can kho na'i don gyi phyir //
NK122(kho)002:12193: thams cad byang chub phyir bsngo'o //
NK122(kho)002:12197: gsang sngags kyi lugs gnyis las /
NK122(kho)002:12201: bsngo brnams sgyu ma'am rmi lam tsam du shes dgos te /
NK122(kho)002:12203: bsod nams dge ba'i tshogs rnams ni //
NK122(kho)002:12204: chu bur bzhin du rab shes shing //
NK122(kho)002:12205: gdod nas dag par rtogs gyur na //
NK122(kho)002:12206: bsngo ba kun gyi mchog tu gsungs //
NK122(kho)002:12208: don dam par de gsum ngo bo ma grub cing /
NK122(kho)002:12209: stong nyid spros bral gyi ngang du bsngo ba yin te /
NK122(kho)002:12211: yongs su bsngo ba khyad par can //
NK122(kho)002:12212: de yi byed pa mchog yin te //
NK122(kho)002:12213: de yang dmigs med rnam pa can //
NK122(kho)002:12214: phyin ci ma log mtshan nyid do //
NK122(kho)002:12217: ma 'dres yongs su rdzogs pa'i ngang du bsngo'o //
NK122(kho)002:12219: bsngo ba mi zad lam pa ste //
NK122(kho)002:12222: mi zad par byed pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:12225: de yang zab pa chos dbyings su bsngosa pa'i dge
NK122(kho)002:12226: ba de bar ma dor chud mi za ba yin
NK122(kho)002:12227: te / blo gros rgya mtshos zhus pa'i mdo las /
NK122(kho)002:12228: ci ltar chu thig rgya mtsho'i chu nang lhung //
NK122(kho)002:12229: rgya mtsho ma skam bar du de mi zad //
NK122(kho)002:12230: de bzhin byang chub yongs bsngosa dge ba yang //
NK122(kho)002:12231: byang chub ma thob bar du de mi zad //
NK122(kho)002:12232: sems can gyi don du bsngosa pas mi zad pa'i thog tu 'phel ba yin te /
NK122(kho)002:12234: dge ba gzhan kun chu shing bzhin du ni //
NK122(kho)002:12235: 'bras bu 'byin nas zad par 'gyur ba nyid //
NK122(kho)002:12236: byang chub sems kyi ljon shing rtag par yang //
NK122(kho)002:12240: chos dbyings yongs su bsngosa pas chos skur 'gyur la /
NK122(kho)002:12241: gzhan don du bsngosa pas gzugs skur 'gyur ba yin te /
NK122(kho)002:12242: dge ba 'di yis skye bo kun //
NK122(kho)002:12243: bsod nams ye shes tshogs bsags te //
NK122(kho)002:12244: bsod nams ye shes las byung ba //
NK122(kho)002:12245: dam pa sku gnyis thob par shog /
NK122(kho)002:12247: spyi don gsum pa 'chad nyan mthar phyin pa'i rgyu mtshan ni /
NK122(kho)002:12248: theg pa'i bye brag mtha' yas pa las /
NK122(kho)002:12250: bla ma rin po che dam pa chen po'i zhal
NK122(kho)002:12251: nas gsungs pa de nyid kyi thugs sras dam par
NK122(kho)002:12252: gyur pa rtsang ston rdo rje rgyal mtshan gyis bris
NK122(kho)002:12255: tshig don lhag ma ma lus pa'i tha tshig gam /
NK122(kho)002:12256: gnas skabs re zhig rdzogs nas bshad du ma mchis pa'i don du gda' 'o //
NK122(kho)002:12257: theg pa spyi bcing gi tshig don cung zad phye ba 'di nyid bshes gnyen rnams kyis bskul nas /
NK122(kho)002:12258: ban sdom ye shes rgyal mtshan gyis lding chu sngon mo'i g.yas phyogs /
NK122(kho)002:12259: stag chen brang sang mched dgu'i zhol /
NK122(kho)002:12260: rje btsun gong ma'i gdan sa /
NK122(kho)002:12261: dpal ldan 'phags mtsho nags khrod du bkod pa'o //
NK122(kho)002:12263: gdul bya rnams mdo rgyud la blo gros kyi snang ba mched nas /
NK122(kho)002:12264: shes bya'i gting mtha' yongs su rdzogs pa dang /
NK122(kho)002:12265: rnam mkhyen sangs rgyas thob par gyur cig /
NK122(kho)002:12266: de ltar tshul 'di bde bar gshegs pa'i bka' //
NK122(kho)002:12267: mkhas pa'i bstan bcos 'grel bshad du ma dang //
NK122(kho)002:12268: gong ma'i yig chung lhan thabs rnams la ni //
NK122(kho)002:12269: rang gi nyer len shes rab kyis dpyad nas //
NK122(kho)002:12270: gzhan phan kho na'i sems kyis yi ger bkod //
NK122(kho)002:12271: 'di la rang bzo pho tshod yin snyam bral //
NK122(kho)002:12272: ban sdom bdag gis bla ma'i gsung ngag ltar //
NK122(kho)002:12273: don du gnyer nas sems la bzhag pa'i chos //
NK122(kho)002:12274: nyams su blangs nas tshigs su brjod pa 'di //
NK122(kho)002:12275: sus kyang ma bcos mkhas pa rnams la dris //
NK122(kho)002:12277: rang rang bsam spyod blo rang ma mthun na //
NK122(kho)002:12278: bden tshig rgyal ba'i bka' la yid mi ches //
NK122(kho)002:12279: zhes sogs lo rgyus rje btsun rnams kyis gsungs //
NK122(kho)002:12280: 'di la sa bcad cung zhig ma 'tshams na //
NK122(kho)002:12281: sngar gyis sa bcad yin pas ma bcos so //
NK122(kho)002:12282: lung 'dren rgyas par sbyar rgyu yod mod kyang //
NK122(kho)002:12283: tshig tshogs mang gis dogs pa'i phyir ma bris //
NK122(kho)002:12284: de min don skyon 'di la ma mchis snyam //
NK122(kho)002:12285: kun mkhyen rgyal ba'i bstan pa'i sa gzhi la //
NK122(kho)002:12286: sangs rgyas gnyis pas theg don rgya mtshor bskyil //
NK122(kho)002:12287: 'di la sngar med 'grel bshad pad tshal 'khrungs //
NK122(kho)002:12288: phyogs phyogs blo gsal rkang drug ldan rnams kyis //
NK122(kho)002:12289: don bcud sbrang rtsi legs bshad len pa dang //
NK122(kho)002:12290: pad tshal 'di la dga' ba'i rtse 'jo mdzod //
NK122(kho)002:12291: gnyis skyes dbang po tshogs pa'i dbus na mdzes //
NK122(kho)002:12292: sde snod rgya mtsho'i gzhung lugs bshad rtsal che //
NK122(kho)002:12293: rang 'dod med cing gzhan phan kho nar sems //
NK122(kho)002:12294: bshes gnyen de 'dra bstan pa'i srog shing byung //
NK122(kho)002:12295: bka' yi dgongs don legs par mi bshad cing //
NK122(kho)002:12296: rang gi zhe 'dod kyis bslad 'chal ba'i gtam //
NK122(kho)002:12297: rnam dbye du ma'i bshad lugs byed na yang //
NK122(kho)002:12298: rnam grol thar pa'i lam du 'gro mi srid //
NK122(kho)002:12299: 'chad nyan bstan pa'i srog shing yin mod kyang //
NK122(kho)002:12300: rang rgyud dul zhing gzhan rgyud grol ba bkod //
NK122(kho)002:12301: phal cher don med sgra phyir 'brang 'brang nas //
NK122(kho)002:12302: snying po'i don chen gtan la phab ma nus //
NK122(kho)002:12303: mi lus chos ldan chud zos byed nyen gda' //
NK122(kho)002:12304: de phyir gcig pu dben pa brten na legs //
NK122(kho)002:12305: de yang da res skye gnas bar do 'dir //
NK122(kho)002:12306: yang dag don gyi gdeng zhig ma thob na //
NK122(kho)002:12307: tshe 'di'i snang ba rmi lam thun gcig 'dra //
NK122(kho)002:12308: bslu bar nges so grogs po dam pa rnams /
NK122(kho)002:12310: thos bsam chu bo brgal ba'i pha rol na //
NK122(kho)002:12311: sgom pa gser gyi bye thang chen mo der //
NK122(kho)002:12312: de na cung zhig ngal bso byed na snyams //
NK122(kho)002:12313: gzhi don gnas lugs rang byung ston pa des //
NK122(kho)002:12314: 'khor ni 'gag med rnam shes tshogs brgyad la //
NK122(kho)002:12315: rang byung gnyis med lhan skyes chos ra btsug /
NK122(kho)002:12316: kha ni phyi bltas tshig tshogs 'chad nyan de //
NK122(kho)002:12317: da ni dran yang mi 'dod zhen pa log /
NK122(kho)002:12318: shes bya'i snying po sku lnga lhun grub ste //
NK122(kho)002:12319: snga rab zab zab smra kham che na yang //
NK122(kho)002:12320: sgo them ma bardzisa phugs kyi rgyus bshad 'dra //
NK122(kho)002:12321: da ni skyon med rig pa thang du pheb //
NK122(kho)002:12322: sus kyang min zhes brjod kyang the tshom bral //
NK122(kho)002:12323: rgyud gzhung zab mo'i chos bshad mkhas na yang //
NK122(kho)002:12324: ri dwags rnams kyis smig rgyu snyeg pa 'dra //
NK122(kho)002:12325: da ni 'chad mkhan rig pa bral nas thal //
NK122(kho)002:12326: bshad pa yul du byas pa ngo re tsha //
NK122(kho)002:12327: snga rabs dang po chos bshad 'di ltar byas //
NK122(kho)002:12328: sdug bsngal mthar thug mnar med dmyal ba de //
NK122(kho)002:12329: bde chen kun tu bzang mo'i dgongs pa yin //
NK122(kho)002:12330: 'di bshad phal cher gcig las snyan par byung //
NK122(kho)002:12331: nyams rtogs ldan gyis thugs khrel shin tu che //
NK122(kho)002:12332: dper na glo ba'i tshod ma bskol ba 'dra //
NK122(kho)002:12333: chos de kha na yod kyang khung na med //
NK122(kho)002:12334: dus ni da lta rig pas nyams su myong //
NK122(kho)002:12335: sngar dus bde gsal mi rtog zhi gnas de //
NK122(kho)002:12336: bsgom de bzang du 'dzin pas blo chung 'khrul //
NK122(kho)002:12337: dper na ri bo gser du bsgom dang 'dra //
NK122(kho)002:12338: de yang da lta'i mnyam bzhag ngar can des //
NK122(kho)002:12339: sngar gyi bde gsal mi rtog dbyings su gtor //
NK122(kho)002:12340: da ni rig pa gtad med thang la phebs //
NK122(kho)002:12341: lta ba gnyis med mtha' bral ri bo la //
NK122(kho)002:12342: bsgom pa yengs med ri dwags rtse bar byed //
NK122(kho)002:12343: spyod pa gang shar 'dzin bral gnyug ma'i ngang //
NK122(kho)002:12344: 'bras bu gzhan na med de de nyid brtan //
NK122(kho)002:12345: dus kyi rgyal po gshin rje ma byung bar //
NK122(kho)002:12346: da ni nyams len phyogs gcig dril bar bya //
NK122(kho)002:12347: yid rang rig ye shes 'gag med de //
NK122(kho)002:12348: don dam skye med chos kyi dbyings nas shar //
NK122(kho)002:12349: de gnyis med rtog pa'i yi dam lha //
NK122(kho)002:12350: lha mtshan bcas ri mo yal du chug /
NK122(kho)002:12351: ngag 'byung 'jug bral ba rdo rje'i bzlas //
NK122(kho)002:12352: sgra gags stong dbyer med sems su rtogs //
NK122(kho)002:12353: yid zhe 'dod bzlas brjod zhig na'ang zhig /
NK122(kho)002:12354: kye ma zas gtsang sras po'i bstan pa nub la nye //
NK122(kho)002:12355: bstan 'dzin dag kyang nyin skar tsam du nyung //
NK122(kho)002:12356: da ni bstan pa yun ring mi gnas pas //
NK122(kho)002:12357: rang don zhe bcad 'di ltar byed na snyam //
NK122(kho)002:12358: chags zhen med pa'i gangs 'dab shing drung na //
NK122(kho)002:12359: chags sdang med pa'i bya dang ri dwags grogs //
NK122(kho)002:12360: rang nyid gcig pu seng ge bzhin du sdod //
NK122(kho)002:12361: zhe bcad dam bca' dam po yang yang mthud //
NK122(kho)002:12362: tshe 'di blos btang mi rtag rgyud la bskyed //
NK122(kho)002:12363: dad gus phul phyin ma yengs don la sems //
NK122(kho)002:12364: sems can rnams la byams sems snying rje bsgom //
NK122(kho)002:12365: bla ma rnams dang mched grogs thams cad la //
NK122(kho)002:12366: dag snang mos gus gting nas bskyed par bya //
NK122(kho)002:12367: bar skabs mdo rgyud zab mor blta ba dang //
NK122(kho)002:12368: nyams myong gnad 'dzin 'khrul 'khor sbyangs na snyam //
NK122(kho)002:12369: bde ba can gyi zhing mchog dam pa der //
NK122(kho)002:12370: 'gro ba'i mgon po 'od dpag med pa dang //
NK122(kho)002:12371: blo gros snying po yab sras zhabs drung du //
NK122(kho)002:12372: 'di nas 'chi 'phos de ru skye bar shog /
NK122(kho)002:12373: de yang ting 'dzin dgongs pa mthar phyin nas //
NK122(kho)002:12374: chos sku mngon 'gyur gzhan snang gdul bya yi //
NK122(kho)002:12375: blo dngos bzhin du dgongs pa bskong ba dang /
NK122(kho)002:12376: dpag med mdzad pas 'gro ba kun grol shog /
NK122(kho)002:12377: bkra shis bde legs nam mkha'i mtha' dang mnyam par shog /
NK122(kho)002:12379: bdag 'dra dman pa'i mun khung shin tu che //
NK122(kho)002:12380: rje rta bdun rgyal po shar nas byung //
NK122(kho)002:12381: bdag gi blo yis pad mo kha phye nas //
NK122(kho)002:12382: dam chos bdud rtsi'i rgya mtsho'i gling du phebs //
NK122(kho)002:12383: gzhung lugs nor bu rin chen len na snyams //
NK122(kho)002:12384: chos dbyings chu gter rgya mtsho chen po'i klong //
NK122(kho)002:12385: sangs rgyas gnyis pa dam chos gzugs skur bzhengs //
NK122(kho)002:12386: 'grel bshad nyi ma'i 'od zer pad tshal 'khrungs //
